Title: sadiyon kaa hai silasilaa pahachaan ye puraanii hai  miit mere man ke
Lyrics: sadiyon kaa hai silasilaa pahachaan ye puraanii hai duniyaa ke gulashan men aa ke bahaar ban ke miit mere man ke  tadapaayaa milane se pahale hamen mil ke bhii tarasaayaa tumane sanam paanv men zanjiir thii sharm kii chaah ke bhii magar badh sake na kadam ab na rahii vo duurii khatm huii majabuurii mil hii gaye aaj ham duniyaa men giit mere man ke  saaye men jis ke mile tumase ham aisii hii barasaat kii shaam thii motii kii jo buund tan pe padii laaii khushii kaa paigaam thii mastaane mausam kii pyaar bharii vo chitthii diivaane ke naam thii duniyaa ke gulashan men threedots  shaakhon pe jaise naye gul khile ham bhii naye ruup men yuun mile khushbuu na badalii kabhii pyaar kii banate rahe pyaar ke silasile ulfat kii raahon men manzil kii chaahon men badhate rahe qaafile duniyaa ke gulashan men threedots

Lyrics: saanware tore bin jiyaa jaaye naa 2 jaluun tere pyaar men karuun intazaar teraa kisii se kahaa jaaye naa saanware tore bin jiyaa jaaye naa  striiswar dhuundhe merii priit re tuu hai kahaan miit re aansuu bane giit re aahen sangiit re  saanware tore bin jiyaa jaaye naa  yaad tihaarii moraa man tadapaaye saarii rainaa niind na aaye 2 birahaa kii maarii dekhuun raah tihaarii do nainon ke diip jalaaye jaluun tere pyaar men karuun intazaar teraa kisii se kahaa jaaye naa saanware tore bin jiyaa jaaye naa  striiswar dhuundhe merii priit re tuu hai kahaan miit re aansuu bane giit re aahen sangiit re  saanware tore bin jiyaa jaaye naa  duub chale merii aas ke taare kaise pahunchuun pii ke dwaare 2 tuut gaye sab sang sahaare bole naiyaa duur kinaare jaluun tere pyaar men karuun intazaar teraa kisii se kahaa jaaye naa saanware tore bin jiyaa jaaye naa  striiswar dhuundhe merii priit re tuu hai kahaan miit re aansuu bane giit re aahen sangiit re  saanware

Title: pahalii nazar men  nazar milate hii aisaa kyaa ho gayaa
Lyrics: pahalii nazar men dil na jaane kaise kho gayaa abhii abhii apanaa thaa paraayaa kaise ho gayaa  haan nazar milate hii aisaa kyaa ho gayaa bataae koii pal men ye kyaa ho gayaa ke aaj tak thaa apanaa jo dil kaise ho gayaa paraayaa nazar milate hii threedots  ye khel hai kyaa kisii ko kabhii na jaane koii na pahachaane kabhii vo kahiin milaa bhii nahiin ke naam pataa koii jaane ho gayaa apanaa ha haan dil men jo kabhii naa are ho gayaa apanaa dil men jo kabhii naa aayaa  nazar milate hii threedots  khulii nazaron kaa khvaab hai ye ajiib hai pyaar kaa aalam basant binaa bahaar khile ke rang barase bin mausam anjaanaa dilabar aisaa tan man par chhaayaa he nazar milate hii threedots

Title: jab nazar band thii vo mere paas thaa  muhabbat hai yaaron gam
Lyrics: jab nazar band thii vo mere paas thaa jab aankh khulii to jaane kyaa ho gayaa jisakii chaahat se roshan thaa dil kaa diyaa aaj vo hii sanam bevafaa ho gayaa  muhabbat hai yaaron gam kaa samandar zaraa sochanaa dil lagaane se pahale nazaren tumhaarii naa khaa jaaen dhokhaa nazaren kisii se milaane se pahale muhabbat hai yaaron threedots  vaadaa to karate hain ye duniyaa vaale magar jag men kaun nibhaataa hai vaadaa kisii duusare ko samajh lenaa yaaron chaahat kaa vaadaa nibhaane se pahale muhabbat hai yaaron threedots  chhotaa saa dil naa kahiin tuut jaae aankhon se dariyaa bhii naa chhuut jaae hazaaron dafaa haath siine pe rakhanaa kisii ko bhii apanaa banaane se pahale muhabbat hai yaaron threedots  milegii zamaane men bas bevafaaii vafaa kii ummiiden na rakhanaa kisii se kahiin biich men naa mahal tuut jaae khvaabon kii duniyaa sajaane se pahale muhabbat hai yaaron threedots

Title: dil men mere bas ik savaal hai javaab do bataao
Lyrics: dil men mere bas ik savaal hai javaab do bataao to laut ke tum kab aaogii dil men mere teraa khyaal hai javaab do bataao ke kab merii tum ho jaaogii  jabase khoyaa tujhe zindagii khaalii khaalii sii lag rahii hai tere bin jaanejaanaan jiine kaa koii matalab nahiin hai mujhe chhod ke tum na jaanaa kabhii tumase duur rahake hai jiinaa nahiin dil men mere threedots  jabase dekhaa tujhe merii jaan main to paagal saaa ho gayaa  huun terii aankhon men un nigaahon men main to bas kho gayaa huun mujhe chhod ke threedots  akelaa akelaa main phirataa rahaa duniyaa kii raahon men girataa rahaa tere hii sapanon men khoyaa huaa jaagaa huaa jaise soyaa huaa ab tuu hii manzil hai tuu aarazuu tuu jaan jiine kii chaahat hai tuu tere binaa zindagii hai adhuurii aakar kar le merii tamannaaen puurii dil men mere threedots  haan aisaa bhii ho jaataa hai pyaar men kabhii kabhii

Title: jaate ho parades piyaa jaate hii khat likhanaa
Lyrics: jaate ho parades piyaa jaate hii khat likhanaa dekho tum bhii khat meraa paate hii khat likhanaa jaate ho parades piyaa threedots  likhanaa kaise safar kataa thaa kaise guzare vo pal chhin kyaa mahasuus kiyaa thaa tumane saanjh dhalii jab mere bin kab kab yaad hamaarii aaii kaise tumane raat bitaaii jaate ho parades piyaa threedots  apanii judaaii ke is pal se pahale khat ke aane tak pal pal kii tum baaten likhanaa puuraa khat bhar jaane tak gumasum gumasum khoii khoii tum chhupakar kitanaa roiin jaate ho parades piyaa threedots  dekh nahiin paayenge tumako ojhal hote ye nayanaa lo main palaken muund rahii huun tum chal do mere sajanaa ye to hai ik tarafaa vidaaii isamen pyaar kii hai rusavaaii jaate ho parades piyaa threedots

Title: chal kar le thodaa pyaar nahiin te mar jaavaange donon
Lyrics: chal kar le thodaa pyaar nahiin te mar jaavaange donon haan kar de merii jaan nahiin te mar jaavaange donon ab na kar intazaar nahiin te mar jaavaange donon chal kar le thodaa threedots  haan kar de mere yaar nahiin te mar jaavaange donon  tere piichhe kabase padii huun main zid pe aaj adii huun main to bechain badii huun kab se taiyaar khadii huun tuu bhii ho jaa taiyaar nahiin te mar jaavaange donon chal kar le thodaa threedots  merii saans chale yuun ruk ruk ke terii nazar uthe yuun jhuk jhuk ke ham saathii donon duhkh sukh ke haay jindadii rah gaii jal phunk kar kar koii jatan diladaar nahiin te mar jaavaange donon chal kar le thodaa threedots  dil men tasviir banaa le mujhe apanii hiir banaa le zulfen zanjiir banaa le ankhiyon ke tiir chalaa le kar tiir jigar ke paar nahiin te mar jaavaange donon chal kar le thodaa threedots

Title: yaaro sun lo zaraa haan apanaa ye kahanaa
Lyrics: ai ai ai ai ai ai ai ai ai ai yaaro sun lo zaraa haan apanaa ye kahanaa  jiinaa ho to apun ke jaise hii jiinaa  gaadii bangalaa nahiin naa sahii naa sahii     inakii hamako kyuun ho fikar jii lo jaise mast kalandar  yaaro sun lo zaraa haan apanaa bhii kahanaa jiinaa ho to apun ke jaise hii jiinaa  gaadii banglaa agar ho to kyaa baat hai     inaki kar lo kuchh to kadar yaaro thodaa jaao sudhar   hamako dekho ham hain yaraa apanii marajii ke raajaa  duniyaa bole to mazaa hai naa kaho kud ko raajaa  naam apun kaa munnaa bhaaii ham karen vo jo dil men samaaii  are dhandaa kiyaa naa kiyaa kyaa fikar  kaun aayaa gayaa duniyaa men kyaa kabar  is duniyaa se tum jo rahe bekabar kahiin duniyaa tumhen naa bhulaaye    kal kaa kyaa hai kisane dekhaa ham to aaj men jiite hain  jin men himmat hai nahiin vo aisii baaten karate hain  isakii to tum baat naa karanaa hamako daadaa sab kahate hain  are sheron ke jaisaa hai apanaa jigar uunchaa hii rahaa hai sadaa apanaa sar  sar se jyaadaa uunchii rahe ye nazar aasmaan phir to sar ko jhukaaye

Lyrics: tere dard se dil aabaad rahaa 2 kuchh bhuul gae kuchh yaad rahaa 2  nasiibaa bhii kyaa rang laayaa kahaan laa ke hamako milaayaa 2 apanii vafaa ke gul khil naa paae mil ke bhii tumase mil naa paae dardedil ham kaise sahen duur bhii ham kaise rahen teraa gam tere jaane ke baad rahaa 2 kuchh bhuul gae kuchh threedots  jaanevafaa tujhako kyaa den dil kah rahaa hai duaa den aramaan bujhe hain sapanen dhuaan hain mar mar ke ham to zindaa yahaan hain bekhudii men ham kho gae phir judaa tujhase ho gae chaahat kaa jahaan barabaad rahaa 2 kuchh bhuul gae kuchh threedots

Lyrics: dil apanaa mayakashii kaa talabagaar bhii nahiin haan wo agar pilaayen to inkaar bhii nahiin  ahadewafaa kii subaho kaa kyaa zikr dosto ahadewafaa kii subaho ke aasaar bhii nahiin  suunaa padaa hai der se mayakaanaaewafaa saaqii kaa zikr kyaa koii mayakaar bhii nahiin  gulashan ujaad ho gayaa duniyaa badal gaii kyaa dhuundhate ho gul ke yahaan kaar bhii nahiin  darshan na puuchho zulmateduniyaaeaashiiqii koii charaag ab to saredaar bhii nahiin

Lyrics: ye kyaa ke sabase bayaan dil kii haalaten karanii faraaz tujhako na aaiin mohabbaten karanii  ye kurb kyaa hai ke tuu saamane thaa aur hamen shumaaragii se judaaii se saaaten karanii  koii kudaa ho ke patthar jise bhii ham chaahen tamaam umr usii kii ibaadaten karanii  sab apane apane kariine se muntazir usake kisii ko shukr kisii ko shikaayaten karanii  mile jab unase to mubaham sii guftaguu karanaa phir apane aap se sau sau wazaahat karanii

Title: ab to binaa tumhaare muhabbat ke vatan men
Lyrics: ab to binaa tumhaare muhabbat ke vatan men yaa ashq barasate hain yaa phir aag saavan men ab to binaa tumhaare threedots  tum se bichhad ke dard ke gheron men aa gae ham roshanii se duur andheron men aa gae ab jaa ke farq jaanaa judaaii men milan men ab to binaa tumhaare threedots  dushman bane aap hii apanii khushii ke ham ai dost bin tumhaare bhii dekhenge jii ke ham khud aag lagaa baithe hain ham apane chaman men ab to binaa tumhaare threedots  tumako na koii shikavaa kabhii ho nasiib se koii bhii gam na guzare tumhaare kariib se aayen tumhaare gam bhii hamaare nasiib men ab to binaa tumhaare threedots

Title: kuu kuu dil ye bole main to jaanuun naa  thodii tuu bhii diivaanii
Lyrics: kuu kuu dil ye bole main to jaanuun naa tere bhii dil men jo huaa hai tuu vo maane naa thodii tuu bhii diivaanii thodaa main bhii diivaanaa kuu kuu dil ye bole threedots  thodii main bhii diivaanii thodaa tuu bhii diivaanaa  mujhe aisaa lagaa dil ne jaise kahaa aajaa ham tum karen dostii bhuul kaise gae kahaa thaa jo tuune ki main huun badii siraphirii arii chhod de diivaanii khatm kar de vo kahaanii kaise bhuuluun main vo baaten jaa jaa chhod meraa haath are kyuun tuu akadatii hai mujhase jhagadatii hai aise bigadatii hai kyuun kuu kuu dil ye bole threedots  ho laakh kar lo jatan pighale naa meraa man ladakii huun jii main to shahar kii koii ruup hai naa rang baat karane kaa na dhang are vaah rii shahar kii parii maanaa tumane kyuun buraa vo majaak thaa meraa ye nakhare ye adaa kisii aur ko dikhaa kyuun tuu akadataa hai mujhase jhagadataa hai aise bigadataa hai kyuun kuu kuu dil ye bole threedots  thodii ye bhii diivaanii haan haan thodaa vo bhii diivaanaa o ho

Title: raah men bichhii hain palaken aao
Lyrics: raah men bichhii hain palaken aao phuul mahake rang jhalake aao aae chaman men phirase nikhaar aao jo tum to aae bahaar ritu lahake ritu bahake kalii khile chaman jhuume raah men bichhii hain palaken aao  raat kiye hai solaa singaar madiraa kii halakii hai phuhaar maan bhii jaao ek baat ab aake thaam lo ye haath tan jhuume man jhuume dharaa gagan pavan jhuume saanjh jaage jaam chhalake aao  rang ruup aur sugandh todate hain saare bandh dil hai ki beqaraar hai aao ke intazaar hai har ghungharuu men jaaduu chhanana chhanana chhanana jhuume paayalon se motii dhalake aao

Title: rab jaisaa ruup tumhaaraa detaa hai dil ko sahaaraa
Lyrics: rab jaisaa ruup tumhaaraa detaa hai dil ko sahaaraa ho suuraj ho yaa taaraa phuul ho yaa angaaraa jisamen ruup tumhaaraa vahii mujhe pyaaraa rab jaisaa ruup tumhaaraa threedots  pyaar men mere itanii agan hai suuraj men bhii na hogii terii lagan ne tabhii to mujhako banaa diyaa teraa jogii jaise motii jaise taaraa vaise chamake ang tumhaaraa rab jaisaa ruup tumhaaraa threedots  rab isalie hasiin nahiin phuulon se vo khilate hain phuul hasiin hai isalie to honthon se vo milate hain aankhen terii jiivan dhaaraa rab jaisaa ruup tumhaaraa threedots  zulfon ke baadal se meraa jiivan siinchatii hai suraj na ho ambar men to chaand kyaa chamakegaa jo tuu na ho to haradam meraa dam na chal sakegaa hai sitaar tere man men baaton men raaginii hai tere chehare kii badaulat duniyaa men chaandanii hai

Title: dil men basaa ke palakon men bithaa ke
Film: jab pyaar kisi se hotaa hai
Lyrics: dil men basaa ke palakon men bithaa ke nazaron men qaid kar liyaa aankhon men band kar liyaa maine tumako pasand kar liyaa  ham donon anjaan raahii raste magar mil gae patajhad ke mausam men jaise dil phuul se khil gae tum duur raho yaa paas raho nazaron men qaid kar liyaa aankhon men band threedots  ab ye bechainiyaan hain aage naa jaane ho kyaa itane kariib aa gae hain ab kaise honge judaa baahon men sanam tuune thaam liyaa nazaron men qaid kar liyaa aankhon men band threedots

Title: ilaa luu ilaa luu terii main aur meraa tuu
Lyrics: ilaa luu ilaa luu terii main aur meraa tuu kore kaagaz pe likhavaa le niiche hastaaxar karavaa le ilaa luu ilaa luu threedots  jaanejaanaan barason se main teraa diivaanaa huun dekh merii aankhon men pyaar kaa paravaanaa huun merii jaan tumase milane kii bekaraarii rahatii hai jaanejaan is dil men khumaarii rahatii hai jaanejaan mujh par kar daalaa kyaa jaaduu ilaa luu ilaa luu threedots  aajakal jo raaton men khvaab tere aate hain manachale aramaanon ko haay dard saa de jaate hain diivaanii aisii haalat men niind kise aatii hai chaahat men na milane kii bebasii tadapaatii hai merii saanson men rahatii terii khushbuu ilaa luu ilaa luu threedots

Title: om namo shivaay  chhod de kal kii fiqar  duniyaa ke gam bhulaae jaa
Lyrics: om namo shivaay chhod de kal kii fiqar kal kyaa hogaa kisako khabar hai kash pe kash lagaae jaa duniyaa ke gam bhulaae jaa om namo shivaay threedots  kuchh na kuchh hone vaalaa hai honii ko kisane taalaa hai paravaah koii karate nahiin duniyaa se ham darate nahiin om namo shivaay threedots  vaqt yuun hii tal jaaegaa phir kahaan ye pal aaegaa ye zindagii hai bevafaa ek din tujhe degii dagaa om namo shivaay threedots chhod de pyaare kal kii baaten

Title: diivaanaa huaa main diivaanaa merii jaan  meraa bas meraa hai ajay
Lyrics: diivaanaa huaa main diivaanaa merii jaan tere ishq men hai thokar jahaan ko lagaanaa merii jaan tere ishq men main paagal huii diivaanii huii terii dilarubaa terii raanii huii meraa bas meraa hai ajay diivaanaa huaa main threedots  tuufaan diivaanagii kaa roke kabhii na ruke sachchii muhabbat ke aage saaraa zamaanaa jhuke ab ye merii zindagaanii hai terii chaahat ke naam chaahuungii tujhako hameshaa chaahe subah ho yaa shaam hai kadamon men dil ko jhukaanaa merii jaan tere ishq men main paagal huii threedots  duniyaa kii saarii hadon se aage guzar jaanaa hai jiinaa hai baahon men terii baahon men terii maranaa hai kaise tujhe main bataauun kaisaa hai diivaanaapan terii vafaaon kaa jaaduu chhaane lagaa jaaneman labon ko labon tak hai laanaa merii jaan tere ishq men mujhako hai sab kuchh lutaanaa merii jaan tere ishq men tuu paagal huii diivaanii huii diivaanii huii main diivaanii

Title: rozaa rozaa merii rozaa  ek nazar men kho gayaa dil
Lyrics: rozaa rozaa  rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa merii rozaa   rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa merii rozaa   ek nazar men kho gayaa dil paaii tujh men pyaar kii manzil   chhuu ne naa duun tujhe chandaa ko chanchal havaa ko bahaaron ko   saavan kii rimajhim phuhaaron ko naa chhuune duungaa naa chhuune duungaa   rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa    saayaa bhii tera gire naa zamiin pe baadal saa chhaayaa rahuungaa tujhape   ke suuraj kii tiiron sii kirane bhii naa chubhane paaye tujhako rozaa   rozaa rozaa   halkaa saa tabassum teraa khilataa hai dekho magar gulasitaan   chhupatii hai nazaaron men tuu puuchhe hai nazar mujhase tuu hai kahaan   roshan hai tujh se meraa ye jahaan ai hasiin sun zaraa mere dil kii zubaan   raatdin hai mujhe terii tadap ab yahaan teraa hii jikr hai terii hii fikr hai rozaa rozaa   rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa merii rozaa  ek nazar men kho gayaa dil paaii tujh men pyaar kii manzil   qudarat kii kuub nishaanii hai ulfat kii jo naa kahii gaii tuu kahaani hai   dil bole umr bhar jii bharbhar padhataa hii rahuun tujhako ai merii rozaa rozaa   sharmohayaa par adaayen terii unape lutii janaan ye jaan merii   phuulon kii nazar naa lage aankhon men aa jaa chhupaa luun merii   meraa kyaa sab kuchh ab to hai teraa dil meraa nazaraanaa diyaa tujhe ai sanam   dil teraa aashiyaanaa hai meraa kyaa sanam kah de zaraa to jaan tujhe de duun rozaa rozaa rozaa   rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa merii rozaa  ek nazar men kho gayaa dil paaii tujh men pyaar kii manzil  rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa rozaa merii rozaa

Title: pyaar hai iishvar pyaar tapasyaa  dil ek mandir pyaar hai puujaa
Lyrics: pyaar hai iishvar pyaar tapasyaa pyaar se sansaar hai pyaar kii jot jalaane vaalaa insaan bhii avataar hai dil ek mandir pyaar hai puujaa pyaar se badh kar koii na duujaa ai mere hamasafar hai ye sabako khabar inase pyaaraa zamaane men koii nahiin dil ek mandir threedots  jag ke saare bandhan jhuuthe sachchii hai ik priit kii dorii jisane kii ho priit vo jaane kyon chandaa ko chaahe chakorii prem kiyaa to sab kuchh chhuutaa pyaar se badh kar threedots  usakii duniyaa svarg banii hai jisako man kaa miit milaa hai usakii baat na puuchhe koii jis par priit kaa rang chadhaa hai us pe rang chadhe naa duujaa pyaar se badh kar threedots

Title: jhonkaa havaa kaa aaj bhiii
Lyrics: jhonkaa havaa kaa aaj bhii zulfen udaataa hogaa na teraa dupattaa aaj bhii tere sar se sarakataa hogaa na baalon men tere aaj bhii phuul koii sajataa hogaa na  thandii havaaen raaton men tujhako thapakiyaan detii hongii na chaand kii thandak kvaabon men tujhako leke to jaatii hogii na suuraj kii kiranen subah ko terii niinden udaatii hongii na mere kayaalon men sanam khud se hii baaten karatii hogii na main dekhataa huun chhup chhup ke tumako mahasuus karatii hogii na jhonkaa havaa kaa aaj bhii zulfen udaataa hogaa na   threedots  kaagaz pe merii tasaviir jaisii kuchh to banaatii hogii na ulat palat ke dekhake usako jii bhar ke hansatii hogii na hansate hansate aankhen tumhaarii bhar bhar aatii hongii na mujhako dhakaa thaa dhuup men jisase vo aanchal bhiigotii hogii na saavan kii rimajhim meraa taraanaa yaad dilaatii hongii na ek ek merii baaten tumako yaad to aatii hogii na yaad to aatii hogii na yaad to aatii hogii na kyaa tum mere in sab savaalon kaa kuchh to javaab dogii na   threedots

Title: nain kabuutar ud gae donon achchhe nain ladaae
Lyrics: nain kabuutar ud gae donon achchhe nain ladaae aise ude kabuutar mere laut ke phir naa aae  2 nain kabuutar ud gae threedots  haay akelaa chhod gae hain bedardii dil tod gae hain kab rukate hain udane vaale ud jaate hain tod ke taale pyaar men hue hain ham saudaaii rabbaa terii duhaaii luut ke le gayaa ik harajaaii pal men merii kamaaii achchhe nain ladaae threedots  kaun thaa jisane pyaar banaayaa dil men miithaa dard jagaayaa pyaar hai ik anamol kazaanaa pyaar kiyaa to maine jaanaa sabase hue hain prem diivaane ban gae hain afasaane duniyaa kii duniyaa hii jaane pyaar to ik naa maane achchhe nain ladaae threedots  kal tak thii vo aaj nahiin huun ab tuu jahaan hai main bhii vahiin huun pyaar men apanaa rang dikhaayaa yaar ko aakir khiinch hii laayaa pyaar kiyaa hai kyaa jiinaa kyaa maranaa pyaar karenge pyaar kiyaa hai pyaar hamen hai karanaa achchhe nain ladaae threedots

Title: dhanak men chaand nahaayaa to terii yaad aaii
Lyrics: dhanak men chaand nahaayaa to terii yaad aaii nashaa sharaab kaa chhaayaa to terii yaad aaii  mere lahuu men tere kaab raks karate rahe mujhe jo saans bhii aayaa to terii yaad aaii  ghate jo din ke ujaale to dam ghutaa meraa badhaa jo shaam kaa saayaa to terii yaad aaii  main tujhako haar chalaa thaa gaye zamaane ko kushii ne dil jo dukhaayaa to terii yaad aaii  kisii ko chot lagii jab bhii dil meraa tadapaa koii kisii ne sataayaa to terii yaad aaii  kise bataauun ke guzarii hai zindagii kaise jahaan men koii bhii bhaayaa to terii yaad aaii

Title: kisii ko de ke dil koii nawaa sanjefugaan kyuun ho
Lyrics: kisii ko de ke dil koii nawaa sanjefugaan kyuun ho na ho jab dil hii siine men to phir munh kyuun ho  wo apanii kuun na chhodenge ham apanii bazzaa kyuun badalen subaksar banake kyaa puuchhe ke hamase saragaraan kyuun ho  kiyaa gamkaar ne rusawaa lage aag is muhabbat ko na laave taab jo gam kii wo meraa raazadaan kyuun ho  ye kah sakate ho ham dil men nahiin hain par ye batalaao ke jab dil men tumhiin tum ho to aankhon se nihaan kyuun ho  kahaa tumane ke kyuun ho gair se milane men ruswaaii bajaa kahate ho sach kahate ho phir kahiyo ki haan kyuun ho  nikaalaa chaahataa hai kaam kyaa taanon se tuu gaalib tere bemehar kahane se wo tujh par meharabaan kyuun ho

Title: mere achchhe sajan mere pyaare sajan mere bhole sajan aajaa
Lyrics: aajaa sajan aajaa mere achchhe sajan mere pyaare sajan mere bhole sajan aajaa uthatii hai kasak aajaa dil kare dhak dhak aajaa kab hogaa milan aajaa mere achchhe sajan threedots  main to khud aap hii pyaasii huun main kaisii raam kii gangaa huun main to bas naam kii gangaa huun merii pyaas bujhaa aajaa mujhe gangaa banaa aajaa kar puuraa vachan aajaa aajaa sajan aajaa threedots  jo aise tuut ke barasaa hai ho sab kahate hai ye baadal hai baadal nahiin meraa kaajal hai ye bijalii nahiin merii bindiyaa kahiin chamakii bairan aajaa aajaa sajan aajaa threedots

Title: ishq teraa tadapaave  rok na paavaan akhiyaan
Lyrics: oe oe oe taare gin gin yaad vich terii main taan jaagaan raataan nuun rok na paavaan akhiyaan vichchon gam diyaan barasaataan nuun ho ho o o ishq teraa tadapaave  vadde mainuun tere bin taan har pal ai tanahaaii daa dasse mainuun naagan vaanguun mausam terii judaaii daa il pal vii main bhul na paavaan terii mithiyaan baataan nuun rok na paavaan threedots  dil jalaa ke roshan kittaa main taa teriiyaan raavaan nuu dhup laike main ghaliyaan tere val sukh diyaa thandiiyaa chhaavaan nuun samajh na paaii kyuun tuu mere pyaar bhare jazbaataan nuun rok na paavaan threedots  ik vaarii tuu aake mil jaa sun le sadaa hun merii tuu jaan na jaave tan ton mere aajaa naa kar derii tuu sah na paavaan duurii terii tarasaan main mulaakaataan nuun rok na paavaan threedots

Title: dil jaan jigar tujhape nisaar kiyaa hai  pyaar kiyaa hai re tujhe
Lyrics: dil jaan jigar tujhape nisaar kiyaa hai kyuun pyaar kiyaa hai re tujhe pyaar kiyaa hai  tuune bhii mujhe kitanaa bekaraar kiyaa hai kyuun pyaar kiyaa hai re bahut pyaar kiyaa hai dil jaan jigar tujhape threedots  main to huun terii adaaon kaa maaraa tuu hii kyuun samajhe na meraa ishaaraa jhuum ke tuu aajaa baahon men samaa jaa ab tak badaa hii intazaar kiyaa hai kyuun pyaar kiyaa hai threedots  merii taraf dekh zaraa nazaren uthaa ke palakon men rakhaa hai tujhako chhupaa ke apanaa banaaenge tujhako rijhaaenge tere lie to ye singaar kiyaa hai kyuun pyaar kiyaa hai threedots

Title: pandit jii meraa haath dekhakar baat kaho mere haal kii

Title: ki tuut gaii tadak karake
Lyrics: haay haay haay haay ki tuut gaii  dekhii hamane biich bajariyaa juganii jaise koii gujariyaa apane man kii baat sunaae juganii naache juganii gaae  suno daastaan ye merii suno merii ye kahaanii koii meraa thaa diivaanaa main bhii jisakii thii diivaanii haay kaise the iraade jiine marane ke the vaade todii thiin duniyaa kii rasmen khaaii thiin ulfat kii kasamen maine khaaii kasam thii sachchii par usakii kasam thii kachchii ki tuut gaii tadak karake ki tuut gaii oe  jab vo milane ko aataa thaa haan mere kaise gun gaataa thaa haan mujhako huur parii kahataa thaa haan mujhako dekhataa hii rahataa thaa haan kahataa thaa jo bhii ho jaae ham naa honge kabhii paraae chaahe saarii duniyaa roke par ye milan rahegaa hoke tere pyaar men vo jaaduu hai ke ab dil men tuu hii tuu hai daakaa daalaa naa koii chorii maine pyaar kiyaa hai gorii chhoduungaa naa baiyaan torii par aisii thii pyaar kii dorii ki tuut gaii threedots  jab thii main usakii manachaahii haan main manzil thii vo thaa raahii haan main dhadakan thii vo meraa dil haan main thii lahar vo meraa saahil haan kaise din the kaisii raaten kaisii pyaarii thiin vo baaten kaisii mauj men ham rahate the kaise khoe se rahate the kaise ruuthate aur manate the kaise jhuuth muuth banate the aankhon men hain vo tasviiren dil par chalatii hain shamashiiren yaad aatii hai vo diladaarii par jhuuthii thii usakii yaarii ki tuut gaii threedots

Title: dil meraa churaane lagaa raaton ko jagaane lagaa
Lyrics: dil meraa churaane lagaa raaton ko jagaane lagaa pyaar jab hotaa hai niind ud jaatii hai roj akele men phir yaad aatii hai jaane jaane dil diivaanaa pyaar teraa dil meraa churaane lagaa threedots  hosh aa rahaa hai premii jaa rahaa hai mujh pe chaahaton kaa rang chadh rahaa hai pyaar zaraa palakon men chhupaanaa tiir chal rahe hain dil machal rahe hain aag bekhudii kii premii jal rahe hain ye kaisaa jaaduu hai bataanaa  chain churaa ke kyuun aankh churaatii hai merii hii saanson men dard jagaatii hai jaane jaane ye diivaanaa threedots  hai samaan suhaanaa aa jaa kariib aanaa main likhuun labon pe ek hasiin fasaanaa chhod merii baahon ko tuu sataa naa hai abhii zaruurii thodii thodii duurii terii aarazuu to main karuungii puurii maan merii baaton ko na jalaanaa tanhaaii sii kyuun tadapaatii hai koii sadaa harapal paas bulaatii hai jaane jaane ye diivaanaa threedots

Title: haay jaanaan haay jaanaan le ke jaan naa jaanaa
Lyrics: haay jaanaan haay jaanaan le ke jaan naa jaanaa  tuune qadar merii jaanii nahiin jaanaan  kaisii huun main kyaa huun tuune kahaan jaanaa  dil ke aramaan wo kyaa ho gaye  sapane suhaane sab kho gaye  dil ko jalaa kar ke piyaa  hansatii huun main jaise diyaa  dekhe zamaanaa   khel ye aisaa jazabaatii hai  jaan hii isamen chalii jaatii hai  chaahen vo jaan jisakii bhii ho  vo merii ho yaa terii ho  sun le fasaanaa

Title: kaalaa shaa kaalaa haay kaale hain dilavaale goriyaa nuun dafaa karo
Lyrics: ho kaalaa shaa kaalaa  haay kaale hain dilavaale goriyaa nuun dafaa karo gore dil ke kaale goriyaa nuun dafaa karo  gorii raadhaa kaa saajan hai kaalaa krishn kanhaiyaa mere lie goraa saajan mat dhuundhiyo merii maiyaa kaale ko jo de de mere shagun kaa ek rupaiyaa main sadake kaale re dilavaale ve o matavaale ve ve kaale hain dilavaale threedots  kaalii raat ke aanchal se jo chamake chaand sitaare kaalii koyaliyaa jab gaaye jhuumen man matavaare gore gaal pe kaalaa til moraa ruup sanvaare main sadake kaale pe o kismat pe o dilavaale ke ai dil kaale ke havaale goriyaa nuun dafaa threedots

Title: javaanii se ab jang hone lagii
Lyrics: javaanii se ab jang hone lagii ye cholii merii tang hone lagii koii maare aankhon se koii maare ishaaron se o javaanii se ab jang threedots  umr kaisii bhalaa aaii hai mastiyaan kaun sii laaii hai kaisii naadaan huun main to pareshaan huun taubaa merii karuun main kyaa koii dil ko churaataa hai koii paise lutaataa hai band botal hai kyuun chuume hosh men na rahe jhuume dekh to dilarubaa sochataa hai tuu kyaa sabase badhake nashaa meraa ishq men koii haaraa hai ho ho ho ho koii kadakaa kunvaaraa hai javaanii se ab jang threedots

Title: piir paigambar mazahab  jab rab ke ghar men pyaar kii tasviir ban gaii
Lyrics: piir paigambar mazahab duniyaa sabase badhakar hiir hai merii hiir men sab hai hiir men rab hai rab jaisii taqadiir hai merii raanjhaa merii haddiyaan ramayaa duniyaa kii kyaa zaruurat main raanjhe kii suurat huun aur raanjhaa merii suurat  jab rab ke ghar men pyaar kii tasviir ban gaii main raanjhaa ban gayaa tuu merii hiir ban gaii  jab rab ke ghar men pyaar kii tasviir ban gaii tuu raanjhaa ban gayaa main terii hiir ban gaii jab rab ke ghar threedots  terii gaharii aankhon men to jhiil kii ravaanii hai palakon ke niiche mere pyaar kii kahaanii hai tuu merii aas hai tuu merii pyaas hai dekh merii zindagii bhii raanjhe tere paas hai jab chaahane vaalon kii taqadiir ban gaii main raanjhaa ban threedots  likh diyaa naam teraa dil kii kitaab men dekhii kudaaii maine tere shabaab men rasmon rivaaz saare duniyaa ke tod duun tere lie to main kudaaii ko bhii chhod duun jab pyaar ke khaabon kii taabiir ban gaii main raanjhaa ban threedots

Title: hamadam pyaaraapyaaraa hai ye mausam
Lyrics: hamadam pyaaraapyaaraa hai ye mausam  mausam aao is kaa mazaa len ham  gussaa naa ho tuu to tujh se main kuchh boluun yaar  kar le ham se thodaa pyaar  naa kar zaraa bhii inkaar  bas baat yahii suujhe tujhe  tuu to thodii paagal lage mujhe   mere raajaa tuu raajaa terii raanii huun main  tuu sayaanaa maanaa par terii divaanii huun main  pyaar se tuu dekh terii dilabar jaanii huun main  naa main raajaa naa hii tuu hai koii raanii chhod ye kahaanii  sapanon men kahiin dhal hii naa jaaye terii ye javaanii   dekhodekho javaanii ke pal do pal  sochosocho rahenge naa pal ye kal  baanhon men baanhen daale pyaar ke raste chal  teremere raste kabhii bhii naa milen hai yahii duaa  sang tere mujhe kabhii bhii naa jaanaa chhod piichhaa meraa

Title: ek tamannaa jiivan kii  chaahen shaadii ke din mar jaauun
Lyrics: ek tamannaa jiivan kii main pyaar teraa hii paauun shaadii tujhii se ho merii chaahen shaadii ke din mar jaauun  na tujhe jaanuun na pahachaanuun kyuun tuu gale padii hai samajh ke mujhako apanaa diivaanaa ghere hue khadii hai teraa hii to thaa ye kahanaa tere bin mujhako nahiin rahanaa teraa vaadaa iraadaa tujhako yaad dilaauun shaadii tujhii se ho merii threedots  hamaaraa dil jo tod diyaa to hasiin ye bhii kar jaaiye hamen yaad karegaa terii chaukhat par mar jaive jo bhuulaa thaa yaad vo aayaa main huun vahii jo tuune banaayaa na ho dukhii o chandramukhii chhod ke kahiin na jaauun shaadii tujhii se ho merii threedots

Lyrics: yaaron main paagal ho gayaa ho gayaa dekho main ghaayal ho gayaa ho gayaa galii galii men tujhe dhuundh rahaa naam pataa teraa puuchh rahaa kis number pe karuun telephone dil men talaash terii chehare pe junuun afalaa afalaa afalaatuun afalaatuun main huun afalaatuun  aisaa lagataa hai vo kahiin pe chhupii huii merii kismat kii gaadii kahiin pe rukii huii vo mil jaae to aa jaae dil ko zaraa sukuun afalaa afalaa afalaatuun threedots  main huun afalaatuun ye hai afalaatuun  apanii zulfon ko merii zanjiir banaa de merii jaan kii paravaah na kar tiir chalaa de maaf kiyaa jaa tujhako qaatil maine apanaa khuun afalaa afalaa afalaatuun threedots  gorii ho yaa kaalii ho yaa koii bhii chalegii par vo paise vaalii ho koii bhii chalegii mujhako kyaa vo saadii pahane yaa pahane pataluun afalaa afalaa afalaatuun threedots

Title: ye ladakii hai yaa khuubasuurat balaa
Lyrics: ye ladakii hai yaa khuubasuurat balaa zaraa isake yauvan kii dekho kalaa adaa men nazar men hai jaaduu bharaa kahiin phans naa jaae koii manachalaa  ye ladakaa huaa hai diivaanaa meraa na karanaa yakiin hai isakaa dil jalaa ye ladakii hai yaa threedots  dil hai isakaa pyaar se khaalii isake mukhade pe gazab lage gusse kii laalii samajho naa tum mujhako aisii vaisii chhuunaa nahiin main huun angaar jaisii o naadaan hasiinaa ye zid chhod de mere paas aa dil se dil jod de tuu jal jaaegaa tuu pighal jaaegaa kabhii bhii tuu na karanaa ye faisalaa ye ladakii hai yaa threedots  uf ye jalave uf ye tevar tiir chalaae dil pe kas ke latake jhatake sabase hat ke chalatii hai kyaa matak matak ke duniyaa se hat ke hain andaaz mere khanakaa duun dil ke sabhii saaz tere main tujhako tuu mujhako zaraa aazamaa akele men chal chal ke nazaren milaa na majanuun na raanjhaa na farahaad tuu diivaanon ke nakshekadam pe chalaa adaa men nazar men threedots

Title: ruuthe ho tum tumako kaise manaauun piyaa
Lyrics: ruuthe ho tum tumako kaise manaauun piyaa bolo naa bolo naa  siine se lag jaauun baanhon men mar jaauun kaise tumako manaauun ruuthe ho tum   tum bin piyaa jiyaa meraa nahiin laage tarase hai tadape hai saarii raat jaage maanoge kaise piyaa ye bataa do jal jal ke mar jaauun aise naa sazaa do aansuu hain aankhon men halachal hai saanson men le bhii lo baanhon men ruuthe ho tum tumako kaise manaauun piyaa bolo naa bolo naa   dekho piyaa aise to naa tadapaao jis dil men rahate ho usako naa dukhaao kyaa main karuun piyaa mujhe ye bataa do tumako mere sar kii qasam ab to muskuraa do varanaa main ro duungii phir na kabhii boluungii apanii jaan de duungii tum jo kaho tumako mar ke manaauun piyaa bolo naa bolo naa

Title: anganaa men baabaa duaare pe maan
Lyrics: anganaa men baabaa duaare pe maan kaise aaen gorii ham tumhare ghar maan khet gae baabaa baazaar gaii maan akelii huun ghar maan tuu aa jaa baalamaa  ghar maan jo aiven to hamain kyaa khilaive garam garam halavaa aur puurii pakaive naram naram haathon se khaa jaa baalamaa anganaa men baabaa threedots  halavaa puurii khaive to nindiyaa na sataive nindiyaa men tohare lie aanchal bichhaive sijiyaa kii kismat jagaa jaa baalamaa khet gae baabaa threedots  kyaa hogaa baazaar se maan jo aaii kah duungii maan ye hai teraa jamaaii haath meraa maangane ko aa jaa baalamaa anganaa men baabaa threedots

Title: yahaanvahaan saaraa jahaan  maan tujhe salaam  vande maataram
Lyrics: maan   vande maataram   yahaanvahaan saaraa jahaan dekh liyaa hai  kahiin bhii tere jaisaa koii nahiin hai  assii nahiin sau din duniyaa ghuumaa huun  nahiin kahiin tere jaisaa koii nahiin hai  main gayaa jahaan bhii bas terii yaad thii  jo mere saath thii mujh ko tadapaatiirulaatii  sab se pyaarii terii suurat pyaar hai bas teraa pyaar hii  maan tujhe salaam   ammaa tujhe salaam   jahaan tuu hai vahaan main teraa huun divaanaa main  jhuumuun naachun gaauun tere pyaar kaa taraanaa main  chandaa nahiin suuraj nahiin duiyaa kii daulat nahiin  bas luutuungaa tere pyaar kaa khazaanaa  ek nazar jab terii  hotii hai pyaar kii  duniyaa tab to merii chamake damake mahake re  teraa cheharaa suuraj jaisaa chaand sii thand hai pyaar men   tere paas hii main aa rahaa huun apanii baanhen khol de  jor se mujhako gale lagaa le mujhako phir vo pyaar de  maan maan maan   tuu hii zindagii hai tuu hii merii mohabbat hai  tere hii pairon men jannat hai tuu hii dil tuu jaan maan

Title: mahabuub mere mahabuub gazab kii garmii hai terii saanson men
Lyrics: mahabuub mere mahabuub gazab kii garmii hai terii saanson men main pighal gayaa huun yaar mere main pighal gaii huun yaar mere aakar terii in baahon men mahabuub mere threedots  diladaar mohabbat se terii kyaa ye merii hastii hai ik ghuut men pii jaauun in honthon men mastii hai dil duub gayaa hai in terii labarez chhalakatii aankhon men mahabuub mere threedots  din raat tasavvur men tere is dil ko main bahalaatii huun tuu saamane jab aa jaataa hai naa jaane kyon sharamaatii huun ye sharmohayaa kii zid kaisii tuune dii mujhe panaahon men mahabuub mere threedots  ye jism sulagataa hai aise jaise koii aag dahakatii hai ye aag sard hogii kis din har vaqt ye ulajhan rahatii hai chal ho jaaen shaamil donon qudarat ke paaq gunaahon men mahabuub mere threedots  ik duuje kii in baahon men

Title: paagal mujhe kar diyaa kyaa jaanam samajhaa karo
Lyrics: paagal mujhe kar diyaa kyaa jaanam samajhaa karo jaanam samajhaa karo kahane ke lie hain kitane yahaan lekin inamen ye baat kahaan kaisii baaten ajii kaise hasiin zaraa khulake bataa main samajhii nahiin paagal mujhe kar threedots  jaanejaan dekho to idhar kyaa tumako aataa hai nazar sach kahanaa tumhen apanii kasam lagataa huun kyaa main jhuuthaa sanam kahatii hai ye dil kii pukaar sunatii huun main roz hii yaar jaane bhii de kyuun banatii hai mujhako gairon men kyuun ginatii hai pahale pal duujaa saa lage duuje pal men apanaa lage aae yahaan tak to yaar kyaa jaanam samajhaa karo threedots  tum mujhako achchhe bhii lage baaton ke sachche bhii lage phir bhii dil to darataa hai dhakadhak dhakadhak karataa hai dar kyaa jab hai saath meraa haathon men hai haath meraa dar hai tum vaadaa tod na do raste men mujhe chhod na do mar bhii jaaen to kyaa gam hai naa bichhadenge dilavaale hai shahanaaii kaa intazaar matalab jaanam samajhaa karo threedots

Title: merii zindagii tere haathon men  main nahiin chhaddanaan
Lyrics: merii zindagii tere haathon men teraa haath teraa haath main nahiin chhaddanaan soniye main nahiin chhaddanaan merii manzil terii baaahon men teraa saath teraa saath main nahiin chhaddanaan saahibaa main nahiin chhaddanaan  phuulon men teraa cheharaa hai khushbuu men hai pyaar teraa mujhako duniyaa kii har shai men ruup milaa hai yaar teraa teraa zikr merii har baaton men terii baat merii manzil terii threedots  tere naam kaa taanaa dekar hansatii hai merii sakhiyaan mujhako aate jaate dekhen shaq se logon kii ankhiyaan badaa mazaa hai in mulaaqaaton men mulaaqaat mulaaqaat main nahiin chhaddanaan makkhanaan main nahiin chhaddanaan merii manzil terii threedots

Title: ham naujavaan hain is duniyaa kii jaan hain
Lyrics: ham naujavaan hain is duniyaa kii jaan hain maano yaa naa maano tum aaj kii ham pahachaan hain  jo bhii karanaa ho vo kar dikhaaenge jaanaa ho jahaan vahiin ham jaaenge chhiin ke taaron ko dharatii pe laaenge naam apanaa itihaas men ham kar jaaenge ho ham naujavaan threedots  rokanaa chaaho to bhii rok na paaoge mere jor ke aage tum jhuk jaaoge ik din mere saamane tum bhii aaoge josh men mere hosh ko bhii tum paaoge ho  javaanii kaun hai ham hain dillagii kaun hai ham hain dostii kaun hai ham hain zindagii kaun hai ham hain

Title: mujh se naaraaz ho to ho jaao
Lyrics: mujh se naaraaz ho to ho jaao kud se lekin kafaakafaa no raho mujh se tum duur jaao to jaao aap apane se tum judaa na raho mujh se naaraaz ho to ho jaao kud se lekin kafaakafaa no raho  mujhape chaahe yakiin karo na karo tumako kud par magar yakiin rahe sar pe ho aasmaan yaa ke na ho pair ke niiche ye zamiin rahe mujhako tum bevafaa kaho to kaho threedots mujhako tum bevafaa kaho to kaho tum magar kud se bevafaa na raho mujh se naaraaz ho to ho jaao  aao ik baat main kahuun tumase jaane phir koii ye kahe na kahe tumako apanii talaash karanii hai hamasafar koii bhii rahe na rahe tumako apane sahaare jiinaa hai threedots tumako apane sahaare jiinaa hai dhuundhati koii aasraa no raho  mujh se naaraaz ho to ho jaao kud se lekin kafaakafaa no raho

Title: ham do premii chhat ke uupar galii galii men shor shor shor
Lyrics: ham do premii chhat ke uupar galii galii men shor shor shor ai aa raa raa raa aa haa o re prem ke kachche dhaage se mujhe khiinch le apanii or or or ai aa raa raa raa aa haa o re ham do premii threedots  ho teraa rastaa kisii ne na rokaa mil gayaa kaise tujhako ye mauqaa o deke aayaa huun main sabako dhokhaa are main to havaa kaa huun jhonkaa chorii chorii cupake chupake aanaaa chhup ke jaanaa chhup ke meraa baapuu pakad na le kahiin tujhako samajh kar chor chor chor aa raa raa raa aa haa o re ham do premii threedots  ho dil kii dushman ye duniyaa nigodii isalie maine duniyaa hii chhodii o ek laakhon men hai apanii jodii gam na kar der bas ab hai thodii kab tak aise ham tarasenge ek din khulakar ham barasenge mere saajan tuu saavan main mast ghataa ghanaghor ghor ghor aa raa raa raa aa haa o re ham do premii threedots

Title: jo sachche premii hain kisii se dar nahiin sakate
Lyrics: jo sachche premii hain kisii se dar nahiin sakate jo pyaar karate hain vo kabhii mar nahiin sakate ham pyaar karane vaale har baar kasam lenge jii jii ke marenge ham mar mar ke janam lenge jo sachche premii hain threedots  hamen saath jiinaa hamen saath maranaa nahiin dar kudaa kaa duniyaa se kyaa hai daranaa pyaar hii hai kudaa pyaar iimaan hai pyaar se premiyon kii pahachaan hai is pahachaan kii rusavaaii premii kar nahiin sakate jo pyaar karate hain threedots  premii jang pyaar vaalii haar nahiin sakate log sachche aashiqon ko kabhii maar nahiin sakate pyaar kii lau naa dushman bujhaa paaenge naam chaahat kaa vo naa mitaa paaenge kat jaate hain aashiq jhukaa vo sar nahiin sakate jo pyaar karate hain threedots  hamaare pyaar ke dushman agar nazadiik aaenge hamaare pyaar kii chingaariyon se jal jaaenge muhabbat mit nahiin sakatii kabhii duniyaa kii nafarat se kudaa kaa naam chalataa hai to ik naamemohabbat se

Title: chuudii jo khanakii  yaad piyaa kii aane lagii
Lyrics: khan khan khanake haath men khan khan haath men chuudii jo khanakii haathon men haay haay yaad piyaa kii aane lagii haay bhiigii bhiigii raaton men khan khan khan khan khan khan khan yaad piyaa kii threedots  thandii thandii pavan chale tan man men haay aag lage tere pyaar kii chingaarii ang ang men haay mere jale rimajhim sii barasaaton men haay haay yaad piyaa kii threedots  baagaan men koyal he bole hai dekho mor papiihaa naache hai  abake baras haay ye saavan jaan na merii le jaae dhak dhak moraa jiyaa kare tan se chunar jab ud jaae bole jo koyal baagon men haay haay yaad piyaa kii threedots

Title: main teraa aashiq huun
Lyrics: tuu mere har kvaab men har kvaab kii taabiir men main tere dilakash kayaalon kii hasiin tasaviir men rang ke badale ye dil kaa kuun bharanaa chaahataa huun  main teraa aashiq huun main teraa aashiq huun tujhase ishq karanaa chaahataa huun jhiilsii aankhon men terii duub maranaa chaahataa huun main teraa aashiq huun tujhase ishq karanaa chaahataa huun  main huun tere ruuthane se maanane se bekabar 2 mujhape terii berukii kaa bhii nahiin koii asar apane har shikave gile se main mukaranaa chaahataa huun main teraa aashiq huun tujhase ishq karanaa chahahataa huun  aanejaane ke lie to aur bhii hain raaste 2 raaste sab mainne chhode yaar tere vaaste main to bas terii galii se hii guzaranaa chaahataa huun main teraa aashiq huun tujhase ishq karanaa chaahataa huun  yaa to apane naam se tuu naam meraa jod le 2 yaa lagaa de ek thokar tuu meraa dil tod de tuutakar qadamon men tere main bikharanaa chaahataa huun main teraa aashiq huun tujhase ishq karanaa chaahataa huun  main teraa aashiq huun threedots

Title: ek kadam teraa ek kadam meraa
Lyrics: ku 	ek kadam teraa ek kadam meraa 	sang ham chalen ho safar puuraa a 	ek kadam teraa ek kadam meraa 	sang ham chalen ho safar puuraa ku 	ek kadam teraa ek kadam meraa a 	sang ham chalen ho safar puuraa  ku 	 raaste kii mushkil se koii kyuun ghabaraaegaa 	gam hai kise jo raat hai kaalii kal suuraj aaegaa a 	hamako isii raste men milegii kushiyon kii baaraat 	sone jaisaa din nikalegaa chaandii jaisii raat  2 	ek diiyaa teraa ek diiyaa meraa 	palakon pe rakho ho safar puuraa ku 	ek kadam teraa threedots  	 kadamon se kadamon kaa milanaa kismat hotaa hai 	dil se dil mil jaae vahaan ik tiirath hotaa hai a 	apane dil men pyaar kaa ek anamol khazaanaa hai 	ek duuje kii dhadakan banakar saath nibhaanaa hai  2 ku 	ek dil teraa ek dil meraa 	donon mile ho safar puuraa a 	ek kadam teraa threedots

Title: piichhe piichhe aajaa merii chaal dekh jaaii  meraa laung gavaachaa
Lyrics: piichhe piichhe aajaa merii chaal dekh jaaii kaale kaale ghungharaale baal dekh jaaii  2 dilavaale yaa dekh yaa aaiive meraa laung gavaachaa nigaah maar ik nigaah maar daa aaiive meraa laung gavaachaa threedots  shabaa shabaarigaa 2 khoii khoii aaii thii main ankhiyon ko miiche yahiin kahiin baithii thii main  ambuaa ke niiche  2 koyal kii kuuk sun na sun na kachu anchhaale ke gir gayaa rab daa aaiive meraa laung gavaachaa threedots  laung binaa dil meraa naiyo nahiin lagadaa khaalii khaalii naak meraa  ruup naiyo sajadaa  2  dhan kii tarah chamacham chamake thaa  2 chab meraa dhuundh ke aaiibe meraa laung gavaachaa threedots

Title: sainyaa maan le dil kii baat jiyaraa dhak dhak dhak dhak bole
Lyrics: dhak dhak dhak o sainyaa maan le dil kii baat jiyaraa dhak dhak dhak dhak bole tuu jo pakade mereaa haath jiyaraa dhak dhak dhak dhak bole mastii chhaae haule haule main jo sochuun terii baat jiyaraa dhak dhak dhak dhak bole main jo aauun tere paas jiyaraa dhak dhak dhak dhak bole mastii chhaae haule haule sainyaa maan le dil kii baat threedots  tuune apane diivaane par aisaa jaaduu daalaa hosh ganvaa ke mastii men jhuume teraa matavaalaa maine bhii apane aap ko atharaa saal sambhaalaa dekhaa jo tujhako to de diyaa is joban kaa pyaalaa paake pyaar bharii saugaat jiyaraa dhak dhak dhak dhak bole sainyaa maan le dil kii baat threedots  main jo aankhen band karuun mere sapanon men tuu aae sapanon men aake mujhako kaise kaise tadapaae jiine naa degii mujhako merii jaan terii angadaaii ab to sahii naa jaae mujhase ik pal kii bhii judaaii karavat badaluun saarii raat jiyaraa dhak dhak dhak dhak bole sainyaa maan le dil kii baat threedots

Title: tumhaare kat men nayaa ik salaam kisakaa thaa
Lyrics: tumhaare kat men nayaa ik salaam kisakaa thaa na thaa raqiib to aakir wo naam kisakaa thaa  rahaa na dil men wo bedard aur dard rahaa muqiim kaun huaa hai maqaam kisakaa thaa   wafaa karenge nibaahenge baat maanenge tumhen bhii yaad hai kuchh ye kalaam kisakaa thaa  guzar gayaa wo zamaanaa kahuun to kisase kahuun kayaal dil ko mere subahoshaam kisakaa thaa   wo qatl karake mujhe har kisii se puuchhate hain ye kaam kisane kiyaa hai ye kaam kisakaa thaa  inhiin safaat se hotaa hai aadamii mashahuur jo lutf aap wo karate to naam kisakaa thaa  na puuchh gachchh kisii kii wahaan na aawbhagat tumhaarii bazm men kal ehataraam kisakaa thaa  hamaare kat ke to purje kiye padhaa bhii nahiin sunaa jo tumane badil wo payaam kisakaa thaa  har ek se kahate hain kyaa daag bewafaa nikalaa ye puuchhe inase koii wo gulaam kisakaa thaa

Title: maayaa machhindraa mujh pe mantar mat karanaa
Lyrics: maayaa machhindraa mujh pe mantar mat karanaa  jaaduu mantar se mujh ko paagal mat karanaa  pyaasaa dil ho to pagal ho jaye mistarii dil kaa shaastarii  baanhon men terii biitegii merii raatarii saarii raatarii  phulvaariiphulvaarii divyadhaam kii phulvaarii  aauungaa sab kuchh de duungaa  tuu bhii hai mardaanaa main bhii huun mastaanii  pyaar kii bajaa le dholakii  honthon se chhuu le tuu baanhon men bhar le tuu sundarii bajaa le baansurii  maayaa machhindraa mantar padane tuu aayaa  jaaduu mantar se paagal karane tuu aayaa  tuune kyaa kar diyaa o mere jaanejaan dhadakan men tuu hii tuu hai baalam  jabase pyaar ho gayaa o merii dilarubaa kaabon men tuu hii tuu hai jaanam  baantane se shahad kam hogaa to kyaa chuumane se shakkar rog aaye to kyaa  har din yuun hii milanaa hai naa dhin dhinnaa karanaa hai  sundarii bajaa le baansurii  vaqt pyaar kaa hai sajanaa miinamekh tuu mat karanaa chhokaraa bajaa le khanjaraa  maayaa machhindraa mantar padane main aayaa  jaaduu mantar se mujh ko paagal mat karanaa  na jaanuun meraa naam naa jaanuun meraa gaanv  puuchhuun main tujhako mere raajaa  bhashaa bhii bhuulaa main jiivan bhii bhuulaa  main bhuulaa huun sab kuchh merii raanii  pyaar men savaal karake faayadaa nahiin  kaamadev der tak rukataa nahiin  barf kii tarah pighalenge pighal ke kavitaa likh denge sohinii merii mohinii  donon mil ke duniyaa kaa naqshaa ham ban jaayenge jaalama o mere baalama  maayaa machhindraa mujh pe mantar mat karanaa jaaduu mantar se mujh ko paagal mat karanaa

Title: palakon men aao kho jaao naa
Lyrics: palakon men aao kho jaao naa zulfon men aa ke so jaao naa mujhako mujhii se churaao naa merii jaan merii jaan merii jaan  saanson men merii chhup jaao naa baahon men merii ruk jaao naa dhiire dhiire mujhamen samaao naa merii jaan merii jaan merii jaan  maathe pe bindiyaa hai bindiyaa men tuu hii tuu aankhon men nindiyaa thii ab inamen rahataa hai tuu  o dil meraa hai magar dhadakanen hain terii jaane ye pyaar kii kaisii hai jaaduugarii merii jaan merii jaan palakon men aao threedots  aasamaan le chalo rut javaan le chalo pyaar hii pyaar ho mujhako vahaan le chalo o zindagii men terii ye nazaare bharuun main terii maang men aa chaand taare bharuun merii jaan merii jaan palakon men aao threedots

Title: tum to dhokhebaaj ho  roz roz tum jo sanam aisaa karoge
Lyrics: tum to dhokhebaaj ho vaadaa karake bhuul jaate ho roz roz tum jo sanam aisaa karoge ham jo ruuth jaaenge to haath maloge  aahaa tum bhii badii chaalaak ho muskuraa ke dil jalaatii ho roz roz tum jo sanam aisaa karoge ham jo ruuth jaaenge to aahen bharoge aahaa tum to dhokhebaaj ho threedots  pahale milan kii ye apanii pahalii raat hai hamako tumase karanii kuchh zaruurii baat hai kyaa hasiin samaan hai kyaa suhaaniii ghadii hai thodii der thaharo jii kyaa jaldii padii hai aao aake chuum lo pyaar aise kyuun badhaate ho haan roz roz tum jo threedots  chhodo gile shikave hamase pyaar karo jii aayaa abhii aayaa intazaar karo jii tumako hai kasam na bekaraar karo jii thodaa saa hamaaraa aitabaar karo jii samajho dil kii bebasii is tarah kyuun aajamaate ho roz roz tum jo threedots

Title: taras naa jaao kahiin manzilewafaa ke liye
Lyrics: taras naa jaao kahiin manzilewafaa ke liye kisii ke pyaar na kar baithanaa kudaa ke liye  kudaa se maang ke tujhako na jab tujhe paayaa uthe na haath mere phir kabhii duaa ke liye  kisii kaa tohafaa kabhii rad nahiin kiyaa jaataa wo dukh jo usane diye mainne muskuraa ke liye  qatiil jab bhii lagegii kahiin adaalateishq bas ek hii tum hii chune jaaoge sazaa ke liye

Title: dekar hamen farebewafaa aap kush rahen
Lyrics: dekar hamen farebewafaa aap kush rahen barabaad ham huye bhii to kyaa aap kush rahen  pesh aayen berukii se to ye aap kii kushii apanii to hai bas itanii aap kush rahen  tarketaalluqaat kaa sadamaa to hai zaruur ham phir bhii kah rahe hain sadaa aap kush rahen  jis dil kaa chain aapase mansuub thaa kabhii us dil men karake hashr bapaa aap kush rahen  sadame diye qatiil ko kyaa kyaa na aapane is par bhii aapakaa ho bhalaa aap kush rahen

Title: bhulaa bhii de use jo baat ho gaii pyaare
Lyrics: bhulaa bhii de use jo baat ho gaii pyaare naye charaag jalaa raat ho gaii pyaare  na terii yaad na duniyaa kaa gam na apanaa kayaal ajiib suuratehaalaat ho gaii pyaare  terii nigaahepashemaan ko kaise dekhuungaa kabhii jo tujhase mulaakaat ho gaii pyaare  kabhii kabhii terii yaadon kii saanwalii rut men bahe jo ashq to barasaat ho gaii pyaare  wafaa kaa naam na legaa koii zamaane men hamahaledil ko agar maat ho gaii pyaare

Title: bataa mujhako sanam mere tujhe kaisii lagatii huun
Lyrics: bataa mujhako sanam mere tujhe kaisii lagatii huun ek se lekar das tak number one hai tuu  tujhase pahale naa koii aayaa merii zindagii men sanam koii bhii dil men naa samaayaa tujhe tere rab kii kasam mujhe tere binaa nahiin rahanaa hai saarii duniyaa se yahii kahanaa hai ek se lekar das tak threedots  maine dekhaa naa kabhii bhii tere jaisaa hasiin javaan merii jaan tuu jaanejaan tuu dekhatii huun bas tere khvaab terii hii yaadon men khoyaa rahataa huun main bhii logon se yahii kahataa huun ek se lekar das tak threedots

Title: mujhe ikaraar karane de  mujhako tuu pyaar karane de
Lyrics: mujhe ikaraar karane de zaraa izahaar karane de ankhiyon ko chaar karane de mujhako tuu pyaar karane de naa naa naa chhod piichhaa chhod meraa jaa diivaanii jaa mujhe ikaraar karane threedots  kyuun meraa tan mahakaa kyuun baaiin aankh phadakii maine to pahale kabhii dekhii naa aisii ladakii dekh lenaa paas aa ke tuu to balaa hai luut legii muskaraa ke kaahe sataae jaanataa huun jaan teraa kyaa iraadaa  mujhe ikaraar karane threedots  dekhaa jo maine tumako diivaanaa dil dhadakaa jaane do kar naa khataa shole ko yuun naa bhadakaa ishq men sab bhuul jaa re jii naa jalaa re kyaa kahenge log saare ham hain gavaah re kaam karane de mujhe tuu rok naa rastaa mujhe ikaraar karane threedots

Title: dil jalaa ke meraa muskuraate hain wo
Lyrics: dil jalaa ke meraa muskuraate hain wo apanii aadat ke kab baaz aate hain wo  puuchh lete hain har raaz mujhase meraa apanii har baat mujhase chhupaate hain wo  aap kud to bade bewafaa hain magar qisse sabako wafaa ke sunaate hain wo  jisane dekhaa unhen apane dil se gayaa tiir nazaron ke aise chalaate hain wo

Title: kyaa karen kyaa naa karen ye kaisii mushkil haay
Lyrics: ye sar ye sar ye ye ye 2 kyaa karen kyaa naa karen ye kaisii mushkil haay  koii to bataa de isakaa haal o mere bhaaii  ki ek taraf to us se pyaar karen ham  aur us ko hii ye kahane se daren ham  rozroz ham sochataa yahii aaj hamako vo agar mil jaaye kahiin  to aisaa bolegaa saalaa vaisaa bolegaa khullamkhullaa us pe dil kaa raaz ham kholegaa  vo saamane chamakatii hai saans hii atakatii hai aur ye zabaan jaatii hai phisal   hey hey hey hey hey 2  koii badii baat nahiin hamen kahanaa thaa jo bhii vo to ham yuun bhii kahate magar  phir bhii kahaa nahiin vajah usakii hai yahii bas inkaar se hamako thaa dar  ab kahen yaa tab kahen kahaan kahen kab kahen  sochsoch men hii vo gaii nikal

Title: terii ummiid teraa intazaar  ai sanam ham to sirf tumase pyaar karate hain
Lyrics: terii ummiid teraa intazaar karate hain ai sanam ham to sirf tumase pyaar karate hain  jaaneman ham bhii tujhape jaan nisaar karate hain ai sanam ham to sirf threedots  khvaab aankhon men ab nahiin aate ab to palakon men tum samaae ho har ghadii saath saath rahate ho dil kii duniyaa men ghar basaae ho terii har baat pe ham etabaar karate hain ai sanam ham to sirf threedots  ham ko jisakii thii talaash vo ho tum khushbuu saanson kii dil kii pyaas ho tum tere aashiq tere diivaane hain saarii duniyaa se ham begaane hain jaan ham pyaar tumhen beshumaar karate hain ai sanam ham to sirf threedots

Title: mujhe raat din bas mujhe chaahatii ho
Lyrics: mujhe raat din bas mujhe chaahatii ho kaho naa kaho mujhako sab kuchh pataa hai haan karuun kyaa mujhe tum bataatii nahiin ho chhupaatii ho mujhase ye tumhaarii khataa hai haan mujhe raat din threedots  merii bekaraarii ko had se badhaanaa tumhen khuub aataa hai baaten banaanaa nigaahen milaake yuun meraa chain lenaa sataake mohabbat men yuun dard denaa mujhe dekhake aise palaken jhukaanaa sharaarat nahiin hai to phir aur kyaa hai haan mujhe raat din threedots  tumhen niind aaegii ab naa mere bin mujhe hai yakiin aisaa aaegaa ik din khulii terii zulfon men soyaa rahuungaa tere hii khyaalon men khoyaa rahuungaa kabhii gaur se merii aankhon men dekho merii jaan tumhaaraa hii cheharaa chhupaa hai haan mujhe raat din threedots

Title: tere pyaar ke tiir ne ghaayal  are tuu hai kamaal
Lyrics: haan tere pyaar ke tiir ne ghaayal kar diyaa diyaa tere ishq ne mujhe paagal kar diyaa diyaa are are tuu hai kamaal  dil jiitane kii hai tujhamen har adaa adaa adaa to bolo kaise na hotaa main fidaa fidaa are are tuu hai kamaal  jabase sanam dil ko teraa pyaar milaa aa aa tan men nayaa man men nayaa shor machaa aa aa itane kariib aa jaaen laharon jaise mil jaaen terii saanson men bechainii hai dil kaa mausam tuufaanii hai tere ishq ne mujhe threedots  kaisii diivaanagii kyuun ye betaabiyaan kaisii ye bekhudii kyuun ye behoshiyaan na hosh men tum aao na hosh men ham aaen ai kaash ke ab ye pal aise hii thahar jaaen ho is pyaar se dekho nahiin dam ye nikal hii na jaae kahiin he o merii jaan merii jaan ho tum tere hii dam se to jiite hain ham tere pyaar ke tiir threedots

Title: haan mujhe pyaar huaa pyaar huaa allaah miyaa
Lyrics: haan mujhe pyaar huaa pyaar huaa allaah miyaa bharii barasaat men ikaraar huaa allaah miyaa haan mujhe pyaar huaa threedots  tujhe nahiin dekhuun to jiyaa nahiin maane haal meraa kyaa hai ye meraa kudaa jaane tujhase milane julane ke mil gae bahaane nazar milii aisii ki ban gae fasaane dekhaa jab kvaab to diidaar huaa allaah miyaa haan mujhe pyaar huaa threedots  terii merii chaahat kaa baras rahaa saavan buund girii dil pe to bhiig gaii dhadakan khul ke mile aashiq to tuut gae bandhan javaan dilavaalon kaa aaj huaa sangam aisaa ik baar naa sau baar huaa allaah miyaa bharii barasaat men threedots

Title: chal kahiin chalen sajanaa pyaar yahaan karanaa manaa
Lyrics: chal kahiin chalen sajanaa pyaar yahaan karanaa manaa bastii na koii ghar ho duniyaa kaa na koii dar ho sach ho gayaa teraa meraa sapanaa chal kahiin chalen threedots  mahakii fizaaen ho thandii havaaen ho dilabar kii baahon men dilabar kii baahen hon mastii lutaaen dil nigaahen sharaabii gaalon pe bikharii labon kii gulaabii dharatii ho na ambar ho nadiyaa ho na saagar ho qudarat kii ho dilakash koii rachanaa chal kahiin chalen threedots  yaadon ke mele hon khvaabon ke rele hon saare zamaane ke gam ko bhulaaen jannat se bhii sundar ho sabase hasiin manzar ho na gair ho koii na ho apanaa chal kahiin chalen threedots

Title: madahosh dil kii dhadakan chup sii ye tanhaaii
Film: jab pyaar kisi se hotaa hai
Lyrics: madahosh dil kii dhadakan chup sii ye tanhaaii chhup gayaa chaand kyon kyaa terii zulf laharaaii phir terii yaad ne dil men lii yaar angadaaii madahosh dil kii dhadakan threedots  ye ratajage lambii raaton ke dil naa laage kyaa karuun ye silasile dil kii baaton ke jaaduu chale kyaa karuun bikharaa zulfen so jaauun dil chaahe kahiin kho jaauun madahosh dil kii dhadakan threedots  ye terii aashiqii kar naa de merii rusvaaii  kahanaa thaa jo honthon se maine aankhon se vo kah liyaa dil men tere rahanaa hai mujhako is duniyaa men rah liyaa aa lag jaa tuu is dil se ki milate hain dil mushqil se madahosh dil kii dhadakan threedots  dil liyaa jaan bhii legaa ye pyaar harajaaii

Title: ishq letaa hai aashiqon ke imtihaan aur diivaane hans ke de dete hain jaan
Lyrics: ishq letaa hai aashiqon ke imtihaan aur diivaane hans ke de dete hain jaan  is duniyaa ne diivaane kaa dard na jaanaa dil kaa dushman sadiyon se bedard zamaanaa sab kuchh badalaa par naa badalaa zulm kaa vah afasaanaa gam kii vahii daastaan ishq letaa hai threedots  dil par gam ke zakhm bade gahare hote hain kaise ho shikavaa honthon pe pahare hote hain mandir jaise dil tuute hain dharatii ne dekhaa hai dekhaa kiyaa aasmaan ishq letaa hai threedots

Lyrics: ko 	krishnaa krishnaa krishnaa 	krishnaa hare krishnaa 	krishnaa raadhe krishnaa ku 	o krishnaa you are the greatest musician of this world 	o krishnaa kyuun vaadaa de ke refusion of the world  a 	baansurii se tuune prem sandeshaa diyaa hai mohanaa  ku 	tuune jo bhii giit sunaayaa giitaa ban ke jag pe chhaayaa 	gyaan kaa man men diip jalaayaa 	tuune hii sab ko lubhaayaa aur sab ko nachaayaa a 	pyaar ko tuune kiyaa hai paavan har insaan ko diyaa hai jiivan 	har aangan men raadhaa mohan 	tuune hii jag ko amar sangiit sunaayaa

Title: ye faasale  hazaar baar ruke ham hazaar baar chale
Lyrics: ye faasale terii galiyon ke hamase tay na hue hazaar baar ruke ham hazaar baar chale  na jaane kaun sii mattii watan kii mattii thii nazar men dhuul jigar men liye gubaar chale  ye kaisii sarahaden ulajhii huii hain pairon men ham apane ghar kii taraf uth ke baar baar chale

Title: churaa lo naa dil meraa sanam
Lyrics: dil meraa churaa lo aankhon men chhupaa lo apanaa banaa lo sanam  naa naa naa naa naa naa naa naa 2 haan haan haan naa naa naa naa  churaa lo naa dil meraa sanam banaa lo naa apanaa sanam ke tere bin na jii sakenge ke tere bin na mar sakenge kuchh bhii na kar sakenge  churaa lo naa dil meraa sanam churaae kyun dil teraa sanam  naa naa naa naa naa naa naa naa haan haan haan naa naa naa naa  masaalaa baant luun main pyaaz kaat luun chhurii kidhar gaii hai nal khulaa huaa main kah rahaa hun kyaa tuu sun rahii hai kyaa tuu sun rahii hai kyaa main kah rahaa hun kyaa teraa diwaanaapan hai yah o bekabar kitchen hai yah yah kyaa hua uthaa dhuaan kyaa jaane kyaa jal gayaa ke tere bin na jii sakenge ke tere bin na mar sakenge kuchh bhii na kar sakenge  churaa lo naa dil meraa sanam churaae kyun dil teraa sanam  na jaane kyaa kahaa kaho naa phir zaraa sunun main gaur se kaho naa zor se kahaa jo zor se to chaaron aur se hansenge ham pe sab hamaare shor se karenge baat phir kabhii jawaab chaahie abhii nahii nahii abhii nahii itanii bhii jaldii hai kyaa ke tere bin na jii sakenge ke tere bin na mar sakenge ham soch kar kahenge  achchhaa huaa jo pyaar kii pahachaan ho gaii dete the jis pe jaan woh anjaan ho gaii mausam to main nahiin huun jo aauungaa jaauungaa ruuthaa jo ek baar to waapas na aauungaa  naa naa naa naa naa naa naa naa haan haan haan naa naa naa naa  churaa lo naa dil meraa sanam banaa lo naa apanaa sanam ke tere bin na jii sakenge ke tere bin na mar sakenge ham soch kar kahenge  dil meraa churaa lo aankhon men chhupaa lo apanaa banaa lo sanam

Title: aajaa aajaa naa naa  paas nahiin aaegii to main
Lyrics: ku 	aajaa aajaa saa 	naa naa ku 	paas aa aa saa 	naa naa ku 	paas nahiin aaegii to main mar jaauungaa saa 	dekho piyaa shaam hone lagii hai ab mujhe ghar jaane do ku 	jaane kyon itanii jaldii padii hai dil zaraa bhar jaane do saa 	ab mujhe ghar jaane do ku 	dil zaraa bhar jaane do  saa 	kal isii jagah pe tujhe miluungii main sajanaa ku 	kal kaa o gorii tuu dikhaa naa mujhe sapanaa saa 	tadapegaa aaj kal miithaa phal paaegaa ku 	jaanataa huun kal teraa kabhii nahiin aaegaa saa 	jaane de naa ku 	naa naa naa naa saa 	jaane nahiin degaa badanaamii ho jaaegii ku 	tuu chalii gaii to merii jaan chalii jaaegii 	aajaa aajaa saa 	naa naa threedots  	sachchii mohabbat men ek duusare ko kabhii nahiin chhuaa karate ku 	chhuunaa to chhodo aaj kal ke do premii jaane kyaa kyaa kiyaa karate hain saa 	kabhii nahiin chhuaa karate ku 	ho jaane kyaa kyaa kiyaa karate hain saa 	aajakal ke premiyon ko duur se salaam hai ku 	duniyaa men pyaar se badaa naa koii kaam hai saa 	dekho mere piichhe piichhe tum nahiin aanaa ku 	main bhii kahiin aur banaa luungaa thikaanaa saa 	aajaa aajaa ku 	naa naa saa 	paas nahiin aaegaa to main mar jaauungii ku 	phir tere honthon pe ye baat nahiin aaegii saa 	kabhii nahiin aaegii o kabhii nahiin aaegii ku 	khaa merii qasam kabhii duur nahiin jaaegii saa 	khaatii huun qasam kabhii duur nahiin jaauungii

Title: kurate kii baiiyaan ko uupar chadhaii ke
Lyrics: kurate kii baiiyaan ko uupar chadhaii ke mastii men rahate hain panavaa chabaii ke khainii men thodaa saa chuunaa milaii ke bhaiyaa tum bhii dekho zaraa thaskaa lagaii ke kurate kii baiiyaan threedots  ham hain banaaras ke baanke bihaarii aankhon se kaajal churaa len tumhaarii duniyaa hai nahalaa ham nahale pe dahalaa har baar apanaa to number hai pahalaa aage sasur ke naatii sun aage jo nikale koii ham se chhailaa sasure ko de ultaa laafaa jamaii ke kurate kii baiiyaan threedots  laharen maare merii javaanii gangaa ghaat kaa pii ke paanii dekho nahiin karanaa naadaanii ye aag hai jise samajhe ho paanii rapat gayaa dil tujhape o raanii kyon karatii hai aanaakaanii tum jaanate ho ki main huun diivaanii mahangii padegii raajaa nazaren ladaanii kurate kii baiiyaan threedots  thumakaa lagaii ke ye dharatii hilaii den jisako bhii chaahen usako nachaii den ghunghate men cheharaa chhipaatii hain goriyaan hamako jo dekhen to khanakaae chuudiyaan bachavaa bajaa dholakii rang jamaii ke rakh de karejavaa pe barchhii chalaii ke kurate kii baiiyaan threedots

Title: maan maan vo bachche duniyaa men  mujhe maaf karanaa om saaiin raam
Singer: abhijit alka yagnik aditya narayan anmol
Lyrics: maan maan vo bachche duniyaa men khushanasiib hote hain jo mummy daddy ke kariib hote hain mujhe maaf karanaa om saaiin raam tum se pahale luungaa mummy daddy kaa naam  jinhen mummy daddy kaa pyaar nahiin milataa unhen khushiyon kaa sansaar nahiin milataa kabhii bhii hamen naa yuun majabuur karanaa ham to bade hote hain in kii uungalii thaam mujhe maaf karanaa threedots  in ke saath rahanaa hai hamen subah shaam mujhe maaf karanaa threedots  mujhe maaf karanaa om saaiin raam tum se pahale luungii apane bachchon kaa naam  o o mujhe maaf karanaa om saaiin raam tum se pahale luungaa apane bachchon kaa naam  hamen maaf karanaa om saaiin raam tum se pahale lenge apane bachchon kaa naam

Title: ankhiyon ne ankhiyon se milake  o rabbaa dil aae mushkil se
Lyrics: ankhiyon ne ankhiyon se milake kar lie saude dil ke o rabbaa dil aae mushkil se  yuun pyaar kaa mausam laharaayaa ik paradesii bhanvaraa aayaa angadaaii kalii ne lii khil ke o rabbaa dil aae threedots  pahalii nazar men jaan nikalii na naa nikalii na naa nikalii bas rah gae sharm se lab sil ke o rabbaa dil aae threedots  ye ishq to hukm kudaa kaa hai kuchh maanguun vaqt duaa kaa hai  ai kaash na bichhaden ham mil ke o rabbaa dil aae threedots  jo phuul yahaan par khil na sake vo phuul vahaan khil jaaenge ham is duniyaa men na mil sake us duniyaa men mil jaaenge likhane vaale ne ashqon se ai ishq terii takadiir likhii ye paanchon dariyaa roye bahut tab vaaris shaah ne hiir likhii

Title: o mere daddy ye kab huaa thaa  o mere bituaa
Lyrics: o mere daddy ye kab huaa thaa kaise huaa thaa bhalaa hoy o tumako bataa duun baat ye kaise dil kaa hai ye maamalaa hoy o mere daddy threedots  kuchh to kaho dil kaa haal puuchho na aise savaal koii ishaaraa karo chup se guzaaraa karo kaise huii thii mulaakaat huun mulaakaat us din huii thii barasaat are baaton men terii main aa gayaa kyaa chaalaak hai tuu badaa hoy o mere daddy threedots  ham bhii kabhii the javaan chhedo to vo daastaan tumase ye sab kyuun kahuun kyaa main koii gair huun pahalii nazar kaa thaa pyaar kaagaz pe likh luun main ye fasaanaa mere bhii kaam aaegaa hoy kaise huaa thaa milan are mat puuchh bhaaii karane pade sau jatan pahalii puraanii koii baat haan haan picture gae the ham saath kyaa thaa us picture kaa naam naam thaa joruu kaa gulaam are terii mummy merii joruu banii main ban gayaa usakaa gulaam hoy o mere bituaa ye kab huaa thaa kaise huaa thaa bhalaa hoy merii bahuu ko kaise pataayaa ye to bataa do zaraa o mere daddy kaise bataa duun dil kaa hai ye maamalaa haay

Title: betaab ham aavaaraa ham hain  yahii zindagii hai apanii
Lyrics: betaab ham aavaaraa ham hain biite sau janam aavaaraa ham hain kabhii chal die kabhii tham gae kabhii gam mile kabhii gam gae yahii zindagii hai apanii betaab ham aavaaraa ham threedots  tumako samajhaaen kyaa hamako bhii pyaar thaa kahatii thii vo sadaa tuu hii to hai meraa vo ladakii magar kho gaii hai kisii aur kii ho gaii hai betaab ham aavaaraa ham threedots  pahale jo khvaab the sab kaamayaab the pahale thii raah men manzil nigaah men magar nahiin ab koii manzil chale ham jidhar bhii kahe dil betaab ham aavaaraa ham threedots

Title: har taraf pattharon kaa saayaa hai
Lyrics: har taraf pattharon kaa saayaa hai mainne shiishe kaa ghar banaayaa hai  kho gaye rezaa rezaa kaab mere tuu bhii mujhape ro ai shabaab mere tujhako mainne ye din dikhaayaa hai  dil meraa kaanch kaa khilaunaa thaa ek din chakanaachuur honaa thaa dil jo tuutaa to yaad aayaa hai  kisakaa shikawaa karuun kudaa mere koii mujarim nahiin siwaa mere apanaa dhokhaa to mainne khaayaa hai

Title: jaaduu bharii aankhon vaalii suno  tum aise mujhe dekhaa na karo
Lyrics: mujhako jab aise dekhatii ho tum rang bhar jaate hain fizaaon men kasamasaatii hai aarazuu dil men giit ghul jaate hain havaaon men  jaaduu bharii aankhon vaalii suno tum aise mujhe dekhaa na karo phir main koii ummiid karuun phir mujhako koii aramaan ho  tum shaayad merii ban jaao phir dil ko aisaa gumaan ho par aisaa na ho achchhaa hai in baaton men kyaa rakhaa hai mujhako aisii ummiid na do jaaduu bharii aankhon threedots  phir dhadakan men tum bas jaao phir koii gazal main gaauun phir chaand men tumako main dekhuun phuulon men tumako paauun par aisaa na ho achchhaa hai isakaa anjaam to hotaa hai vo dard hii detaa hai dil ko jaaduu bharii aankhon threedots

Title: rekhaa kii aankhon ko dekhaa  na milii kahiin vo heroine
Lyrics: rum jhum tum jhum taa naa naa naa tum tum tik tik tik tik rekhaa kii aankhon ko dekhaa dekhii shriidevii kii chaal mastii miinaaxii kii dekhii dekhe raviinaa ke gaal muskaan dekhii hai maadhurii kii dekhe hain dimpal ke baal na milii kahiin vo heroine jo is hero ko bhaa jaae laao koii parii kahiin se jisape isakaa dil aa jaae na milii kahiin vo threedots  kaalii kaalii lat ghungharaalii aankhen tirachhii tirachhii tiikhii tiikhii lagatii hai ye kolhaapur kii mirachii kahade pore se ai laajavaab porii ye hai chandaa to ye hai chakorii kahiin hogii nahiin aisii jodii aake jaldii se baandh le priit dorii kahade pore se threedots  sabake sab naadaan ho tum itanii bhii pahachaan nahiin jo bik jaae baazaaron men aurat vo saamaan nahiin shaadii hai janmon kaa bandhan ik do din kaa mel nahiin jab jii chaahe isase khelen aurat koii khel nahiin  aaii hai kis duniyaa se lagatii hai huur ke jaisii sach kahataa huun dharatii par hogii na ladakii aisii kyaa aankhen hain kyaa mukhadaa hai kamasin hai chaand kaa tukadaa hai luutii hain merii niinden isane meraa chain churaayaa hai haan yahii to hai vo heroine jis pe meraa dil aayaa hai

Title: jaamomiinaa merii nazaron se hataa de saaqii
Lyrics: jaamomiinaa merii nazaron se hataa de saaqii ye jo aankhon men chhalakatii hai pilaa de saaqii  sholaaeishq se chhalakaa de mere shiishe ko aur betaab ko betaab banaa de saaqii  phir kabhii hosh na aaye to koii baat nahiin aaj ham jitanii piyen utanii pilaa de saaqii  joshemastii men bagalagiir hon bichhade huye dil aaj insaan ko insaan banaa de saaqii  zindagii kaabemusalasal ke siwaa kuchh bhii nahiin isakii taabiir to darshan ko bataa de saaqii

Title: main kudii anjaanii shahar anjaanaa ho
Lyrics: main kudii anjaanii shahar anjaanaa ho kahaan main chalii aaii ho kahaan thaa mujhe jaanaa ho yahaan par bhanvare vahaan par bhanvare kahaan hai vo meraa paravaanaa  sab nigaahon men dhokhaa hai dil ne mujhe mere rokaa hai dil lene vaale dekhe dil dene vaale dekhe dekhaa nahiin hai koii jaan dene vaalaa nigaahen sab dekhen adaaen sab dekhen dekhe na koii meraa sharamaanaa main kudii anjaanii threedots  aankhen churaa ke mujhe jaane do daaman bachaa ke mujhe jaane do vo pyaar karane vaale zamaane se niraale baakii to saare rang ruup ke shikaarii alag hai vo dil kaa lagaanaa main kudii anjaanii threedots

Title: rappaa rappaa ram pam pam  mummy papa hamako pyaare
Lyrics: rappaa rappaa ram pam pam rappaa rappaa ram threedots  jab koii bole mummy se bachche hain pyaare aur ye kahatii hain hamako ghar se baahar jaao kam  har pal unakii aankhon men jhilamil karate rahate ham  aur ye phulavaarii donon ne naazon se paalii dekho apanii bagiyaa men khushiyaan naachen chham

Title: sarakii jo sar se vo  terii chunariyaa dil le gaii
Lyrics: laa laa laa sarakii jo sar se vo dhiire dhiire paagal huaa re main dhiire dhiire terii chunariyaa dil le gaii sarakii jo sar se threedots  terii ye bindiyaa dil le gaii  tumase milakar ye jaanaa hai hotaa kyuun dil ye diivaanaa hai tay kar liyaa tumhen paanaa hai kyaa pyaar hai ye dikhaanaa hai mere bhole sanam mere pyaare sanam diivaane sanam anajaane sanam bole meraa kanganaa dhiire dhiire bole merii paayal dhiire dhiire o bole teraa kanganaa dhiire dhiire bole terii paayal dhiire dhiire terii chunariyaa threedots  teraa meraa janmon kaa naataa hai yuun hii nahiin dil lubhaataa hai rishte ye rab hii banaataa hai karake bahaane milaataa hai merii yaadon men tum merii baaton men tum merii saanson men tum merii raahon men tum bole merii dhadakan dhiire dhiire bole merii tadapan dhiire dhiire o bole terii dhadakan dhiire dhiire bole terii tadapan dhiire dhiire terii chunariyaa threedots

Title: mujh se muhabbat kaa iqaraar karataa
Lyrics: a  mujh se muhabbat kaa iqaraar karataa     kaash koii ladakaa mujhe pyaar karataa  ku mujh se muhabbat ka iqraar karatii     kaash koii ladakii mujhe pyaar karatii  a  merii maang men chaand taare sajaataa     jo main ruuth jaatii mujhe vo manaataa     haalat merii vo jaanataa     dhadakan merii pahachaanataa     apnii bhii chaahat kaa izahaar karataa     kaash koii ladakaa mujhe pyaar karataathreedots  ku o o     vo bechain hotii main betaab hotaa     nigaahon men usakii meraa kvaab hotaa     sharamaa ke vo lagatii gale     rakhataa use palakon tale     chorii chorii vo meraa diidaar karatii     kaash koii ladakii mujhe pyaar karatiithreedots

Title: jay maataa dii he ambe balihaarii  asht bhujaaen vesh anokhaa
Lyrics: jay maataa dii jay maataa dii he ambe balihaarii lage sabako tuu pyaarii terii sheron kii savaarii dekhen sab nar naarii he ambe balihaarii threedots  asht bhujaaen vesh anokhaa khadag teg hai terii shobhaa tere jaisaa koii na hogaa maan ab aankhen khol jay maataa dii jay maataa dii jay maataa dii bol  he maataa koharaam machaa hai kathin ghadii hai jagadambe tuu jaag ke mushkil aan padii hai phuunk ke apanaa desh aag jo senk rahe hain kar unakaa sanhaar vatan jo bech rahe hain kaii shumbh nishumbh maare tuune kaii daitya yahaan janme hain phir se maan ambe trishuul to le tuu unape bijalii banake gir asht bhujaaen threedots  kare bharosaa koii yahaan pe kis vyakti kaa log yahaan pe dhong rachaate hain bhakti kaa ye saarii dharatii maataa darabaar hai teraa is dharatii pe lagaa huaa hai paap kaa deraa he shakti maan khappar vaalii hai amar ajey akhand ruup he jagadambe he mahaakaalii phir dhaar le tuu prachand ruup asht bhujaaen threedots

Title: pyaar ke giit ye dil jo gaane lagaa  dhadakanon ko nae jo
Lyrics: pyaar ke giit ye dil jo gaane lagaa ik nashaa saa nigaahon pe chhaane lagaa dhadakanon ko nae jo taraane mile hamako diivaanagii ke bahaane mile zaraa mere paas aa zaraa mujhe ye bataa zaraa saa jo hosh thaa zaraa bhii na kyuun rahaa pyaar ke giit ye threedots  duniyaa men jo hai chaandanii jo dhuup hai tumhiin se hai duniyaa men jo ye rang hai ye ruup hai tumhiin se hai ik nayaa mod apanii kahaanii men hai ik nayaa husn ab zindagaanii men hai dhadakanon ko nae threedots  ab soch men ab dhyaan men har baat men tumhiin to ho ab subah men ab shaam men din raat men tumhiin to ho tumako paayaa to kyaa ho gaii zindagii ik hasiin kvaab men kho gaii zindagii dhadakanon ko nae threedots

Title: o mere duulhe raajaa baaje galiyon men baajaa
Film: ek thaa dil ek thi dhadkan
Lyrics: o mere duulhe raajaa baaje galiyon men baajaa milane sasuraajii tere aae re le ke aaii tilak hai samadhan samadhii le ke aae hain tan man dhan baaje galiyon men baajaa aaj re  kyaa main bataauun kaise hain tere sasuraajii munh se nikal na jaae koii gaalii ho dulhan kii ammaa yahii mote nakhare vaalii dulhan kii bhaabhii ek number kam vaalii dulhan kii hai jo bahanaa vaah jii vaah kyaa usakaa kahanaa kyaa main bataauun kuchh na kahaa jaae re le ke aaii tilak hai threedots  duulhe raajaa hain kaise tere gharavaale kyon tuune hain mustande paale are baap uthaaiigiraa chaachaa hai bhikhaarii bhaaii lafangaa bahanaa badasuurat bechaarii aur jo hai terii maiyaa usakii kyaa boluun bhaiyaa bhainson kaa jaise chaaraa khaae re o le ke aaii tilak hai threedots  he duulhe raajaa tum ye ladaaii rukavaa do donon gharon ke logon ko ye samajhaa do duulhe dulhan ko sab mil ke duaa do jug jug jien ye donon phuulen phalen ye donon ghar khushiyon se bhar jaae re ho le ke aaii tilak hai threedots

Title: aajaa aajaa mere sapanon ke raajakumaar
