Lyrics: dekhe hain kaii chehare jahaan men magar ek tere hii chehare pe pyaar aayaa honge hasiin laakhon jahaan men magar ek tujhape hii dil diladaar aayaa pyaar aayaa pyaar aayaa ek tere hii chehare threedots  aankhon men aisii kaajal kii rekhaa hue javaan duniyaa men magar kitane yuun kisii pe na aisaa nikhaar aayaa pyaar aayaa ek tere hii chehare threedots  tujhape lutaa dii ye zindagaanii betaabii is dil kii badhatii gaii pyaar aisaa kisii pe pahalii baar aayaa pyaar aayaa ek tere hii chehare threedots

Title: kisii roz tum se mulaakaat hogii  merii mahabuubaa
Lyrics: kisii roz tum se mulaakaat hogii merii jaan us din mere saath hogii magar kab naa jaane ye barasaat hogii meraa dil hai pyaasaa meraa dil akelaa zaraa tasviir se tuu nikal ke saamane aa merii mahabuubaa merii taqadiir hai tuu machal ke saamane aa merii mahabuubaa merii mahabuubaa   nahiin yaad kab se magar main huun jab se mere dil men terii muhabbat hai tab se main shaayar huun teraa tuu merii gazal hai badii bekaraarii mujhe aajakal hai zaraa tasviir se tuu threedots  bhalaa kaun hai vo hamen bhii bataao ye tasviir usakii hamen bhii dikhaao ye kisse sabhii ko sunaate nahiin hai magar doston se chhupaate nahiin hai tere dardedil kii davaa ham karenge naa kuchh kar sake to duaa ham karenge tadap kar aaegii vo tujhe mil jaaegii vo terii mahabuubaa kisii roz apanii mulaakaat hogii zaraa tasviir se tuu threedots

Title: tere lie laayaa huun main laal laal chuudiyaan
Lyrics: tere lie laayaa huun main laal laal chuudiyaan sajengii kalaaiyon pe pyaar kii ye chuudiyaan  mujhako pasand hain ye laal laal chuudiyaan pahanuungii pyaar se main yaar kii chuudiyaan tere lie laayaa threedots  ghar jaaegii tuu mujhase milane ke baad re ye jab chhanakengii aaegii merii yaad re apane pyaar ke ikaraar kii ye chuudiyaan mujhako pasand hain threedots  laaya tuu jaise ye tohafaa apane saath re mere ghar laanaa yuun hii ek din baaraat re mere lie to aitabaar kii ye chuudiyaan tere lie laayaa threedots

Title: dil se mere duur na jaanaa
Lyrics: dil se mere duur na jaanaa tum merii zindagii tum merii ho khushii dil se mere duur threedots  kyuun hain ye duuriyaan jaane tum ho kahaan main to huun vahaan tum raho jahaan tere sang main rahuungii sadaa merii nazar se na palaken jhukaanaa tum merii zindagii threedots  terii bas ik nazar kar de dil pe asar main to huun idhar kyuun ho bekhabar thaam lo tum mujhe hamasafar dil se mere duur threedots

Title: nainon men mahabuub ke  kanvaaraa nahiin maranaa
Lyrics: nainon men mahabuub ke dekhuungii main duub ke shaadii ke baad main mar jaauun to gam nahiin kanvaaraa nahiin maranaa  saahil pe baith ke dariyaa ke tuufaan kaa nazaaraa nahiin karanaa kanvaaraa nahiin maranaa threedots  ye laaj kaa ghuunghat kholuungii ye baat main sabase boluungii mere gharavaalon chup rahane kaa tum mujhe ishaaraa nahiin karanaa kanvaaraa nahiin maranaa threedots  jaa chutakii bhar sinduur mangaa jaldii se merii maang sajaa main mar gaii to leke meraa naam tuu pukaaraa nahiin karanaa kanvaaraa nahiin maranaa threedots  paanii men aag lagaanii hai is dil par chot bhii khaanii hai hansanaa hai ronaa hai jiinaa hai dil thaam ke guzaaraa nahiin karanaa kanvaaraa nahiin maranaa threedots  o dil kaa aramaan nikal jaae phir chaahen jaan nikal jaae o duniyaa vaalon tum do dilon ko judaa kudaaraa nahiin karanaa kanvaaraa nahiin maranaa threedots  ye dil kaa phuul nahiin khilataa to marake bhii chain nahiin milataa milane se pahale terii judaaii mujhe ganvaaraa nahiin karanaa kanvaaraa nahiin maranaa threedots

Title: kitanaa pyaar tumhen karate hain
Lyrics: saanu kitanaa pyaar tumhen karate hain aaj hamen maaloom huaa jiite nahiin tuma par marate hain aaj hamen maaloom huaa  saadhanaa kitanaa pyaar tumhen karate hain aaj hamen maaloom huaa jiite nahiin tum par marate hain aaj hamen maaloom huaa  saanu kitanaa pyaar tumhen karate hain aaj hamen maaloom huaa  saanu idhar aao ki diiwaanaa tumhaaraa hamako bananaa hai saadhanaa ham in baanhon men kho jaaen hamaarii bhii tamannaa hai saanu isake lie ab tak tarase hain aaj hamen maaloom hua threedots  saadhanaa wahii tum ho magar kyon tumape itanaa pyaar aayaa saaanu tumhaare paas main bhii aaj kitanaa beqaraar aayaa saadhanaa isake lie maare phirate hain aaj hamen maaluum huaa  threedots

Title: tumhen dil se chaahaa thaa hamane magar tum hue na hamaare
Lyrics: tumhen dil se chaahaa thaa hamane magar tum hue na hamaare hamiin se hii ye berukhii kyon sabhii dost hain tumako pyaare  jo kaabil na the dostii  ke rahe paas vo aap hii ke hamen bas adaavat se dekhaa na ik din muhabbat se dekhaa karo laakh inake nazaare kisii ke na honge sitaare ye bas dekh le mere pyaare chhuo to ye shole sharaare  hasiin jitanii jisakii adaa hai ke utanaa hii vo bevafaa hai ke patthar kaa inakaa jigar hai vafaa kaa na in pe asar hai

Title: tuu maange dil
Lyrics: chitraa tuu maange dil main de duun jaan tuu jo kahe main kar duun haan le le sanam meraa tuu imtahaan  hariharan tuu maange dil main de duun jaan tuu jo kahe main kar duun haan le le sanam meraa tuu imtahaan  chitraa tuu maange dil main de duun jaan  hariharan tuu jo kahe main kar duun haan  chitraa zulfon ke saaye men so jaa tuu  palakon pe aajaa tujhe main bithaa luun  hariharan main terii baanhon men chhup jaauun  is dil kii galiyon men tujhako chhupaa luun  chitraa bas dhuundhataa phire saaraa jahaan  hariharan tuu maange dil main de duun jaan  chitraa tuu jo kahe main kar duun haan  hariharan main teraa aashiq huun tuu merii mahabuubaa phir kaisii majabuuriyaan hain  chitraa main terii aankhon men tuu merii aankhon men phir kaisii ye duuriyaan hain  hariharan mausam hai ye hasiin ham hain jawaan  chitraa tuu maange dil main de duun jaan  hariharan tuu jo kahe main kar duun haan

Title: chhotaa bachchaa jaan ke na koii  dubii dubii dab dab
Lyrics: chhotaa bachchaa jaan ke na koii aankh dikhaanaa re dubii dubii dab dab akl kaa kachchaa samajh ke hamako na samajhaanaa re dubii dubii dab dab bholii suurat jaan ke hamase na takaraanaa re dubii dubii dab dab naa dhin dhinnaa naa dhin dhinnaa naach nachaa denge chhotaa bachchaa jaan ke threedots  ik din deke do athanniyaan maan bolii jaa le aa dhaniyaa paise deke dukaanadaar se main bolaa baabuu de do dhaniyaa badaa saa kaagaz le kar usane rakh diyaa usamen thodaa saa dhaniyaa maine bolaa baabuu baniyaa kaagaz bech rahe yaa dhaniyaa kaagaz rakho baajuu men dhanie ko rakho taraazuu men sun merii baat vo rahaa na kaabuu men kyaa bolaa bolaa tujhako bataauun main main bhii kahaan kam thaa maine bhii kah diyaa bachche ko thagataa hai shor machaauun main usake baad huaa kyaa ye bhii to batalaanaa re usake baad usake baad to jaise usakaa mar gayaa naanaa re biich bajariyaa gaayaa maine jab ye gaanaa re chhotaa bachchaa jaan ke threedots  kishan bhaiyaa kishan bhaiyaa mere aam kii guthalii gir gaii aam ko khaa guthalii na dekh aage chal piichhe na dekh siidhaa siidhaa chal varanaa paanv men phans jaaegii ret phir kyaa kare ye ghar jaa ke jab maan ne maaraa re chup kyuun ho gae bolo naa sun re chhotuu sun re hariyaa maan hotii mamataa kii nadiyaa daant ke hamako khud bhii roe khaanaa de badhiyaa se badhiyaa maan ko jaa ke kabhii sunaanaa na ye gaanaa re chhotaa bachchaa jaan ke threedots

Title: dhol bajane lagaa
Lyrics: dhol baajne lagaa gaanv sajane lagaa koii laut ke aayaa hai sang apane vo rang kisane laayaa hai aayaa re hamaraa mitavaa  ham jhuum jhuum gaaye  naache re hamaraa manavaa   aanevaale na ab jaanaa kabhii chhod ke padate ham painyyaa kabhii haath kabhii jodake  jaane na denge ham ab dil todake  apana kunvar aayaa rajeshvar aayaa sang apane vo rang kisane laayaa hai   threedots  muhabbat se bharaa ek dil hai jaise  mere bachapan kaa saathi mera gaanv  bahut miithaa hai paanii is kune kaa bharadii thandii hai een pairdon ki chaaoun  khulaa sangiit hai jaise havaa men  zaraa aavaaz to sun chakiyon ki  rahet ghata hai bhini bhini ley mein  surili boliyan hai panchiyon ki  mein barso baad lauta houn  to jaana ye gaaoun geet hai sadiyon puraana

Title: dil ke jharokhe men aajaa  chaand saa mukhadaa dikhaa jaa  saathiyaa beliyaa
Lyrics: saathiyaa beliyaa saathiyaa beliyaa aajaa aajaa aajaa aajaa dil ke jharokhe men aajaa chandaa saa mukhadaa dikhaa jaa ritu yahii pyaar kii hai dilabar yaar kii hai sunane kii ek baat hai aajaa saathiyaa beliyaa  ab to aajaa pukaaren tujhe pyaar kii vaadiyaan har tamannaa merii raah dekhe terii jaanejaan bekaraar intazaar ye is dil kii viiraaniyaan dil ke jharokhe men aajaa threedots  kho gayaa bachapanaa aa rahe hain javaanii ke din dekho naa laae hamako kahaan zindagaanii ke din aur naa jaane kyaa aage dikhalaaen terii meharabaaniyaan dil ke jharokhe men aajaa threedots

Title: thodaa matake se paanii zaraa de gorie
Lyrics: thodaa matake se paanii zaraa de gorie main to kab se huun pyaasaa khadaa gorie jaa jaa matakii naa chhuunaa javaan chhore paanii piine ke bahaane daalegaa dore  gahare gahare kunve kaa thandaa thandaa paanii thodaa saa pilaa de terii hogii meharabaanii tuu hai harajaaii terii jhuuthii hai kahaanii chor lafange tujhe  kaun de javaanii  2 koii rastaa hamen bhii dikhaa de gorie main to kab se khadaa threedots  yuun hii chalaa jaauungaa bahut pachhataaegii aisaa dilavaalaa kahiin dhuundhe se na paaegii jaaegaa tuu kaise main jaane nahiin duungii pyaar se rokuungii  nazar se pilaauungii  2 laa pilaa de pilaa de pilaa de gorie puurii matakii kaa paanii pilaa duun chhore

Title: mausam kii saragam ko sun
Lyrics: mausam kii saragam ko sun kyaa gaa rahaa hai samaan 2 tuu bhii gaa tere sang gaae saaraa jahaan gaae jaa gaae jaa gaaejaa  mausam kii threedots  har sur pe dil yuun dhadake saanson men agan bhadake sun kar yah sadaa 2 aise aaj gaa kaamoshii bol uthe palaken bhiig jaaen jal barase binaa ghataa gaae jaa gaae jaa gaae jaa mausam kii saragam threedots  phir ik din le jaaegaa ghunghata teraa uthaaegaa koii raajakumaar 2 phir yeh ruuprang ban jaaegaa chaman hogaa angang ek mastii bharii bahaar gaae jaa gaae jaa gaae jaa mausam kii saragam threedots

Title: kahanaa hai tumase kahanaa hai  sau baar janam len tere lie
Lyrics: ye saathii ho jo aisaa mil jaae jo pyaar men sau baar janam len tere lie tere ishq men mar jaaen jo kiyaa na ho kisii aashiq ne kuchh aisaa kar jaaen  kahanaa hai tumase kahanaa hai rahanaa hai dil men rahanaa hai  kaamosh palakon tale sapanen tumhaare palen tumhii ho nazar men jigar men tumhiin ho saanson men tum ho duaa men sadaa men tumhiin ho baaton men kahanaa hai tumase threedots  aao tumhen main pyaar duun donon jahaan vaar duun parii ho sabaa ho kalii ho machalatii shabanam ho koii nashaa ho fazaa ho suhaanaa mausam ho kahanaa hai tumase threedots

Title: kar lo pyaar  pyaar gazab kii chiiz hai
Lyrics: kar lo pyaar kar lo pyaar pyaar gazab kii chiiz hai padh lo aaj subah kaa parchaa pyaar karoge muft men ho jaaegaa yaaron charchaa pyaar gazab kii chiiz hai threedots  lagate hain phiike sab mausam jab pyaar kaa mausam aataa hai chehare pe chamak aa jaatii hai jab ishq kahiin ho jaataa hai binaa mol milataa hai ye nahiin hotaa isamen kharchaa pyaar karoge muft men threedots  aashiq badaa niraalaa hai jo yaar kii aankhon men duubaa vo ladakii bhii kyaa ladakii hai jo ban jaatii hai mahabuubaa jisane pyaar kiyaa sabase uunchaa hai usakaa darjaa pyaar karoge muft men threedots

Title: mausam kii tarah tum bhii badal to na jaaoge
Lyrics: duniyaa kii tarah rasmon kii tarah vaadon kii tarah kasamon kii tarah mausam kii tarah tum bhii badal to na jaaoge  duniyaa badalatii hai mausam badalate hain lekin mere dil ko badal nahiin paaoge mausam kii tarah threedots  aasamaanon ke aage tumane vaadaa kiyaa hai dil ke badale men maine pyaar tumako diyaa hai dharatii kii ambar kii kasam mujhako hai tere sar kii kasam nazaren badalatii hain sapane badalate hain lekin merii dhadakan ko tum dhadakaaoge mausam kii tarah threedots  merii pahalii tamannaa aakharii pyaar ho tum ruuh men bas gae ho mere diladaar ho tum aise hii tumhen chaahuungaa main tumhen dulhan bhii banaauungaa main sahare badalate hain khushbuu badalatii hai pal pal merii saanson ko tum mahakaaoge mausam kii tarah threedots  tumane dhokhaa diyaa to kuchh bhii kar jaauungii main tum judaa jo hue to dekho mar jaauungii main merii manzil terii raahon men hai merii jannat terii baahon men hai raahii badalate hain raste badalate hain main daud ke aauungaa jo mujhako bulaaoge mausam kii tarah threedots

Title: mere sarhaane jalaao sapane
Lyrics: mere sarahaane jalaao sapane               mujhe zaraa sii to niind aaye mere sarahaane jalaao sapane   threedots  kayaal chalate hain aage aage main unakii chhanv men chal rahii huun na jaane kis mom se banii huun jo qataraa qataraa pighal rahii huun main sahamii rahatii huun niind men bhii kahiin koii kvaab das na jaaye mere sarhaane jalaao sapane   threedots  kabhii bulaataa hai koii saayaa kabhii udaatii hai dhuul koii main ek bhatakii huii sii khushabuu talaash karatii huun phuul koii zaraa kisii shaak par to baithuun zaraa to mujhako havaa jhulaaye mere sarhaane jalaao sapane   threedots

Title: rim jhim rim jhim rum jhum rum jhum
Lyrics: rim jhim rim jhim rum jhum rum jhum  bhiigii bhiigii rut men tum ham ham tum  chalate hain chalate hain  bajataa hai jalatarang par ke chhat pe jab  motiyon jaisa jal barasaae  buundon kii ye jhadii laai hai vo ghadii  jisake liye ham tarase ho ho ho rim jhim rim jhim   badal kii chaadaren odhe hain vaadiyaan  saarii dishaayen soii hain  sapanon ke gaaon men bhiigii sii chhaanv men  do aatmaaen khoii hain   aaii hain dekhane jhiilon ke aaine  baalon ko khole ghataaen  raahen dhuaan dhuaan jaaenge ham kahaan  aao yahiin rah jaaen

Title: saajanaa ve  ni main samajh gaii
Lyrics: saajanaa ve  me soneyaa ve  raanjhanaa ve soneyaa ve maahiyaa ve  ni main samajh gaii ni main samajh gaii  is gal dii ramaj main samajh gaii  naa samajhii thii to ulajh gaii ab ulajhan terii sulajh gaii  ni tuu samajh gaii   ni main samajh gayaa ni main samajh gayaa is gal di ramaj main samajh gayaa raanjhanaa ve soneyaa ve maahiyaa ve maahiyaa ve soneyaa ve raanjhanaa ve   naasamajh mujhe batalaaye naa ye kuchh bhii mujhe samajhaaye naa  rang itanaa chadhaa ki damak gayaa honthon se aankh men thahar gayaa  ban ke phir vo ghanaghor ghataa zulfon men phir vo ulajh gayaa  ainuun pyaar daa chaskaa e saaiin te ishq hii aidii riyaasat e  aite matthe taaj muhabbat daa akkhaan vich nashaa ibaadat daa e  darbaar aide vich kaii raanjhe te miraje boliyaan paunde ne  ai husn de charane husn de charane husn de charane pii jaandaa  o tere husn de charane pii jaandaa  o tere husn de charane pii jaandaa jiijii jaandaa jiijii jaandaa  o saaiin aidaa saaiin mereyaa saaiin aidaa kii jaandaa  hath lajaaye sharmaa jaandaa te todeyaa ai murajhaa jaandaa  to saaii aidaa kii jaandaa  o saaiin mereyaa saaiin mereyaa saaiin mereyaa kii jaandaa  nii tu samajh gaii  nii tu samajh gayaa

Title: chhallaa tuu le jaa nishaaniyaan terii terii meharabaaniyaan
Lyrics: chhallaa tuu le jaa nishaaniyaan terii terii meharabaaniyaan tere bin main naa rahuun mere bin tuu naa rahe o saun nihaaniyaan  chhallaa tuu de jaa threedots  baahon kaa sahaaraa jo mil jaae yaar kaa nazaraanaa dil kaa ham denge tumhen pyaar kaa aur ham javaaniyaan terii terii terii meharabaaniyaan threedots  har pal yaad terii dil tadapaae re tuune kaisaa jaaduu kiyaa nindiyaa na aae re o dilabar jaaniyaan terii terii terii meharabaaniyaan threedots  maathe pe bindiyaa tere naam kii lagaaenge tod ke sitaare terii maang ham sajaaenge yaad rahen kahaaniyaan terii terii terii meharabaaniyaan threedots

Title: aankhon men niinden na dil men karaar  muhabbat bhii kyaa chiiz hotii hai yaar
Lyrics: aankhon men niinden na dil men karaar muhabbat bhii kyaa chiiz hotii hai yaar kabhii bekhudii to kabhii intazaar muhabbat bhii kyaa chiiz hotii hai yaar  dard uthe pyaas jage yaad sataae koii sadaa shaamosahar paas bulaae raat dhale dhuup khile aae terii yaad chaahaton ke aashiyaan men dil kaa baseraa bekaraarii hai jaane kyuun sanam aankhen hain khulii niind men hain ham har ghadii dil pe hai kaisaa ye khumaar aankhon men niinden threedots  main to tujhe ek pal bhii bhuul na paauun jaanevafaa paas tere daud ke aauun tuu jo kahe rasmen sabhii tod duun sanam tere lie donon jahaan chhod duun sanam raat na kate na kate ye din kaise kategii umr tere bin pyaar zindagii men hotaa hai ek baar aankhon men niinden threedots

Title: lamahon kii jaagiir lutaa kar baithe hain
Lyrics: lamahon kii jaagiir lutaa kar baithe hain ham ghar kii dahaliiz pe aa kar baithe hain  likhane ko unawaan kahaan se laayen ab kaagaz se ik naam mitaa kar baithe hain  ho paaye to hans kar do pal baat karo ham paradesii duur se aa kar baithe hain  utthenge jab dil teraa bhar jaayegaa kud ko teraa khel banaa kar baithe hain  jab chaaho gul shmmaa kar denaa shahazaad ham andar kaa diip jalaa kar baithe hain

Lyrics: aajakal lagataa nahiin dil aajakal jabase hai pyaar huaa dil bekaraar huaa man men hai har pal halachal aajakal lagataa nahiin threedots  haal hogaa aisaa jo hotii khabar ye kabhii na milaate tumase nazar ye tere kyaa hue sanam ham na rahe ham aasaar mere gae badal gae badal aajakal aajakal lagataa nahiin threedots  apanaa hii dil ho gayaa hai paraayaa jabase hai tumane apanaa banaayaa sapane gulaabii hain aramaan sharaabii hain mahakaa lage hai har pal har pal aajakal aajakal lagataa nahiin threedots

Title: kaayapochhe  dhiil de dhiil de de re bhaiyaa
Singer: shankar mahadevan dominic bordel kaykay jyotsana hardikar chorus
Lyrics: kaayapochhe o o o ai dhiil de dhiil de de re bhaiyaa us patang ko dhiil de jaise hii mastii men aae are jaise hii mastii men aae us patang ko khiinch de dhiil de dhiil de de re threedots  tez tez tez hai maanjaa apanaa tez hai uungalii kat sakatii hai baabuu hon to patang kyaa chiiz hai dhiil de dhiil de de re threedots  ai kaayapochhe ai lapet terii patang to gaii kaam se kaise katii udii thii shaan se chal sarak ab khisak terii nahiin thii vo to gaii kisii ke sang o gam na kar ghumaa phirakii tuu phir se gharr ghar aasamaan hai teraa pyaare hausalaa buland kar dam nahiin hai aankhon men na maanje kii pakad hai kannii kaise baandhate hain isako kyaa khabar hai ladaa le pench phir se tuu hone de jang nazar sadaa ho uunchii sikhaatii hai patang ho dhiil de dhiil de de re threedots

Title: ham tere bin kahiin rah nahiin paate  haay pyaar kyaa chiiz hai
Lyrics: ham tere bin kahiin rah nahiin paate tum nahiin aate to ham mar jaate haay pyaar kyaa chiiz hai ye jaan nahiin paate ham tere bin kahiin threedots  ude khushbuu kalii mahake ye rut badale bahaar aae muhabbat karane kii jaanam umr ek baar aae tumhen pyaar karane ko jii karataa hai ikaraar karane ko jii karataa hai tum nahiin hote to dil na lagaate dil kii tadap ham kisako bataate haay pyaar kyaa chiiz hai threedots  tum nahiin hote to ham mar jaate  bhulaaye se na bhuulen mere dilabar terii baaten terii yaadon men guzariin kaii subah kaii raaten tujhase duur jo kahiin ham jaaenge har ghadii ham tujhe yaad aaenge terii in baaton se ham ghabaraate taubaa tum hamen kitanaa tadapaate haay pyaar kyaa chiiz hai threedots  kabhii dekhuun jo main darpan cheharaa teraa nazar aaye jab jab letii huun main saansen terii khushbuu bikhar jaaye tere bin ab jiinaa mushkil hai main dil huun teraa tuu meraa dil hai sarii umr to ham pachhataate raaz koii jo tujhase chhupaate haay pyaar kyaa chiiz hai threedots

Title: jahaan bahataa hai gangaa kaa paanii  kasam se sanam pyaar tumase
Film: hum aapke dil mein rehte hain
Lyrics: jahaan bahataa hai gangaa kaa paanii ye raajaa vahiin kaa hai raanii tujhe dhokhaa na degaa teraa rahegaa ye dil hai hindustaanii kasam se kasam se sanam pyaar tumase karate the karate hain ham umr bhar karate rahenge jahaan bahataa hai threedots  chhod ke aise hamen kahaan tuu chalii chuum len aajaa tere honthon kii kalii jaa re jaa dekho yuun naa karo dillagii varanaa ham aaenge naa milane phir kabhii zid hai burii chhedo naa abhii paas to aa yuun naa sataa terii adaaon pe fidaa ham jhuuthe ho kasam se threedots  jaaneman tere binaa kate naa ye pal niind bhii aae nahiin hamen aajakal dilarubaa tujhe nahiin zaraa bhii khabar kyaa karen terii yaaden aaen raat bhar khoe khoe ham bahake kadam bas na chale lag jaa gale tere khyaalon men nashaa hai sambhaalo jii kasam se threedots

Title: kaalii terii chotii hai paraandaa teraa laal nii
Lyrics: kaalii terii chotii hai paraandaa teraa laal nii ruup kii o raanii tuu paraande ko sambhaalanii kisii manachale kaa tujh pe aa gayaa jo dil hogii badii mushkil kaalii terii chotii hai threedots  maine bhii mushkilon se khelanaa hai siikhaa merii bhii tamannaa mujh pe aae dil kisii kaa aashiq kaa paraande naal baandh luungii dil hogii kaise mushkil kaalii terii chotii hai threedots  daavaten detii hai tere gaalon kii ye laalii ban baithaa meraa dil teraa hii savaalii phuul nahiin gaal damakate hain shole dhone dhone hii bade dil ke hain bhole o sholon se lipat ke patange jhuumate hain jal jaayen chaahen shamaa ko chuumate hain kisii siraphire kaa tujh pe aa gayaa jo dil hogii badii mushkil threedots  mar mitane kii tuune baat kaise sochii naa tuu meraa maahii na tuu meraa padosii koii jo malaaii sii kalaaii thaam legaa kyaa hote hain maahii tujhe pataa tab chalegaa jaauungii tabhii jab maahii dolaa laaegaa tere jaisaa haath malataa hii rah jaaegaa sajanaa ke saath main to jaauungii nikal hogii kaise mushkil threedots

Lyrics: ik suuraj nikalaa thaa kuchh taaraa pighalaa thaa ik aandhii aayii thii jab dil se aah nikalii thii dil se re dil to aakhir dil hai na miithii sii mushakil hai na piyaa piyaa jiyaa jiyaa piyaa piyaa dil se re   threedots  do patte patajhad ke pedon se utare the pedon kii shaakhon se utare the phir itane mausam guzare vo patte do bechaare phir ugane kii chaahat men vo saharon se guzare vo pattee dil dil dil the vo dil the dil the dil dil the dil hai to phir dard hogaa dard hai to dil bhii hogaa mausam guzarate rahate hain dil se dil se dil dil se dil se re dil to aakhir dil hai na   threedots  bandhan hai rishton men kaanton kii taaren hain patthar ke daravaaze diivaareb belen phir bhii ugatii hain aur gunche bhii khilate hain aur chalate haib afasaane kiradaar bhii milate hain vo rishte dil dil dil the vo dil the dil the dil dil the gam dil ke bas chulabule hain paanii ke ye bulabule hain bujhate hain banate rahate hain dil se dil se dil dil se dil se re dil to aakhir dil hai na   threedots

Title: nazaren miliin dil dhadakaa merii dhadakan ne kahaa love you raja
Lyrics: nazaren miliin dil dhadakaa merii dhadakan ne kahaa love you raja jaaduu koii chhaane lagaa mujhako mazaa aane lagaa bas men nahiin hai aramaan mujhe siine se lagaa kiss me aajaa nazaren miliin dil dhadakaa threedots  khvaabon men bhii jaaneadaa maine teraa naam liyaa aaii jo tuu mere saamane maine dil ko thaam liyaa tere lie main huun bechain kitanii sanam kyaa hai tujhe pataa ab to hai jiinaa mushkil merii jaan tere binaa love you raja nazaren miliin dil dhadakaa threedots  dam dam daadii dam dam daadii diidaa dam dam daadii diidaa daa  ab raat din dilabar meraa mere kariib hogaa sabase hasiin sabase judaa meraa nasiib hogaa mil ke kiyaa hai hamane ye faisalaa ham kabhii bhii na honge judaa ham jo mile to aayaa hasiin mausam pyaar kaa kiss me aajaa nazaren miliin dil dhadakaa threedots

Title: tum ho merii nigaahon pe chhaaii  bolo kaun ho bolo naa
Lyrics: tum ho merii nigaahon pe chhaaii  tum ho saanson pe jaise samaaii  bolo kaun ho bolo kaun ho bolo naa  tum ho ye chaandanii saath laaii  tum ho kushbuu men jaise nahaaii  bolo kaun ho bolo kaun ho bolo naa  jaane kyuun lagaa mujhe ki jaise hasiin  tum mujhe kisii janam men ho milii kahiin   cheharaa jaise jaanaapahachaanaa  jisane mujhako kiyaa divaanaa  bolo kaun ho bolo naa  aa aa aa aa aa aa 2  yuun lage mujhe ki tum ho koii raaginii  yuun lage ki saanche men dhalii hai chaandanii  ujalaaujalaa ruup jo dekhuun gumasumgumasum hairaan saa huun  bolo kaun ho bolo naa  tum jo apanii ho na paraaii  tum jo yuun paas ho mere aaye  jaise laharonlaharon naav chale  jaise haulehaule phuul khile  jaise kvaab koii aaye aankhon men  jaise giit koii aaye honthon men  tum ho merii nigaahon pe chhaaii tum ho saanson pe jaise samaaii bolo kaun ho bolo kaun ho bolo naa bolo naa bolo naa bolo naa

Title: haadase kyaa kyaa tumhaarii berukii se ho gaye
Lyrics: haadase kyaa kyaa tumhaarii berukii se ho gaye saarii duniyaa ke liye ham ajanabii se ho gaye  kuchh tumhaare gesuon kii barahamii ne kar diye kuchh andhere mere ghar men roshanii se ho gaye  gardishedauraan zamaane kii nazar aankhon kii niind itane dushman ek rasmedostii se ho gaye  bandaa parawar khul gayaa hai aastaanon kaa bharam ham asiiredaamegul apanii kushii se ho gaye  har qadam saagar nazar aane lagiin hain manzilen marahale ai merii kuchh aawaaragii se ho gaye

Title: sainyaa jii se chhip ke huii kyaa terii baat bataa de beliyaa
Lyrics: sainyaa jii se chhip ke huii kyaa terii baat bataa de beliyaa  aankh jhuk jaaegii o mujhako sharm aaegii o aise kaise bataa duun huaa kyaa mere saath huun sun to beliyaa  hai kasam tujhako tuu hamase kuchh naa chhipaa kaise bikharaa ye juude kaa gajaraa bataa bataa naa bataa naa  mere gajare men baithaa thaa bhanvaraa sakhii main jo haathon se usako udaane chalii dor naazuk thii oe oe dor naazuk thii chhuute hii tuut gaii chhuut ke aise gajare se bikharii kalii oe oe sainyaa jii se chhip ke threedots  tere honthon pe daanton ke hain kyon nishaan yuun lage naakhuun tujhako kaise kahaan bataa naa bataa naa  raaste men mujhe ek totaa milaa dekhate hii use meraa man jo khilaa pyaare tote ko main sahalaane gaii chonch honthon pe vo maar ke ud gayaa oe oe sainyaa jii se chhip ke threedots  puuchhatii hain terii kaalii ulajhii laten terii cholii men kaise padiin salavaten bataa naa bataa naa  dard dil men uthaa thaa koii ajanabii bekaraarii huii main tadapane lagii piidaa mujhase sahii na gaii jab sakhii apane haathon se dil ko dabaane lagii oe oe  kuchh samajh men na aae hai ye maajaraa tuune pahanaa hai kyuun ultaa ye ghaagharaa bataa naa bataa naa pakadii gaii ho pakadii gaii pakadii gaii dekho pakadii gaii  aao aao yahaan sab bataauungaa main bhed tumase naa koii chhipaauungaa main mainaa tote se chhipake jo karatii hai jo diyaa baatii ke saath karataa hai dharatii jo aasamaan ko sunaatii hai bhanvaraa kaliyon se jo baat karataa hai hamane to kii vahii baat to sun le beliyaa

Title: tujhe maangaa thaa tujhe paayaa hai
Lyrics: vaah re vaah kyaa baat hai tuu mere saath hai taaron kii raat hai pyaar kii baaraat hai  tujhe maangaa thaa tujhe paayaa hai ab jaake raam pe yakiin aayaa hai raam raam tujhe maangaa thaa threedots  sadiyon se thii apanii duurii din the adhuure raat adhuurii janmon se huun teraa diivaanaa jindaa rahanaa thaa bahaanaa saajan jab tuu aur kahiin thaa is duniyaa men kuchh bhii nahiin thaa jis din apanaa pyaar banaa hai us din se sansaar banaa hai mujhe chhod na denaa raam kasam dil tod na denaa raam kasam haathon kii lakiiron men tujhako paayaa hai ab jaake raam pe threedots  indradhanush angadaaii hai terii chaand nahiin parachhaaiin hai terii jab tak chamakenge do taare duniyaa legii naam hamaare pyaar kii dhun pe gaataa rahuungaa

Title: dil men hai tuu dhadakan men tuu
Lyrics: dil men hai tuu dhadakan men tuu apanaa tujhe banaa ke le jaauungaa udaa ke o jaanaa huun huun  sapanon men tuu hii tuu hai terii hii aarazuu hai o jaanaa huun huun  dil men hai tuu dhadakan men tuu haan mil ke bhii kyuun sanam milane kii aas hai pahale aisaa na thaa kaisaa ahasaas hai ye aalam nayaa hai chhaaii hai bekhudii main bhii huun bekhabar sunate hain pyaar men hotaa hai ye asar ye kaisaa nashaa hai madahosh ho gaii huun o jaanaa huun huun threedots  pahalii nazar men hii jaaduu ye chal gayaa diivaane dil kaa to mausam badal gayaa dil de de nazaraanaa haay chaahat bharii terii baahon men jhuul ke jhuume hai zindagii duniyaa ko bhuul ke dil le le nazaraanaa main pyaar kar rahaa huun kyaa zurm kar rahaa huun o jaanaa huun huun threedots

Title: ho ho aahaa  dil kii lagii kahii jaae naa sajanaa re
Lyrics: ho ho aahaa 2  dil kii lagii kahii jaae naa sajanaa re sajanaa re sajanaa diivaanii main diivaanaa tuu diivaanaa mausam suhaanaa ho ho ho diivaanii main diivaanaa tuu diivaanaa mausam suhaanaa  2 ho ho ho diivaanii main threedots   pyaar tujhe karatii huun kitanaa ye kaise samajhaauun paas mere tuu aa jaa tere kvaabon men bas jaauun  2 aur koii sun paae na sajanaa re sajanaa re sajanaa diivaanii main diivaanaa threedots   tan se lapetuun priit main terii tuu meraa aanchal hai in aankhon men bhar luun tujhako pyaar kaa ye kaajal hai  2 kaalii ghataa ab chhaae na sajanaa re sajanaa re sajanaa  diivaanii main diivaanaa threedots

Title: terii yaad aanaa dil se jaanaa aisaa lagataa hai kyaa yahii pyaar hai
Lyrics: terii yaad aanaa dil se jaanaa aisaa lagataa hai kyaa yahii pyaar hai  kabhii kabhii rotaa kabhii muskuraataa aisaa lagataa hai kyaa yahii pyaar hai  thandii havaaon kaa jhonkaa jo aae lagataa hai duur se tuu mujhako bulaae in sard raaton kii tanahaaiiyon men terii saans meraa tan gudagudaae karavaten badalanaa niind na aanaa aisaa lagataa hai kyaa yahii pyaar hai threedots  kabhii dil tadapaataa kabhii dil dhadakaataa nas nas bijalii sii laharaaen mere thaharaa huaa hai jaise zamaanaa aisaa lagataa hai kyaa yahii pyaar hai threedots  benuur lagatii hai saarii kudaaii sahii nahiin jaatii terii judaaii kahake diivaanaa hansataa zamaanaa hansatii hai mujhase merii parachhaaii tab gunagunaaen teraa hii taraanaa aisaa lagataa hai kyaa yahii pyaar hai threedots

Title: mere sanam mujhako terii kasam
Lyrics: mere sanam mujhako terii kasam tujhase bichhad kar mar jaaenge ham ke marane se pahale jii len zaraa ham mere sanam mujhako threedots  aisii lagii hai ye dil kii lagii saavan kaii barase ye naa bujhii is aag men ek din jal jaaenge ham ke marane se pahale threedots  idhar aa tujhe main gale se lagaa luun tujhe apanii aankhon kaa kaajal banaa luun hazaaron hai baaten magar vaqt hai kam ke marane se pahale threedots  ye pyaasii muhabbat ye pyaasii javaanii adhuurii adhuurii ye dil kii kahaanii jhukii huii hai raat ye rukii huii hai baat ye ye chaandanii raat aage chale ho kuchh pyaar kii baat aage chale  kab kaun jaane kahaan chalaa jaae mausam yahaan se vahaan chalaa jaae aisaa na ho ye samaa chalaa jaae jhukii huii hai aankh bhii rukii huii hai saans bhii kuchh to mulaakaat aage chale ho kuchh pyaar kii baat threedots  bole ye nazar ye jubaan chalii jaae ye dil gayaa ab ye jaan chalii jaae

Title: gambler gambler tuu hai gambler
Lyrics: aavaaraa nahiin saudaagar nahiin diivaanaa are nahiin anaadii khilaadii jaaduugar baaziigar nahiin nahiin naa tuu khilaadii na tuu baaziigar naa tuu anaadii na tuu jaaduugar jaane tujhe dekh kar kyon lagataa hai dar  dil ko churaa ke apanaa banaa ke dhokhaa tuu degaa hai mujhe khabar  na main khilaadii na main baaziigar na main anaadii na main jaaduugar jaaneman o jaanejaan kuchh bharosaa kar  dil ko churaa ke apanaa banaa ke dhokhaa na duungaa o bekhabar  baaton hii baaton men tum par kar luun main kaise bharosaa jisane kiyaa hai bharosaa hotaa hai usako hii dhokhaa main aisaa insaan nahiin huun chaahe mujhe aazamaan le aashiq vahii jo mohabbat men ho jaan apanii lutaa de nazaron men mere dil kii jubaan hai dekhuun to pahachaan kar  phir to mubaarak ho tumako ab ye mulaakaat merii le kar karavaten guzaregii na raat merii yaadon ko dil lagaakar karanaa padegaa guzaaraa yaadon men maanegaa kaise dil terii chaahat kaa maaraa aankhon ke raste tasviir merii le jaanaa tum khiinchakar

Title: nahiin saamane ye alag baat hai
Lyrics: dekho chhodake kis raste vo jaate hain saare raste vaapas mere dil ko aate hain           nahiin saamane ye alag baat hai mere paas hai tuu mere paas hai mere saath hai  teraa naam main ne liyaa hai yahaan mujhe yaad tuu ne kiyaa hai vahaan bade zor kii aaj barasaat hai  2 mere paas hai threedots  bichhadake bhii mujhase judaa to nahiin kafaa hai magar bewafaa to nahiin mere haath men hii teraa haath hai  2 mere paas hai threedots

Title: sanam tum ham pe marate ho muhabbat tum bhii
Lyrics: sharamiilii aankhon ne niichii nigaahon ne chupake se ye kah diyaa sanam tum ham pe marate ho muhabbat tum bhii karate ho magar poshiidaa poshiidaa sanam tum ham pe threedots  ye jo muhabbat hai jaise qayaamat hai dekhaa to kyaa ho gayaa ke dekhen khvaab hain jabase hamaarii aankhen hain tabase badii khvaabiidaa khvaabiidaa sanam tum ham pe threedots  sunaa hai tum to ho diivaane suno to mere dil ke taraane sunaa ke phir lage doharaane sune hain tumane kab ye fasaane tumako sunaanii hai kyaa vo kahaanii hai hamako hai isakaa pataa inhiin baaton ne chhiinaa dil hasiin jalave adaa qaatil nazar dusbiidaa dusbiidaa sanam tum ham pe threedots  kabhii tum hamase duur na jaanaa kabhii tum itane paas na aanaa kabhii tum dil ko naa thukaraanaa kabhii tum dil ko bhii samajhaanaa jaano nahiin jaano maano nahiin maano ham to karenge vafaa chalo ab yuun bhii naa ruutho ki hamane chhedaa thaa tumako na ho ranjiidaa ranjiidaa sanam tum ham pe threedots

Title: phir chalane vaale  hamaraahii jab ho mastaanaa
Lyrics: phir chalane vaale rukate hain kahaan  hamaraahii jab ho mastaanaa mauj men ho dil diivaanaa  phir chalane vaale rukate hain kahaan  ye khumaar ye nashaa javaan bekudii  ab na koii nagar na koii galii  din vahaan raat yahaan  dagamag chalanaa shaharon men baazaaron men  mahakemahake phiranaa gulazaaron men  ham dilavaale chanchal aise taubaa  halachal sii pad jaaye diladaaron men  is mastii men sab chalataa hai  ab koii kyaa soch rahaa hai  ham matavaale kyaa jaanen   chadhatii javaanii teriimerii  mil jaane men kaahe kii hai derii  josh men aake chal nikale hain ham yaaraa  hone de dhadakan kii heraapherii  pyaar kii rasmen phir sochenge  thiik hai kyaa aur galatii kyaa hai  ham matavaale kyaa jaanen

Title: jhumake bumake latake jhatake  main kolhaapur se aaii huun
Lyrics: jhumake bumake latake jhatake tirachhii mirachhii aaii huun main kolhaapur se aaii huun  patalii kamar hai tirachhii nazar hai chadhatii umr kii javaanii gore badan men menhadii mahake man men khushbuu hai raat kii raanii jab bolii to sab kii tabiyat machalatii hai dil vaalon kaa dil dolaa hai jab bhii dupattaa giraaii huun main kolhaapur se threedots  miithii kataarii tiikhii supaarii nakhare mere niraale hain saare ke saare aashiq kvaare mujh pe nigaahen daale hain main daratii huun koii diivaanaa na ban jaae chup rahatii huun koii fasaanaa na ban jaae koii maane yaa na maane koii jaane yaa na jaane chunarii men kyaa kyaa chhipaaii huun main kolhaapur se threedots

Title: deenan dukh haran dev
Lyrics: uv ravindra and sushil sharma deenan dukh haran dev santan hitakaarii  ajaamiil giidh byaadh inamen kah kaun saadh panchhii ko pada padhaat ganikaasii taarii 1  dhruv ke sar chhatra det prahlaad ko ubaar let bhakt het baandhyo set lankapurii jaarii 2  tandul det riijh jaat saag paat son aghaat ginat nahin juuthe phal khaate miithe khaarii 3  itane hari aaye gaye basanan aaruudh bhaye suuradaas dvaare khado aandharo bhikaarii 4 newpage  some mythological stories to help understand the bhajan   i ajaamila sanskrit name is a character from the srimad bhagavatam  the story as i remember it in short is that ajamila is a braahman who gets involved with a woman of loose morals gives up his family and begins living with this woman and in the process ends up leading a life full of sin  as ajamila is lying on his death bed he sees the horrifying spectre of a yamadoota approaching him in order to take away his life breath and this causes him to remember and scream out the name of the person dearest to him in his life his young son  naaraayana naaraayana thats it  a vishnudoota roaming nearby overhears this thinks this poor man is invoking vishnus name and drives away the yamadoota so ajamila gets a new lease of life eventually ajamila regrets his bad deeds renounces the world and accumulating punya due to his penitence and penance that he ends up going to heaven  the moral of the story supposedly is that if you invoke the name of the lord even by proxy as ajamila did your sins are washed away im not sure i agree about this moral part but okay whatever  ii giidh refers to jataayu while he was born in the lowly lifeform of a vulture he is said to have been blessed by rama at the time of his death rama himself performed the last rites for jataayu well known story from ramayana  iii byaadh birdhunter baheliyaa in hindi a very sinful profession according to hindu sacredbooks here it refers to the byaadh named ratnaakar who had a change of heart after sage narada enlightened him and became sage valmiki the legendary author of the ramayana according to some other commentaries the byaadh might also refer to the hunter who shot krishna in the heel thus  causing his departure from the mortal world ie death this byaadh was blessed by krishna just before he left for his heavenly abode  iv ganikaa  courtesanharlot when parashuraam vaishya died of asthma his wife left him choosing to become a  courtesanprostitute instead  but she taught her pet parrot to say raama and in teaching this word to the bird  ended up reciting it umpteen times thanks to having  repeatedly uttered raamanaam with a pure heart ie with no personal gain in mind except for teaching the bird she was blessed and received mukti after her death  v sudaamaa  wellknown story of krishnas poor classmate krishna ate the grains of rice sudama brought him as a gift and blessed him with health wealth and eternal happiness in return  vi vidura and his wife  again a wellknown story from the mahabharata and the srimadbhagavatam viduras wife  offered plain saagpaat banana peels according to another version to krishna which he relished and of course blessed the host and hostess in return  vii shabarii  old tribeswoman from the ramayana who offered fruits that she had tasted herself and thus  turned juuthe to rama  her unconventional rural  and simpleminded yet purehearted Lyrics: baahon men le luun zulfon se kheluun betaab mohabbat kahatii hai aajaa aajaa paagal diivaanaa aavaaraa kis naam se tujhako pukaaruun main palakon ke saae men rakhuun yaa dil men tujhako utaaruun main  jo dil ko tere bhaa jaae us naam se mujhako pukaar le tuu aankhon kii sunaharii galiyon se mujhe apane dil men utaar le tuu  merii tamannaa meraa yaar hai merii mohabbat meraa pyaar hai kaise bataauun tujhako bhalaa main mujhako teraa intazaar hai honthon pe mere terii baat hai apanaa to janamon kaa saath hai maine chhodaa saaraa zamaanaa haathon men teraa haath hai  rangiilaa aashiq mastaanaa kis naam se tujhako pukaaruun main palakon ke saae men threedots  jannat se aaii koii huur hai ishq men mere tuu to chuur hai bhuule tujhe naa ik pal meraa dil is men meraa kyaa kasuur hai duniyaa mere pairon kii dhuul hai mere juude men teraa phuul hai tere lie jo mujhako milaa vo dard bhii mujhako kabuul hai

Lyrics: kadd dittii jaan oe hoe oe main kurabaan oe hoe kadd dittii jaan oe main kurabaan jhumakaa kangan paayal na vajaa kudiye oe thumakaa thumakaa thumakaa na lagaa kudiye  oe jhilamil kurataa gaal gulaabii utton nain sharaabii haay haay tak tak munde marade vekh kudii panjaabii oe lambii chotii das gaii naagan kar gaii saarii kharaabii kamalaa ho gayaa siidhaa saadaa dekh ke chaal sharaabii kadd dittii jaan threedots  kajaraa gajaraa laalii naa sajaa kudiye oe thumakaa threedots  honth hain khuunii laal uupar se paan hai tuune chabaayaa haay haay teraa jalavaa kis kis kaa murder kar aayaa oe daanton men phulakaarii dupattaa jab jab tuune dabaayaa main ban jaandaa teraa aanchal khyaal ye man men aayaa kadd dittii jaan threedots  oe thumakaa threedots  apane gesuu kaa ik phiitaa mainuu banaa le raanii ulajh ulajh ke mar jaauungaa kasam hai terii diivaanii jaan merii kadake tuu kitthe jaandii hai marajaanii bal bal khaatii dekh kamariyaa luut gaii mastaanii kadd dittii jaan threedots  oe thumakaa threedots

Lyrics: jhuum jhuum kahataa hai meraa jiyaa baandh mere pairon men paayal piyaa chhed tuu pyaar kii saragam saragam naachuungii main chham chham chham chham naachuungii main chham threedots  bechain tuune jo mujhako kiyaa maine tujhe apanaa dil de diyaa chheduungaa main pyaar kii saragam saragam naachegii tuu chham chham chham chham naachuungii main chham threedots  pinjaraa khulaa panchhii ude niil gagan ke tale hon naa kabhii ab ham judaa aajaa lagaa luun gale do labon pe ek taraanaa gunagunaae dil diivaanaa aayaa pyaar kaa mausam mausam naachuungii main chham threedots  aankhon men hai mukhadaa teraa saanson men saragam terii jab naam luun teraa saajan khanake ye chuudii merii khushiyon se man muskaraae jis galii men gam na aae chalo chalen ham vahaan haradam haradam naachuungii main chham threedots  sajanaa saath nibhaanaa sajanii dil men basaanaa  saathii tere duhkh sabhii bhagavaan de de mujhe hansate hue har ghadii dekhuun main tujhe janamon kaa hai saath apanaa hogii priit naa ab kam ab kam naachuungii main chham threedots

Title: jaaduu saa chhaane lagaa  ye dil kyaa kare
Lyrics: chal mitaraa hun otthe chaliye jitthe hor na koii hove saanuun vekh ke koii hanse naa saanuun sonuu vekh ke koii rove sej sajaaii phuulon kii aur ham kaanton pe soe ishq daa dariyaa maajhii naav musaafir sab duboe is dariyaa ko jo paar kare bas vo diivaanaa pyaar kare mainuun lagan lagii mere sajan lagii mainuun lagan lagii  panaghat se aisaa dhuaan uthaa paanii men jaise agan lagii mainuun lagan lagii threedots  ho meraa dil tere dil se mil na sakaa merii jaan terii jaan se milane lagii mainuun lagan lagii threedots  apane sar pe ilzaam liyaa phir maine teraa naam liyaa terii yaadon ke daaman ko apanii yaadon se thaam liyaa naa rastaa naa koii manzil main sang pavan ke chalane lagii mainuun lagan lagii threedots  jo aag kaa dariyaa paar kare bas vo diivaanaa pyaar kare haan haan kho jaae khud is raste men vo yaar talaasheyaar kare ho meraa haath pakad le saajan main majhadhaar men duub ke marane lagii mainuun lagan lagii threedots  man meraa mujhase ruuth gayaa jo sapanaa dekhaa tuut gayaa main birahan kyaa singaar karuun meraa darpan hii tuut gayaa naa chutakii bhar sinduur milaa jab apanii maang main bharane lagii mainuun lagan lagii threedots

Title: jo bhii dukh yaad na thaa yaad aayaa
Lyrics: jo bhii dukh yaad na thaa yaad aayaa aaj kyaa jaaniye kyaa yaad aayaa  yaad aayaa thaa bichhadanaa teraa phir nahiin yaad ke kyaa yaad aayaa  haath uthaaye the ke dil baith gayaa jaane kyaa waqteduaa yaad aayaa  jis tarah dhundh men lipate hue phuul ek ik naqsh teraa yaad aayaa  ye muhabbat bhii hai kyaa rog faraaz jisako bhuule wo sadaa yaad aayaa

Title: jabase bulabul tuune do tinake liye
Lyrics: jabase bulabul tuune do tinake liye tuutatii hain bijaliyaan inake liye  kaun wiiraane men dekhegaa bahaar phuul jangal men khile kinake liye  saarii duniyaa ke hain wo mere siwaa mainne duniyaa chhod dii jinake liye  wasl kaa din aur itanaa muktasar din gine jaate the is din ke liye  baagabaan kaliyaan hon halke rang sii ye ummiden ek kamasin ke liye

Title: halkaa halkaa dard hai dard ye bedard hai  merii tuu tuu hii tuu
Lyrics: halkaa halkaa dard hai dard ye bedard hai chal gayaa hai pyaar kaa jaaduu haan merii tuu tuu hii tuu  halkaa halkaa dard hai dard ye bedard hai dhadakanon pe chhaa gayaa hai tuu hii tuu meraa tuu tuu hii tuu tuu hii tuu  ghanere the jitane andheron ke saae muhabbat ke utane diye jagamagaae kabhii tum the tanhaa ye dil se bhulaa do betaab huun main apanaa banaa lo halkaa halkaa dard hai threedots  vafaaon ne terii sambhaalaa hai mujhako main apanii aankhon men basaa luungaa tujhako tumhen chuumatii hain ye merii nigaahen mujhe mil gaii hain chaahat kii raahen halkaa halkaa dard hai threedots

Title: saans aatii hai  zindaa rahane ke lie  ik mulaakaat zaruurii hai sanam
Lyrics: saans aatii hai saans jaatii hai sirf mujhako hai intazaar teraa aansuon kii ghataaen pii pii ke ab to kahataa hai yahii pyaar meraa zindaa rahane ke lie terii kasam ik mulaakaat zaruurii hai sanam  terii chaahaton ne ye kyaa gam diyaa tere ishq ne yuun diivaanaa kiyaa zamaane se mujhako begaanaa kiyaa diivaane tere pyaar men badaa hii buraa haal hai khadii huun terii raah men na hosh hai na khyaal hai ik mulaakaat zaruurii hai sanam zindaa rahane ke lie threedots  mere saath men ro rahaa aasamaan meraa pyaar khoyaa hai jaane kahaan use dhuundhatii main yahaan se vahaan milan kii mujhe aas hai nikalatii nahiin jaan hai main kitanii majabuur huun ye kaisaa imtahaan hai ik mulaakaat zaruurii hai sanam zindaa rahane ke lie threedots  aaj mulaakaat zaruurii hai sanam  merii aankhon men jale tere khvaabon ke diye kitanii bechain huun main yaar se milane ke lie mere bichhade dilabar tuu jo ik baar mile chain aa jaae mujhe jo teraa diidaar mile masiihaa mere duaa de mujhe karuun ab main kyaa bataa de mujhe koii raastaa dikhaa de mujhe mere yaar se milaa de mujhe mere dard kii davaa de mujhe aa kahiin naa ab sukuun hai kahiin naa ab karaar hai milegaa mera saathiyaa mujhe to aitabaar hai ik mulaakaat zaruurii hai sanam  saans aatii hai threedots zindaa rahane ke lie threedots

Title: ye to sach hai ke bhagavaan hai
Film: hum saath saath hain we stand united
Singer: hariharan ghanshyam vasvani pratima rao santosh tiwari
Lyrics: ye to sach hai ke bhagavaan hai hai magar phir bhii anjaan hai dharatii pe ruup maan baap kaa us vidhaataa kii pahachaan hai ye to sach hai ke threedots  janmadaataa hain jo naam jinase milaa thaamakar jinakii ungalii hai bachapan chalaa o kaandhe par baithake jinake dekhaa jahaan gyaan jinase milaa kyaa buraa kyaa bhalaa itane upakaar hain kyaa kahen ye bataanaa na aasaan hai dharatii pe ruup threedots  janm detii hai jo maan jise jag kahe apanii santaan men praan jisake rahen o loriyaan honthon par sapane bunatii nazar niind jo vaar de hans ke har dukh sahe mamataa ke ruup men hai prabhuu aapase paayaa varadaan hai dharatii pe ruup threedots  aapake khvaab ham aaj hokar javaan us param shakti se karate hain praarthanaa o inakii chhaayaa rahe rahatii duniyaa talak ek pal rah saken ham na jinake binaa aap donon salaamat rahen sabake dil men ye aramaan hai dharatii pe ruup threedots

Title: kar lo meraa aitabaar  sone chaandii se mahangaa
Lyrics: kar lo kar lo meraa aitabaar yaaron sone chaandii se mahangaa hai pyaar yaaron dardedil ko ye degaa karaar yaaron sone chaandii se threedots  isake jaisaa yahaan bol koii nahiin isakaa hotaa yahaan mol koii nahiin isamen khushiyaan chhupii beshumaar yaaron sone chaandii se threedots  aandhiyaan tham gaiin kaaravaan bhii ruke takht aur taaj bhii isake aage jhuke karake dekho ise ek baar yaaron sone chaandii se threedots

Title: chham chakaa chham chakaa gaae sapanaa
Lyrics: chham chakaa chham chakaa gaae sapanaa pyaar kii saragam pe sajaa nagamaa mere is rang men tum bhii rang jaaoge main bhii gaauungii tum bhii gaaoge lag jaane do ye giit apanaa  mere in labon pe bas naam ho teraa tumako chaahanaa hii bas kaam ho meraa tuune kah diyaa kyaa dil jhuum jhuum uthaa khil gaii huii main jo ye pyaar hai teraa hansataa khilataa cheharaa teraa ye dekhe jaba jab tujhako dekhen mere nayan aajaa pyaar men yuun kho jaaenge ham do se sanam ek ho jaaenge mujhako jii bhar ke yaar pyaar karanaa chham chakaa chham threedots

Title: sholaa jaise bhadake re  kamariyaa lachake re
Lyrics: sholaa jaise bhadake re dil meraa dhadake re kamariyaa lachake re baabuu zaraa bach ke re sholaa jaise bhadake threedots  jale re moraa jiyaa chhuunaa naa mohe piyaa he aaii kahaan se o dilarubaa jaaduu saa teraa sab pe chalaa are diivaanon ko naa aise jalaa yuun naa dilon par chhuriyaan chalaa kamariyaa lachake re threedots  aaii re aaii re aaii sapanon kii raaanii hai aaii aaii re aaii ho ho he he ik naa ik din mil jaaegii hamako bhii sapanon kii raanii aaii re aaii re aaii  saanson men hain chingaariyaan siine men koii chubhan hai nas nas men jaagii agan hai rok naa tuu is aag ko jalane de jo bhii agan hai dekh zamaanaa magan hai mere kaleje men koii tiir hai gadaa chadhaa re chadhaa re chadhaa ye kaisaa zahar hai chadhaa tujhako nahiin kuchh bhii hosh hai terii umar kaa ye dosh hai diivaanon ko naa aise threedots  saaraa jahaan piichhe padaa dushman banii ye javaanii mushkil men hai zindagaanii dar hai tujhe kis baat kaa ham tere saathii hain jaanii phir kaahe soche diivaanii kahiin diivaanaa to kahiin qaatil hai khadaa jaanaa meraa jaanaa oho mushkil hai badaa jaaegii bach ke ab tuu kahaan tuu hai jahaan ab ham hain vahaan diivaanon ko naa aise threedots

Title: aa kahiin duur chale jaaen ham
Lyrics: aa kahiin duur chale jaaen ham duur itanaa ki hamen chhuu na sake koii gam aa kahiin duur threedots  phuulon aur kaliyon se mahake hue ik jangal men ik hasiin jhiil ke saahil pe hamaaraa ghar ho os men bhiigii huii ghaas pe ham chalate hon rang aur nuur men duubaa huaa har manzar ho main tujhe pyaar karuun mere sanam tuu mujhe pyaar kare mere sanam aa kahiin duur threedots  aa aa shaam kaa rang ho gaharaa to sitaare jaage raat jo aae to resham se andhere laae chaand jab jhiil ke paanii men nahaane utare merii baahon men tujhe dekh ke sharamaa jaae main tujhe pyaar karuun mere sanam tuu mujhe pyaar kare mere sanam aa kahiin duur threedots

Title: raajaa ko raanii se pyaar ho gayaa
Lyrics: raajaa ko raanii se pyaar ho gayaa pahalii nazar men pahalaa pyaar ho gayaa dil jigar donon ghaayal hue tiirenazar dil ke paar ho gayaa raajaa ko raanii se threedots  ho raahon se raahen baahon se baahen milake bhii milatii nahiin ho hotaa hai aksar aramaan kii kaliyaan khil ke bhii khilatii nahiin o phir bhii na jaane kyuun nahiin maane diivaanaa dil bekaraar ho gayaa raajaa ko raanii se threedots  raanii ko dekho nazaren miliin to aankhen churaane lagii ho karatii bhii kyaa vo sar ko jhukaa ke kanganaa ghumaane lagii ho raajaa ne aisaa jaaduu chalaayaa na karate karate ikaraar ho gayaa raajaa ko raanii se threedots

Title: kaantaa lage nikal jaae magar na nikale nazar kaa tiir
Lyrics: kaantaa lage nikal jaae magar na nikale nazar kaa tiir bach jaae yaa mar jaae ye aashiq kii taqadiir kaantaa lage nikal jaae threedots  ye duniyaa jaane na jaane ham ek duuje ke diivaane dil men terii yaad sanam aankhon men terii tasviir kaantaa lage nikal jaae threedots  phuul kahiin kahiin ye khilataa hai pyaar kahaan sabako milataa hai kisii kisii ke haath men hotii hai ye prem lakiir kaantaa lage nikal jaae threedots  ye duniyaa hai bhuul bhulaiyaa thaam le saiyaan merii baiiyaan ham donon phir bichhad na jaaen main raanjhaa tuu hiir kaantaa lage nikal jaae threedots

Title: do terii ankhiyaa do merii  log isii ko kahate hain ishq mohabbat pyaar
Lyrics: do terii ankhiyaa do merii ankhiyaan ankhiyaan ho gaiin chaar log isii ko kahate hain ishq mohabbat pyaar ik teraa dil ik meraa dil do dil ik jhankaar log isii ko kahate hain threedots  hai teraa naam sipaiiyaa naam to main jaanuun teraa ek chor hai  vo jisake kaaran chor sipaiiyaa ban gayaa vo tuu hai yaa koii aur hai ab kuchh hotaa nahiin hotaa ab isase intazaar log isii ko kahate hain threedots  aur tujhe main kyaa duun aa terii in zulfon men ye dil kaa phuul lagaa duun mere gale men bas rahane de in baahon kaa haar log isii ko kahate hain threedots  laaj mujhe laakh manaa karatii hai ye joban letaa hai angadaaiiyaan he aatii hai jab jab terii yaad to bajatii hain bajatii hain duur kahiin shahanaaiiyaan raat ho din ab tadape dil aataa nahiin karaar log isii ko kahate hain threedots

Title: meraa mahabuub aaegaa khaaq men tujhe milaaegaa
Lyrics: ye lo ye lo ai le le aajaa aa aa  meraa mahabuub aaegaa khaaq men tujhe milaaegaa muhabbat karane vaalon ko judaa tuu kar na paaegaa  muhabbat aisii aandhii hai jo roke se nahiin rukatii kisii ke saamane aae kabhii ulfat nahiin jhukatii terii auqaat kyaa hai jo mujhe tuu aajamaaegaa meraa mahabuub aaegaa threedots  zamiin kyaa aasamaan tak bhii merii aavaaz aaegii koii diivaar duniyaa kii use na rok paaegii vo aa ke terii hastii mitaaegaa terii bastii mitaaegaa  meraa mahabuub aaegaa threedots

Title: kho die jitane lamhe maine terii nigaah men
Lyrics: kho die jitane lamhe maine terii nigaah men utane janam mere sanam guzare terii chaah men kho die jitane lamhe threedots  terii khushii teraa hii gam terii vafaa teraa saath ho sapane tere yaad merii dil men sanam din raat hon kho gae jitane bhii pal ye terii panaahon men utane janam mere sanam threedots  jaanechaman bandhane lage ham nazaron kii dor men dil kii sazaa sunane lage ham saanson ke shor men chal die jitane kadam maine sanam terii raahon men utane janam mere sanam threedots

Title: kuchh der pahale kuchh bhii na thaa  ye pyaar na jaane kab ho gayaa
Lyrics: kuchh der pahale kuchh bhii na thaa kuchh der men hii ye gazab ho gayaa kuchh der pahale kuchh bhii threedots  ye pyaar ye pyaar na jaane kab ho gayaa kab ho gayaa  ham donon men thii badii dushmanii ye dushmanii ban gaii dostii ye dostii ban ban gaii dillagii sab kuchh abhii aaj ho gayaa aaj ho gayaa kuchh der pahale kuchh bhii threedots  is dil ne dhokhaa diyaa hai mujhe gussaa bahut aa rahaa hai mujhe mujhako zaraa sii bhii khabar na huii tab maine jaanaa ye jab ho gayaa jab ho gayaa kuchh der pahale kuchh bhii threedots

Lyrics: tujhase hamaaraa vaadaa hai hamadam jiyenge marenge tumhaare lie ham badalegii duniyaa badalegaa aalam jiyenge marenge threedots  pal men lage jo sadiyon puraanaa ye kaisaa hai naataa kisii ne na jaanaa naye phuul kaise khilaataa hai mausam mohabbat ne hamako milaayaa hai jaanam tujhase hamaaraa vaadaa threedots  palaken jhukiin aur nazaren hain soii naa muddat se mujhase milaa aur koii khushiyaan milen yaa hamako milen gam pyaar hamaaraa naa hogaa kabhii kam tujhase hamaaraa vaadaa threedots

Title: ab aur kyaa kisii se maraasim badhaayen ham
Lyrics: ab aur kyaa kisii se maraasim badhaayen ham ye bhii bahut hai tujhako agar bhuul jaayen ham  is zindagii men itanii faraagat kise nasiib itanaa na yaad aa ke tujhe bhuul jaayen ham  tuu itanii dilazadaa to na thii ai shabefiraaq aa tere raaste men sitaare lutaayen ham  wo log ab kahaan hain jo kahate the kal faraaz ai ai kudaa na karanaa tujhe bhii rulaayen ham

Lyrics: hoke man aaj magan naache re chhanan chhanan aajaa piyaa ab to aajaa sun ke terii paayal kii chham chham dekh main aa gayaa hoke man aaj magan threedots  raaton ko niind aatii nahiin mujhako bolo sajan aa gaii tujhape javaanii pyaar hotaa hai kyaa zaraa mujhako bataa itanii bholii na ban mujhe yuun naa banaa gorii han tohe haan sab pataa re hoke man aaj magan threedots  jo main gayaa ruuth kar tujh se to kyaa karegii bataa yaad tujhako karuungii gar lautakar phir naa aayaa to kyaa haal hogaa teraa main to jii na sakuungii jaan maine to kii tere sang dillagii terii ye dillagii jaan legii merii chhod gussaa muskaraa re hoke man aaj magan threedots  terii merii jodii lagatii hai kaisii bataao piyaa jaise chandaa chakorii ek duuje ke ang lagakar chalen sang kaise bataa ho jyon patang aur dorii tuu hai meraa sanam tuu hai meraa kudaa miit main tuu sadaa kaise honge judaa pyaar haan main huun haan tuu vafaa re hoke man aaj magan threedots

Lyrics: sonuu  aaiinaa bataa kaise unakaa dil churaanaa hai aaj phir akele men unase milane jaanaa hai vinod  aaiinaa bataa kaise unakaa dil churaanaa hai aaj phir akele men unase milane jaanaa hai sonuu  muhabbat hai muhabbat hai muhabbat hai muhabbat hai aaiinaa bataa kaise unakaa dil churaanaa hai aaj phir akele men unase milane jaanaa hai vinod  muhabbat hai muhabbat hai muhabbat hai muhabbat hai  vinod  vo hansatii rahatii hai kuchh bolatii nahiin raaz muhabbat kaa vo kabhii kholatii nahiin sonuu  kyaa hai usake dil men main jaanataa nahiin meraa dil paagal hai ab maanataa nahiin vinod  yaar duaa kar unase izahaar ho jaae donon kii chaahat kaa iqaraar ho jaae iqaraar ho jaae sonuu  beqaraarii kahanii hai dard bhii bataanaa hai aaj phir akele men unase milane jaanaa hai vinod  muhabbat hai muhabbat hai muhabbat hai muhabbat hai  sonuu  vo baagon men meraa intazaar karegii sharamaake dekhegii beqaraar karegii vinod  usakii har baaton kaa aitabaar karuungaa main baanhon men leke use pyaar karuungaa sonuu  dar lagataa hai vaadaa kahiin bhuul naa jaae main chalaa jaauun phir vo der se aae vo der se aae vinod  kyaa hasiin mausam hai kyaa samaan suhaanaa hai aaj phir akele men unase milane jaanaa hai sonuu  muhabbat hai muhabbat hai muhabbat hai muhabbat hai

Title: ai dil laayaa hai bahaar apanon kaa pyaar kyaa kahanaa
Lyrics: o o o ai dil laayaa hai bahaar apanon kaa pyaar kyaa kahanaa mile ham chhalak uthaa khushii kaa khumaar kyaa kahanaa khile khile cheharon se aaj ghar hai meraa gulegulazaar kyaa kahanaa khile khile cheharon se threedots  ham tum yuun hii milate rahen mahafil yuun hii sajatii rahe bas pyaar kii yahii ek dhun har subahoshaam bajatii rahe gale men mahakataa rahe pyaar bharii baahon kaa haar kyaa kahanaa khile khile cheharon se threedots dil kaa koii tukadaa kabhii dil se judaa hotaa nahiin apanaa koii jaisaa bhii ho apanaa hai vo duujaa nahiin yahii vo milan hai jo sachamuch hai dil kaa karaar kyaa kahanaa khile khile cheharon se threedots  kuchh apane hii tak yuun nahiin ye hai savaal sabake lie jiinaa hai to jag men jiyo banake misaal sabake lie dekho kaisaa mahak rahaa pyaar bharii baahon kaa haar kyaa kahanaa khile khile cheharon se threedots  jo ho gayaa so ho gayaa logon se tuu daranaa nahiin saathii tere hain aur bhii duniyaa men tuu tanahaa nahiin saamanaa karenge milake chaahen das hon chaahen das hazaar kyaa kahanaa khile khile cheharon se aaj jag hai meraa meraa gulegulazaar kyaa kahanaa ho o ho o ai dil laayaa hai bahaar threedots

Title: chalii aaiyo raadhe raanii jamanaa ke tiir
Lyrics: chalii aaiyo raadhe raanii jamunaa ke tiir likhenge prem kahaanii jamunaa ke tiir main to ban gaii mohan terii tasviir aauungii re jamunaa ke tiir chalii aaiyo raadhe raanii threedots  dhuundho milaa na mujhako meraa dil kho gayaa haal mujhe bin batalaae vo to teraa ho gayaa dekh lo jo chaahe meraa kalejaa chiir chalii aaiyo raadhe raanii threedots  sakhiyon ko apane dil kii baat na bataaiyo jiivan bhar priit nibhaaiyo chhod ke na jaaiyo tuu hii to raadhe merii takadiir likhenge prem kahaanii threedots

Title: dekhaa hai pahalii baar saajan kii aankhon men pyaar
Lyrics: dekhaa hai pahalii baar saajan kii aankhon men pyaar tab jaa ke aayaa mere bechain dil ko karaar dilabar tujhe milane ko kab se thaa main bekaraar ab jaa ke aayaa mere bechain dil ko karaar dekhaa hai pahalii baar threedots  palaken jhukaauun tujhe dil men basaauun ab bin tere main to kahiin chain na paauun tuu mera jigar hai tuu merii nazar hai tuu merii aarazuu tuu meraa hamasafar hai dekhaa hai pahalii baar threedots  merii adaaen ye merii javaanii bas tere lie hai ye merii zindagaanii tuu merii gazal hai tuu meraa taraanaa aa terii dhadakanon pe likh duun dil kaa fasaanaa dekhaa hai pahalii baar threedots  dekhaa hai pahalii baar jaanam kii aankhon men pyaar tab jaa ke aayaa mere bechain dil ko karaar dilabar tujhe milane ko kab se thii main bekaraar ab jaa ke aayaa mere bechain dil ko karaar dekhaa hai pahalii baar threedots

Title: bulabulaa re bulabulaa mujhako baahon men sulaa
Lyrics: bulabulaa re bulabulaa mujhako baahon men sulaa kho ke merii aashiqiin men saarii duniyaa ko bhulaa  bulabulaa re bulabulaa dilarubaa kah kar bulaa saathiyaa tere lie to dil kaa daravaazaa khulaa bulabulaa re threedots  manachalii in vaadiyon men khushbuen hain pyaar kii kar de puurii aaj saarii khvaahishen diladaar kii kah rahe hain ye nazaare rut yahii diidaar kii naa rahegii ab adhuurii aarazuu mere yaar kii bulabulaa re threedots  goraa goraa ruup teraa kaale kaale baal hain honth tere hain rasiile phuul jaise gaal hain main diivaanii ho rahii huun aur naa taariif kar badh rahii hai bekaraarii daal naa aisii nazar bulabulaa re threedots

Title: guunje gagan guunje lalakaaren ham
Lyrics: he jii re guunje gagan guunje lalakaaren ham dharatii kaanpe din rainaa chalii mahaarathiyon kii senaa he jii re guunje gagan guunje threedots  ruup tum pralay kaa lie ran men jalo jalo ran men jalo shastra khanakate hain badho aakraman karo badho aakraman karo suuramaa ho tumhiin haan tum hii viir ho yuddh kii belaa men chhod do sanyam guunje gagan guunje threedots  antim vikat yuddh hogaa yahiin yuddh hogaa yahiin ai rakt hii upalegaa dharaa se har kahiin dharaa se har kahiin thaan lo tum nahiin yaa shatru nahiin arjun bhii tum ho tum hii shivam guunje gagan guunje threedots

Title: kahate hain jisako mohabbat vo ho tum
Lyrics: kahate hain jisako mohabbat vo ho tum rab ne banaayaa jise dil se vo ho tum husn ye gazab kaa adaaen hain qaatil jaise qayaamat ke lut hii gayaa dil tere naam se hotii hain subahen aavaaraa tere naam se hotii hain shaamen aavaaraa din bhar teraa khyaal tere khvaab raaton men teraa paagalapan hai mujhapar jaaneman kahate hain jisako threedots  ham kaanton par soenge terii chaahat men angaaron par bhii chalenge terii chaahat men tere kadamon ke niiche main apanii hathelii rakh duungaa ik kaantaa bhii chubhane na duun tujhako kahate hain jisako threedots  hamako hai yakiin par phir bhii itanaa hai kahanaa kisii aur kii soch bhii dil men naa aane denaa jo milatii nahiin hamako tumase aisii mohabbat o hamadam sochenge kyon gairon kii ham bolo kahate hain jisako threedots

Title: jo ham naa milenge to gul naa khilenge
Lyrics: jo ham naa milenge to gul naa khilenge hai milanaa zaruurii hamaaraa sanam jaan kii qasam o merii jaan kii qasam  ye kaisii hai halachal nahiin chain ek pal bataao sanam jaan kii qasam threedots  samandar men uthatii ye kaisii lahar hai machalataa hai har vaqt ye kaisii umar hai aajaa merii baanhon men aa aise na tuu baaten banaa hato chhod do mujhe na sataao karo na mujhape aise sitam jaan kii qasam threedots  nazar men basaa lo gale se tum lagaa lo agan jo lagii sanam kuchh mujhe hone lagaa dil meraa haan khone lagaa ye zulfen hataao cheharaa dikhaao tumhen dekhe bin jii na paaenge ham jaan kii qasam threedots

Title: mere dil kaa pataa tumhen kisane diyaa  o jaanam merii jaanam
Lyrics: mere dil kaa pataa tumhen kisane diyaa kyaa tum bhii akele the merii tarah jaanam jaanam o jaanam merii jaanam  tere dil kaa pataa mere dil ne diyaa haan ham bhii akele the terii tarah jaanam jaanam threedots  main akelaa jii rahaa thaa jiivan beiraadaa thaa na kisii se thii muhabbat na koii bhii vaayadaa thaa tum merii raah men jaane kab aa gaye kyaa tum bhii akele threedots  zindagii ke ye hasiin pal bas yuun hii guzar jaate aur kuchh din jo tumhen ham na milate to mar jaate vaayadaa hai ye meraa tumase kyaa hai chhupaa haan ham bhii akele threedots

Title: jab giit havaaon ne gaaye tum yaad aaye
Lyrics: jaaved piile patton kaa mausam jaa chukaa hai zamiin pe har taraf rang hii rang hain shok aur dilakash ujale aasamaan men safed baadalon kii tukadiyaan tair rahii hain vaadiyon men harii ghaas ke qaaliin bichh gae hain yahii sab kuchh thaa jab hamtum mile the vahii sab kuchh hai lekin tum nahiin ho  alakaa  jab giit havaaon ne gaae tum yaad aae jab kushbuu ke baadal chhaae tum yaad aae jab subahon ne rang chhalakaae tum yaad aae jab mahake shaamon ke saae tum yaad aae tum yaad aae jab giit havaaon ne gaae tum yaad aae jab kushbuu ke baadal chhaae tum yaad aae  jab koii sunaharaa din aayaa jab mausam jhuumaa laharaayaa jab rut ne lii ik angadaaii jab dhuup men narmiisii aaii jab rang nae kaliyon ko mile jab daaliidaalii phuul khile jab phuulon pe bhanvare mandalaae tum yaad aae jab giit havaaon ne gaae tum yaad aae  jab koii suhaanii raat aaii jab sapanon kii baaraat aaii jab anbar men taare damake jab aangan men juganuu chamake jab huii ghanerii kaamoshii jab chhaaii halkii behoshii jab raat ne tanman pighalaae tum yaad aae jab giit havaaon ne gaae tum yaad aae

Title: kal nahiin thaa vo kyaa hai aaj ye  chaar hii din kii thii ye rahaguzar
Lyrics: kal nahiin thaa vo kyaa hai aaj ye  kah gaiin ye havaayen kyaa mujhe  kahiin ye kaab to nahiin kahiin ye pyaar to nahiin  haradam aas ho gaii kyuun man men   kal nahiin thaa vo kyaa hai aaj ye kah gaiin ye havaayen kyaa mujhe  ye kyaa haal ho gayaa mujh ko ye kyaa ho gayaa  haradam aas ho gaii kyuun man men   hai kudaa bhii kahaan maan kii mamataa binaa  svapn aate nahiin pyaar jaage binaa  hai kahaan ye mohabbat chaahaton ke binaa  dhadakanon kii zubaan dhadakanon ne sunii  uth rahaa hai dhuaan aag to hai vahiin  pyaar milataa jahaan par zindagii hai vahiin    aasamaan hai jahaan hain sitaare vahaan  chaandanii hai jahaan chandramaa hai vahaan  manzilen hain vahii pe pyaar hotaa jahaan  pyaar kii raah men aap jo mil gae  raah men hazaaron diip kyuun jal gaye  aaj kyuun mere man men phuul khil gaye   kal nahiin thaa vo kyaa hai aaj ye kah gaiin ye havaayen kyaa mujhe  gaharii niind so gaii viiraanon men kho gaii  kaise merii zindagii gujaregii   chaar hii din kii thii ye rahaguzar  ho gayaa aaj puuraa ye safar  tere pyaar kii qasam merii yaad men sanam  ab ye terii zindagii guzaregii   katm hotii nahiin pyaar kii daastaan  khil rahii hai sadaa pyaar se hii fizaa  vaqt se bhii puraanaa hai ye silasilaa  barasane talak hai baadalon kaa safar  zindagii talak hai zindagii kaa safar  pyaar kaa ye safar to hai sadaa amar   kyaa pataa thaa mujhe kyaa hai merii manzil  kyaa pataa thaa tujhe tuut jaayegaa dil  jaa rahe the kahaan ham aa gaye kidhar  mil ke hai bichadanaa ye havaa kah gaii  gam kaa ye haadasaa kis tarah sah gaii  zindagii to gujar gaii yaad rah gaii

Title: bambaii kii chhoriyaan bachaa baappaa moriyaa
Lyrics: moriyaa moriyaa re baappaa moriyaa re  bambaii kii chhoriyaan bachaa baappaa moriyaa inhen aae hai phansaanaa ye jaanen dil lubhaanaa inakii miithii baaton men yaaron tum naa aanaa haay haay ye ladakiyaan bilkul taporiyaan bambaii kii chhoriyaan threedots  aashiq ye haay dil lagaanaa naa jaane palakon pe sapane sajaanaa naa jaane honthon kii rangat churaanaa naa jaane pyaar karake nibhaanaa naa jaane suno suno re jaano jaano re merii batiyaan maano maano re bholii suratiyaa pe naa jaanaa inhen pahachaanon re taubaa inake bahaane hathakande puraane bhole bhaale mardon ko jaal men phansaane daalen dilon pe nainon kii doriyaan bambaii kii chhoriyaan threedots  dekho ye kaisaa bedardii balam hai detaa hai jo apane dilabar ko gam hai maanaa pahalavaan men dam hii dam hai chaahat men lekin ye thodaa saa kam hai o merii jaanaan main huun diivaanaa tuu hai shamaa to main paravaanaa jaane zamaanaa yahii to hai bas meraa fasaanaa ye muhabbat kii baazii to maine hii maarii ki mujhase bhii pahale dil apanaa ye haarii haarii re haarii paagal nigodiyaan bambaii kii chhoriyaan threedots

Title: har ghadii mere pyaar kaa saayaa chalegaa tere
Lyrics: har ghadii mere pyaar kaa saayaa chalegaa tere saath sajanaa mere sajanaa har qadam mere pyaar kaa saayaa haan ab to tere saath sajanaa mere sajanaa har ghadii mere threedots  teraa pyaar to saagar se bhii gaharaa lagataa hai tere binaa to gulashan mujhako saharaa lagataa hai saath teraa ho to har rang sunaharaa lagataa hai har ghadii mere threedots  dil se tere dil kaa rishtaa aise jodenge sadiyon tak saathii teraa saath naa chhodenge mar ke bhii hamaraahii teraa haath naa chhodenge har ghadii mere threedots

Title: aaiinaa aaiinaa tuu bataa de zaraa  kyaa mere yaar ko bhaae cheharaa
Lyrics: aaiinaa aaiinaa tuu bataa de zaraa kyaa mere yaar ko bhaae cheharaa meraa aaiinaa aaiinaa tuu threedots  sach hai kyaa jhuuth kyaa yah kar faisalaa kyaa mere yaar ko threedots  main to jaanuun haal saare apane jiyaa ke ye na jaanuun kyaa dil men piyaa ke ai havaa ai ghataa tuu hii sandesh laa kyaa mere yaar ko threedots  kyaa main huun pasand unhen bhed zaraa khol de nahiin main jaanuun tuu hii ab kuchh bol re dekh yuun na sataa baat aage badhaa kyaa mere yaar ko threedots

Title: haay merii ankhiyon ne sapanaa dekhaa re  sapane men saajan apanaa
Lyrics: haay merii ankhiyon ne sapanaa dekhaa re sapane men saajan apanaa dekhaa re haay merii ankhiyon ne threedots  ye naa boluungii vo kaisaa thaa jaisaa sochaa thaa bilkul vaisaa thaa koii duujaa naa koii duujaa naa aisaa dekhaa re haay merii ankhiyon ne threedots  merii saanson se usakii saanson se usakii aankhon se merii aankhon se tiir kamaanon kaa tiir kamaanon kaa chalanaa dekhaa re haay merii ankhiyon ne threedots

Title: jay dev jay dev jay jay jay jay jay
Lyrics: shenduur laal chadhaayo achchhaa gajamukha ko dondil laal biraaje sut gauriihar ko haath liye guda ladduu saanii sukhar ko mahimaa kahe na jaay laagat huun pad ko jay dev jay dev  jay jay jay jay jay jay jay jii ganaraaj vidyaasukhadaataa dhany tumhaaro darshan meraa mat ramataa jay dev jay dev jay jay jay threedots  bhaavabhagat se koii sharanaagat aave santati sampatti sabahii bharapuur paave aise tum mahaaraaj moko ati bhaave gosaaviinandan nishidin gun gaave jay dev jay dev jay jay jay threedots  ghaalin lotaangan vandiin charan dolyaannii paahin ruup tujhe preme aalingin aananden puujin bhaaven ovaalin mhane naamaa tvamev maataa pitaa tvamev tvamev bandhushch sakhaa tvamev tvamev vidyaa dravinm tvamev tvamev sarvam mam dev dev kaayen vaach manasendriyairvaa buddhyaatmanaa vaa prakritisvabhaavaa karomi yadyat sakalam parasmai naaraayanaayeti samarpayaami achyut keshavm raamanaaraayanam krishnadaamodaram vaasudevam hari shriidharam maadhavam gopikaavallabham jaanakiinaayakam raamachandram bhaje hare raam hare raam raam raam hare hare hare krishna hare krishna krishna krishna hare hare

Title: dhuundh rahe hain mere lie ladakaa  ye sun ke vo niind se jaag gayaa
Lyrics: dhuundh rahe hain mere lie ladakaa mere ghar vaale are kitane ladake dekhe lambe gore thigane kaale  ek ladake ne puuchhaa kyaa kuchh naachanaa gaanaa aataa hai maine kahaa aataa hai kyaa tujhe tabalaa bajaanaa aataa hai bhaii vaah kyaa kahane kyaa javaab maaraa hai ye sun ke vo niind se jaag gayaa maidaan chhod ke bhaag gayaa kuchh mat puuchho taubaa hai bas in ladakon kii maangon se udate hain ye pankh lagaa kar chalate nahiin ye taangon se  ek ladake ne kahaa mujhe ye meraa ghar baar sambhaalegii maine kahaa na mere bachche terii ammaa paalegii ye sun ke vo niind se threedots  phir ik ladakaa aayaa jisakaa qad mujhase bhii chhotaa thaa daravaaze ke biich phans gayaa taubaa kitanaa motaa thaa us mote ne puuchhaa tujhe ghode kii savaarii aatii hai maine kahaa aatii hai par tuu ghodaa hai ki haathii hai ye sun ke vo niind se threedots  rangamahal men sotii thii main yauvan kii rangaraliyon men duur se ik din ik paradesii aayaa merii galiyon men us zulmii ne itanaa kahakar merii zid ko tod diyaa naa kar haan kar terii marzii tere lie jag chhod diyaa ye sun kar main niind se jaag gaii main saath piyaa ke bhaag gaii

Title: no problem
Lyrics: haa haa haa haa  namaste sat sirii akaal salaam vaalekum  to an vaalekum to all tamil masses   piichhe ho ke dekho  balle balle good bye  mujhe saarii pahanaa do no problem no problem  mujhe ghodii men bithaal do no problem no problem  main shave na banaauun to no problem no problem  tujhe siine se lagaauun to no problem no problem  ek zamaanaa aisaa thaa goron kii huquumat chalatii thii  ab tum pe huquumat chalaayenge no problem  ham pahale bhii tumase aage the  aur aaj bhii tumase aage hain  ham aur bhii aage jaayenge no problem   main tumase kaalaa huun no problem no problem  main tumase chhotaa huun no problem no problem  main pyaar men anaadii huun no problem no problem  jai jai hindustaan no problem

Title: mahajabiin no  mujhako diladaar yaar aisaa chaahie
Lyrics: mahajabiin no naazaniin no gulabadan no dilanashii no mujhako diladaar yaar aisaa chaahie cheharaa jisakaa tere jaisaa ho haan mujhako to diladaar aisaa chaahie cheharaa jisakaa tere jaisaa ho mahajabiin no threedots  sharaarat hai nigaahon men muhabbat hai sadaaon men tere honthon pe shabanam hai ke hain anguur ke daane tere gesuu niraale hain ye kaajal se bhii kaale hain terii aankhen maikhaane hain terii baaton men jaaduu hai terii saanson men khushbuu hai tujhe dekhe binaa dilabar diivaanaa dil nahiin maane sivaa mere kisii kii tum kabhii taariif na karanaa yahii ik raaz tumako samajhaanaa hai apsaraa no sundarii no gulabadan no threedots  qayaamat kii adaa aaii tuu jannat se chalii aaii tere jaisaa nahiin koii mere hamadam zamaane men jise chaahaa khyaalon men jinhen dekhaa thaa khvaabon men unhiin khvaabon kii tuu taabiir hai  mere mahabuub merii jaan merii hasarat mere aramaan teraa hii naam likhaa hai mere dil ke fasaane men mere majanuun mere raanjhaa mere aagosh men aajaa judii tujhase merii takadiir hai chaandanii no manachalii no gulabadan no threedots

Title: kesariyaa baalamaa o rii
Lyrics: kesariyaa baalamaa o rii  ki tumase laage nain nain re  rang liyo main aaj ang ang tere rang men tan huaa man huaa kesariyaa chaandanii hai raat ab to aa jaa piyaa aa chaandanii hai raat ab to aa jaa piyaa kesariyaa baalamaa o rii   threedots  takaraa ke sar ko jaan na de duun to kyaa karuun  kab tak firaaqeyaar ke sadame sahaa karuun main to hazaar chaahuun ki boluun na yaar se qaabuu men apane dil ko na paauun to kyaa karuun chaandanii hai raat ab to aa jaa piyaa chaandanii hai raat ab to aa jaa piyaa aa jaa piyaa chaandanii hai raat ab to aa jaa piyaa kesariyaa baalamaa o rii   threedots  kesariyaa baalamaa o rii  ki baanvarii bole log na main jiutii na mariyo main biarahaa mhaaro rog re baanvarii bole log log re kesariyaa   threedots  chadhate din kii aanch batoruun til til til til sab jal jaauun dhalate saanjh kii raakh kureduun ret men ret men sab ral jaaye na mil paayii na bichhadii main kaiso ye sanjog re baanvarii bole log re   threedots  mhaaro thal kii laambii saainyaa nis din nis din kuchh likh jaauun mero sandeso koii sunaa do  jis ko vo jis ko vo dikh jaaye priit ko dekhe nagarii vaale piir na dekhe log re baanvarii bole log kesariyaa   threedots

Title: bhangadaa paale aajaa aajaa  bolo bolo bolo jindadii hai kahaan
Lyrics: ho ho ho bhangadaa paale aajaa aajaa bolo bolo bolo jindadii hai kahaan jindadii vahaan teraa sang hai jahaan zindagii mile to ise mat khonaa jiite jii judaa hamase mat honaa bhangadaa paale aajaa aaja threedots  aangan men paayal khanakegii panaghat phir se gaaegaa muskaanon ko aramaanon ko qaid na koii kar paaegaa chhalake ankhiyon se pyaar dil huaa bekaraar naachen log magan matavaale bhangadaa paale aajaa aaja threedots  sachchaaii ko kaat sake jo aisii koii talavaar kahaan pyaar ko bandii banaakar rakh le aisii koii diivaar kahaan na ho koii majabuur na ho koii gam se chuur aajaa khushiyon ke mele lagaa le bhangadaa paale aajaa aaja threedots

Title: merii jaan chalii dushman ke ghar rab khair kare
Lyrics: merii jaan chalii dushman ke ghar rab khair kare  merii jaan chalii anajaanii dagar rab khair kare  duniyaa kii lage na burii nazar rab khair kare  tere sar pe rahe allaah kii mehar rab khair kare merii jaan chalii threedots

Title: waqt kii umr kyaa badii hogii

Title: kaamosh kyuun khadaa hai sukanjaan baat kar

Lyrics: palakon ko kalam banaa ke kaajal men use dubaa ke aajaa aahaa uuhuun tere dil pe naam na likh duun to meraa naam nahiin koshish kar le tere bas kaa ye kaam nahiin tuu paagal ho jaae to mere sar ilzaam nahiin tere dil pe naam na threedots  main laal chunariyaa odhuungii main terii zid ko toduungii jhuuthaa ilzaam lagaa duungii badanaam tujhe kar chhoduungii tuu mere dil se kyuun guzaraa ye rastaa aam nahiin haan tere dil pe naam na threedots  merii ungalii men anguuthii hai anguuthii kaa tuu motii hai kaisii bhii ho kitanii bhii ho har chiiz kii kiimat hotii hai saari duniyaa kii daulat bhii is dil kaa daam nahiin haan tere dil pe naam na threedots  nahiin dekhaa husn ye khvaabon men ye khushbuu kahaan gulaabon men terii mastaanii aankhon sii ye mastii kahaan sharaabon men tuu band nashe kii botal hai par meraa jaam nahiin haan tere dil pe naam na threedots

Lyrics: tere pyaar men main mar jaavaan tere naam ye dil kar jaavaan hamen naa bhulaanaa saajan hamen naa bhulaanaa duur nahiin jaanaa hamase duur nahiin jaanaa vaadaa kiyaa to vaadaa karake nibhaanaa hamen naa bhulaanaa threedots  tere pyaar men main mar jaavaan tere naam ye dil kar jaavaan hamen naa bhulaanaa sajanii hamen naa bhulaanaa duur nahiin jaanaa hamase duur nahiin jaanaa vaadaa kiyaa to vaadaa karake nibhaanaa hamen naa bhulaanaa threedots  apanaa bhii nasiibaa oe oe oe kyaa khuub milaa hai oe oe oe sapanon se bhii sundar oe oe oe mahabuub milaa hai oe oe oe teraa khvaab terii chaahat merii zindagaanii aankhon se duur mere dilabar naa jaanaa tere pyaar men main threedots  ban jaauun dulhan main oe oe oe tuu meraa sajan ho oe oe oe maanguun ye duaaen oe oe oe jaldii se milan ho oe oe oe sahii jaae ab naa mujhse sanam ye judaaii aao baaraat leke chhodo tadapaanaa ho tere pyaar men main threedots

Lyrics: chaahaa hai tujhako chaahuungaa haradam marake bhii dil se ye pyaar naa hogaa kam terii yaad jo aatii hai mere aansuu bahate hain apanaa to milan hogaa pal pal ye kahate hain kyaa ye zindagaanii hai bas terii kahaanii hai bas terii kahaanii hai ye jo zindagaanii hai chaahaa hai tujhako threedots  terii vo baaten vo chaahat kii rasmen jhuuthe the vaade kyaa jhuuthii thii kasamen jaanetamannaa kyaa ye sach hai bas itanaa kah de tuut jaae naa lamhaa aitabaar kaa de koii silaa mere intazaar kaa  chaahaa hai tujhako chaahuungii haradam marake bhii dil se threedots  terii huun terii jo chaahen kasam le le mujhako hamaraahii tuu apane gam de de saarii umar hai mujhako dard judaaii kaa sahanaa raaste men khoii hain manzilen merii mere saath jaaengii mushkilen merii chaahaa hai tujhako threedots  tuu saamane hai mere phir kyuun ye duurii hai tujhe kaise bataauun main haay kyaa majabuurii hai ye bhii koii jiinaa hai sirf aansuu piinaa hai sirf aansuu piinaa hai ye bhii koii jiinaa hai

Lyrics: ja ankhiyaan milaa ke channaa paanviin naa judaaii ve ankhiyaan milaa ke channaa paanviin naa judaaii ve deve na taane main nuun saarii kudaaii ve ankhiyaan milaa ke  saa taare hain baaraatii chaandanii hai ye baaraat saaton phere honge ab haathon men leke haath 2 jiivan saathii ham diyaa aur baatii ham re jiivan saathii ham diyaa aur baatii ham ja taare hain baaraatii chaandanii hai yah baaraat saaton phere honge ab haathon men leke haath 2 jiivan saathii ham diyaa aur baatii ham 2 saa taare hain baaraatii chaandanii hai yah baaraat  saa gangaajamunaa se bhii paavan teraa meraa bandhan teraa prem hai phulawaari aur meraa man hai aangan janamonjanamon kaa hii sajanii teraa meraa saath saaton phere honge ab haathon men leke haath jiivan saathii ham diyaa aur baatii ham ja jiivan saathii ham diyaa aur baatii ham  ja tuu hai jiivan men jo priitam sukh nahiin maanguun duujaa aaratii nainon se karatii huun man se terii puujaa main to dharm hii samajhuun terii kahii huii har baat saaton phere honge ab haathon men leke haath jiivan saathii ham diyaa aur baatii ham saa jiivan saathii ham diyaa aur baatii ham taare hain baaraatii chaandanii hai ye baaraat  ja ankhiyaan milaa ke channaa aave na judaaii ve deve na taane terii mainnuun saarii kudaaii ve  ankhiyaan milaa ke threedots

Lyrics: puurab se ik pyaaraa jhonkaa pavan udaakar laaii aaj achaanak dilabar aayaa yaad vatan kii aaii  vatan ke fasaane vatan kii kahaanii sataane lagii hain vo yaaden puraanii vatan ke fasaane threedots  meraa ek nanhaa saa betaa thaa pyaaraa kabhii usako dekhaa nahiin phir dubaaraa kisii haadase men vo gum ho gayaa thaa achaanak kahiin bhiid men kho gayaa thaa lie ghuumataa huun main usakii nishaanii vatan ke fasaane threedots  tadapatii rahii merii biivii bechaarii kaii saal karatii rahii intazaar vatan chhodakar aisaa parades aayaa bahut der usako naa main dekh paayaa badal gaii budhaape men usakii javaanii vatan ke fasaane threedots  main rotii huii apanii maan chhod aayaa main mamataa bharaa usakaa dil tod aayaa naa paradesh jaa tuu mujhe tokatii thii vo ro ro ke rastaa meraa rokatii thii magar ek bhii usakii maine naa maanii vatan ke fasaane threedots
