Lyrics: tere pyaar men terii yaad men main apanaa naam bhuulii saaraa jahaan bhuulii ye subahoshaam bhuulii main bekaraar tere pyaar men threedots  teraa bhii haal aisaa meraa bhii haal aisaa jaane ye saal kaisaa hoy main apanaa naam bhuulii threedots  jaane aur kyaa kyaa ab hone vaalaa hai tere pyaar men niind merii chain meraa khone vaalaa hai tere pyaar men ham donon dekho kaise paagal hain ham donon panchhii hain paagal hain premii hain ghaayal hain mastii men aajakal hain main apanaa naam bhuulaa ye subahoshaam bhuulaa saaraa jahaan bhuulaa main bekaraar main apanaa naam bhuulii threedots  anjaanaa saa koii jaaduu chalataa hai tere pyaar men  bin tere jalate hain barasaaton men bin tere bas terii baaton men jagate hain raaton men le ke dil haathon men main apanaa naam bhuulii threedots  teraa bhii haal aisaa meraa bhii haal aisaa sohanii mahivaal jaisaa hoy main apanaa naam bhuulii threedots  koii dekh rahaa chhup chhup ke kyon nain uthe ruke ruke ye bataa vo ruup sahaa naa jaae bin dekhe rahaa naa jaae kahiin duur nahiin jaa paae aur paas nahiin paa aae lade nain to meraa teraa chain gayaa ankhiyon men terii koii aan basaa dil men hai nayaa mehamaan basaa ho palaken jhukaa ke naa lajaanaa ho nii kudiye dikhaa de josh naa rahe khaamosh ho apanon se kaisaa sharamaanaa ye bataanaa teraa sajanaa sajanaa vahii to hai jo khvaab men roz milaa mile nain to kudiye teraa chain gayaa tuune jaal bichhaae  tuu raaj kare hai merii duaa jiivan ho teraa khushiyon se bharaa hansanaa sabhii ko tuu hansaanaa tuu bol de bas ek baar ki tuu khush hai merii bitiyaa raanii sar ko hayaa se yuun jhukaa ke muskuraa ke chaahe kahanaa bahanaa rahanaa nahiin hai ab aur yahaan maan liyaa lade nain to kudiye teraa chain gayaa

Lyrics: sunataa hai meraa kudaa dilojaan se chaahuun tujhako yaaraadilarubaa   ye zindagii tere liye tere liye aur tuu mere liye dil kii sadaa hai  sajan sun tuu bhii itanaa ki tuu hai meraa sapanaa tuu hii to merii aarazuu  sanam ye baaten kaisii kahaan merii qismat aisii kii ban jaauun terii aarazuu  kaho to main tere aage kamar biich gajaraa baandhe doluun nashiilii chaal se  adaa haay aisii qaatil sahegaa to kaise ye dil taras khaao mere haal pe  ye gulbuute bhii dil hain yahaan kaante sab gul hain ye raste hain apane pyaar ke  haay kahuungaa par main itanaa qadam dekh kar hii rakhanaa kahiin koii thokar naa lage  jo mil gaye do dil aise judaa ye phir honge kaise hamaarii kahaanii hai yahii  mujhe bhii ab kyaa karanaa hai tujhii pe jiinaamaranaa hai ke ab zindagaanii hai yahii

Lyrics: kahataa hai meraa ye dil piyaa koii hai koii hai hii nahiin  kaayaa hai tuu chhaayaa huun main tuu na ho to main bhii nahiin  tuu na ho to main bhii nahiin   chuudii jo khanake to kahaten hain khankhan  ghungharuu jo chhanake to kahate hain chhanchhan  khankhan ho ya phir chhanchhan ho  matalab inakaa hai jab tak hon do  main bhii huun tab tak jab tak tum ho  jo sach hai vo tum maan hii lo  subah ke pal yaa shaam ke hon din to saaraa ek hi hai  do aankhon se dekhen ham phir bhii nazaaraa ek hii hai  dil hain do lekin sanam pyaar kii dhaaraa ek hii hai  kahataa hai meraa ye dil piyaa koii hai koii hai hii nahiin koii hai koii hai hii nahiin   sunii kahaanii hai ye puraanii hanson kaa raajaa hanson kii raanii  phirate hain ek sang har pal hii  nain men jab ek niir bhar aaye judavaan aankh bhii niir bahaaye  pyaar kii ho man men jal thal bhii  kahane ko do jism sahii lekin bas ik jaan hain ham  kahane ko ham do sapanen hain lekin ik aramaan hain ham  itanaa pyaar huaa kaise soch ke kud hairaan hain ham  kahataa hai meraa ye dil piyaa 2 kahataa hai meraa ye dil piyaa koii hai koii hai hii nahiin koii hai koii hai hii nahiin  kaayaa hai tuu chhaayaa huun main tuu na ho to main bhii nahiin tuu na ho to main bhii nahiin

Lyrics: milate milate hasiin vaadiyon men dil kho gayaa to kyaa karoge o merii jaan o jaanetamannaa kuchh ho gayaa to kyaa karoge  milate milate hasiin vaadiyon men main kho gayaa to kyaa karoge o merii jaan threedots  hai isakaa diivanaa to saaraa jahaan nasiibon se milatii hai muhabbat yahaan dilon ke fasaane banaate rahenge nagmen vafaa ke to gaate rahenge milate milate hasiin vaadiyon threedots  yuun naa adaaon kii bijalii giraao lab chuum luun zaraa paas aao samajhe naa tuu merii majabuuriyaan rahane de thodii sii ye duuriyaan milate milate hasiin vaadiyon threedots  anajaane men ai jaanetamannaa kuchh ho gayaa to kyaa karoge

Title: paradesii paradesii jaanaa nahiin
Singer: alka yagnik udit narayan kumar sanu suresh wadkar bela sulakhe padma menon
Lyrics: bhaag 1  gaayak  alkaa yaaganik va udit naaraayan  a paradesii paradesii jaanaa nahiin mujhe chhod ke    paradesii mere yaaraa vaadaa nibhaanaa    mujhe yaad rakhanaa kahiin bhuul na jaanaa  u paradesii paradesii jaanaa nahiin mujhe chhod ke    paradesii mere yaaraa vaadaa nibhaanaa    tum yaad rakhanaa kahiin bhuul na jaanaa  a mainne tumako chaahaa tumase pyaar kiyaa    sab kuchh tum pe yaar apanaa vaar diyaa    ban gaii jogan mainne priit kaa jog liyaa    na sochaa na samajhaa dil kaa rog liyaa u paradesii mere yaaraa laut ke aanaa    tum yaad rakhanaa kahiin bhuul na jaanaa  a paradesii paradesii jaanaa nahiin mujhe chhod ke    tum yaad rakhanaa kahiin bhuul na jaanaa   bhaag 2  gaayak  kumaar shaanu va alkaa yaaganik  ku phuulon ke mausam men milane aate hain    patajhad men panchhii ban kar ud jaate hain    hansatii aankhon men aansuu de aate hain    vaadaa kar ke bhii na vaapas aate hain    paradesii mere yaaraa guzaraa zamaanaa    use yaad rakhanaa kahiin bhuul na jaanaa  a sach kahate hain duniyaa vaale pyaar na kar    pyaar to hai ik rog buraa is rog se dar    diivaanon kii qismat men tanhaaii hai    ishq kaa duujaa naam to yaar judaaii hai    paradesii mere yaaraa mujhe na rulaanaa    tum yaad rakhanaa kahiin bhuul na jaanaa   bhaag 3  gaayak  suresh vaadakar belaa sulaakhe va padhmaa menan  su paradesii paradesii jaanaa nahiin be tuu jaanaa nahiin su hamen chhod ke hamen chhod ke    paradesii mere yaaraa vaadaa nibhaanaa    hamen yaad rakhanaa kahiin bhuul na jaanaa    paradesii paradesii jaanaa nahiin    hamen chhod ke hamen chhod ke

Title: biivii hai chiiz sajaavat kii  balle balle o yaaraa balle balle
Lyrics: biivii hai chiiz sajaavat kii balle balle o yaaraa balle balle biivii se ghar ko sajaate hain balle balle o yaaraa balle balle sautan kaa shauq puraanaa hai sautan ko sar pe bithaate hain bharatii nahiin niiyat sautan se sautan kii sautan laate hain balle balle o yaaraa balle balle biivii hai chiiz threedots  o jise duniyaa sautan kahatii hai vo do nambar kaa khaataa hai balle balle o yaaraa balle balle jise kaale dhan kii tarah sabakii nazaron se chhupaayaa jaataa hai biivii hai chiiz threedots  oe shiyaa laahuu shiyuu oe shiyaa laahuu har roz nae kapadon kii tarah badale hai sahelii saajan kii balle balle o yaaraa balle balle o ik tan se kahaan man maanataa hai karate hain chaahat sau tan kii par sautan ko bhii khabar kahaan balle balle o yaaraa balle balle mil paatii hai inake man kii ye mard bade hii chaaluu hain chautarafaa jaal bichhaate hain balle balle o yaaraa balle balle biivii hai chiiz threedots  sautan ke chakkar ko saajan chaahen laakh chhipaae hazaaron se balle balle o yaaraa balle balle lekin ye pakade jaate hain biivii kii tez nigaahon se biivii kii puuchhataachh kaa dhang balle balle o yaaraa balle balle kuchh kam nahiin thaanedaaron se biivii to pulis se badhakar hai ye pulis ke log bataate hain balle balle o yaaraa balle balle biivii hai chiiz threedots

Lyrics: aa rahaa hai mazaa terii baahon men aa rahaa hai nashaa terii nigaahon men aa rahaa hai mazaa threedots  merii aarazuu bhii tum ho merii zindagii bhii tum ho jaanejaan suno zaraa mere dil kii sadaa aa rahaa hai mazaa threedots  kabhii jalan kabhii chubhan bujhatii nahiin saanson kii agan zaraa paas aa jaaegaa mujhe chain aa jaaegaa aa rahaa hai mazaa threedots  javaan javaan ye hasiin samaan jaane kaisii ye pyaas jagii kyaa bebasii kyaa bekhudii saare tan men aag lagii ye pyaar aur kitanaa tadapaaegaa aa rahaa hai mazaa threedots

Lyrics: jab kisii kii taraf dil jhukane lage baat aakar zubaan tak rukane lage aankhon aankhon men iqaraar hone lage bol do agar tumhen pyaar hone lage 3 jab kisii kii taraf threedots  chaahane jab lage dil kisii kii kushii dillagii ye nahiin ye hai dil kii lagii aandhiyon ko dabaane se kyaa faayadaa pyaar dil men chhupaane se kyaa faayadaa jaan se pyaaraa jab diladaar hone lage bol do agar tumhen pyaar hone lage 3 jab kisii kii taraf threedots  usakii kushbuu agar apanii saanson men ho usakaa sapanaa agar apanii aankhon men ho jab na dil ke bahalane kii suurat lage jab koii zindagii kii zaruurat lage aur jiinaa bhii dushwaar hone lage bol do agar tumhen pyaar hone lage 3  jab kisii kii taraf threedots  pyaar to honaa hii thaa 2

Title: dulhan tuu duulhaa main ban jaauungaa
Lyrics: dulhan tuu duulhaa main ban jaauungaa meraa intazaar karanaa baaraat lekar aauungaa  duulhaa tuu dulhan main ban jaauungii dekh sajanaa pyaar men tere mar jaauungii  mere jiivan saathii jab se dil men mere aae ho janm janm ke pyaar ko apane saath men jaise laae ho dekhaa maine tujhako jab se maang liyaa tumhen apane rab se tujh bin jii na paauungii duulhaa tuu dulhan main threedots

Title: yah ped piipal kaa  tuu hai kharaa sonaa saaraa jag piital kaa
Lyrics: yah ped piipal kaa tuu hai kharaa sonaa saaraa jag piital kaa hoy hoy saaraa jag piital kaa  ho sone kii anguuthii sach ek rab ek tuu saarii duniyaa jhuuthii  rang piilaa sarason kaa ik vaadaa kar tuu sau sau barason kaa  kyaa daulat laakhon kii duniyaa ke paas nahiin kiimat terii aankhon kii yah ped piipal kaa threedots  mausam hai mastaanaa paradesii panchhii dil le ke na ud jaanaa  kaanton men kaliyon men jiinaa maranaa hai mujhe terii hii galiyon men   main raanjhaa hiir hai tuu main tasviir terii merii tasviir hai tuu  2  maine sach jaan liyaa haan maine sach jaan liyaa qaafir ho gaii main rab tujhako maan liyaa yah ped piipal kaa threedots

Title: bahaa naa aansuu bhulaa de har gam  teraa kudaa hai
Lyrics: bahaa naa aansuu bhulaa de har gam ke teraa hamadam teraa kudaa hai nahiin jo saathii ye saaraa aalam to ye hai kyaa kam teraa kudaa hai teraa kudaa hai  kariib hai subaheyaar terii chhupegii kab tak bahaar terii vo sun rahaa hai pukaar terii hameshaa haradam teraa kudaa hai threedots  naa hogaa ye bhii galat kuchh itanaa jo tuu samajhe le hamen bhii apanaa ke hamako gar teraa dard kitanaa jo kahate hain ham teraa kudaa hai threedots

Title: sayyaad ne chhupaayaa bebas pe sitam dhaayaa  qaid men hai bulabul
Lyrics: sayyaad ne chhupaayaa bebas pe sitam dhaayaa koii zor na chal paaye qaid men hai bulabul qaid men hai bulabul sayyaad ne chhupaayaa threedots  main tujhako dhuundhataa huun paatiyon ke chaubaaron men cheharaa teraa dekhataa huun ashqon kii kataaron men dil meraa kahataa hai duniyaa ko jalaa duun hoke judaa hamaraahii apanii hastii mitaa duun mujhe paas bulaatii hai terii yaad sataatii hai din raat rulaatii hai qaid men hai bulabul threedots  khushbuu ke jhonke mahakii fizaaon men udatii thii main bulabul chanchal havaaon men dharatii ke pairon men ambar kii baahon men sapanon kii duniyaa men terii nigaahon men jharane tale machalatii thii main giratii thii kabhii sambhalatii thii main saragam koii gaatii thii main sakhiyon ko bhii sunaatii thii main nadiyaa kinaare baithii akele karatii thii main intazaar saare jahaan ko thokar lagaa ke aataa thaa milane yaar hansatii thii gaatii thii baahon men so jaatii thii dil kii baaton men khvaabon men kho jaatii thii aayaa kahiin se shikaarii zaalim ne jaal bichhaayaa band kiyaa pinjare men panchhii andheraa har or chhaayaa bejaan sii rahatii hai kuchh bhii nahiin kahatii hai har dard vah sahatii hai qaid men hai bulabul threedots

Title: chalo hans lo jhuum lo gaa lo mere saath
Lyrics: la la la la lall lall laa chalo hans lo jhuum lo gaa lo mere saath o dilavaalon kyaa baat hai chalo hans lo threedots  tusii great ho yaar yahii riit hai yahii giit hai yahii priit jiit yaaron duniyaa se kuchh lo duniyaa ko kuchh do chalo hans lo threedots  aahaa aahaa vo achchhe padosii hote hain jo saath men hansate rote hain kuchh aise hain jo auron kii niindon ko churaa kar sote hain aise logon kaa naam na lo aise logon se duur raho chalo hans lo threedots  vo baat karo ke dil jaae kisii dil se jaa kar mil jaae patthar ko pyaar se yuun dekho vo phuul ke jaise khil jaae naa buraa kaho naa buraa suno sab yaad karo apane rab ko chalo hans lo threedots

Lyrics: a 	mile jo tere nainaa hamaare nainaa se ku 	chalaa kaisaa jaaduu puuchho ye rainaa se a 	palak nahiin hotii hai band hotii hai koii miithii chubhan ku 	palak nahiin threedots a 	kaise main bataauun kaise ye dhadakataa hai jiyaa saathiyaa ku 	mile jo tere nainaa threedots a 	chalaa kaisaa jaaduu threedots ko 	dhintaanaa dhintaanaa dhintaanaa aanaa aanaa tuu mere paas aanaa 2  ku 	 tasviir terii aankhon men le luun itane kariib aa a 	nazadiik kaise aauun main bhalaa lagataa hai dar piyaa  2 ku 	aise na dekh mujhe tadapataa hai jiyaa saathiyaa aa aa a 	mile jo tere nainaa threedots ku 	chalaa kaisaa jaaduu threedots ko 	dhintaanaa threedots  a 	 karavat badal badal ke kasam se jaagii huun raat bhar ku 	nazaron men tum raho gar sanam chaahuun main umr bhar  2 a 	aise na baahon men men le bahakataa hai jiyaa o piyaa aa aa 	mile jo tere nainaa threedots ku 	chalaa kaisaa jaaduu threedots ko 	dhintaanaa threedots

Title: ai chahuun or vyaapt andher raaj  santoshii jab man se bulaae
Lyrics: ai chahun or vyaapt andher raaj kare traahimaam janataa samaaj degaa prachand vo tujhako dand paapii sambhal na kar koii bhuul jo paap teraa had se badhegaa aake giregaa shankar kaa shuul  santoshii jab man se bulaae ruup badal ke sadaashiv aae saare jag se adharm mitaae dharm kaa paavan diip jalaae degaa prachand vo threedots  main ishvar ko saaxii maan kar shapath letaa huun ki main sadaa sach boluungaa main nirbhay banuungaa tathaa dharm ke raaste par chaluungaa main desh kii janataa kii sevaa samvidhaan sammat kaanuun ke anusaar karuungaa main pulis vibhaag ke variiy padaadhikaariyon kaa sammaan karuungaa evam unake aadesh kaa axarashah paalan karuungaa santoshii jab man se threedots

Title: ye meraa shaharewafaa aur main akelaa aadamii
Lyrics: ye meraa shaharewafaa aur main akelaa aadamii mere laakhon aashanaa aur main akelaa aadamii  ek hii sar hai jhukaa sakataa huun kis kis ke liye anaginat mere kudaa aur main akelaa aadamii  ghuumataa phirataa huun shaayad mujhasaa koii aa mile gam ke mele jaabajaa aur main akelaa aadamii  meraa saayaa mar na jaaye raat ke is dasht men kitanaa lambaa raastaa aur main akelaa aadamii  milake hawwaa se kiyaa aabaad ise mainne qatiil ye jahaan merii ataa aur main akelaa aadamii

Title: dil kii kalam se chaahat kaa ham  nayaa itihaas likhenge
Lyrics: dil kii kalam se huun huun chaahat kaa ham huun huun pahalaa ehasaas likhenge likhenge ham apanii mohabbat kaa nayaa itihaas likhenge  o khvaabon men rahate hain palakon men ghar hai hamaaraa ambar pe chamakegaa apanii vafaa kaa sitaaraa in aasamaanon men uunchii to paravaaz hai roke kabhii na rukegii dhadakanon kii aavaaz is prem granth men he he ham naam apanaa he he dharatii aakaash likhenge likhenge ham apanii mohabbat kaa threedots  siine par sar rakhakar sone ko jii chaahataa hai naa jaane kyon mil ke rone ko jii chaahataa hai ham donon aashiqii men had se guzarane lage hain ham apanii saanson kii galiyon men hoke jahaan se utarane lage hain lab pe sanam ke he he mahake shabanam sii he he honthon kii pyaas likhenge likhenge ham apanii mohabbat kaa threedots

Title: dil mere tuu diivaanaa hai paagal hai maine maanaa hai
Lyrics: dil mere tuu diivaanaa hai paagal hai maine maanaa hai pal pal aahen bharataa hai kahane se kyuun darataa hai dil mere tuu diivaanaa threedots  khaamoshiyon kii jubaan koii na samajhe yahaan saharaa men gul khilate nahiin mil ke kabhii milate nahiin jaane hai kisakii khataa anjaanii ye raahen manzil kaa dengii pataa dil mere tuu diivaanaa threedots  nadiyon ko ehasaas hai saagar men bhii pyaas hai maanaa ke hai andheraa ghanaa kisane kiyaa tujhako manaa taaron kii shamaa jalaa sach hote sapane bhii maine hai aisaa sunaa dil mere tuu diivaanaa threedots

Title: duubaa duubaa nashe men bahakaa
Singer: asha jolly mukherjee r d burman
Lyrics: haan duubaa duubaa nashe men bahakaa ye samaa kahataa hai koii milane ko aaegaa yahaan ru ru ru ru aaj mulaaqaat hai hone koii baat hai intezaar ek pal aur merii jaan  pa pa ra paa paa paa threedots  jo ye jaam khanake to aanchal bhii dhalake bataao chale koii kaise sanbhalake adaaon kii naramii nigaahon kii garamii se tan pighale aur bahake dil bahut se fasaane bahut se taraane  sunaane ko aae hain tere diivaane  zaraa paas aa jaa dilon men samaa jaa tuu ai jaanejaan aake mil   ho rang pe aane ko hai mehafil aane vaalaa hai koii qaatil ho aaj mulaaqaat hai hone koii baat hai intezaar ek pal aur merii jaan  in anajaanii raahon men hai tuu nigaahon men ye dil to meraa hai sach hai ki teraa hai tujhase ujaalaa hai varnaa andheraa hai  tuu hai to phir kyaa hai gam magar phir bhii mujhako ye tujh se gilaa hai  ki donon men ab tak ye kyon faasalaa hai ye parde giraa de ye duurii mitaa de ke ab ek ho jaaen ham   itanii betaabii hai kyaa hamadam aa rahaa hai milane kaa mausam ho aaj mulaaqaat hai hone koii baat hai intezaar ek pal aur merii jaan

Title: padosan ke ghar kal raat bhar
Lyrics: padosan ke ghar kal raat bhar bajatii rahiin chuudiyaan chhan chhanaa chhan chhan chhan chhanaa chhan chhan jalatii rahii main machalatii rahii main bajatii rahiin chuudiyaan chhan chhanaa chhan chhan chhan chhanaa chhan chhan  karavat badalatii rahii niind naa aaii nikalii kaii baar dil se duhaaii kabhii aise kabhii vaise dhal gayaa vaqt ho gaii sahar padosan ke ghar threedots  main haal apanaa bataauun to kaise dardejigar bhii dikhaauun to kaise vo na jaane vo na maane meraa dilabar badaa bekhabar padosan ke ghar threedots

Title: haath chhuute bhii to rishte nahiin chhodaa karate
Lyrics: haath chhuute bhii to rishte nahiin chhodaa karate vaqt kii shaakh se lamhen nahiin todaa karate haath chhuute bhii to threedots  jisakii aavaaz men silavat ho nigaahon men shikan aisii tasviir ke tukade nahiin jodaa karate  shahd jiine kaa milaa karataa hai thodaa thodaa jaane vaalon ke lie dil nahiin todaa karate  lag ke saahil se jo bahataa hai use bahane do aise dariyaa kaa kabhii rukh nahiin modaa karate vaqt kii shaakh se threedots

Title: kat likhanaa hai  mujhe tumase muhabbat ho gaii hai
Lyrics: lataa  kat likhanaa hai par sochatii huun 2 ye kaise likhuun mujhe tumase muhabbat ho gaii hai mujhe tumase muhabbat ho gaii hai aziiz  merii maano itanaa likh do  2 in aankhon par kvaabon kii inaayat ho gaii hai kvaabon kii inaayat ho gaii hai  lataa  kaagazkalam jaise hii uthaauun dil hai ki dhadake jaae haana dil hai ki dhadake jaae aziiz  jo bhii likho tum dil kii baaten ab na chhupengii chhupaae haana ab na chhupengii chhupaae lataa  main achchhii huun ye to likh duun   2 ye kaise likhuun mujhe tumase muhabbat ho gaii hai mujhe tumase muhabbat ho gaii hai  lataa  ye sochaa hai itanaa likh duun kuchh din se mujhe kyaa jaane kyuun ye duniyaa hasiin lagatii hai 2 aziiz  ye bhii likhanaa ab saare din hai saath koii ki jisake bin tabiiyat hii nahiin lagatii hai 2 lataa  bataao bataao kin lafzon men main ye likhuun mujhako tum samajhaao mujhe tumase muhabbat ho gaii hai mujhe tumase muhabbat ho gaii hai  lataa  main kuchh likhuun vo kuchh samajhe aisaa nahiin ho jaae haana aisaa nahiin ho jaae aziiz  aisaa hai to saaf likho tum apanii to hai ye raay haana apanii to hai ye raay lataa  haan sach to hai kyuun sharamaauun 2 kyuun ye na likhuun mujhe tumase muhabbat ho gaii hai aziiz  to likh do muhabbat ho gaii hai lataa  likh duungii muhabbat ho gaii hai aziiz  mujhe tumase muhabbat ho gaii hai lataa  mujhe tumase muhabbat ho gaii hai

Title: sir bhii ruuthe ruuthe hain
Lyrics: aapane sikhaayaa hamen hansaa karo haradam haradam khush raho pyaar karo gussaa karo kam kam khud phir to hanso naa gussaa kam karo naa ham jo ruuth gae to nahiin chalegaa koii zor  main nahiin ruuthii tumase bachchon kisii ne mujhe sataayaa kisane vahii jo saath hamaare piknik men aayaa gusse men teacher tumhaarii aur bhii achchhii lagatii hai  jhaanjhariyaa usakii khanak gaii chunarii bhii sar se sarak gaii merii nazar usase milii to usakii nazar sharamaa ke jhuk gaii jhaanjhariyaa  kitaaben bahut sii padhii hongii tumane magar koii cheharaa bhii tumane padhaa hai padhaa hai merii jaan nazar se padhaa hai bataa mere chehare pe kyaa kyaa likhaa hai

Title: betaa apanii maan se kabhii ruuth bhii jaae
Lyrics: betaa apanii maan se kabhii ruuth bhii jaae maan apane bete se kabhii ruuthatii nahiin duniyaa kaa har bandhan shaayad tuut bhii jaae mamataa kii dorii to kabhii tuutatii nahiin betaa apanii maan se threedots  tuune hii sikhalaayaa mujhe muskuraanaa kaise kahaan se siikhaa tuune ruuth jaanaa bhuul huii hai mujhase mujhe maaf kar de phir naa karuungii galatii insaaf kar de betaa apanii maan se threedots  maan kii baahon men saaraa sansaar hotaa hai maan kii aankhon men to bas pyaar hotaa hai duniyaa jalatii dhuup hai maan kaa aanchal hai chhaayaa vo kismat vaalaa hai jisane maan ko hai paayaa betaa apanii maan se threedots

Title: ki aaii ab aunty kii baarii  aunty no 1
Lyrics: main puraanii huun magar puraanii sharaab jaisii huun gaur se dekhie main ek gulaab jaisii huun nashaa meraa chadh ke utarataa nahiin aur mujhe dekhakar dil bhii bharataa nahiin apane jigar ko thaam ke baitho  ki baandhii kamariyaa se saadii ki aaii ab aunty kii baarii apane jigar ko thaam ke threedots   anguuron kii mast ladii thii par botalon men band padii thii chhodakar saarii duniyaa kii laaj botalon se baahar nikalii huun aaj chaandii kaa biidaa sone kii thaalii main huun sharaabon kii ek pyaalii ki chhaaii banake khumaarii ki aaii ab aunty kii threedots  shakarakand pyaar karane de hamako karo nazaraband  har dil kii aarazuu huun mere aashiqon se puuchho main kaisii chiiz huun kisii ne sach kahaa hai ki old is gold badii tez badii bold dekhe hain maine mahale domahale aise hii jalave the mere pahale kii haath lagaa naa duungii gaalii ki aaii ab aunty kii threedots  shakarakand pyaar karane de hamako kar na nazaraband

Title: giiton men haradam saragam tumhaarii ho
Lyrics: giiton men haradam saragam tumhaarii ho   dhun ho tumhaarii aur aavaaz merii  ham sab ke jiivan men sangiit pran hai  aaj ham gunagunaayen pyaar ke giit donon   andaaz do hain magar sur to ek hai  mil ke ham roz gaayen sukhdukh men saathii donon  laharen hazaaron hain nadiyaa to ek hai  mil ke ham paar kar len jaaneman aaj donon

Title: kal college band ho jaaegaa  tum mujhase judaa ho jaaogii
Lyrics: kal college band ho jaaegaa tum apane ghar ko jaaoge phir ek ladakaa ek ladakii se judaa ho jaaegaa vo mil nahiin paaegaa tum mujhase judaa ho jaaogii bolo kaise rah paauungaa tum mujhase judaa threedots  main teraa diivaanaa piichhe piichhe tere ghar tak aauungaa tujhe apanaa banaauungaa tum mujhase judaa threedots  ab kitaabon men lagataa nahiin dil padhanaa likhanaa huaa meraa mushkil dekhate hii tujhe kah uthaa dil mil gaii hai mujhe merii manzil merii aankhon men bolo to kyaa hai sach kahuun isamen meraa cheharaa hai tujhe aankhon men basaauungaa tum mujhase judaa threedots  ghar men mummy kii nazaren hongii baahar daddy kaa paharaa hogaa jitanaa rokegaa hamako zamaanaa pyaar utanaa hii gaharaa hogaa tuu hai diivaanaa khud se begaanaa thodaa paagal hai thodaa anajaanaa merii nindiyaa tum churaaoge kal college band threedots  ik mahiine kii hii baat hogii phir to har din mulaakaat hogii ek pal bin kate na tumhaare kab din hogaa kab raat hogii tujhe dulhan banaauungaa kal college band threedots  tere piichhe main ab na aauungaa meraa vaadaa hai na sataauungaa duur tujhase main chalaa jaauungaa main tumase judaa ho jaauungaa bolo kaise rah threedots

Title: jaan tum ho merii duuriyaan kyuun ham se
Lyrics: jaan tum ho merii duuriyaan kyuun ham se  ab to aa ke mil jaa pyaas man men kab se  ye suhaanii shaam hai pyaar kar le ham se  chuum lo aao mujhe hai guzaarish tum se  jaan tum ho merii pyaar ho gayaa tum se  main bhii to huun pyaasaa tum ko dekhaa jab se  ye javaanii kaa nashaa chhaa rahaa hai kab se  ho naa jaaye josh men bhuul koii ham se   aaj tum lagatii ho sundar khilate phuulon kii jaisii  jhilamilaatii terii aankhen chandaa taaron ke jaisii  saath mil kar jaanejaan aao ham naachenge  mastiyon men jhuumenge aao ham gaayenge  ye nazaare aur tum saath mere hamadam  aaj apane pyaar kaa ho gayaa hai sangam   tuufaanon men bhii ai saathii tum ko ham naa chhodenge  mushkil se hotii hai mohabbat janamjanam naa todenge  aaj meraa dil bole phuulon pe so jaayen  jaan merii kah do tum baanhon men kho jaayen  jaan terii hai sadaa kah rahii hai dhadakan  dil men rahate ho sadaa tum hii mere hamadam

Title: tan tanaa tan tan tan taaraa chalatii hai kyaa nau se baarah
Lyrics: aankh ladaa ke tuune maaraa ghaayal ho gayaa dil bechaaraa sunaa hai tere chaahane vaale aage das hain piichhe baarah mujhako apanaa chaand banaa le chamakaa de kismat kaa taaraa ek baar se dil nahiin bharataa mud ke dekh mujhe dobaaraa tan tanaa tan tan tan taaraa chalatii hai kyaa nau se baarah khadii khadii kyaa soch rahii hai chal ho jaaen nau do gyaarah tan tanaa tan threedots  raat ke show kii do tikaten hain khol ke purse main dikhalaauun chipak ke baithuun saath tere main taxi men le jaauun samajh na mujhako aisaa vaisaa mere batue men hai paisaa tujhe khilaauungaa jii bhar ke garam samosaa idalii dosaa tuu hai merii pepsii kolaa main teraa huun kokaa kolaa jaldii kar ki chadh na jaae thermometer kaa ye paaraa ek baar se dil threedots  filmii dhun pe dekh ke tujhako siitii roz bajaauun bahut dinon se soch rahaa thaa film main tujhe dikhaauun shukravaar kii shaam hasiin hai naii naii ye film lagii hai garmii kii na hogii tension theatre hai vo air conditioned film hasiin vo jaaneman hai ye filmon men number one hai govindaa hai hiiro usakaa aur maadhurii hiiroin hai pichhalii siit kii do tikaten hain gupachup pyaar karenge yaaraa ek baar se dil threedots

Title: tere pyaar ne sanam jaaduu kyaa kar diyaa
Lyrics: tere pyaar ne sanam jaaduu kyaa kar diyaa haan jaane kaisaa nashaa chhaa rahaa tere pyaar ne sanam threedots  jhuumatii havaaon bataao zaraa main kahaan huun ho chhedatii fizaaon samajhaao zaraa anjaane hii mujhe kyaa huaa tere pyaar ne sanam threedots  baazuon men aake ye mujhako lagaa sharm kyaa hai naa kabhii ye pahale thaa mujhako pataa haan tuune hamanavaan kyaa kiyaa tere pyaar ne sanam threedots tere pyaar ne sanam jaaduu kyaa kar diyaa haan jaane kaisaa nashaa chhaa rahaa tere pyaar ne sanam threedots  jhuumatii havaaon bataao zaraa main kahaan huun ho chhedatii fizaaon samajhaao zaraa anjaane hii mujhe kyaa huaa tere pyaar ne sanam threedots  naa koii kamii hai ab jaanevafaa zindagii men haan har khushii milii jo mujhe tuu milii laaii hai rang kyaa ye duaa tere pyaar ne sanam threedots

Title: cheharaa teraa cheharaa sapanaa hai meraa
Lyrics: cheharaa teraa cheharaa sapanaa hai meraa chaahuun tujhe kitanaa na mujhe hai pataa cheharaa teraa cheharaa threedots  aa dhuundh le main kahaan kho gayaa ye ishq men hamako kyaa ho gayaa chaahat kii ye jaane kaisii manzil hai ham kahaan hai ye bataanaa mushkil hai ab hamen inhiin raahon pe chalanaa hai kuchh bhii ho ye rastaa naa badalanaa hai tanhaa ye do premii koii naa tiisaraa cheharaa teraa cheharaa threedots  ye jism hai khushbuon se banaa main huun tere pyaar kaa aaiinaa tere chhuune se badan to jalataa hai jaane kitane rangon men ye dhalataa hai chingaarii hai merii jalatii saanson kii garmii hai ye merii pyaasii aankhon kii main pyaasaa saharaa huun saavan kii tuu ghataa cheharaa teraa cheharaa threedots

Lyrics: ladakii diivaanii dekho ladakaa diivaanaa milane kaa kaise kaise dhuundhe bahaanaa ladakii diivaanii dekho threedots  kuchh bhii na jaane bahut anaadii kaise chalegii chaahat kii gaadii ladakii diivaanii dekho threedots  khaamoshiyon kaa matalab bataa de mujhako tuu apane dil kaa pataa de aise na yaaraa palaken jhukaa tuu aaj tuu mujhase mujhako churaa le he ladakii diivaanii dekho threedots  mere gamon ko apanaa banaayaa tuune mujhe phir jiinaa sikhaayaa ye zindagii hai terii amaanat mujhase kii hai tuune muhabbat mere sanam kyaa tujhako khabar hai meraa ye dil to teraa hii ghar hai apanii adaa se isako sajaa de pyaar kaa mandir isako banaa de he ladakii diivaanii dekho threedots

Lyrics: tum aae to aayaa mujhe yaad galii men aaj chaand nikalaa jaane kitane dinon ke baad galii men aaj chaand nikalaa 2 galii men aaj chaand nikalaa tum aae to aayaa mujhe yaad galii men aaj chaand nikalaa  ye nainaa bin kaajal tarase baarah mahiine baadal barase sunii rab ne merii fariyaad galii men aaj chaand nikalaa galii men aaj chaand nikalaa jaane kitane dinon ke baad threedots  aaj kii raat jo main so jaatii khulatii aankh subah ho jaatii main to ho jaatii bas barabaad galii men aaj chaand nikalaa galii men aaj chaand nikalaa jaane kitane dinon ke baad threedots  mainne tumako aate dekhaa apanii jaan ko jaate dekhaa jaane phir kyaa huaa nahiin yaad galii men aaj chaand nikalaa galii men aaj chaand nikalaa jaane kitane dinon ke baad threedots    aaj kaa din ummiid kaa din hai aaj to merii iid kaa din hai ai mere dil mubaarakabaad galii men aaj chaand nikalaa galii men aaj chaand nikalaa jaane kitane dinon ke baad threedots

Title: ye ladakaa hai diivaanaa hai diivaanaa
Lyrics: ye kaisaa ladakaa hai tu tu tu ru ye kaisii ladakii hai tu tu tu ru isakaa main kyaa karuun isakaa main kyaa karuun ye ladataa hai haan haan akadatii hai he he jhagadataa hai bigadatii hai diivaanaa hai diivaanii hai  haay haay re haay ye ladakaa haay haay re haay ye he karataa naadaaniyaan kyuun puuchho to haay yo kabhii ye hamase ladataa hai kabhii jhagadataa hai koii paas isake naa aanaa ye ladakaa hai diivaanaa hai diivaanaa  haay haay re haay ye ladakii haay haay re haay karatii naadaaniyaan kyuun puuchho to haay kabhii ye hamase ladatii hai kabhii akadatii hai karo duur se chhedakhaanii ye ladakii hai diivaanii hai diivaanii  isakii baaten yahii jaane koii bhii to jaane naa aisii vaisii kaisii hai ye koii pahachaane naa to bhaago o yaaron kar naa de shaitaanii ye ladakii hai diivaanii threedots  aate jaate chhede hamako ke maane naa ye kahanaa dekho dekho paagal hai ye haan bachake zaraa rahanaa ye aisaa hai phir bhii apanaa isako maanaa ye ladakaa hai diivaanaa threedots

Title: tere dil ke paas meraa dil hai aaj meraa dil machal rahaa hai
Lyrics: tere dil ke paas meraa dil hai aaj meraa dil machal rahaa hai haan merii jaan nikal rahii hai yaa koii aramaan nikal rahaa hai haay haay tere dil ke paas threedots  dil chaahe aise men ik duuje ko thaam len tere dil ke paas threedots  yahaan husn bhii hai yahaan ishq bhii hai mahafil men kyaa nahiin hai zaraa mud ke dekh ham jaisaa ek koii duusaraa nahiin hai are logon ke ho ho ho honthon pe teraa meraa naam hai main huun tere sang mahafil kaa rang palapal badal rahaa hai o merii jaan nikal rahii threedots  aankhen jhukaa ke baaten dabaa ke honthon ko sii rahe hain karade salaam chaahat ke jaam aankhon se pii rahe hain haa haa haa dil de de haay dil le le duniyaa men rakhaa hai kyaa tere mere biich nahiin aur koii jaaduu saa chal rahaa hai merii jaan nikal rahii threedots

Lyrics: jaane kyon dekhataa hai insaan aaiinaa detaa nahiin sahii jab pahachaan aaiinaa jaane kyon dekhataa threedots  aaiinaa kuchh bhii nahiin aankhon kaa dhokhaa hai aataa jo nazar dil men jo hotaa hai aaiinaa aur dil kaa kyaa ek fasaanaa hai anjaam in donon kaa bas tuut jaanaa hai jii chaahe tod duun beiimaan aaiinaa jaane kyon dekhataa threedots  berukhii se pahale dilabar zakhm dekhe jaate hain kaanton kii nok se phir maraham lagaate hain ek aaiinaa ho jisamen dil dikhaaen ham mujha pe agar ho jaae itanaa karam jaane kyon dekhataa threedots

Lyrics: baahon men kas le honthon kaa ras le aise mujhe na tadapaa aake lipat jaa thodaa simat jaa siine se mujhako lagaa  haathon se badan sahalaauungii main pyaar kii garmii badhaauungii main tere dil ko bhii pighalaauungii main thodaa laharaane de mastii chadh jaane de chhaane de thodaa nashaa  duniyaa men dekhe maine laakhon javaan tere jaisaa dekhaa nahiin koii yahaan aankhon men basaa lo mujhe jaanejahaan aisaa mujhe mard milegaa kahaan bhiige mere khyaalon ko chhuu le mere gaalon ko pyaasii huun pyaas bujhaa

Lyrics: dhiire dhiire haule haule dil kii dhadakan mujhase bole re ho gayaa mujhe pyaar kaa bukhaar nabz dikhaa le check karavaa le main bhii huun biimaar chadh gayaa pyaar kaa bukhaar  jaaduu kar gayaa ek ladakaa jor se meraa dil dhadakaa badan meraa kuchh garm huaa main sick huun tan garm huaa chadh gayaa pyaar kaa threedots  ye kaisii biimaarii hai jalatii body saarii saarii raat ko niind nahiin aatii sar kuchh bhaarii bhaarii hai pyaar kaa do injection mujhako ho jaae bedaa pyaar chadh gayaa pyaar kaa threedots  duur tere gam kar duungaa fever bhii kam kar duungaa aa lag jaa ik baar gale se o mere diladaar chadh gayaa pyaar kaa threedots

Title: columbus columbus chhuttiii hai aaii
Lyrics: aao koii nayaa mulk dhuundhen chal ke bhaaii  aao koii nayaa mulk dhuundhen chal ke bhaaii chhuttii chhuttii chhuttii koii lahar dil men utthii 2   columbus columbus chhuttiii hai aaii aao koii nayaa mulk dhuundhen chal ke bhaaii  2 chhuttii chhuttii chhuttii koii lahar dil men utthii 2  aisii jagah dil kahataa hai chalo  duniyaa kii koii buraaii jahaan na ho  faujii taiyaarii jang aur ladaaii  bhuukh aur biimaarii gandii raajaniitii  in sabase duur kahiin to hogii hansatiigaatii zindagii    mehanat hamane paanch dinon kii  paaii tab hai do din kii chhuttii  aao kushii se jhuumen havaaon kii tarah ghuumen  kaliyon ko ham chuumen laharon se khelen  bachapan men laut jaayen pankh lagaa ke  udanaa siikhen is ambar kii sair karen  paradesii hain panchhii ban ke nagarnagar kii sair karen  phir dariyaa kii or jaayen uunchiiniichii mauj aaye  aise jhuule jhulaayen aaye niind hamen  aao koii nayaa mulk dhuundhen chal ke bhaaii chhuttii chhuttii chhuttii koii lahar dil men utthii 2   dekho jo koii ladakii pyaarii  apanii in aankhon men tum usake sapane rakh lo  saagar kii laharon kii saadii usako pahanaao  ambar ke taaron ke bunde usako banavaao  usako bhii pyaar se kud se kahate raho  pyaaraa ye kaab hai do din to dekh lo  kaabon men hii do din raho  aao koii nayaa mulk dhuundhen chal ke bhaaii chhuttii chhuttii chhuttii koii lahar dil men utthii 2

Title: ho gorii kahaan tuu jaaegii  tum din ko din kah do kah den
Lyrics: ho gorii ho gorii kahaan tuu jaaegii saajan kaa aayaa bulaavaa laut ke tuu aayegii tum din ko din kah do kah den tum raat kaho doharaaenge jiine kii ijaazat do jii len marane ko kaho mar jaaenge tum din ko din threedots  sapanon men sajaayaa hai tumako saanson men chhupaa kar dekhenge ai jaanevafaa tasviir terii ham dil men chhupaa kar dekhenge ek baar bulaa lo paas hamen sau baar gale lag jaaenge tum din ko din threedots  aankhon men tumhaare sapane hain honthon pe tumhaarii baaten hain har shaam tumhaare naam se hai tumase hii mahakatii raaten hain tuu shaad rahe aabaad rahe har dard teraa sah jaaenge tum din ko din threedots  dekhaa hai tumhen ab kyaa dekhen chaahaa hai tumhen ab kyaa chaahen tumase hii muhabbat kii manzil tum tak hii muhabbat kii raahen ik pyaar tumhaaraa mil jaae tabhii duniyaa thukaraaenge tum din ko din threedots

Title: miladii nasiibaan naal mohabbat yaar mile to rab mil jaae

Title: sandese aate hain  ki ghar kab aaoge
Lyrics: sandese aate hain hamen tadapaate hain jo chitthii aatii hai vo puuchhe jaatii hai ki ghar kab aaoge likho kab aaoge ki tum bin ye ghar suunaa suunaa hai  kisii dilavaalii ne kisii matavaalii ne hamen khat likhaa hai ye hamase puuchhaa hai kisii kii saanson ne kisii kii dhadakan ne kisii kii chuudii ne kisii ke kangan ne kisii ke kajare ne kisii ke gajare ne mahakatii subahon ne machalatii shaamon ne akelii raaton men adhuurii baaton ne tarasatii baahon ne aur puuchhaa hai tarasii nigaahon ne ki ghar kab aaoge likho kab aaoge ki tum bin ye dil suunaa suunaa hai sandese aate hain threedots  muhabbat vaalon ne hamaare yaaron ne hamen ye likhaa hai ki hamase puuchhaa hai hamaare gaanvon ne aam kii chhaanvon ne puraane piipal ne barasate baadal ne khet khaliyaanon ne hare maidaanon ne basantii melon ne jhuumatii belon ne lachakate jhuulon ne dahakate phuulon ne chatakatii kaliyon ne aur puuchhaa hai gaanv kii galiyon ne ki ghar kab aaoge likho kab aaoge ki tum bin gaanv suunaa suunaa hai sandese aate hain threedots  kabhii ek mamataa kii pyaar kii gangaa kii jo chitthii aatii hai saath vo laatii hai mere din bachapan ke khel vo aangan ke vo saayaa aanchal kaa vo tiikaa kaajal kaa vo lorii raaton men vo naramii haathon men vo chaahat aankhon men ve chintaa baaton men bigadanaa uupar se muhabbat andar se kare vo devii maan  yahii har khet men puuchhe merii maan ki ghar kab aaoge ki tum bin aangan suunaa suunaa hai  ai gujarane vaalii havaa bataa meraa itanaa kaam karegii kyaa mere gaanv jaa mere doston ko salaam de mere gaanv men hai jo vo galii jahaan rahatii hai merii dilarubaa use mere pyaar kaa jaam de vahaan thodii duur hai ghar meraa mere ghar men hai merii buudhii maan merii maan ke pairon ko chhuu use usake bete kaa naam de  ai gujarane vaalii havaa zaraa mere doston merii dilarubaa merii maan ko meraa payaam de unhen jaa ke tuu ye payaam de main vaapas aauungaa phir apane gaanv men usii kii chhaanv men ki maan ke aanchal se gaanv kii piipal se kisii ke kaajal se kiyaa jo vaadaa hai vo nibhaauungaa main ek din aauungaa

Lyrics: taubaa taubaa ye jalawe kaise koii naa bahake  puure hii badan men jaise roshanii bharii  tuu hai koii huur yaa koii parii hai  taubaa taubaa ye jalawe kaise koii naa bahake  pyaarii sii muurat bholii sii suurat phuul kii jaise ho pankhadii  teraa badan hai yaa hai koii ras kii gangaa chhalak padii  gaharii nashiilii gaharii niilii aankhon men hai mastii badii  honth gulaabii muskaayen to chhalake ek motii kii ladii  husn kii maliqaa kaabon kii raanii tere jaisaa koii nahiin  is duniyaa men laakhon hasiin hain lekin aisaa koii nahiin  taubaa taubaa ye jalawe kaise koii naa bahake  haay ye chaand jaisaa cheharaa aur kanval kii danthal gardan  moranii sii chaal hai terii hiranii jaisii chanchal chitavan  tuu jahaanjahaan se guzare mahake vo raahen saarii  rangrang tuu chhalake to mahake nigaahen saarii  chaandnagar men thandii havaayen pyaar kii main le aauungaa  phir main chaand ke chaandii aur sone se mahal banaauungaa  taare tod ke laauungaa aur saaraa mahal sajaauungaa  narm mulaayam baadal main vahaan tere liye bichhaauungaa  phuulon se shabanam laauungaa phir main tujhe nahalaauungaa  aur us bhiige husn ko jaanaan aankhon se pii jaauungaa  taubaa taubaa ye jalawe taubaa taubaa ye jalawe kaise koii naa bahake puure hii badan men jaise roshanii bharii tuu hai koii huur yaa koii parii hai  taubaa taubaa ye jalawe kaise koii naa bahake

Lyrics: bikharatii zulf kii parachhaaiyaan mujhe de do tum apanii shaam kii tanhaaiyaan mujhe de do  ye lahar lahar badan tuut hii na jaaye kahiin khumaarehusn kii angadaaiyaan mujhe de do  main tumako yaad karuun aur tum chale aao mohabbaton kii ye sachchaaiyaan mujhe de do  main duub jaauun tumhaarii udaas aankhon men tum apane dard kii gaharaaiyaan mujhe de do

Title: chupake chupake raat din aansuu bahaanaa yaad hai
Lyrics: apanii aawaaz kii larzish pe to qaabuu paa lo pyaar ke bol to honthon se nikal jaate hain apane tewar to sambhaalo ke koii ye na kahe dil badalate hain to chehare bhii badal jaate hain  chupake chupake raat din aansuu bahaanaa yaad hai  ab main samajhaa tere rukasaar pe til kaa matalab daulatehusn pe darabaan bithaa rakhaa hai gar siyaahbakt hii honaa thaa nasiibon men mere zulf hotaa tere rukasaar pe yaa til hotaa  chupake chupake raat din aansuu bahaanaa yaad hai hamako ab tak aashiqii kaa wo zamaanaa yaad hai  tujhase milate hii wo kuchh bebaak ho jaanaa meraa aur teraa daanton men wo ungalii dabaanaa yaad hai  chorii chorii hamase tum aa kar mile the jis jagah muddaten guzariin par ab tak wo thikaanaa yaad hai  dopahar kii dhuup men mere bulaane ke liye wo teraa kothe pe nange paanv aanaa yaad hai  khainch lenaa wo meraa parde kaa konaa dafatan aur dupatte se teraa wo munh chhupaanaa yaad hai  tujhako jab tanhaa kabhii paanaa to azraahelihaaz haaledil baaton hii baaton men jataanaa yaad hai  aa gayaa gar wasl kii shab bhii kahiin zikrefiraaq wo teraa ro ro ke bhii mujhako rulaanaa yaad hai  waan hazaaraan iztiraab yaan sadhazaaraan ishtiyaak tujhako wo pahalepahal dil kaa lagaanaa yaad hai  jaan kar honaa tujhe wo kasadepaabosii meraa aur teraa thukaraa ke sar wo muskuraanaa yaad hai  jab sivaa mere tumhaaraa koii diiwaanaa na thaa sach kaho kuchh tumako ab bhii wo zamaanaa yaad hai  gair kii nazaron se bach kar sabakii marzii ke kilaaf wo teraa chorii chhipe raaton ko aanaa yaad hai  dekhanaa mujhako jo baragashtaa sau naaz se jab manaa lenaa to phir khud ruuth jaanaa yaad hai  shauq men mehandii ke wo bedastopaa honaa teraa aur meraa wo chhedanaa wo gudagudaanaa yaad hai

Title: saavan kaa mahiinaa aayaa hai  ve maahiyaa bujhaa de pyaas jiyaa kii
Lyrics: saavan kaa mahiinaa aayaa hai ghataa se barasaa hai paanii ve maahiyaa bujhaa de pyaas jiyaa kii ho  aise men tuune jo chhuaa merii bhii mahakii javaanii ve maahiyaa bujhaa de threedots  tere husn shabaab kii baat huii yaa madiraa kii barasaat huii mausam bhii sharaabii lagataa hai mujhe bhii chadhiyaa nashaa hai ve maahiyaa bujhaa de threedots  koii zor na dil pe chalataa hai baarish men badan meraa jalataa hai buundon men chhupii hai chingaarii havaa bhii suiyaan chubhaaye ve maahiyaa bujhaa de threedots  ham milate rahe janam janam na honge judaa ham mil ke sanam aa ik duuje men kho jaayen rahe na koii bhii duurii ve maahiyaa bujhaa de threedots

Title: aa jaao kii sab mil ke  ek tuu hii bharosaa
Lyrics: aa jaao ki sab mil ke rab se duaa maangen  jiivan men sukuun chaahen chaahat men vafaa maangen  haalaat badalane men ab der na ho maalik  jo de chuke phir le andher na ho maali   ek tuu hii bharosaa ek tuu hii sahaaraa  is tere jahaan men nahiin koii hamaaraa  he ishvar yaa allaah ye pukaar sunale  he ishvar yaa allaah he daataa   hamase naa dekhaa jaaye barabaadiyon kaa samaan  ujadii huii bastii men ye tadap rahe insaan  nanhe jismon ke tukade liye khadii hai ek maan  baaruud ke dhuven men tuu hii bol jaaye kahaan   naadaan hain ham to maalik kyuun dii hamen ye sazaa  yaa hai sabhii ke dil men nafarat kaa zahar bharaa  inhen phir se yaad dilaa de sabak vahii pyaar kaa  ban jaaye gulashan phir se kaanton bharii duniyaa  merii pukaar sun le

Lyrics: ai merii bekhudii tuu kahaan le chalii vo hasiin ik nazar kar gaii bekhabar ai hamasafar tum kyaa mile duniyaa kii halachal men ai merii bekhudii threedots  kam ho gae har faasale duniyaa kii halachal men ai merii bekhudii threedots  har taraf bekhudii ye kahaan aa gae saath mere yahaan do jahaan aa gae zindagii ke lie ye zaruurii huaa maang le aaj to zindagii kii duaa tham tham ke har dhadakan chale duniyaa kii halachal men vaah khuub hain ye silasile duniyaa kii halachal men  khvaahishon ke lie bandishen tod den aaj har mod ko ik nayaa mod den jhuum ke jhuum ke chuum len aasamaan ab naa bas men rahiin dil kii betaabiyaan dil hosh se kab kaam le duniyaa kii halachal men ab aa ke koii thaam le duniyaa kii halachal men ai merii bekhudii threedots  ye kaun dil men aa gayaa duniyaa kii halachal men ehasaas ban ke chhaa gayaa duniyaa kii halachal men ai merii bekhudii threedots  ye na sochaa kabhii yon bhii ho jaaegaa besabab bevajah dil ye kho jaaegaa ruuh men karavaten saans men garmiyaan kyaa huaa kyaa kahen kaun hai darmyaan ye kaun dilabar chhaa gayaa duniyaa kii halachal men saayaa kaun laharaa gayaa duniyaa kii halachal men ai merii bekhudii threedots

Title: chanchal chuudiyaan khanakaa ke  maike kii galii chhod ke tujhe jaanaa hogaa
Lyrics: chanchal chuudiyaan khanakaa ke menhadii haathon men rachaa ke jhuumar maathe pe sajaa ke ghunghataa laaj kaa giraa ke maike kii galii chhod ke tujhe jaanaa hogaa maike kii galii chhod ke threedots  laao sakhii laao jodaa suhaag laado ko sajaa den ham pyaar se pairon men lagaa den haldii mahaavar mukhadaa chamakaa den shrringaar se phuulon sii javaanii pe vo lalachaaenge chandaa sii bindiyaa chamakaa ke ghunghataa laaj kaa threedots  panchhii paradesii har ladakii bahanaa kisii ko hameshaa yahaan rahanaa nahiin ladakii ko jaise har dard sahanaa kisii ke kabhii kuchh kahanaa nahiin saaye men piyaa ke ab jiinaa maranaa maike vaalon kaa sir naa niiche karanaa sapanen palakon pe basaa ke sainyaa jii kaa dil churaa ke jhuumar maathe pe sajaa ke ghunghataa laaj kaa threedots  daataa mere daataa tuune likhii kyon betii kii judaaii taqadiir men betii ko naa koii rok paae chaahe ise baandhe zanjiir men aae rabbaa aae kyon vidaaii kii ghadii roke se ruke naa ansuan kii ladii maan kii mamataa ko bhulaa ke bhaiyaa bhaabhii ko rulaa ke sakhiyon se daaman chhudaa ke aankhon se aansuu chhalakaa ke maike kii galii chhod ke threedots

Title: dil men kyaa hai teraa pyaar  meraa pyaar hai tuu diladaar hai tuu
Lyrics: dil men kyaa hai teraa pyaar o aankhon men kyaa hai intazaar o dil men kyaa hai threedots  meraa pyaar hai tuu diladaar hai tuu tere dam se hai ye bahaar dil men kyaa hai threedots  pahale bhii phuul khilate the aatii thiin bahaaren gulashan men phuulon kii hai ye naa to bahaar kii hai ye khushbuu to hamaare pyaar kii hai merii jaan hai tuu aramaan hai tuu mere dil kaa tuu karaar hai dil men kyaa hai threedots  thandii havaaon men sanam garmii hai pyaar kii shaamil hai mere pyaar men diladaar teraa pyaar bhii kahe dil meraa piyaa pyaar teraa paauun main baar baar dil men kyaa hai threedots

Title: jaanaa to jaanaan bas ye jaanaa pyaar diivaanaa hotaa hai
Lyrics: jaanaa to jaanaan bas ye jaanaa pyaar diivaanaa hotaa hai kar detaa hai dil ko diivaanaa pyaar diivaanaa hotaa hai jaanaa to jaanaan bas ye threedots   mere dil men terii dhadakan pyaar teraa nas nas men tujh bin zindaa rahanaa jaanam ab to nahiin hai bas men  2 ai duniyaa kuchh naa samajhaanaa pyaar diivaanaa hotaa hai kar detaa hai dil ko threedots   yuun to jalatii har ik shai se duur hii rahanaa achchhaa lekin shamaa ke jalane men jaane asar hai kaisaa  2 hans kar jal jaae paravaanaa pyaar diivaanaa hotaa hai kar detaa hai dil ko threedots

Title: are dillii shahar men mhaaro ghaagharo jo ghuumyo
Lyrics: are dillii shahar men mhaaro ghaagharo jo ghuumyo uii uii sab mar gyaa re mhaaro ghaagharo jo ghuumyo  thii men khet men khadii khaa rii thii kakadii uukii laal pagadii jo mhaarii baanh pakadii manne gussaa ghano aayo unen maarii lakadii unen muunchhaa ghumaaii manhe aankhyaan dikhaaii phir kaanii hoyo phir kaanii hoyo chhorii kyuun akadii kyuun maarii lakadii bolii main sun sun ore laal pagadii thii main khet men khadii khaa rii thii kakadii tuune baanh pakadii maine maarii lakadii tuu kaanii bolii tuu kaanii bolii are duur jaa re hat jaa re chhoraa duur hat jaa re hat jaa duungii main thane aisaa jhatakaa duur hat jaa re hat jaa phir dillii shahar men threedots  ai ghuumyo re ghuumyo  zyaadaa baaten na banaa tuu na jaane main huun kaun chhoraa ministar ko dillii maaruun telifon main samajh na paaii uukii hansii udaaii dillii jaake unhen maarii rapat likhavaaii phir kaanii hoyo phir kaanii hoyo siitii sar sar bajaate pulis daudii chalii aaii kangan mhaaraa utaaraa hathakadiyaan pahanaaii thaanedaar ke aage phir main muskaaii maine diyo latako unhen khaayo jhatako thodii tedhii huii thodii medhii huii mhaarii kamar ko maine jaraa sii matakaaii thaanedaar ne apanii saarii akal ganvaaii tuu kaanii bolii tuu kaanii bolii are duur hat jaa re threedots  huii mhaarii charchaa nikalaa ghanaa morchaa koii presavaalaa koii motaa laalaa koii santarii jii koii mantarii jii koii yaa bole koii vaa bole manhe uthe le gyaa manhe vathe le gyaa manhe rupayaa khilaayo manhe bade dhamakaayo main phir bhii na maanii maine man men thii thaanii tuu kaanii bolii tuu kaanii bolii are duur hat jaa re threedots  bolaa sun sun sun chhorii sun sun sun baat hansii men udaa de baat yahii tuu bataa de nahiin to hogii pitaaii sunale gaanv kii lugaaii main jor se chillaaii inspektar ne bulaaii mhaare saamane vo aayo unhen dekhake sharamaaii thodii sii main hansii thodii sii muskaaii phir kaanii hoyo phir kaanii hoyo bolyo inspektar jii bado mantrii jii  uuko ladako ye hai bado tagado ye hai paisaa jeb men rakh le mundo band kar le tuu kaanii bolii tuu kaanii bolii are duur hat jaa re threedots  aayo mantrii jii bolii main suno jii thaaro laadalo kanvar daale hai najar main na ruup kanvar marake banuun jo amar thaaro laadalo kamiinaa mushkil kare jiinaa nahiin main huun amiinaa ike haath men bikuun naa mhaare aage inhen ab aaegaa pasiinaa phir kaanii hoyo phir kaanii hoyo mhaarii cholii tuu dekh aagaraa ko tuu dekh chunar ko dekh ghaagharaa ko tuu dekh are duur hat jaa re threedots  nahiin ladakii main aisan nahiin ladakii main vaisan mhaarii baat pe chaale garmii men seshan mhaarii baataan kare tii en sheshan mhaare kaun hai baap mhaaro kaun saa gaanv saarii baaten jaane dillii ko raav ilekshan men mhaaro naam le adavaanii mardaan se aage nikalegii Lyrics: kyaa bemurawwat kalq hai sab jamaa hain bismil ke paas tanhaa meraa qaatil rahaa koii nahiin qaatil ke paas  jinake honthon pe hansii paanv men chhaale honge haan wohii log tumhen dhuundhane waale honge  haan wohii log tujhe chaahane waale honge   andaaz apane dekhate hain aaiine men wo aur ye bhii dekhate hain koii dekhataa na ho  may barasatii hai fazaaon pe nashaa taarii hai mere saaqii ne kahiin jaam uchhaale honge  unase mafahuumegameziist adaa ho shaayad ashq jo daamanemijagaan ne sambhaale honge  shammaa le aaye hain ham jalwaagahejaanaan se ab do aalam men ujaale hii ujaale honge  ham bade naaz se aaye the terii mahafil men kyaa kabar thii labeizahaar pr taale honge

Title: paayal kare ye chham chham  paas mere aa jaa tarase man jaanam

Lyrics: paayal kare ye chham chham chuudii kare ye chhan chhan ye chham chham kyaa bole ye chhan chhan kyaa bole paas mere aa jaa tarase man jaanam paayal kare ye chham threedots  kuchh dekhuun to sanam main dekhuun bas tujhe kuchh sochuun to sanam main sochuun bas tujhe paaiin maine khushiyaan tujhako jo paa liyaa duur nahiin jaanaa mujhase tuu kabhii mere piyaa saath na chhoduungaa teraa haath na chhoduungaa teraa sang men rahuungaa tere haradam jaanam paayal kare ye chham threedots  nainon kaa ye likhaa nainon ne padh liyaa is dil ne jo kahaa us dil ne sun liyaa honthon pe bhii aa gayaa pyaar hamen ho gayaa maine tujhe tuune mujhe saathii kab chun liyaa main banii huun tere lie tuu banaa hai mere lie tuu hai dil meraa to main huun dhadakan jaanam paayal kare ye chham threedots  chupake chupake sabase chhupake man haar gaii apanaa diivaanii huii hai tuu jisakii kaisaa hai teraa sajanaa diidii cheharaa hai kaisaa bolo chandaa ke jaisaa pakadii hii gaii terii chorii mushkil hai teraa bachanaa tuune pyaar kiyaa dil kisako diyaa kaisaa hai teraa sajanaa bahanaa  lagataa hai kaisaa bolo phuulon ke jaisaa phir vo kaamadev jaisii usakii vo nazar tirachhii le gayaa udaa ke vo in honthon kii surkhii lipatii jo mere tan se priitam kii garam saansen na jaane sharm se kyon merii jhuk gaiin ye aankhen bilkul hai sahii honaa hai yahii yahii dhiiraj tuu zaraa rakhanaa tuune pyaar kiyaa threedots  main kaise kahuun tujhase kyaa jaane huaa mujhako jab pahalii dafaa usane dhiire se chhuaa mujhako nas nas ko merii usane taaron kii tarah chhedaa sur pyaar ke jab jaage jab usane mujhe chhedaa hairaan huun main bechain hai tuu ye sach hai yaa sapanaa tuune pyaar kiyaa threedots

Lyrics: do raaton ke biich ek chhotaasaa din bechaaraa hai kyaa kare   do dinon ke biich ek chhotii sii raat hai  raat ke idhar ek din raat ke udhar ek din  din to hain do bas raat ek hai  kar lo jo chaaho ban lo jo chaaho  aaj hai tumhaaraa aur kal bhii tumhaaraa hai   do ghaaton ke biich ek pataliisii dhaaraa hai kyaa kare   ghaat nahiin chalate dhaaraa chalatii hai  pataliisii dhaaraa chal kar samundar se milatii hai  samundar se milatii hai mil kar kho jaatii hai  ghaat ghaat hii rahate hain vo samundar ho jaatii hai   samundar ko baandhe aisaa koii ghaat nahiin  qadamon ko thaame aisii koii baat nahiin   kar lo jo chaaho ban lo jo chaaho  tum kar nahiin sakate aisaa kahiin kuchh bhii nahiin   is liye yah na kahanaa kabhii kaise karen kyaa karen   main kar sakataa huun main karataa huun   mujhe karanaa hii hai main karuungaa 4   main kar sakataa nahiin aisaa kahiin kuchh bhii nahiin   samundar ko baandhe aisaa koii ghaat nahiin  qadamon ko thaame aisii koii baat nahiin  pataliisii dhaaraa chal kar samundar se milatii hai  samundar se milatii hai aur mil kar kho jaatii hai   ghaat ghaat hii rahate hain vo samundar ho jaatii hai

Lyrics: aa aa dil lene kii rut aaii dil dene kii rut aaii jogan pe joban aayaa joban ne lii angadaaii dil lene kii rut aaii threedots  mujhako jo ho gayaa hai kyaa isakaa naam hai kahate hain pyaar isako par ye badanaam hai to mujhako badanaam kar do pakado merii kalaaii jogan pe joban aayaa threedots  dil chaahe baandhuun paayal naachuun main jhuumake koii nishaanii de do rakh luun main chuum ke tum maango jaan de duun de ke main raam duhaaii are jogan pe joban aayaa threedots  dolii baaraat mehandii aisaa din aaj kaa ye sun ke tod aaii paharaa main laaj kaa zulfon ke ghuunghat men tuu dulhan ban ke sharamaaii jogan pe joban aayaa threedots
