Title: main bevafaa nahiin huun  lekin jo kuchh huaa hai vo bhii vafaa nahiin hai
Lyrics: main bevafaa nahiin huun tuu bevafaa nahiin huun lekin jo kuchh huaa hai vo bhii vafaa nahiin hai main bevafaa nahiin threedots  dil todane se pahale itanaa to sochaa hotaa main jaa rahaa thaa mujhako kuchh kah ke rokaa hotaa raste men lut gayaa huun manzil pataa nahiin hai lekin jo kuchh huaa hai threedots  kismat men pyaar ke kyon jaane likhaa hai ronaa tumhen pyaar kii kasam hai hamase judaa na honaa jisakii sazaa milii hai merii khataa nahiin hai lekin jo kuchh huaa hai threedots  tujhase bichhad ke jaanii mar jaaen na kahiin ham jisakii davaa nahiin hai aisaa kyon de diyaa gam apane pe zulm karanaa merii adaa nahiin hai lekin jo kuchh huaa hai threedots

Title: gair se aankh ladaaii to ladaaii hogii
Lyrics: hans ke sah lenge agar tujhamen buraaii hogii gair se aankh ladaaii to ladaaii hogii  gam naa hogaa jo kabhii thodii judaaii hogii gair se aankh ladaaii threedots  maaf kar denge tumhen jaane yaa anjaane men baat jo tumane koii hamase chhupaaii hogii gair se aankh ladaaii threedots  ham sanam saath nibhaaenge saat janmon tak yuun kisii ne bhii muhabbat naa nibhaaii hogii gair se aankh ladaaii threedots

Title: o merii jaan dil ho gayaa teraa
Lyrics: o merii jaan dil ho gayaa teraa   tuu hii bataa rastaa meraa kahaan   jalataa rahaa dil kaa diyaa khilatii rahii chaahat sadaa   jaayen to ham jaayen kahaan o merii jaan tuu hii bataa   jalataa rahaa dil kaa diyaa khilatii rahii chaahat sadaa  jaayen to ham jaayen kahaan o merii jaan tuu hii bataa  o merii jaan dil ho gayaa teraa   barakhaa se bhiige nahiin aasamaan aandhii se udataa nahiin chandramaa   kahane se chaahat hotii nahiin ho jaaye to phir maratii nahiin   jalatii hai agnii uthataa dhuvaan bujhatii nahiin hai dil kii shamaa   o merii jaan dil ho gayaa teraa  siine men bas ek dil thaa meraa vo bhii to maine tujhako diyaa   ab ek jaan hai baakii merii kah do de duun tumhen dilarubaa   aabaad tumase hai dil kaa jahaan tere bin jaanam jaanaa kahaan   o merii jaan dil ho gayaa teraa tuu hii bataa rastaa meraa kahaan  jalataa rahaa dil kaa diyaa khilatii rahii chaahat sadaa  jaayen to ham jaayen kahaan o merii jaan tuu hii bataa  2

Title: sayyonii  bol katiilii re  dil dhak dhak dhadake
Lyrics: aa sayyonii sayyonii tuii tuii tuii tuii bol katiilii bin saajan ke biite kaise raat ghabaraaii sii lagatii hai kyaa julm huaa tere saath bol katiilii re bol katiilii  saas sasur aangan men soe main souun chaubaare ghar ke baahar khadaa khadaa muaa devar kare ishaare kabhii kahiin aahat aae kabhii jo kundii khadake dil dhadake dil dhadake dil dhak dhak dhadake jaalimaan merii baaiin aankh bhii phadake sayyonii  gorii ye na chhupaa ye bhed bataa tere joban kaa kyuun rang udaa o o subah subah saare gharavaale jab jaaen khaliyaan chorii chorii ghar ke andar aa jaae beiimaan sune koii na merii duhaaii kahiin na ho jaae rusavaaii uuii maan maane na kahanaa harajaaii kasake pakade merii kalaaii uuii maan paanii paanii main ho jaauun e chingaarii sii bhadake dil dhadake dil dhak dhak threedots  teraa devar muaa re badaa paajii pahale maare ankhiyaan kahe vaah bhaabhii dopaharii men chauraahe se sharabat le ke aae usake andar naa jaane vo kaun sii chiiz milaae piite hii bichchhuu lad jaae nas nas koii jahar samaae uuii maan ghuunte badan ko suii chubhaaen ang ang men dard sataae uuii maan raat raat bhar karavat le ke e merii javaanii tadape dil dhadake dil dhak dhak threedots

Title: jaataa hai tuu kahaan re baabaa sun pyaare
Lyrics: jaataa hai tuu kahaan re baabaa sun pyaare ruk jaa re duniyaa ke bade tedhe ye raaste khatare hii khatare hain tere vaaste jaataa hai tuu kahaan threedots  aajakal aisii bhii luut hai kahane ko pyaar hai samajho to jhuuth hai dekh tuu lutane lagaa teraa ishtahaar kisake haathon men jaataa hai tuu kahaan threedots  pyaar kaa jo karate hain shor dhyaan hai teraa jinakii or aa main bataauun kaun hai vo raat men daakuu din men chor jaataa hai tuu kahaan threedots  haath joduun tere paduun tere paiyaan chhod ke na jaa mujhe chhod ke merii baiyaan sun le merii arj o sajan jaane vaale ye to bataa jaataa hai tuu kahaan threedots  bikate hain iimaan yahaan baazaaron men  anjaane tuu na jaane koii jaal phailaa terii raahon men koii baat hai terii baaton men ye jaan le merii baaton men faisalaa tujhako aaj karanaa hai duub jaanaa hai yaa ubharanaa hai is taraf jhuuth hai dikhaavaa hai us taraf laalachii nigaahen hai is taraf mere dil kii raahen hain jaataa hai tuu kahaan threedots

Title: is kadar pyaar hai tumase hai hamasafar
Lyrics: is kadar pyaar hai tumase ai hamasafar ab to jiite hain ham bas tumhen dekhakar tumhaarii har adaa tumhaarii har nazar ye kyaa kahane lagii tumhen hai kyaa khabar is kadar pyaar hai threedots  dil men hain betaabiyaan niind udane lagii tere khyaalon se hii aankh judane lagii har pal tumako dekhaa maine kahatii hai merii nazar tumhaarii har adaa threedots  saanson men basane lagii jabase tuu o jaanejaan apanaa saa lagane lagaa mujhako saaraa jahaan o mahakaa mahakaa lagataa mujhako khushiyon se dil kaa nagar tumhaarii har adaa threedots

Title: aaj main uupar aasamaan niiche
Lyrics: pa da ni ni ah re ve taara reve taa raaraa ni pa da ni ni rivi taaraa rivi ri ri paa ram  aaj main uupar aasamaan niiche aaj main aage zamaanaa hai piichhe ab main kyaa karuun cahluun siidhii ki ultii chaluun aaj main uupar aasamaan niiche threedots  yuun hii bin baat ke chhalake jaaye hansii dole jab havaa laage gudgudii sambhaalo gir paduun are are are are are taubaa kyaa karuun chaluun siidhii kii ultii chaluun aaj main uupar threedots  aaj main uupar aasamaan niiche aaj main aage zamaanaa hai piichhe ab main kyaa karuun sar ke bal yaa kadam se chaluun aaj main uupar threedots  jhuumen jaa mauj men rukanaa na jaanejaan dekhuun ye tarang rukatii hai kahaan main bhii tere sang in laharon pe chaluun sar ke bal yaa kadam se chaluun aaj main uupar threedots

Title: zahar hai ki pyaar hai teraa chummaa
Lyrics: zahar hai ki pyaar hai teraa chummaa kaisaa ye khumaar hai teraa chummaa 2 maine dekhaa nahiin tere jaisaa kahiin tujhako mere sar kii kasam zahar hai ki pyaar hai threedots  tuu na mujhe dansatii chadhatii naa mastii jaaneman varanaa kyaa hai terii hastii ye merii aashiqii kam na hogii kabhii qaayam hai jab tak ye dam zahar hai ki pyaar hai threedots  pyaar kaa nashaa hai dardejigar se dekh mujhe jaanam dil kii nazar se ye merii bekhudii aur badhane lagii bahak jaaenge kadam zahar hai ki pyaar hai threedots  tuu hai shikaarii main huun nishaanaa mujhe barfiilii aag men jalaanaa dekh le bekhabar pyaar kaa ye asar ghutane lagaa meraa dam zahar hai ki pyaar hai threedots

Title: paapaa main paapaa ban gayaa
Film: hum aapke dil mein rehte hain
Lyrics: paapaa paa paa paa paa paa paa paipaa paa paa paa paa paa paa paipaa paa paa pa ra pa paa paa paa paapaa main paapaa ban gayaa dekho main paapaa ban gayaa socho main paapaa ban gayaa paapaa main threedots  sonuu monuu kii khaatir main unakaa ghodaa ban jaauungaa taaron se bahalaauungaa baagon men tahalaauungaa main uungalii thaam ke usakii use chalanaa sikhalaauungaa are he aaegaa badaa mazaa paapaa main threedots  he shaakaa maakaa naakaa maakaa chikii daa buudaa shaakaa maakaa naakaa maakaa paa paa paa paa paa chup gup chup goluu moluu kii khaatir ye muunchhe badhavaauungaa nanhen munne haathon se muunchhon ko khinchavaauungaa are aise vo khiinchegaa ye daadaa phir chiikhegaa are ye ye ye koii pakado ise zaraa betaa main daadaa ban gayaa socho main daadaa ban gayaa paapaa main threedots  daa daa daa daa daa paa paa paa daa daa  aa naa chaandii hamane maangii naa chaahaa hamane sonaa maangaa thaa hamane rab se ye chandaa saa khilaunaa isane hamako milavaayaa ab duur kabhii na honaa are he jo maangaa vo mil gayaa dekho ye paapaa ban gayaa socho ye paapaa ban gayaa paapaa main threedots

Title: kyaa adaa kyaa jalave tere paaro  dil ke tukade ho gae hazaaron
Lyrics: haiiyaa tar ram tam taaram he kyaa adaa kyaa jalave tere paaro o paaro dil ke tukade ho gae hazaaron are kyaa adaa kyaa jalave threedots  jaaegii ab jaan bhii merii aankh na maaro kyaa adaa kyaa jalave threedots  taubaa teraa ruup mere hosh udaa le jaae qaatil terii javaanii hai kaun tujhe samajhaae uf ye aankhen uf ye baahen teraa honaa dil ye chaahe kyaa adaa kyaa jalave threedots  aanaa chaahuun paas tere kyuun tuu mujhase bhaage tujhako to bas paanaa hai jo anjaam ho aage zindagii kaa tuu khazaanaa zindagii se tuu na jaanaa kyaa adaa kyaa jalave threedots  yahii hai right choice paaro ho paaro

Title: tadap tadap ke is dil se aah nikalatii rahii
Lyrics: bejaan dil ko 2 bejaan dil ko tere ishq ne zindaa kiyaa phir tere ishq ne hii is dil ko tabaah kiyaa tadap tadap ke is dil se aah nikalatii rahii mujhako sazaa dii pyaar kii aisaa kyaa gunaah kiyaa to lut gae haan lut gae to lut gae ham terii muhabbat men  ajab hai ishq yaaraa threedots  pal do pal kii kushiyaan gam ke kazaane milate hain phir milatii hain tanahaaiiyaan kabhii aansuu kabhii aahen kabhii shikave kabhii naale teraa cheharaa nazar aae teraa cheharaa nazar aae mujhe din ke ujaalon men terii yaaden tadapaaen terii yaaden tadapaaen raaton ke andheron men teraa cheharaa nazar aae machal machal ke is dil se aah nikalatii rahii mujhako sazaa dii threedots  agar mile kudaa to threedots puuchhuungaa kudaayaa jism mujhe de ke mittii kaa shiishe saa dil kyuun banaayaa aur usape dii ye fitarat ke vo karataa hai muhabbat vaah re vaah terii qudarat  vaah re vaah terii qudarat usape de dii ye qismat kabhii hai milan kabhii furaqat kabhii hai milan kabhii furaqat hai yahii kyaa vo muhabbat vaah re vaah terii qudarat sisak sisak ke is dil se aah nikalatii rahii mujhako sazaa dii threedots

Title: tumase milane ko main bekaraar huun
Lyrics: tumase milane ko main bekaraar huun jabase tujhe dekhaa sanam mujhako lagaa main teraa pyaar huun  tumase milane ko main bekaraar huun jisakaa tumhen thaa har ghadii main to vahii intazaar huun tumase milane ko main threedots  kuchh kahataa huun main tumase kuchh chhupaataa huun terii yaadon men din main bitaataa huun tujhe in aankhon men chhupaae baithii huun tere hii khvaabon ko sajaae baithii huun dhadakan terii betaab hai jaaneman main teraa karaar huun tumase milane ko main threedots  terii baahon men bahakane ko dil karataa hai in fizaaon men mahakane ko dil karataa hai mujhe terii chaahat ne bahut tadapaayaa hai milane kaa ye mausam sanam ab aayaa hai dolii piyaa le ke tuu aa tere sang chalane ko taiyaar huun tumase milane ko main threedots

Title: i love you  o merii niindon men tuu
Lyrics: o merii niindon men tuu mere khvaabon men tuu o merii dhadakan men tuu merii saanson men tuu mere chaaron taraf bas tuu tuu hii tuu  ajanabii hai abhii tuu mere des men o tuu nae ruup men main nae bhes men tujhako dekhaa to sab dil lage thaamane chaandanii kuchh nahiin hai tere saamane teraa cheharaa mile chaand se huu ba huu  kar sitamagar sitam yuun naa dil par mere aa samaa jaa mere dil men dilabar mere der achchhiii nahiin ishq ke khel men baith jaa tuu mere pyaar kii rail men main shuruu ho gayaa tuu bhii ho jaa shuruu

Title: duniyaa hasiinon kaa melaa  ik dost dhuundhataa huun
Lyrics: hai duniyaa hasiinon kaa melaa mele men ye dil akelaa ik dost dhuundhataa huun main dostii ke lie  yahaan vahaan idhar udhar chehare hain kitane hasiin magar jahaan ruke nazar suurat vo dekhii nahiin vo husn dhuundhataa huun main aashiqii ke lie duniyaa hasiinon kaa threedots  adaa nashaa nazar badan sab kuchh tere paas hai magar tuu vo ghataa nahiin jisakii mujhe pyaas hai ik jaam dhuundhataa huun main mayakashii ke lie duniyaa hasiinon kaa threedots

Title: ai chaandanii terii chaahaten dil se nahiin chhuut rahiin
Lyrics: ai chaandanii terii chaahaten dil se nahiin chhuut rahiin   saanson men hai terii aarazuu saansen nahiin tuut rahiin  tuu hai merii jaanejahaan itanaa na bhuul jaanaa  tere binaa jaanevafaa jaauun to jaauun kahaan   chaahatii ho tum kise ik baar bol do tum  kis ne hai teraa dil liyaa itanaa to bataa do tum  jaanevafaa jaanevafaa jiinaa kahaan ye to bataa  hamadam merii qismat merii kis baat se ruuth gaii   dekh le tuu ek nazar ai man ke miit sun le  zindagii tere naam hai gaatii hai priit sun le  tere pyaar men tere pyaar men dil jal rahaa meraa pyaar men  pahale se hii jo lut chukaa tuu phir kyuun luut rahii

Title: tanahaa tanahaa dil dhadake tanahaa dil ghabaraae
Lyrics: alakaa tanahaatanahaa dil dhadake tanahaa dil ghabaraae 2 do dil hamaraahii hon to donon manzil paaen aao ham paas aaen abhi tanahaatanahaa dil dhadake tanahaa dil ghabaraae 2 do dil hamaraahii hon to donon manzil paaen aao ham paas aaen  abhi donon ne ek sazaa hai paaii donon ko ghere hai ek tanahaaii alakaa hoa donon ne ek sazaa hai paaii donon ko ghere hai ek tanahaaii abhi kitane gam in par barase kitane donon hain tarase kaise bataaen abhi tanahaatanahaa dil dhadake tanahaa dil ghabaraae alakaa tanahaatanahaa dil dhadake tanahaa dil ghabaraae  abhi do dil hamaraahii hon to donon manzil paaen alakaa aao ham paas aaen  alakaa donon ko ek hii jaise gile hain donon ko duniyaa se gam hii mile hain abhi hoa donon ko ek hii jaise gile hain donon ko duniyaa se gam hii mile hain alakaa donon men pyaar ho behad  to donon milake shaayad gam ko bhulaaen alakaa tanahaatanahaa dil dhadake tanahaa dil ghabaraae abhi tanahaatanahaa dil dhadake tanahaa dil ghabaraae  alakaa do dil hamaraahii hon to donon manzil paaen abhi aao ham paas aaen alakaa aao ham paas aaen abhi aao ham paas aaen alakaa aao ham paas aaen

Title: kuchh to mere dil men ho rahaa hai
Lyrics: kuchh kuchh kuchh kuchh kuchh to mere dil men ho rahaa hai kahiin dard saa uthaa kahiin pyaas hai jagii kahiin aag lagii hai sajanaa kuchh to mere dil threedots  thodaa saa hosh hai thodaa khyaal hai kaisaa kaisaa lagataa hai puuchho naa dilarubaa meraa kyaa haal hai aisaa vaisaa lagataa hai tuune chhuaa jo jaaneman aane lagaa mazaa aisaa lagaa ki saharaa pe chhaaii kahiin ghataa kabhii ho rahii yahaan kabhii ho rahii vahaan jaane piir ye kahaan hai sajanaa kuchh to mere dil threedots  main bhii javaan huun tuu bhii javaan hai mausam bhii matavaalaa hai mere nasiib aa mere kariib aa kab se khud ko sambhaalaa hai dekhaa tujhe to dilajaanii aashiq banaa teraa tere lie mere dilabar goraa badan meraa merii niind kho gaii meraa chain kho gayaa mujhe pyaar ho gayaa hai sajanaa kuchh to mere dil threedots

Title: shambo shambo bole shambo  mastii pyaar ki duungii tumhen
Lyrics: shambo shambo bole shambo baanhon men tum le lo hamako  mohabbat kii duniyaa men le jaauun o jaanam aao tumako   mastii pyaar ki duungii tumhen kushiyaan sansaar kii duungii tumhen  aao tum dilarubaa baanhon men le luungii main tumhen   thodii pii le aajaa paas tuu de duungii jiine kii davaa  tuu kyaa jaane chhuu ke hii mujhe kushbuu laatii hai ye havaa  raajaa puune kaa aashiq meraa jayapur mahaaraajaa aashiq meraa  daaluun jis par ye tirachhii nazar ban jaaye majanuun meraa   hotii jo bhii mastii pyaar men saarii kii saarii duun tumhen  kaisii rangiin pyaarii shaam hai svarg de duungii main tumhen  teraa vaqt hai aayaa balam aajaa ho jaaye thodaa sitam  tere chhuune se jaaduu huaa janmon kii pyaasii sanam

Title: chandaa ne dii chaandanii  meraa munnaa ban gayaa
Lyrics: ka 	chandaa ne dii chaandanii suuraj ne dii roshanii 2 	phuulon ne diyaa rang to meraa munnaa ban gayaa 	ki meraa munnaa ban gayaa ku 	priit ne pyaar diyaa prem se pyaar liyaa 	milaa jo teraa sang to meraa munnaa ban gayaa 	ki meraa munnaa ban gayaa ka 	chandaa ne dii chaandanii threedots  	tuu mere man kii gangaa hai sadaa jo paavan rahatii hai ku 	tuu mere man kii jamunaa hai yug yug se bahatii hai ka 	sach hogaa sapanaa o mere sajanaa 	lagii jo tere ang to meraa munnaa ban gayaa ku 	chandaa ne dii chaandanii threedots  ka 	ye ghar meraa mandir hai tuu puujaa kii thaalii hai ku 	maan kii mamataa is thaalii men jot jalaane vaalii hai ka 	jiivan ke aadhaar tuu meraa shrringaar 	man men uthii tarang to meraa munnaa ban gayaa ku 	chandaa ne dii chaandanii threedots  	shabanam phuul kalii aur kiranon jaisii terii suurat hai ku 	mujhako salonii tere mere jaisii muurat hai ka 	mujhako milaa sammaan mere paavan dhaam 	khilaa hai sabakaa rang to meraa munnaa ban gayaa ku 	chandaa ne dii chaandanii threedots

Title: ham laakh chhupaaen pyaar magar duniyaa ko
Lyrics: ham laakh chhupaaen pyaar magar duniyaa ko pataa chal jaaegaa lekin chhup chhup ke milane se milane kaa mazaa to aaegaa  tum kitane bhole bhaale ho har baat ko khel samajhate ho main jab duniyaa kii kahataa huun tum apane dil kii kahatii ho yah pyaar hamaaraa rab jaane  jaane kyaa rang laaegaa  2 lekin chhup chhup ke threedots  ye mast havaa mahakii ye fizaa aankhon men nashaa saa chhaataa hai ik rang kushii kaa aataa hai ik rang kushii kaa jaataa hai ye miithaa miithaa dard mujhe din raat yuun hii tadapaaegaa lekin chhup chhup ke threedots  tum in baanhon ke ghere men aankhen band karake so jaao kal kyaa hogaa ye bhuul ke tum miithe sapanon men kho jaao main rakhavaalaa is tan man kaa jo hogaa dekhaa jaaegaa lekin chhup chhup ke threedots

Title: har taraf hai ye shor he aayaa gokul kaa chor
Lyrics: tujhaa gharaat naahiin paanii ghaaghar utaanii re gopaalaa are govindaa re gopaalaa govindaa re gopaalaa yashode chaa kaanyaavaadaa yashode chaa kaanyaavaadaa  are tolii banaa ke nikale gvaale karane ko hudadang govindaa ke din sab ho gae hain govindaa ke sang are samajhe har taraf hai ye shor he aayaa gokul kaa chor aaj ham log mastii karegaa kahiin matakii tode kahiin nainaa jode aaj gadabad ghotaalaa chalegaa har taraf hai ye shor threedots  aalaa re aalaa govindaa aalaa he chhat ke uupar khadii dekhanaa phulajhadii ham karenge koii chhedakhaanii o ham chale jhuumane aasamaan chuumane aaj mastii men hai zindagaanii haan de do duaaen maan jii maarenge ham to baajii dushman zamaanaa jalegaa har taraf hai ye shor threedots  dagaduu maamaa dagaduu maamaa petii vaazav maamaa petii vaazav don konbadyaa deiin naahiitar pathavuun sodav is galii us galii baat apanii chalii ho gayaa apanaa hii bolabaalaa re ha haa ho gayaa apanaa hii bolabaalaa ho josh men hosh kaa doston kaam kyaa hamase takkar na le koii saalaa ham sab hain dil ke raaje apanaa hii dankaa baaje apanaa hii sikkaa chalegaa har taraf hai ye shor threedots  bilkul chalegaa aalaa re aalaa govindaa aalaa

Title: uunchii hai building lift terii band hai
Lyrics: uunchii hai building lift terii band hai kaise main aauun dil razaamand hai aajaa aajaa aajaa band baajaa leke aajaa terii yaad sataae duulhe raajaa ab to aajaa kaise main aauun threedots  tere vaaste daud kar aauungaa main sau siidhiyon ko bhii chadh jaauungaa main tuu meraa dilabar hai aanaa padegaa tujhe meraa nakharaa uthaanaa padegaa aayaa tuufaan hai mushkil men jaan hai aanaa main chaahuun dil beiimaan hai uunchii hai building threedots  tuu aage aage main piichhe piichhe chumbak kii tarah tuu mujhako khiinche kahaan jaa rahaa hai ankhiyon ko miinche utanii hii duur tuu jitanii kariib hai aankh maaratii hai ladakii ajiib hai mumbaii band hai train nahiin chalatii bijalii band hai batii bhii gul hai kaise main aauun threedots

Title: ik hasiin nigaah kaa dil pe saayaa hai
Lyrics: ik hasiin nigaah kaa dil pe saayaa hai jaaduu hai junuun hai kaisii maayaa hai ye maayaa hai  paanv ke tale kahiin dil padaa mile agar chuum kar uthaaiye khuub dekh bhaal kar jo koii puuchh le to kyaa raah se uthaayaa hai ik hasiin nigaah kaa   threedots  chalii gayii vo manchalii pukaaruungaa galii galii vo le ke merii zindagii chalii chalii udhar chalii vo ruuthii ruuthii rahatii hai bahut bahut manaayaa hai vo ruuthii ruuthii rahatii hai bahut bahut manaayaa hai ik hasiin nigaah kaa   threedots  tere niilii aankh ke bhanvar bade hasiin hain duub jaane do mujhe ye kvaabon kii zamiin hai utha lo apanii palakon ko ye padraa kyon giraayaa hai ik hasiin nigaah kaa   threedots

Title: shaam se aankh men namii sii hai
Lyrics: shaam se aankh men namii sii hai aaj phir aapakii kamii sii hai shaam se aankh threedots  dafn kar do hamen ke saans mile nabz kuchh der se thamii sii hai aaj phir aapakii threedots  vaqt rahataa nahiin kahiin tik kar isakii aadat bhii aadamii sii hai aaj phir aapakii threedots  koii rishtaa nahiin rahaa phir bhii ek tasaliim laazamii sii hai shaam se aankh threedots

Title: achako machako kaa karuun raam
Lyrics: achako machako kaa karuun raam ho goraa mukhadaa hai haan achako machako kaa karuun raam meraa jiivan hai phulavaa kii daalii  achako machako kaa karuun raam jab jab dekhuun main aaiinaa sharm mujhe kyon aae anjaanii sii pyaas uthe koii naagin sii das jaae  koii kaantaa chubhaa kyaa are naa re naa kahiin dard huaa kyaa are naa naa naa chhod mujhe gorii naa kar joraa jorii baat kisii kii bhii main maanuun naa pahale gul thii ab gulanaar huii aisii haalat to pahalii baar huii ye javaanii badii dushvaar huii dhiire dhiire bachapan biitaa lambii ho gaii chotii jab se aaii mast javaanii ho gaii kurtii chhotii koii sapanon men aayaa are naa re naa saarii raat jagaayaa are naa re naa bol sakhii aise gazab huaa kaise ye kaisaa zahar hai main jaanuun naa merii cholii ke tuute sab dhaage dhak dhak jiyaraa pe current laage achako machako kaa karuun raam raam jaane kyaa hogaa aage achako machako kaa karuun threedots

Title: munde aur kudiyaan disko bhaangadaa karane
Lyrics: kudii kudii kudii kudii kudii munde aur kudiyaan disko bhaangadaa karane aaye hain haayo rabbaa haayo rabbaa aise karane vaalii saarii chiizen laaii hai munde aur kudiyaan threedots  milanaa hai mil kar kisii bahaane se raat ko na roko kisii paravaane se ham khul ke karenge pyaar ki ab kisii se naiyon daranaa munde aur kudiyaan threedots  mausam hai piine kaa pii lo yaar dilabar kii aankhon se haayo rabbaa haayo rabbaa usakii ravaanii kaa sokhiyaan zindagaanii kaa luut le mazaa javaanii kaa ham khul ke karenge pyaar ki ab naiyon daranaa munde aur kudiyaan threedots  inako bataao ye javaanii kaa mazaa hai do ghadii do pal kaa nashaa hai inako samajhaao ye zid par ad gae hain ki munde bigad gae hain are sab ke sab hairaan pade hain puuchhoo inake ghar jaake padhanaa likhanaa bhuul gae hain ye kudiyon ke hosh udaate hain vaqt inake aage hai par ye bigad gae hain munde aur kudiyaan threedots

Title: lo lo jii main aa gaii har dil pe chhaa gaii
Lyrics: lo lo jii main aa gaii har dil pe chhaa gaii jo bhii yahaan mujhako dekhe vo to yahii hans ke bole vaah re vaah lo lo jii main aa gaii haan  ruup hai sirf dhokhaa pahachaan le haan baat dil kii diivaane ab maan le o merii jaan maanegaa naa kahanaa meraa pachhtaaegaa lo lo jii main threedots  hosh men aa anaadii zaraa soch le haan kyaa se kyaa ho gaii main zaraa dekh le jaanevafaa tujhape meraa jaaduu nayaa chal jaaegaa lo lo jii main threedots

Title: jo giit nahiin janamaa vo giit banaaenge
Lyrics: jo giit nahiin janamaa vo giit banaaenge tere pyaar kaa sur lekar sangiit banaaenge jo giit nahiin janamaa threedots  koii sukh bhii nahiin apanaa koii duhkh bhii nahiin apanaa duniyaa jise kahate hain hai sundar ik sapanaa is khvaab ko bhii apane nagamon se sajaaenge tere pyaar kaa sur lekar threedots  rah jaae to rastaa hai mil jaae to manzil hai jo pyaar samajhataa hai sab kahate use dil hain har saaj se ham dil kii aavaaz milaaenge tere pyaar kaa sur lekar threedots  ye sach hai mohabbat kaa dushman ye zamaanaa hai kahiin duur pahaadii par ghar apanaa banaanaa hai ham jhuuthe rivaajon kii diivaar giraaenge tere pyaar kaa sur lekar threedots

Title: kaise jiuungaa main agar tuu na banii merii saahibaan
Lyrics: kaise jiuungaa main agar tuu na banii merii saahibaan duub maruungii main agar main na banii terii saahibaan  laakhon hazaaron men saiyaan maine chun liyaa laakhon hazaaron ne faisalaa ye sun liyaa ek duuje ke vaaste ham bane mere saajanaa merii saahibaan threedots  raaten guzaratii hain saarii raat jaag ke dil chaahe aa jaauun ghar se main bhaag ke o aanaa magar dolii men baith kar merii saahibaan merii saahibaan threedots  kahatii hai kyaa mujhase paayal tere paanv kii ek siidhii saadii sii ladakii main gaanv kii tere honthon kii baansurii ban gaii mere saajanaa  terii saahibaan threedots

Title: thii wasl men bhii fikrejudaaii tamaam shab
Lyrics: thii wasl men bhii fikrejudaaii tamaam shab wo aaye bhii to niind na aaii tamaam shab  yak baar dekhate hii mujhe gash jo aa gayaa bhuule the wo bhii hoshrubaaii tamaam shab  mar jaate kyuun na subaho ke hote hii hijr men takaliif kaisii kaisii uthaaii tamaam shab  garmejawaabeshikawaaejaureuduu rahaa us sholaabuu ne jaan jalaaii tamaam shab  momin main apane naalon ke sadaqe ke kahate hain unako bhii aaj niind na aaii tamaam shab

Title: ab mujhe raat din tumhaaraa hii khyaal hai
Lyrics: ab mujhe raat din tumhaaraa hii khyaal hai kyaa kahuun pyaar men diivaanon jaisaa haal hai diivaanon jaisaa haal hai tumhaaraa hii khyaal hai  tujhako dekhe binaa chain milataa nahiin dil pe ab to koii zor chalataa nahiin jaaduu hai kaisaa dil kii lagii men duub gayaa huun is bekhudii men ab mujhe raat din threedots  har pal dhuundhen nazar tumako hii jaaneman had se badhane lagaa meraa diivaanaapan dil men basaa luun apanaa banaa luun yaa phir nazar men tumako chhupaa luun ab mujhe raat din threedots

Title: tum mere ho bas mere hii mere ho
Lyrics: tum mere ho bas mere hii mere ho puuchh lo havaaon se suramaii ghataaon se baarishon ke paanii se puuchho nadiyaa diivaanii se tum mere ho bas threedots  aankhon kii galiyon se aa ke ruuh men tum bas jaao saath chalen aur saath ruken saanson men yuun mil jaao puuchh lo khyaalon men baadalon kii shaalon se khvaahishon se sapanon se puuchho gairon se yaa apanon se tum mere ho bas threedots  main tumako mahasuus karuun ban jaao tum ehasaas ek duuje ko dekh naa paauun aa jaao itane paas puuchh lo bahaaron se champaii nazaaron se khushbuon kii vaadii se puuchho is rut shahazaadii se tum mere ho bas threedots

Title: kyaa ye sach hai tumako bhii mujhase pyaar ho gayaa
Lyrics: he he he he he he he he kyaa ye sach hai tumako bhii mujhase pyaar ho gayaa nigaahon ne jo kahaa nigaahon ne jo sunaa sach hai kyaa bolo zaraa  sharamaaii sii hain aankhen magar honthon pe halkii hansii hai akhir tumhaare andaaz men kyaa baat hai jo chhupii hai bechain huun main ke tumase sunuun main dil men tumhaare hai kyaa sach hai kyaa bolo zaraa  kaise bataauun kaise kahuun mere lie kaun ho tum tumase milii hai manzil mujhe varanaa main hone ko thii gum tum saath laae mohabbat ke saae kvaabon ke jaisii fizaa haan sach kahaa sach kahaa  haan ye sach hai tumase hii mujhako pyaar ho gayaa nigaahon ne jo kahaa nigaahon ne jo sunaa haan sach kahaa sach kahaa   o pyaar men duubii ye dhadakanen pahale hii mujhako sunaatiin raste men thokar lag jaae to lagatii hai der aate aate ab jo saath hain ham kyuun ho koii gam ab jo saath hain ham to kyuun ho koii gam jo bhii huaa so huaa kyaa ye sach hai  haan ye sach hai tumako bhii mujhase pyaar ho gayaa tumase hii mujhako pyaar ho gayaa nigaahon ne jo kahaa nigaahon ne jo sunaa sach hai kyaa haan sach kahaa sach hai kyaa bolo zaraa haan

Title: ai doston gorii kanvaarii sii hasiinaa ke  diidaar ho gayaa
Lyrics: ai doston gorii kanvaarii sii hasiinaa ke bhiige gulaabii narm honthon kaa jhiil sii niilii niilii aankhon kaa diidaar ho gayaa mujhako pyaar ho gayaa  samajhe na koii bhii ishaaraa aankhen jhukaae muskaae baaten karuun bhii to kaise dekho mujhe to sharam aae dil ko churaaen usakii adaaen usako nihaaren merii nigaahen jaane na vo dilarubaa ai doston gorii kanvaarii threedots  chandaa ke mukhade pe dekho zulfon kaa pardaa giraae gairon ke paas hai baithii mere kariib na aae diivaanaa kar de usakii javaanii le angadaaii aise diivaanii chhaa jaae dil pe nashaa ai doston gorii kanvaarii threedots

Title: sitaaron kii mahafil men  are dil ne dil ko pukaaraa
Film: kaho naa pyaar hai believe in love
Lyrics: sitaaron kii mahafil men guunjegaa taraanaa ki honthon pe aayaa hai dil kaa fasaanaa are dil ne dil ko pukaaraa lo main aayaa milane dubaaraa manzil he he he pyaar tumhaaraa ho ho ho main huun saagar tum ho kinaaraa sitaaron kii mahafil threedots  ajab shaam hai ye pyaar kii pahaluu men sabake yaar hai ajab raat hai jazbaat kii pahaluu men pyaar hii pyaar hai ye pyaar tumhaaraa ye pyaar hamaaraa hai kuub nazaaraa zamaanaa usii kaa hai saaraa zamaanaa ki jisane bhii siikhaa hai pyaar nibhaanaa are dil ne dil ko threedots  kadam aaen hain us mod pe ham tum hain jahaan saamane nazar se nazar karane ab lagii baaten bade hii raaz se ye raaz tumhaaraa ye raaz hamaaraa kare hai kyaa ishaaraa nishaane pe dil hai ke dil pe nishaanaa diivaanaa hai apanii hii dhun men diivaanaa are dil ne dil ko threedots

Title: aashiqii men har aashiq ho jaataa hai majabuur  is men dil kaa kyaa kasuur
Singer: kumar sanu anuradha paudwal sadhana sargam
Lyrics: aashiqii men har aashiq ho jaataa hai majabuur is men dil kaa mere dil kaa is men dil kaa kyaa kasuur aashiqii men har aashiq threedots  nigaahen na milatii na ye pyaar hotaa na main tujhase milatii na izahaar hotaa mere aashiq mere dilabar mere jaanejaan ab tere bin ek pal na jiinaa yahaan tujh se mil ke kaisaa chhaayaa hai suruur is men dil kaa threedots  na puuchho kaisii hai ye bekaraarii mohabbat kii pyaasii hai ye duniyaa saarii na jaane dil kisakaa kab kho jaae haan yahii chaahat kaa aksar hotaa hai dastuur is men dil kaa threedots

Title: tum jo mile ham ko tum jo mile ho
Lyrics: shriikumaar are tum jo mile hamako tum jo mile ho ab jaane kyaa ho tum jo mile ho ho tumako pataa ab honaa hai kyaa to hamako bhii samajhaao o o o aashaa ho tum jo mile hamako tum jo mile ho ab jaane kyaa ho tum jo mile ho ye aankh jhukii ye saans rukii zaraa hamako sahaaraa do shriikumaar tum jo mile hamako tum jo mile ho aashaa ab jaane kyaa ho tum jo mile ho  shriikumaar dil diivaanaa kab thaa jaanaa hotaa hai pyaar kyaa tan kii chaandii man kaa sonaa baanhon kaa haar kyaa 2 tum aa gae to dil kahe aaii bahaar kyaa aashaa tum jo mile hamako  shriikumaar tum jo mile hamako   aashaa tumako paayaa hosh ganvaayaa aur ab ye haal hai bahakii nazaren bahakii adaaen bahakiisii chaal hai  2 main kyaa karuun kaise kahuun ki hai kumaar kyaa shriikumaar tum tum tum tum tum jo mile hamako tum jo mile ho aashaa ab jaane kyaa ho tum jo mile ho

Title: chaand saa lallaa ghar aayaa hai
Lyrics: haay haay mubaarak ho mubaarak ho haay ladakaa huaa hai haay chaand saa lallaa ghar aayaa hai haay main vaarii jaauun aasamaan se utar kar kamar aa gayaa chaand saa lallaa maan tere ghar aa gayaa  ab masarrat kii baajengii shahanaaiiyaan aur phuulon se mahakengii anganaaiiyaan terii nazaron kaa ai jamiilaa zaraa jam ke hilaa terii nazaron kaa nuurenazar aa gayaa chaand saa lallaa threedots  haay tumako hamaarii umar lag jaae maan husn ke tere ye aks hain gahare baap aur bete ke ek jaise chehare munne ke abbaa haay haay tum kahaan the ab tak haay haay chhodenge na tumako haay haay kuchh mile na jab tak haay haay munne kii ammaa haay haay shauhar ko bolo haay haay kuchh gaanth rupayon kii haay haay jaldii se kholo haay haay munne ke abbaa jii aise naa bolo haay haay sab gher lo milakar haay haay are jeb tatolo haay haay are naach naach ke apanaa nikal gayaa juice are munne teraa abbbaa badaa hii kanjuus biich vaalon kaa ai maatii milii zaraa uchhaal biich vaalon kaa dekho juluus aa gayaa chaand saa lallaa threedots

Title: sabakii baaraaten aaiin dolii tuu bhii laanaa
Lyrics: ho raanjhe majiiyaan charaaiiyaan dolii le gae ne kede ve lag gae nain avede o lag gae nain avede ve lag gae nain avede  sabakii baaraaten aaiin dolii tuu bhii laanaa dulhan banaake hamako raajaajii le jaanaa sabakii baaraaten aaiin threedots  chaahaa thaa maine sochaa thaa maine kyaa kyaa the aramaan dilenaadaan ke aankhon men aansuu aae par koii na aayaa ab to kisii ko bhii apanaa ke hai bulaanaa sabakii baaraaten aaiin threedots  in aankhon men thii ik raat sajii haathon men kabhii chuudii sii bajii par aankh khulii to aayaa nazar naa raat sajii naa chuudii bajii meraa tuutaa thaa dil usakii jhanakaar thii saaraa vo rang thaa mere khuunedil kaa ye to hai ronaa dil kaa kaahe kaa taraanaa ab to kisii ko bhii apanaa ke hai bulaanaa sabakii baaraaten aaiin threedots  chalo jo bhii huaa vo khuub huaa ab har koii mahabuub huaa hai sabake lie ye raat merii ab to hai yahii aukaat merii hans ke bhiigii palak chamakaanaa hai suunii baahen adaa se laharaanaa hai gam khaa ke aansuu pii ke mahafil men gaanaa ab to kisii ko bhii apanaa ke hai bulaanaa sabakii baaraaten aaiin threedots sabakii baaraaten aaiin dolii tuu bhii laanaa dulhan banaake hamako raajaajii le jaanaa sabakii baaraaten aaiin threedots  baandh ke seharaa hamase mil ke nikalenge saare aramaan dil ke aankhon men taare naachen ghunghataa yuu uthaanaa phir hamako haule haule baahon men chhupaanaa sabakii baaraaten aaiin threedots  apanon se judaa main hotii huii kuchh hansatii huii kuchh rotii huii jab chhoduungii baabul kii galii tumhare anganaa aauungii chalii jab tanaman se terii banuungii gorii baiiyaan merii dharanaa haule se mehandii vaale haathon kii chuudii khanakaanaa phir haule haule mujhako baahon men chhupaanaa sabakii baaraaten aaiin threedots  phir bindiyaaa kii sab chaandaniyaan aur paayal kii sab raaginiyaan tere ghar sansaar men lutaa degii dulhe raajaa terii dulhaniyaa pahale tum khelanaa mere rang ruup se phir chun daalanaa ang ang kii kaliyaan kore tan ke phuulon se sejiyaa sajaanaa phir haule haule hamako baahon men chhupaanaa sabakii baaraaten aaiin threedots

Title: kabhii to shaam dhale apane ghar gae hote
Lyrics: kabhii to shaam dhale apane ghar gae hote kisii kii aankh men rahakar sanvar gae hote gazal ne bahate hue phuul lie varnaa gamon men duub kar ham log mar gae hote aavaaraa havaa kaa jhonkaa huun aa nikalaa huun pal do pal ke lie  daulat na koii taazamahal chhod jaaenge ham apanii yaadagaar gazal chhod jaaenge tum jitanii chaaho hamaarii hasiin udaao ruuthaa huaa magar kal chhod jaaenge aa nikalaa huun threedots  pahachaan apanii duur talak chhod jaauungaa khaamoshiyon kii maut ganvaaraa nahiin mujhe shiishaa huun tuut kar khanak bhii chhod jaauungaa aa nikalaa huun threedots  tum aaj to patthar barasaa lo kal rooge mujh paagal ke lie khushbuu na sahii rangat na sahii phir bhii hai vo ghar kaa nazaraanaa  phuul mazaar tak nahiin pahunchaa daamaneyaar tak nahiin pahunchaa ho gayaa vo kafan se to aazaad phir bhii gulazaar tak nahiin pahunchaa phir bhii hai vo threedots  jo tiir bhii aataa vo khaalii nahiin jaataa maayuus mere dar se savaalii nahiin jaataa are kaante hii kiyaa karate hain phuulon kii hifaazat phuulon ko bachaane koii maalii nahiin jaataa phir bhii hai vo threedots  patajhad se churaa kar laayaa huun do phuul tere aanchal ke lie maikvaar ko itanaa hosh kahaan rishte kii hakiikat ko samajhe  zark se badh ke to itanaa nahiin maangaa jaataa pyaas lagatii hai to dariyaa nahiin maangaa jaataa aur chaand jaisii bhii ho betii magar uunche gharavaalon se rishtaa nahiin maangaaa jaataa rishte kii hakiikat threedots  ek ek saans usake lie qatlagaah thii usake gunaah the vo begunaah thii vo ek mitii huii sii ibaarat banii rahii cheharaa khulii kitaab kaa kismat siyaah thii shahanaaiyaan use bhii bulaatii rahiin magar har mod par dahez kii qurbaanagaah thii vo chaahatii thii use saunp de magar us aadamii kii sirf badan pe nigaah thii rishte kii hakiikat threedots  betii kaa saudaa kar daalaa daaruu kii ek botal ke lie dil aur jigar to kuchh bhii nahiin ik baar ishaaraa to kar de  aaj vo bhii ishq ke maare nazar aane lage unakii bhii niind ud gaii unako bhii taare nazar aane lage aankh viiraan dil pareshaan zulf barahan lab khaamosh ab to vo kuchh aur bhii pyaare nazar aane lage ik baar ishaaraa to kar de ai aaiine jo tumhen kam pasand karate hain ik baar ishaaraa to threedots  main khud ko jalaa bhii sakataa huun terii aankhon ke kaajal ke lie ham log hain aise diivaane jo zid pe kabhii aa jaaen to  ishq men jo bhii muqatilaa hogaa usakaa andaaz bhii judaa hogaa aur bhaav kyon gir gayaa hai sone kaa usane piital pahan liyaa hogaa jo zid pe kabhii threedots  shahar kii ek amiirazaadii ko kal in aankhon se maine dekhaa thaa thiik us vaqt mufalisii ne merii hans ke meraa mijaaz puuchhaa thaa jo zid pe kabhii threedots  seharaa uthaa kar laaenge jhanakaar terii paayal ke lie ye khel tamaashaa lagataa hai taqadiir ke gulashan kaa shaayad  phuul ke saath saath gulashan men sochataa huun babuul bhii honge kyaa huaa usane bevafaaii kii usake apane usuul bhii honge taqadiir ke gulashan threedots  yuun badii der se paimaanaa lie baithaa huun koii dekhe vo ye samajhe pie baithaa huun zindagii bhar ke lie ruuth ke jaane vaale main abhii tak tasviir lie baithaa huun taqadiir ke gulashan threedots  kaante hain mere daaman ke lie phuul tere aanchal ke lie

Title: tumane jo kahaa maine vo sunaa
Lyrics: tumane jo kahaa maine vo sunaa sun ke maine jo sapanaa bunaa dekho usako tod na denaa tanhaa mujhako chhod na denaa har gam se bachaa luungaa main rakhanaa yaad apanaa vaadaa baahon men chhupaa luungaa main kar lo pakkaa iraadaa tumane jo kahaa maine threedots  tumako har pal chaahuungii main rakhanaa yaad apanaa vaadaa tumhaarii ban jaauungii main kar lo pakkaa iraadaa tumane jo kahaa maine threedots  zindagii men agar aae mod koii ho na jaanaa kahiin tum judaa raat ho yaa ho din gam ho yaa ho khushii main tumhaaraa rahuungaa sadaa tum bin maanegaa naa ye man rakhanaa yaad apanaa vaadaa tuutegaa naa ab ye bandhan kar lo pakkaa iraadaa tumane jo kahaa maine threedots  tumase milane se pahale main thaa bekhabar pyaar kyaa hai muhabbat hai kyaa ab tumhen zindagii bhar kaa main hamasafar maan luun ye ijaazat hai kyaa jiivan bhar tumako chaahuungaa rakhanaa yaad apanaa vaadaa tumako hii apanaauungaa kar lo pakkaa iraadaa tumane jo kahaa maine threedots

Title: rut aa gaii re rut chhaa gaii re
Lyrics: rut aa gaii re rut chhaa gaii re  piiliipiilii sarason phuule  piilepiile patte jhuumen  piihuupiiihuu papihaa bole  chal baag men  dhamakdhamak dholak baaje  chhanakchhanak paayal chhanake  khanakkhanak kanganaa bole  chal baag men  chunarii jo terii udatii hai ud jaane de  bindiyaa jo terii giratii hai gir jaane de    giiton kii mauj aaii  phuulon kii fauj aaii  nadiyaa men jo dhuup ghulii sonaa bahaa  ambuaa se hai lipatii ek bel bele kii  tuu hii mujh se hai duur aa paas aa  mujh ko tuu saanson se chhuu le  jhuul in baahon ke jhuule  pyaar thodaa saa mujhe de ke  mere jaanodil tuu le    tuu jab yuun sajatii hai  ek dhuum machatii hai  saarii galiyon men saare baazaar men  aanchal basantii hai us men se chhanatii hai  jo mainne puujii hai muurat tihaare men  jaane kaisii hai ye dorii  main bandhaa huun jis se gorii  tere nainon ne merii niindon kii kar lii hai chorii

Title: dil jo hamaaraa aahen na bharataa  to duniyaa men koii muhabbat
Lyrics: dil jo hamaaraa aahen na bharataa to duniyaa men koii muhabbat na karataa dil jo hamaaraa threedots  na khushii koii hotii na aankhon men paanii sazaa ban gaii hotii ye zindagaanii binaa isake jo yuun hii jiivan guzarataa dil jo hamaaraa threedots  mohabbat kii kiimat lagaaii na jaae na mausam agar yuun machalakar ubharataa dil jo hamaaraa threedots

Title: aajaa aajaa aa ab aa sun le sadaa dil kii  mere hamasafar jaanejigar

Title: jiine vaalon o jiine vaalon  jiivan chhuk chhuk gaadii kaa khel
Lyrics: jiine vaalon o jiine vaalon jiivan chhuk chhuk gaadii kaa khel koii kahiin pe bichhad gayaa kisii se ho gayaa mel jiine vaalon o jiine vaalon threedots  aage guard driver hai piichhe guard muqaddar hai vo siitii vo hii bajaataa hai jhandii harii dikhaataa hai kabhii chale patarii pe kabhii patarii se utar jaae rel jiine vaalon o jiine vaalon threedots  siitii bajii gaadii chal dii tum badalo kaantaa jaldii bahate aansuon ko roko aur hansii kaa signal do jiine vaalon o jiine vaalon threedots  meraa station guzar gayaa hai main raste men utar gayaa merii manzil badal gaii gaadii aage nikal gaii binaa ticket  main pakadaa gayaa siidhaa pahunch gayaa jel jiine vaalon o jiine vaalon threedots

Title: tumhiin ne merii zindagii kharaab kii hai
Lyrics: tumhiin ne merii zindagii kharaab kii hai tumhaare lie hii maine sharaab pii hai tumhiin ne merii threedots  maine to tumase pyaar kiyaa chaahat pe yakiin diladaar kiyaa main paagal aashiq bechaaraa mujhe hans hans ke tumane maaraa ai kaash pataa pahale hotaa hokar barabaad na main rotaa tumhiin ne merii threedots  koii naa puuchhe kyuun piitaa huun ab pii pii ke main jiitaa huun jo aadat pad gaii piine kii to aag bujhii mere siine kii in haathon men jab jaam milaa mujhako thodaa aaraam milaa tumhiin ne merii threedots

Title: kanganaa kanvaare kanganaa  tere bin mere din na katen
Lyrics: kanganaa kanvaare kanganaa sajanaa pukaaren teraa naam bindiyaa ye terii bindiyaa dekhuun main subahoshaam tere bin mere din na katen na katen merii rainaa ab to kahiin bhii ek pal aae naa chainaa kanganaa kanvaare threedots  menhadii lagaauungii main to tere pyaar kii khushbuu lutaauungii tujhape bahaar kii ban jaauun main teraa kajaraa ban jaauun main teraa gajaraa dekhe tujhako hanse kajaraa meraa man ye kahe tere man kaa banuun main gahanaa tere bin mere din na katen threedots  lipataa rahuungaa main to tere ang se rang churaauungaa gorii tere rang se sun to zaraa kyaa kahe jhumakaa dil dhadakaae teraa thumakaa terii raah nihaaren sadaa ab to mere nainaa ab to kahiin bhii threedots  saiyaan terii yaad men zindagii guzaar duun terii tasviir aankhon men utaar luun tere lie hai meraa jiivan jaldii se banaa mujhako dulhan ab ho ke judaa tumase mujhako nahiin rahanaa tere bin mere din na katen threedots

Title: guunj rahaa hai dil men  gahariiniilii shaam
Lyrics: jaaved tumhaaraa naam merii dhadakanon men shaamil hai tumhaaraa naam merii saanson men basaa hai tumhaaraa naam mere tanbadan men zindagii banake rahataa hai sun sako to suno ki in fizaaon ke honthon par bhii tumhaaraa hii naam hai aa sako to aa jaao ki mere saath ye fizaaen bhii sadiyon se tumhaare intazaar men hain  alakaa guunj rahaa hai dil men na jaane kabase tumhaaraa naam aao rastaa dekh rahii hai gahariiniilii shaam gahariiniilii shaam  baadal parabat jhiil parinde jharane phuul havaa puuchh rahe hain ye sab mujhase tum aaoge kyaa tum aaoge kyaa inakii umiiden mere sapane hone na do naakaam aao rastaa dekh rahii hai gahariiniilii shaam gahariiniilii shaam  sar ko jhukaae ped khade hain gumasum hain raahen main huun gam hai tanahaaii hai aur thandii aahen aur thandii aahen ab aa jaao hone nahiin do pyaar kaa ye anjaam aao rastaa dekh rahii hai gahariiniilii shaam gahariiniilii shaam

Title: chaandanii raat bhar jagaayegii
Singer: chhaya ganguly spoken lines by anita kanwar
Lyrics: chaandanii raatabhar jagaayegii aaj phir niind nahiin aayegii 2 chaandanii raat  kaisii hai ye ajiib sii tanhaaii niind kyaa meraa ghar bhuul gayii har chaharaa sawaalii lagataa hai bharaa huaa ghar khaalii lagataa hai  mere qadamon se lipatii bechainii 2 aaj jaane kahaan le jaayegii  chaandanii raat chaandanii raatabhar jagaayegii aaj phir niind nahiin aayegii chaandanii raat  mere paas kyaa hai jo koii aayegaa mujhe dekhegaa aur ruk jaayegaa phir kyaa koii nahiin aayegaa ab yahaan koii nahiin aayegaa  ye kisakaa intazaar hai mujhe 2 kisake aane kii kabar laayegii  chaandanii raat chaandanii raatabhar jagaayegii aaj phir niind nahiin aayegi chaandanii raat

Title: pyaar ke lie chaar pal kam nahiin the
Lyrics: pyaar ke lie chaar pal kam nahiin the kabhii tum nahiin the kabhii ham nahiin the pyaar ke hasiin kab ye mausam nahiin the kabhii tum nahiin the threedots  ye din barason ke baad aayaa kuchh tumhen kuchh hamen yaad aayaa kasak phir ye dil men uthii hai honthon pe baat aake rukii hai kabhii itane majabuur to ham nahiin the pyaar ke lie threedots  agar tum ye dil maang lete jaaneman ham tumhen jaan dete ye kaise ham bhuul jaate mar ke bhii tum hamen yaad aate tumhen hai pataa bevafaa ham nahiin the pyaar ke lie threedots

Title: vallaah ye ladakii naazuk sii ladakii jise dekhake pyaar aae
Lyrics: vallaah ye ladakii naazuk sii ladakii jise dekhake pyaar aae jab do yaaron ke biich aa jaae yaarii men daraar aae  vallaah ye ladakii taubaa taubaa re naazuk sii ladakii are baabaa re jise dekhake pyaar aae o yaa yaa yaa jab do yaaron ke dekho dekho naa  biich aa jaae socho socho naa yaarii men daraar aae  o gorii churaae dil chorii churaae dil chorii vallaah ye ladakii threedots  yuun isakii nazar diladaar bhii hai phir jaae to ye talavaar bhii hai isakii gulabadanii par mat jaa are gul hii nahiin ye khaar bhii hai sholaa hai lekin shabanam sii thandii jise dekhake pyaar aae jab do yaaron ke threedots  kare khel ye kvaahishamandon se ham jaise kunvaare bandon se duniyaa men agar kuchh karanaa hai to duur zaraa in phandon se phir bhii ye zaalim aisii hai dilakash jise dekhake pyaar aae jab do yaaron ke threedots

Title: ik ladakii hai diivaanii sii us ladakii pe main marataa huun
Lyrics: ik ladakii hai diivaanii sii us ladakii pe main marataa huun jo dekhuun to sharamaatii hai is adaa se mohabbat main karataa huun  ik ladakaa hai anjaanaa saa us ladake pe main maratii huun jo dekhuun to ghabaraataa hai is adaa se mohabbat main karatii huun ik ladakii hai threedots  dil men tamannaa jagaa ke chorii se palaken jhukaanaa usane to pahalii nazar men mujhako banaayaa diivaanaa usake binaa kaise rahuun karanaa hai jo kaise kahuun kuchh bhii bataane se daratii huun ik ladakaa hai threedots  ab to yahii aarazuu hai usape vafaaen lutaa duun saanson men usake basaa ke donon jahaan ko bhulaa duun niinden merii le ke gaii dardejigar de ke gaii raat aahen main bharataa huun ik ladakii hai threedots

Title: jungle hai aadhii raat hai lagane lagaa hai dar
Lyrics: duniyaa ko bhuul jaauun kuchh aisii baat kar darane vaalii kyaa baat hai jab saath men hai dilabar aajaa merii baahon men so jaa rakh ke sar haay jungle hai aadhii raat threedots  dil men kyaa hotii hai halachal betaabii chhaaii hai palapal gaalon kii rangat luun le le o main to yahii chaahatii huun tanhaaii kaa aalam taare bhii soe hain ham bhii ik duuje kii chahat men khoe hain baahar mausam sardii kaa kyuun garmii hai andar haay jungle hai aadhii raat threedots  tujhe paagal main kar duun kar de aagosh men bhar luun bhar le haay siine se lag jaauun lag jaa ho ye lo sanam aa gaii ho aankh to khulii hai lekin tum so gaii ho jaanataa huun main tum diivaanii ho gaii ho ham donon aaj akele koii bhii naa ghar par

Title: yah log puuchhate hain mujhe kitanaa pyaar hai
Lyrics: yah log puuchhate hain mujhe kitanaa pyaar hai kaise bataauun tujhape dilojaan nisaar hai  yah log puuchhate hain mujhe kitanaa pyaar hai kaise bataauun tuu meraa hamadam hai yaar hai hamaraaz hamasafar hai meraa hamanavaa hai tuu dil men jo mere baat hai sab jaanataa hai tuu  milate hii tum se dil ko ye ehasaas ho gayaa rishtaa meraa tumhaaraa koii khaas ho gayaa duniyaa men isase badhake bhii kyaa koii pyaar hai kaise bataauun tujhape threedots  vah dostii hai jo ye karishmaa dikhaa sake ik buund men bhii pyaar kaa saagar samaa sake taakat hai sirf pyaar men yah gul khilaa sake patthar ko bhii taraash ke hiiraa banaa sake tuu hii mere nasiib kii pahalii bahaar hai kaise bataauun tujhape threedots

Lyrics: ku 	aa ye hasiin raat mohabbat men guzaar den 	dil kii kashtii pyaar ke saagar men utaar den 2 a 	aa ye hasiin raat threedots  ku 	kyaa pataa kal kyaa ho kal kaa nahiin bharosaa 	maaluum nahiin kis pal de ye zindagaanii dhokhaa a 	aisaa hone se pahale kahiin khone se pahale 	ek duusare ko ham jii bhar ke pyaar den ku 	dil kii kashtii pyaar ke threedots  	ek aag sii lagii hai siine men hasaraton kii 	barasaa do ghataaen tum mujhape chaahaton kii 	honthon kii naramii se saanson kii garmii se 	bechain umangon ko hans ke nikaal den a 	dil kii kashtii pyaar ke threedots

Lyrics: ku 		 	haan merii jaanejaan mere paas aa zaraa 	ab kahiin mujhako chain aae naa 	bin tere meraa man lagataa nahiin  ka 	diivaanaa diivaanaa tuu meraa diivaanaa 	ho mere jaanejaan sun le merii sadaa 	ab kahiin mujhako chain aae naa 	bin tere meraa dil lagataa nahiin ku 	diivaanaa diivaanaa main threedots  ka 	baanhon men tuune liyaa dhadakan machalane lagii ku 	chhaaii koii bekhudii har saans jalane lagii ka 	pyaas badhane lagii kyaa huaa kyaa pataa ku 	diivaanaa diivaanaa main threedots  	mil ke banaaen chalo ham ik nayaa aashiyaan ka 	tuu jo mujhe mil gayaa mujhako mile do jahaan ku 	tuutegaa na kabhii vaadaa ye pyaar kaa ka 	diivaanaa diivaanaa main threedots

Title: gheradaar ghaagharo  duungar uupar duungarii re
Lyrics: gheradaar ghaagharo lachchhedaar chundadii agge pichchhe easy hai romance o baby duungar uupar duungarii re usape naache mor mere saare diivaane karate hain dekho shor he gheradaar ghaagharo threedots  ye dilavaale matavaale hain mere chaahane vaale piichhe aate hain jaauun main jahaan koii dil men hii marataa hai koii aahen bhii bharataa hai koii mujhe pukaare sun le merii jaan are duungar uupar threedots har din ye paagal mujhako karate hain kitanaa bore he he gheradaar ghaagharo threedots  tumhen kyaa khabar mere dil men bhii koii miithii miithii aag hai mere tanabadan ko ye lagataa hai jaise das rahaa koii naag hai mujhe thiik se ye pataa nahiin ki main raah kisakii huun dekhatii koii aaegaa koii aaegaa mere dil kaa ab yahii raag hai ik din to koii aaegaa jo rang nayaa laaegaa vo aaegaa to badalegaa samaan sholaa saa koii bhadakegaa dil zor zor dhadakegaa machalegaa jo dil men koii aramaan duungar uupar threedots aaegaa ik naa ik din to mere dil kaa chor he gheradaar ghaagharo threedots

Title: baahon men aao zaraa kahanii hain baaten kaii
Film: ek thaa dil ek thi dhadkan
Lyrics: baahon men aao zaraa kahanii hain baaten kaii siikhii hain tumane kahaan aisii adaaen naii ho nain milaate hii chain ganvaate hii diivaanagii aa gaii baahon men aao threedots  dhadakan kii taal pe saanson ke saaj par chaahat kii raaganii paas aakar suno kaliyaan hain khvaab kii merii aankhon men khilii inhen apanii in hasiin palakon se chuno khvaabon ke hain ye nae nae silasile  abhii kal hii to ham tum se mile rahane do kuchh faasale baahon men aao threedots

Title: paan kaa ek biidaa  phir chaal dekho banaarasii baabuu kii
Lyrics: paan kaa ek biidaa khilaa do phir chaal dekho banaarasii baabuu kii isamen thodaa saa zardaa milaa do phir chaal dekho banaarasii baabuu kii chaal dekho banaarasii baabuu threedots  honthon ke pyaale rasiile nain tumhaare nashiile gorii patalii kamar tum hilaa do phir chaal dekho threedots  andaaz meraa hai sabase niraalaa buddhuu naa samajho main huun bholaa bhaalaa zaraa gangaa kaa paanii pilaa do phir chaal dekho threedots  main bigade logon ko raaste pe laauun main achchhe achchhon ke chhakke chhudaauun ho mere haathon bambuu dilaa do phir chaal dekho threedots

Title: jaane kyaa haal ho is dil kaa agar tuu aaye
Lyrics: jaane kyaa haal ho is dil kaa agar tuu aaye na to jazbaat pe na kud pe hii qaabuu aaye  chaarjaanib terii parachaaii nazar aatii hai tuu hii kushbuu saa mahakataa huaa harsuu aaye  tere jalawe kii nigaahon ko nahiin taab rahii aisaa mahasuus huaa chaand ko ham chhuu aaye  terii diladaar nigaahon kaa dilaasaa paa ke merii palakon pe chamakate huye juganuu aaye

Title: rut naii naii badii suhaanii
Lyrics: rut naii naii badii suhaanii o ho ho tan jale gale merii javaanii haan haan haan aankhon men pyaas hai mausam bhii khaas hai dilabar bhii paas hai haan rut naii naii threedots  diivaane dilabar aa adharon ko chhuu zaraa saanson men garmiyaan yauvan hai madabharaa yaar mere bhiige bhiige gaalon kaa tuu ras le tuutane lagaa badan baahon men tuu kas le aankhon men pyaas hai threedots  main tujhamen kho gayaa diivaanaa ho gayaa pahaluu men pyaar ke pal do pal so gayaa dekh to diivaanii merii saanson men simat ke chuum le mujhe merii panaahon men lipat ke aankhon men pyaas hai threedots  tan jale gale terii javaanii o ho ho

Title: tujhase puuchhuun ek savaal  kyaa merii tarah tuu bhii tadapataa hai
Lyrics: tujhase puuchhuun ek savaal bol zaraa kyaa hai teraa haal kyaa merii tarah tuu bhii tadapataa hai  ab hai niind kise ab hai chain kahaan hosh udaae teraa shabaab mere savaal kaa de tuu javaab kyaa teraa dil bhii aise dhadakataa hai ab hai niind kise threedots  nindiyaa churaa ke le gaii bindiyaa diivaanii jiyaa churaa ke le gae kunvaare kanganaa dolii men bithaa ke tujhe chunarii udhaa ke main to le aauungaa mere anganaa pyaar kaa phuul dil men mahakataa hai ab hai niind kise threedots  saarii saarii rainaa terii yaad sataae barasaat sataae sajanaa kaate na katen ye din ab tere bin mulaaqaat sataae sajanaa paas aake bhii tuu duur rahataa hai ab hai niind kise threedots

Title: muhabbat naam hai kisakaa shuruu kahaan se hotii hai
Lyrics: muhabbat muhabbat muhabbat muhabbat muhabbat naam hai kisakaa shuruu kahaan se hotii hai kiyaa kisane ise paidaa khatm kahaan pe hotii hai muhabbat muhabbat threedots  muhabbat naam hai man kaa shuruu aankhon se hotii hai kiyaa dil ne ise paidaa khatm saanson pe hotii hai muhabbat muhabbat threedots  ho muhabbat men ye miithaa dard saa kyuun dil men hotaa hai yahii to pyaar hai jaanam ke dil hans hans ke rotaa hai koii puuchhe to kyaa batalaaen hotii hai muhabbat kyaa ye vo anamol tohafaa hai kudaa sabako nahiin detaa muhabbat vo ibaadat hai jo dilavaalon se hotii hai kiyaa kisane ise paidaa threedots  ho muhabbat kyaa hai kaisii hai ye aakhir kyaa fasaanaa hai muhabbat ek jaaduu hai muhabbat ek karishmaa hai muhabbat kaisii hai jo dil ke andar bhii hai baahar bhii ye sholaa bhii hai shabanam bhii ye shiishaa bhii hai patthar bhii ye dil kii aag hai aisii jo bas ashqon se hotii hai kiyaa kisane ise paidaa threedots

Title: suno zaraa havaaon men ye kaisii hai sadaa
Lyrics: suno zaraa suno zaraa havaaon men ye kaisii hai sadaa koii to hai jo ye kah rahaa hai kii raah men vo mod aa gayaa hai ki jisake aage naa zamiin hai na aasamaan na manzilen na raastaa suno zaraa threedots  yaadon ke gam hii hain usamen gaatii hain tanahaaiyaan haan din dhal rahaa hai to kitanii lambii hain parachhaaiyaan bas ek pal men hogaa dhuaan hai aarazuu ki ye sadaa suno zaraa threedots  dhundhalaa gae hain sitaare phuulon ko niind aa gaii gumasum se ham sochate hain baaten adhuurii kaii huiin na puurii kyuun koii bhii daastaan kise khabar kise pataa suno zaraa threedots

Title: huii hai shaam to aankhon men bas gayaa phir tuu
Lyrics: huii hai shaam to aankhon men bas gayaa phir tuu kahaan gayaa hai mere shahar ke musaafir tuu  main jaanataa huun ke duniyaa tujhe badal degii main maanataa huun ke aisaa nahiin bazaahir tuu  hansii kushii se bichhad jaa agar bichhadanaa hai ye har maqaam pe kyaa sochataa hai aakir tuu  faraaz tuune use mushqilon men daal diyaa zamaanaa saahibezar aur sirf shaair tuu

Title: ladanaa jhagadanaa jhagad ke akadanaa
Lyrics: ladanaa jhagadanaa jhagad ke akadanaa chhodo chhodo in baaton ko in se hogaa kyaa chhotii chhotii baaton pe chidhanaa bigadanaa samajho samajho in baaton se kuchh bhii nahiin milataa aao darling ham donon ab ghul mil ke rahenge tum hamen good kahanaa ham tumako very good kahenge  ham tumako bolen sorry tum hamako bolo sorry gusse kaa pade naa tum par koii dauraa yaa koii daurii bahon men hamen tum le lo hon paas tumhaare jab ham tum hamako bolo thank you ham tumako bolen welcome ladanaa jhagadanaa threedots  ham donon kii ho marriage aur marriage kaa ho function chehare ke balb hon jalate ho dil kaa dil se connection main ghar se jab bhii jaauun tum kaho mujhe good bye main laut ke jab ghar aauun tum bolo darling hi ladanaa jhagadanaa threedots

Title: dil jab se tuut gayaa kaise kahen kaise jiite hain

Lyrics: gaanv ke aage ek piipal hai usake aage ik naalaa main huun tan kii ujalii re sajanaa tuu hai man kaa kaalaa  naale naale main chalii to mujhe milaa ik mor tuu mujhe yuun taake jaise main sonaa huun tuu chor  naale naale main chalaa to mujhe milii ek koyal tuu apane ko sonaa samajhe par main samajhuun piital  tujhe main samajhaauungii sau adaaen dikhaauungii tuu tadapataa rahegaa sadaa tere paas na aauungii tuu chaahen haath jode tuu chaahen pair jode main kahuungii jaa re jaa re aa mujhe naale naale main chalii threedots  merii paravaah nahiin tujhe jhaankatii kyon hai ghar se tuu mujhe bhejii thii kyon parchii bataa milane aa jaanaa baarah baje tuu kare laakh jatan kabhii na hogaa milan meraa aisaa nahiin chaalachalan naale naale main chalaa mujhe milaa ik bangalaa tujhase jo milane aaegaa vo hogaa koii pagalaa naale naale main chalaa naale naale main chalii threedots  oe naale  kyaa samajhataa hai tuu khud ko pahale apanaa munh dekho kitane hii marate hain mujh par piichhe hansate hain vo tujh par tujhe kahaan pataaa ruup hotaa hai kyaa tuu ganvaar hai gaanv kaa o naale naale main chalaa to mujhe milaa ek sher tuu apane ko ruupamatii samajhe to hai andher naale naale main chalii to mujhe milaa ik chiitaa ek do tiin maan bhii jaa ki tuu ye baajii haarii main jiitaa naale naale main chalaa  naale naale main chalaa to mujhe milaa ek bhaaluu puure gaanv ko chakkar de duun main huun kitanaa chaaluu

Title: na jaane dil vich kii aayaa  ramataa jogii
Lyrics: na jaane dil vich kii aayaa ek prem pyaalaa pii aayaa main jii aayaa main jii aayaa main prem pyaalaa pii aayaa oy ramataa jogii hoy hoy   threedots  main prem daa pyaalaa pii aayaa ek pal men sadiyaan jii aayaa oy ramataa jogii hoy hoy  main prem daa pyaalaa pii aayaa ek pal men sadiyaan jii aayaa saarii madhushaalaa pii aayaa main pii aayaa main pii aayaa main pii aayaa jaa pii aayaa main jii aayaa oy ramataa jogii hoy hoy tuu ramataa jogii hoy hoy   threedots  tuu prem daa pyaalaa pii aayaa ai tere dil vich kii aayaa saarii madhushaalaa pii aayaa ek pa men sadiyaan jii aayaa main pii aayaa main pii aayaa main pii aayaa jaa pii aayaa main jii aayaa tuu ramataa jogii hoy hoy oy ramataa jogii hoy hoy   threedots  ye jog liyaa kis kaaran ye rog liyaa kis kaaran ho ik jogan dekhii bastii men ek mauj uthii to mastii men dil bhii aayaa main pii aayaa main prem pyaalaa pii aayaa main pii aayaa main pii aayaa main prem pyaalaa pii aayaa main jii aayaa tuu ramataa jogii tuu ramataa jogii jogii jogii jogii ho man men lagan ye jaagii jag chhuutaa hoy hoy jag chhuutaa jiyaa main raagii ye baat vahaan tak na pahunchii ye chot jiyaa tak na laagii ho ye dard zubaan tak na aayaa ye tere dil vich kii aayaa  saarii madhushaalaa pii aayaa ek pal men sadiyaan jii aayaa main pii aayaa main pii aayaa main pii aayaa jaa pii aayaa main pii aayaa oy ramataa jogii hoy hoy   threedots

Title: der se aanaa jaldii jaanaa ai saahab ye thiik nahiin
Lyrics: der se aanaa jaldii jaanaa ai saahab ye thiik nahiin roj bahaanaa ek banaanaa chaahane vaalon ko tadapaanaa ai saahab ye thiik nahiin  khaalii haath main kyaa aataa isalie der se aayaa huun jhumake kanganaa gajaraa paayal itanii chiizen laayaa huun  baaton se dil ko bahalaanaa  chaahane vaalon ko tadapaanaa threedots  shikavaa aur shikaayat hai aadat aap hasiinon kii chhuttii le kar aauungaa main agalii baar mahiinon kii jaane do mujhako hai jaanaa sarakaarii naukar ko sataanaa ai saahab ye thiik nahiin threedots  phir aisaa tum mat karanaa varanaa main nahiin boluungii khidakii se dekhuungii tamaashaa daravaazaa nahiin kholuungii ho jaauungaa main diivaanaa chaahane vaalon ko tadapaanaa threedots

Title: sarazamiinehindustaan  meraa naam baadashaah khaan hai
Lyrics: sarazamiinehindustaan assalaam vaalekum  meraa naam baadashaah khaan hai ishq meraa mazahab muhabbat meraa imaan hai muhabbat jisake lie shiirii aur farahaad ne pahaadon kaa siinaa chiir kar duudh kii nahar bahaa dii jisake lie majanuun ne saharaa kii kaak chhaanii hai aaj bhii jindaa hain tavaariikh ban kar usii muhabbat ke lie kaabul chhod paavan hindostaan kii sarazamiin se muhabbat kii kair maangane aayaa hai aajamaaish kathin hai imtihaan mushkil hai lekin hausalaa buland hai lekin jiit hameshaa mohabbat kii huii hai sadiyon se yahii hotaa aayaa hai roshanii agar kudaa ko manjuur to ankhiyon ke chiraag jalate hain kudaa gavaah kudaa gavaah

Title: tere pyaar ne ye kyaa kar diyaa bahakane lagaa diivaanaa dil
Lyrics: tere pyaar ne ye kyaa kar diyaa bahakane lagaa diivaanaa dil sambhalataa nahiin sambhaale se bhii sanam ho gaii badii mushkil tere pyaar ne ye kyaa threedots  vaadii men jaise havaa phuulon men khushbuu rahe aise hii jaanevafaa dil men mere tuu rahe rangii nazaare hue aa mausam sunaharaa dikhe aa dekhuun jahaan tak vahaan aa teraa hii cheharaa dikhe tere pyaar ne ye kyaa threedots  dulhan lage ye zamiin duulhaa lage aasamaan tuu saamane jab rahe achchhaa lage ye jahaan terii vafaa chaahie aa is zindagii ke lie aa har dard sah luungii main aa terii kushii ke lie tere pyaar ne ye kyaa threedots tere pyaar ne ye kyaa kar diyaa bahakane lagaa diivaanaa dil sambhalataa nahiin sambhaale se bhii sanam ho gaii badii mushkil tere pyaar ne ye kyaa threedots  bechain karane lage kvaabon kyaalon ke din guzare na ab ek pal saathii mere tere bin tuune mujhe de diyaa diivaanagii kaa silaa chalataa rahe umr bhar chaahat kaa ye silasilaa tere pyaar ne ye kyaa threedots  jii chaahe aise tujhe bhar luun main aagosh men main bhuul jaauun jahaan tuu naa rahe hosh men tujhako banaake kudaa terii ibaadat karuun bhuule naa tujhako kabhii itanii mohabbat karuun tere pyaar ne ye kyaa threedots

Lyrics: banno terii ankhiyaan suramedaanii banno teraa mukhadaa laakh kaa re banno teraa kangan hai hazaarii banno teraa kangan threedots  banno terii ankhiyaan suramedaanii banno teraa jhumakaa laakh kaa re banno terii jhaanjhar hai hazaarii banno terii jhaanjhar threedots  banno terii ankhiyaan suramedaanii banno terii mundarii laakh kii re banno terii nathanii hai hazaarii banno terii nathanii threedots  banno terii ankhiyaan suramedaanii banno teraa jodaa laakh kaa re banno teraa tiikaa hai hazaarii banno terii tiikaa threedots  banno terii ankhiyaan suramedaanii banno teraa bannaa laakh kaa re banno terii jodii hai hazaarii banno terii jodii threedots

Lyrics: do baje aankh ladii tiin baje pyaar huaa chaar baje thodaa thodaa dil bekaraar huaa paanch baje logon meraa jiinaa dushvaar huaa haay haay haay kyon pyaar huaa are haay haay haay kyon pyaar huaa do baje aankh ladii threedots  ye ladakii to sholaa thii shabanam huii hamen hai pataa kisakii jaanam huii machaa denge ham isakii chaahat kaa shor ki chalataa nahiin ishq pe koii zor chhah baje chuum liyaa saajan ke naam ko aur love letter likhaa saat baje shaam ko aath baje tadapane lagii aur dil bekaraar huaa haay haay haay kyon pyaar threedots  chehare pe gussaa na takaraar hai baaton men naramii kaa izahaar hai mohabbat kaa jaaduu asar kar gayaa koii dil men aayaa aur ghar kar gayaa nau baje raat huii das baje kamaal gyaarah baje taare gin gin buraa huaa haal baarah baje phir subah kaa intazaar huaa haay haay haay kyon pyaar threedots

Title: zamiin hans rahii hai  tuune zamaane ye kyaa kar diyaa
Lyrics: zamiin hans rahii hai falaq ro rahaa hai mohabbat men ye kyaa ho rahaa hai tuune zamaane ye kyaa kar diyaa lau se diye ko judaa kar diyaa thukaraayaa tuune agar aasamaan jaaenge phir ye sitaare kahaan tuune zamaane ye kyaa threedots  kyaa hai zaalim sansaar teraa paane ko pyaar main to taqadiir se bhii laduungaa sanam dil tod ke gaii chhod ke to bataa phir main kaise jiyuungaa sanam kyaa jaane tuu kitanii tuutii huun main tujhase nahiin khud se ruuthii huun tuune zamaane ye kyaa threedots  naa to terii khataa naa merii khataa do dilon men padii duuriyaan hain sanam kuchh hain terii aur kuchh hain merii ham donon kii majabuuriyaan hain sanam saagar se jaise kinaare judaa hamase hue hain hamaare judaa tuune zamaane ye kyaa threedots

Title: tum to thahare paradesii saath kyaa nibhaaoge
Lyrics: tum to thahare paradesii saath kyaa nibhaaoge subah pahalii gaadii se ghar ko laut jaaoge subah pahalii gaadii se threedots  khinche khinche hue rahate ho kyuun khinche khinche hue rahate ho dhyaan kisakaa hai zaraa bataao to ye imtehaan kisakaa hai hamen bhulaa do magar ye to yaad hii hogaa naii sadak pe puraanaa makaan kisakaa hai jab tumhen akele men merii yaad aaegii aansuon kii baarish men tum bhii bhiig jaaoge  gam kii dhuup men dil kii hasaraten na jal jaaen tujhako ai tujhako dekhane sitaare to jiyaa maangenge apane kaandhe se dupattaa na sarakane denaa varanaa buudhe bhii javaanii kii duaa maangenge iimaan se gesuon ke saae men mujhako qatl kar daalo shauq se magar socho is shaharenaamuraad kii izzat karegaa kaun are ham bhii chale gae to muhabbat karegaa kaun is ghar kii dekhabhaal ko viiraaniyaan to hon jaale hataa diye to hifaazat karegaa kaun mere baad tum kis par ye bijaliyaan giraaoge  yuun to zindagii apanii maikade men guzarii hai ashqon men husnorang samotaa rahaa huun main aanchal kisii kaa thaam ke rotaa rahaa huun main nikharaa hai jaa ke ab kahiin cheharaa shauur kaa bahakii huii bahaar ne piinaa sikhaa diyaa piitaa huun is garaz se ke jiinaa hai chaar din marane ke intazaar men piinaa siikh liyaa in nashiilii aankhon se are kab hamen pilaaoge  jab tum se ittefaakan merii nazar milii thii ab yaad aa rahaa hai shaayad vo janavarii thii tum yuun miliin dubaaraa phir maahefaravarii men jaise ki hamasafar ho tum raahezindagii men kitanaa hasiin zamaanaa aayaa thaa maarch lekar raahevafaa pe thiin tum vaadon kii torch lekar maangaa jo ahadeulfat aprail chal rahaa thaa duniyaa badal rahii thii mausam badal rahaa thaa  lekin maii jab aaii jalane lagaa zamaanaa har shakhs kii zubaan par thaa bas yahii fasaanaa duniyaa ke dar se tumane badalii thiin jab nigaahen thaa juun kaa mahiinaa lab pe thiin garm aahen julaaii men jo tumane kii baatachiit kuchh kam the aasamaan pe baadal aur merii aankhen puranam maaheagast men jab barasaat ho rahii thii bas aansuon kii baarish din raat ho rahii thii kuchh yaad aa rahaa hai vo maah thaa sitambar bhejaa thaa tumane mujhako tarqevafaa kaa letter tum gair ho rahii thiin aktuubar aa gayaa thaa duniyaa badal chukii thii mausam badal chukaa thaa  jab aa gayaa navambar aisii bhii raat aaii mujhase tumhen chhudaane sajakar baaraat aaii vo qaif thaa disambar jazbaat mar chuke the mausam thaa sard usamen aramaan bikhar chuke the lekin ye kyaa bataauun ab haal duusaraa hai are vo saal duusaraa thaa ye saal duusaraa hai kyaa karoge tum aakhir kabr par merii aakar thodii der ro loge aur bhuul Title: o jaanejaan terii nazar pe
Lyrics: o jaanejaan terii nazar pe terii adaa pe main huun fidaa sharamaao naa ghabaraao naa ab gaao naa naa naa naa naa naa naa naa se kyaa hotaa hai bolo bolo bolo naa se haan naa gaauungii main saath tumhaare tuu kisii aur se ishq ladaa mujhe chhedo naa bahakaao naa ajii jaao naa o jaanejaan threedots  gaa gaa gaa gaa gaa gaa gaa naa naa naa naa naa naa dekh lenaa sabase chhupaake tujhako udaake le jaaenge ham ho aajamaa le merii mohabbat merii chaahat hogii nahiin kam dhiire dhiire ek din tumako ham sikhaaenge kyaa chiiz hai ye muhabbat sanam o jaanejaan threedots sharamaao naa ghabaraao naa ab aao naa  gaa gaa gaa gaa gaa gaa gaa naa naa naa naa naa naa miithii miithii baaten na karanaa baaton men terii naa aauungii main hosh udaa duungii main tumhaare aisii adaaen dikhalaauungii main chupake chupake tuu mujhe dil men yuun basaaegii tujhako khabar bhii naa hogii sanam na aauungii main paas tumhaare tuu kisii aur se ishq ladaa mujhe chhedo naa bahakaao naa ajii jaao naa o jaanejaan threedots

Title: rukasat huaa to baat merii maan kar gayaa
Lyrics: rukasat huaa to baat merii maan kar gayaa jo usake paas thaa wo mujhe daan kar gayaa  bichhadaa kuchh is adaa se ke rut hii badal gaii ik shaks saare shahar ko viiraan kar gayaa  dilachasp waaqayaa hai ke kal ik ajiiz dost apane mufaat par mujhe qurabaan kar gayaa  kitanii sudhar gaii hai judaaii men zindagii haan wo jafaa se mujhape to ehasaan kar gayaa  kaalid main baat baat par kahataa thaa jisako jaan wo shaks aakarat mujhe bejaan kar gayaa

Title: chhup gayaa badalii men jaa ke chaand bhii sharamaa gayaa
Film: hum aapke dil mein rehte hain
Lyrics: chhup gae saare taare baadalon men chhup gae chhup gae vo nazaare baadalon men chhup gae aa aa chhup gayaa badalii men jaa ke chaand bhii sharamaa gayaa aapako dekhaa to phuulon ko pasiinaa aa gayaa are maahii re o o aapane yuun chhed ke to dil meraa dhadakaa diyaa ham mile to pyaar karane kaa mahiinaa aa gayaa are maahii re o o aa  aapakii ye chuudiyaan hamako jagaaen raat bhar aapakii ye boliyaan hamako sataaen raat bhar aapakaa aanchal udaa ambar pe baadal chhaa gayaa ham mile to threedots are maahii haay ho ho aa  aankhon se niinden churaanaa koii siikhe aapase pyaar men paagal banaanaa koii siikhe aapase aapakii chaahat kaa ye andaaz hamako bhaa gayaa aapako dekhaa to threedots

Title: qissaaemaharowafaa kab kaa puraanaa ho gayaa
Lyrics: qissaaemaharowafaa kab kaa puraanaa ho gayaa unase bichhade bhii hamen ab to zamaanaa ho gayaa  raat ke pichhale pahar dekhaa thaa jinako kaab men zindagii bhar ab unhen mushkil bhulaanaa ho gayaa  pyaar ke do bol hii to the merii ruswaaii ke ik zaraa sii baat kaa itanaa fasaanaa ho gayaa  unakii zulfon kii ghanerii chhaanv kyaa aaii ke phir dekhate hii dekhate mausam suhaanaa ho gayaa  jis galii men hichakichaate the kabhii jaate huye us galii men ab hasan kaa aanaa jaanaa ho gayaa

Title: jaan le luungii main aisaa khel tere saath kheluungii
Lyrics: jaan le luungii main aisaa khel tere saath kheluungii ye honaa hai ho jaaegaa zaalim anjaam teraa mit jaaegaa is duniyaa ke naamon se naam teraa jaan le luungii threedots  haan javaanii ko barabaad tuune kiyaa hai ye dil kii aavaaz hai haan merii mohabbat ko badanaam tuune kiyaa hai haan tuu dagaabaaz hai do chaar pal jii le zaraa jii bhar ke tuu pii le zaraa girane vaalaa hai tere haathon se ye jaam teraa mit jaaegaa is duniyaa ke threedots  na tujhako maaruungii na jindaa chhoduungii sun le ye hai iraadaa meraa haan saarii umr yaad karataa rahegaa mujhe tuu tujhase ye vaadaa meraa mujhase na tuu nazaren churaa o bekhabar o bevafaa merii mahafil men aaii hai leke naam teraa mit jaaegaa is duniyaa ke threedots

Title: ye gayaa vo gayaa dil meraa kho gayaa
Lyrics: ye gayaa vo gayaa dil meraa kho gayaa kuchh tujhe ho gayaa kuchh mujhe ho gayaa  main aaii tuu gayaa koii baat na huii tuu gaii main aayaa mulaakaat naa huii ki baadal to jhuke barasaat na huii aaj phir ye huaa main chalaa lo gayaa ye gayaa vo gayaa threedots  na niind hai mujhe na karaar hai mujhe yahii meraa haal ikaraar hai mujhe tuu saaf saaf bol intazaar hai tujhe haan kaho naa kaho pyaar to ho gayaa ye gayaa vo gayaa threedots

Title: baabuu lo chal gayaa naa jaaduu nazaron kaa
Singer: s p balasubrahmanyam a r rahman kavita krishnamurthy
Lyrics: ai ai ai ai  baabuu lo chal gayaa naa jaaduu nazaron kaa   dekho ilzaam chaahat kaa ham pe nahiin  zaraa sachsach bataanaa bhale aadamii  ye to kahatii hai har manachalii naazaniin  aashiqon ko jagaataa hai ye husn hii  dil men dhukdhuk hone lagii  dhadakanen kuchhkuchh kahane lagiin  baabuu lo chal gayaa naa jaaduu nazaron kaa  aayen chaahen kitane hii gam bas ho teraa saath sanam  merii kushiyaan tujhape nichhaavar kar duun saarii terii qasam  pyaar ke raaste ho gaye roshan jal uthii hai vafaa kii agan  ab to bujhane naa paaye shamaa pyaar kii  pyaar hii hai davaa tere biimaar kii  ek duuje se ruuthe hon donon kabhii aane paaye na aisii ghadii  baabuu lo chal gayaa naa jaaduu nazaron kaa dekho ilzaam chaahat kaa ham pe nahiin zaraa sachsach bataanaa bhale aadamii ye to kahatii hai har manachalii naazaniin aashiqon ko jagaataa hai ye husn hii dil men dhukdhuk hone lagii dhadakanen kuchhkuchh kahane lagiin  ruup teraa rang teraa jaise sonaa chaandii hai  dil ye teraa hiire jaisaa pyaar teraa motiimotii hai  pyaar ki manzil mil gaii hamako jabase milii hai mohabbat terii  terii baanhon men guzaregii ye zindagii ham karenge sadaa ab terii bandagii  meraa din hai sanam ab ye suurat terii merii raaten hain zulfen terii  baabuu lo chal gayaa naa jaaduu nazaron kaa dekho ilzaam chaahat kaa ham pe nahiin zaraa sachsach bataanaa bhale aadamii ye to kahatii hai har manachalii naazaniin aashiqon ko jagaataa hai ye husn hii dil men dhukdhuk hone lagii dhadakanen kuchhkuchh kahane lagiin  baabuu lo chal gayaa naa jaaduu nazaron kaa

Title: ghuum aaye sabhii dishaaon men
Lyrics: ghuum aaye sabhii dishaaon men sukh milaa aa ke apane gaanv men  sabako apanii tarah samajhate hain ham bhii rahate hain kin hawaaon men  tumase ham duur hain musaafir hain yaad rakhanaa hamen duaaon men  aadamii to zamiin pe rahataa hai kyaa milegaa tumhen kalaaon men  daur har simt zard chehare hain ghir gaye log kin balaaon men

Title: haan pahalii baar huaa hai  tujhe mujhase pyaar huaa hai
Lyrics: haan pahalii baar huaa hai tujhe mujhase pyaar huaa hai binaa tujhe dekhe kahiin na chain hai binaa tere jiinaa dushvaar hai pahalii baar huaa hai threedots  niind aatii nahiin chain aataa nahiin jaan ke to koii dil lagaataa nahiin haalat kyaa hai merii tujhase kyaa main chhipaauun dekhataa huun har ghadii rastaa teraa hal pal teraa hii intazaar hai haan pahalii baar huaa hai threedots  ek din agar main na dekhuun tujhe log mujhase kahen kyaa huaa hai mujhe kaisaa mere saathii maine dil ko hai lagaayaa bin piye hii dagamagaate hain kadam mujhape na meraa akhtiyaar hai haan pahalii baar huaa hai threedots

Title: kisii din banuungii main raajaa kii raanii  zaraa phir se kahanaa
Lyrics: kisii din banuungii main raajaa kii raanii zaraa phir se kahanaa badii dilarubaa hai ye saarii kahaanii zaraa phir se kahanaa abhii to mile ho abhii tum na jaanaa ki dil ban gayaa hai tumhaaraa diivaanaa ho zaraa phir se kahanaa kisii din banuungii threedots  jhukii jhukii nazar terii kamaal kar gaii uthii jo ek baar sau savaal kar gaii merii javaan dhadakanon men terii pyaas thii lagaa ye tujhako dekhake terii talaash thii tasviir terii dilabar main dil men utaaruungaa ulajhe ulajhe tere gesuon ko sanvaaruungaa  zaraa phir se kahanaa kisii din banegii tuu raajaa kii raanii zaraa phir se threedots  abhii to mile ho abhii tum na jaanaa ki main ban gayaa huun tumhaaraa diivaanaa  tuu phuul hai chaman kaa main kalii bahaar kii mere labon pe likh de daastaan pyaar kii tuu ishq kii jubaan husn kaa bayaan hai tuu jaan nashiin jaanejaan tuu merii jaan hai taariif na kar itanii main hosh ganvaa baithuun aisaa na ho chaahat men duniyaa bhulaa baithuun zaraa phir se threedots

Title: ye mausam bhii gayaa vo mausam bhii gayaa  ab to kaho mere sanam
Lyrics: ye mausam bhii gayaa vo mausam bhii gayaa ab to kaho mere sanam phir kab miloge milenge jab haan haan haan baarish hogii ye mausam bhii gayaa threedots  bin tere kahiin katen na ye pal ye din ye raat mere balamaa ab to dhuundhe yahaan hameshaa tujhe merii nazar merii dilarubaa hongii bhalaa kaise khatm terii merii duuriyaan ye mausam bhii gayaa threedots  kyuun banaae bhalaa bahaane lagaa mujhe gale na aise sataa main mitaa duun terii bechainii mere hasiin sanam zaraa paas aa mil ke bhalaa milane kii ab kaisii majabuuriyaan ye mausam bhii gayaa threedots

Title: kyon chhede hamako soneyaa tuu kyon sataataa hai
Lyrics: kyon chhede hamako soneyaa tuu kyon sataataa hai tuu to bansii bajaiyaa phir kyon kapade churaataa hai tuu to bansii threedots  kuchh ham bhii shikaayat kar len kuchh tuu bhii shikaayat kar le kapadon kii sharaarat kaisii koii aur sharaarat kar le kyon dil men hamaare mundeyaa tuu aag lagaataa hai tuu to bansii threedots  teraa cheharaa natakhat pyaaraa dil aur machal naa jaae tuu dekh naa aise hamako kahiin jaan nikal naa jaae suiiyaan sii hamaare dil men kaahe ko chubhaataa hai tuu to bansii threedots  kapade nahiin honge to ham khud bhii sharamaaenge diivaane bin kapadon ke ham ghar kaise jaaenge re hamako thand lagatii hai tuu dil bahalaataa hai tuu to bansii threedots

Title: raajadulaaraa tuu merii aankh kaa taaraa  tuu hai mujhe jaan se pyaaraa
Lyrics: raajadulaaraa tuu merii aankh kaa taaraa bhaaii mere tuu hai mujhe jaan se pyaaraa chaand dhal gayaa raat so gaii dekh to kitanii der ho gaii lorii gaauun main sulaauun so jaa so jaa so jaa raajadulaaraa tuu threedots  terii bhalaaii kii duaa maangataa rahuun tere lie saarii umar jaagataa rahuun tere saare gam hans ke main sahuun har ghadii tere saamane rahuun lorii gaauun threedots  tere vaaste milaa mujhako to ye jiivan sadiyon tak naa tuutegaa ye pyaar kaa bandhan de duun main tujhe terii har khushii bin tere hai kyaa merii zindagii lorii gaauun threedots

Title: ek din college gayaa thaa  do duunii chaar huaa re
Lyrics: ek din college gayaa thaa mil gaii ladakii hasiin maine ye sochaa kar duun ishaaraa ladakii hansii to phansii do duunii chaar huaa re pyaar huaa pyaar huaa re  main bhii college gaii thii ek ladakaa piichhe padaa jaauun jahaan main nazaren bachaa ke dekhuun vahaan vo khadaa do duunii chaar huaa threedots  main sair karane gayaa thaa nadiyaa kinaare pahalii baar gayaa thaa bhiigii bhiigii milii vahiin ek ladakii mere dil men bhii koii aag bhadakii maine ye sochaa kar duun threedots  kuchh lene main baazaar gaii thii jaake vahaan dil haar gaii thii javaan javaan milaa vahaan ek ladakaa dekhaa jab use meraa dil dhadakaa maine sochaa threedots  naadaan hai tuu itanaa na jaane vo ladakii tuu hii to thii naadaan hai tuu itanaa na jaane vo ladakaa tuu hii to thaa do duunii chaar huaa threedots

Title: dhiire dhiire ham donon men  diivaanii kudii dil le gaii
Lyrics: dhiire dhiire ham donon men pyaar huaa hai pakkaa are aajaa baabaa ham donon ab kar len nain matakkaa are haay haay haay mere rabbaa diivaanii kudii dil le gaii he he he he he he he he  dhiire dhiire ham donon threedots are haay haay haay mere rabbaa diivaanaa mundaa dil le gayaa haan  khadii khadii kyaa soche tuu kah de mujhase i love you dekhake tujhako ho jaataa hai diivaanaa dil beqaabuu chal gayaa hai teraa jaaduu main piichhe aur aage tuu baaton hii baaton men tuune kar liyaa meraa dil qaabuu haay haay haay mere rabbaa threedots  duur naa honaa tuu hamase jaldii aajaa tuu chham se jabase pyaar kiyaa hai tumase hosh hain mere gumasum se haath pakad ke chhod na denaa bas ye kahanaa hai tumase haay haay haay mere rabbaa threedots
