Lyrics: vo sikandar hii doston kahalaataa hai haarii baazii ko jiitanaa jise aataa hai nikalenge maidaan men jis din ham jhuum ke dharatii dolegii ye kadam chuum ke vo sikandar hii doston threedots  jo sab karate hain yaaron vo kyon ham tum karen yuun hii kasarat karate karate kaahe ko ham maren gharavaalon se teacher se bhalaa ham kyon daren yahaan ke ham sikandar chaahen to rakh len sabako apanii jeb ke andar are hamase bachake rahanaa merii jaan nahiin samajhe hain vo hamen to kyaa jaataa hai haarii baazii ko jiitanaa threedots  ye galiyaan apanii ye raste apane kaun aaegaa apane aage raahon men hamase takaraaegaa jo hat jaaegaa vo ghabaraa ke yahaan ke ham sikandar threedots  ye bholii bhaalii matavaalii pariyaan jo hain ab daulat par qurbaan jab kiimat dil kii ye samajhengii to ham pe chhidakengii apanii jaan yahaan ke ham sikandar threedots  are ham bhii hain shahzaade gulafaam

Title: terii banjaaran raastaa dekhe  kab aaegaa mere banjaare
Lyrics: terii banjaaran raastaa dekhe kab aaegaa mere banjaare 2 o tuu nahiin aayaa aa gae saare kab aaegaa mere threedots  duur bahut thaa desh teraa pahunchaa nahiin sandesh meraa sapanon ke raajaa jaldii se aa jaa der na kar saajan pyaare kab aaegaa mere threedots  aisaa na ho ki tuu na aae 2 dolii aur koii le jaae 2 tadap tadap ke taras taras ke main mar jaauun gam ke maare terii banjaaran raastaa dekhe threedots  sapanon men sapanaa tod gayaa tuu aag sulagatii chhod gayaa tuu phuulon pe chalake lagataa hai aise paanv ke niiche hain angaare 2 kab aaegaa mere threedots

Title: laaj saram tuune chhiinii re mose nainaa milaaii ke
Lyrics: rang lagaii lo ang lagaii lo goriyaa hamare sang kaa kahat ho aaj zaraa saa pyaar karo tum thiik kahat ho kal kar laiiyo jang  laaj saram tuune chhiinii re mose nainaa milaaii ke karanii na thii jo kar diinii re tose nainaa milaaii ke laaj saram sab chhiinii re tose nainaa milaaii ke karanii na thii jo kar diinii re tose nainaa haan tose nainaa milaaii ke  rang nikal jaae to kahiyo saarii umariyaa dhote rahiyo torii chunar rang diinii re tose nainaa milaaii ke haan nainaa tose nainaa milaaii ke  o o kuchh dekhaa phir kuchh naa dekhaa kuchh dekhaa haay naa dekhaa kuchh dekhaa phir kuchh naa dekhaa kaun kasam aur kaun sii rekhaa tod ke bas rakh diinii re tose nainaa milaaii ke laaj saram tuune threedots  ang hamaare sang lagaao phir zaraa saa rang lagaao araj garaj kar diinii re tose nainaa milaaii ke araj garaj kar diinii tose nainaa milaaii ke laaj saram tuune threedots  aa prem dagar men bhuul bhulaiyaa dhuup sadak par dekhii chhaiyaan raat basar haay raat basar kar liinii re tose nainaa milaaii ke laaj saram tuune threedots

Title: yaaron ko jaan hai pyaarii  main huun ruup kii raanii
Film: roop ki raani choron kaa raajaa
Lyrics: yaaron ko jaan hai pyaarii kaun kare mujhase yaarii main huun sholaa main chingaarii pyaar kii baazii main naa haarii mujhase haare kitane juaarii jo ye pukaare praan pyaarii luut ke usakii duniyaa saarii ban jaauun anjaanii main huun ruup kii raanii yaaron ko jaan hai threedots  main apsaraa main huun parii merii adaa jaaduugarii jo dilajale mujhako mile vo bechaare phirate maare pyaar men apanaa tan man haare ginate hain vo raat men taare unase kahuun main sun le pyaare in kadamon men dil rakhanaa ye maanguun main nishaanii main huun ruup kii raanii yaaron ko jaan hai threedots  koii na koii to aaegaa jo mere dil ko bhaaegaa kabhii naa kabhii kahiin naa kahiin dhiire dhiire haule haule dil meraa le legaa pyaar mujhe de degaa usakii banuungii diivaanii main huun ruup kii raanii yaaron ko jaan hai threedots

Title: nigaahemastesaaqii kaa salaam aayaa to kyaa hogaa
Lyrics: nigaahemastesaaqii kaa salaam aayaa to kyaa hogaa agar phir tarketaubaa kaa payaam aayaa to kyaa hogaa  haram waale to puuchhenge bataa tuu kisakaa bandaa hai kudaa se pahale lab par unakaa naam aayaa to kyaa hogaa  mujhe manzuur unase main na boluungaa magar naaseh agar unakii nigaahon kaa salaam aayaa to kyaa hogaa  mujhe tarketalab manzuur lekin ye to batalaa do koii kud hii liye haathon men jaam aayaa to kyaa hogaa  muhabbat ke liye tarketaalluq hii zuruurii ho muhabbat men agar aisaa makaam aayaa to kyaa hogaa

Title: ai aalaa re paaus aalaa  barasaa re paanii
Lyrics: aalaa re aalaa aalaa re aalaa ai aalaa re paaus aalaa are aalaa re paaus aalaa re barasaa re paanii huii main to diivaanii mujhe o mujhe ho mujhe ye kyaa hone lagaa ai aalaa re paaus aalaa threedots  ham bekhabar aa gae kidhar pighalaa huaa ye samaa hai baahon men hai saarii zamiin kadamon tale aasamaan hai ai hotii kyaa hai bekhudii ye ab pataa chalaa ang ang men samaa rahaa koii nashaa mujhe mujhe o mujhe threedots  ham the kabhii do ajanabii ab aisaa lagataa nahiin hai tum bhii yahaan main bhii yahaan ab to na koii kamii hai mahakii mahakii kyuun lage hai aaj kii ghataa are main to kuchh na jaanuun mujhe tuu hii de bataa o mujhe mujhe o mujhe threedots  barasaa re paanii huii paagal javaanii

Title: pii ke jab shukr kaa sajadaa kiyaa mayakaane men
Lyrics: pii ke jab shukr kaa sajadaa kiyaa mayakaane men betalab aa gaii may phir mere paimaane men  ye tagodau ye talaalum ye tadap kar giranaa wo kahaan shammaa men jo aag hai parawaane men  ik dhadakataa huaa dil ek chhalakataa huaa jaam yahii le aate hain mayanosh ko mayakaane men  dilebesabr ko bewaqt qafas kii suujhii huye do chaar hii din honge bahaar aane men

Title: naaraaz saveraa hai  nazadiik saveraa hai
Lyrics: naaraaz saveraa hai har or andheraa hai koii kiran to aae kahiin se aae aae naaraaz saveraa hai  zindagii tanhaaiiyon kaa karz hai naam hai har khushii dhalatii huii dukh bharii shaam hai saanson ke khazaanon kaa ye vaqt luteraa hai koii kiran to threedots  raat kii khaamoshiyon men anasunaa shor hai khiinchatii baandhe binaa hii kaun sii ye dor hai bejaan salaakhon ne merii ruuh ko gheraa hai koii kiran to threedots  vo mere bachapan kaa mausam vo zamaanaa kho gayaa maut ke saae men rah ke bejubaan main ho gayaa zakhmon kii zamiinon pe zulmon kaa baseraa hai koii kiran to threedots nazadiik saveraa hai pal bhar kaa andheraa hai mere lie naa ashq bahaao jaao jaao nazadiik saveraa hai  de rahaa mujhako sadaaen vo khulaa aasamaan le rahiin merii balaaen vo hasiin vaadiyaan tum laao ujaalon ko sapanaa yahii meraa hai din hain khushii ke giit milan ke gaao gaao

Title: milane kii tum koshish karanaa  vaadaa to tuut jaataa hai
Lyrics: milane kii tum koshish karanaa vaadaa kabhii na karanaa vaadaa to tuut jaataa hai milane kii tum koshish threedots  jab bhii teraa jii chaahe tuu paas mere aa jaanaa meraa pyaar bas tere lie hai tuu na kabhii ghabaraanaa lekin sapanon men milane kii kabhii na koshish karanaa sapanaa to tuut jaataa hai  hotii hain bedard bahut hii is duniyaa kii rasmen mushkil kar detii hain nibhaanaa pyaar vafaa kii kasamen shiishe jaise aramaan lekar raahon se na guzaranaa shiishaa to tuut jaataa hai milane kii tum koshish threedots

Title: ajiiz itanaa hii rakho ke jii sambhal jaaye
Lyrics: ajiiz itanaa hii rakho ke jii sambhal jaaye ab is qadar bhii na chaaho ke dam nikal jaaye  muhabbaton men ajab hai dilon ko dhadakaa saa ke jaane kaun kahaan raastaa badal jaaye  zahe wo dil jo tamanaaetaazaatar men rahe khushaa wo umr jo kwaabon men hii bahal jaaye  main wo charaagesarerahguzaareduniyaa huun jo apanii zaat kii tanhaaiyon men jal jaaye  har ek lamhaa yahii aarazuu yahii hasarat jo aag dil men hai wo she men bhii dhal jaaye

Title: mangataa hai kyaa vo bolo
Lyrics: jaaduu jaaduu jaaduu jaaduu  o o o o o o o  aaii aaii yo kil vo mangataa hai kyaa vo bolo  haan bolo  mangataa hai jaan ye le lo  ye suhaanii shaam  jaaduu aisaa hai hamaaraa  jo mangataa hai vo milegaa aa aa  tumako  aaii yo  aaii aaii yo kil bo mangataa hai jo vo de do  aa de do  mangataa hai dil vo de do  mangataa hai pyaar  bas is ke sivaa o jaanaa  aur kuchh nahiin mangataa hai  yaaii yaaii yaaii yaaii  hamako  dekhodekho ye phuul aur ye ujaale ye sab hain tumhaare  nahiinnahiin in se hamen hai matalab kyaa diivaane ham tumhaare  aaii aaii yu kil vo mangataa hai jaan vo bolo  aaii aaii yuu kil vo haal mera tum kuchh to suno   are suno  kabhii kabhii o jaanejaanan  dil de dil le dil de dil lene kaa socho to  suno suno  baat merii samajho  aajaa aajaa tujhako nazaare ham dikhaayen  bahaaron se milaayen  chhodochhodo kaisii bahaaren kyaa nazaare  are aao dil milaayen

Title: sunday kii raat thii pahalii mulaakaat thii
Lyrics: main thaa vo thii main thaa vo thii halkii barasaat thii haay  aaliishaan kisii bangale se gaadii men vo nikalii mere pyaar men jaal men phans gaii paise vaalii titalii naukar chaakar ghuumenge ab mere aage piichhe ab to saarii daulat hogii in kadamon ke niiche saarii duniyaa usake piichhe par vo mere saath thii haan  vo thaa main thii vo thaa main thii halkii barasaat thii haay maine usako dekhaa to dil meraa dhak se dhadakaa sardii ke mausam men bhii garmii kaa sholaa bhadakaa pahalii pahalii nazar men ban gaii main usakii diivaanii vo mere sapanon kaa raajaa aur main usakii raanii sab kuchh usako de diyaa maine usane aisii baat kii saiyaa

Title: bakaaedil ke liye jyuun lahuu zuruurii hai
Lyrics: bakaaedil ke liye jyuun lahuu zuruurii hai isii tarah mere jiiwan men tuu zuruurii hai  ye akl waale nahiin ahaledil samajhate hain ke kyuun sharaab se pahale wuzuu zuruurii hai  kudaa ko munh bhii dikhaanaa hai ek din yaaro wafaa mile na mile justajuu zuruurii hai  kalii ummiid kii khilatii nahiin har ik dil men har ek dil men magar aarazuu zuruurii hai  hai ahataraam bhii laazim ke zikr hai usakaa jigar kaa chaak bhii honaa rafuu zuruurii hai

Title: yaa tuu sayaanaa ban jaa yaa main budhiyaa ban jaauun
Lyrics: yaa tuu sayaanaa ban jaa yaa main budhiyaa ban jaauun ye pyaar kaa rog buraa hai kaise tujhako samajhaauun ye pyaar kaa rog buraa hai threedots  main dil lagaa ke tujhase bemaut mar jaauun  are o mere gudde raajaa aa  kyuun mujhase aankh churaataa hai palaken sharm se jhukaataa hai bholaa huun main naadaan huun in baaton se main anjaan huun o o mere raam bharose mujhako main dil men bithaauun aa o mere gudde raajaa tujhe kaise pyaar sikhaauun main  bach kahaan mujhase paaegaa kaise tuu piichhaa chhudaaegaa kyon hai mere aage khadii piichhe mere kyon padii aa terii soii soii dhadakan men pyaas jagaa duun yaa tuu sayaanaa ban jaa  threedots

Title: in mast nigaahon se mujhako na pilaa denaa  main aisii chiiz nahiin jo ghabaraa
Lyrics: in mast nigaahon se mujhako na pilaa denaa tum ek musalamaan ho qaafir na banaa denaa oy vallaa meraa javaab nistaa oy loshe oy qurbaan oye laale dii jaan aise meraa maashuuq chale oy khoche jaise banduuk chale banduuk ye chalane vaalaaii terii jaan main aisii chiiz nahiin jo ghabaraa ke palat jaauungaa mere saamane se hat jaa 2 nahiin to main tujhase lipat jaauungaa  ho main aisii chiiz nahiin jo sharamaa ke simat jaauungii main kaat ke rakh duungii tujhako yaa aap hii kat jaauungii main aisii chiiz nahiin jo ghabaraa ke threedots  dariyaaemohabbat men gussaa tinakaa ban ke rah jaae main tere tukade kar duungii kisakaa tuu rah jaae main tere husn ke sadake kii khairaat men bant jaauungaa main aisii chiiz nahiin jo ghabaraa ke threedots  yaar vaii vaii 2 yaar men kuchh dam nahiin faisalaa ye aaj hogaa tum nahiin yaa ham nahiin ham yuun hii mar jaaegaa bas dekh le tuu pyaar se ho tuu kaun hai meraa dushman hai 2 dushman se pyaar nahiin karate 2 dushman par tiir chalaate hain nazaron se vaar nahiin karate main titalii nahiin bijalii huun 2 chamakii to chimat jaauungii ho main aisii chiiz nahiin jo sharamaa ke threedots

Title: gore gore mukhade pe kaalaa kaalaa chashmaa
Lyrics: gore gore mukhade pe kaalaa kaalaa chashmaa taubaa kudaa khair kare khuub hai karishmaa gore gore mukhade pe threedots  dekho isako gaur se ladakii hai ki huur hai jaaduu isake ruup men ye kitanii magaruur hai dekhuun jab dekhuun ise dil dhadake tadape javaanii haay aankh phadake taubaa kudaa khair kare threedots  aadat apanii chhod de kahanaa meraa maan le yaanii main kyaa chiiz huun tuu mujhako pahachaan le jaa re jaa anaadii aisii baaten naa banaa jaanuun main huun jaanuun terii marzii hai kyaa tuune merii jaan meraa dekhaa naa karishmaa gore gore mukhade pe threedots

Title: kyaa khabar thii jaanaan tumase pyaar ho jaaegaa
Lyrics: kyaa khabar thii jaanaan tumase pyaar ho jaaegaa rahane de dil kii baaten varanaa pachhataaegaa tumase pyaar ho jaaegaa achchhaa kyaa khabar thii jaanaan threedots  dil meraa ye jaanejaanaan anamol hai ye khazaanaa tujh par lutaauungaa sadake main jaauungaa mujhasaa hai aashiq kahaan haay kyaa khabar thii jaanaan threedots  tumase karuun pyaar kaise kar luun main ikaraar mujhako sataaoge niind udaaoge achchhii hain ye duuriyaan kyaa khabar thii jaanaan threedots

Title: telephone dhun men hansane vaalii
Lyrics: o o o o o o o o o o 4      zaakir hussain tabalaa tuu hai kyaa  sonaa sonaa teraa chamake ruup salonaa  sonaa sonaa cellular phone tum to ho naa     tum naa hote to dhuup nahiin hotii rimajhim bhii naa hotii  tum naa hote to chaand nahiin hotaa sapanaa bhii nahiin sajataa  tum ko pukaaraa saansen kushbuu phailaa rahiin merii  tumase bichhadaa to bahatii havaayen band ho gaiin kyuun  paanii naa hotaa jharane naa hote ye vaadii naa hotii  milataa naa tuu to merii jaan nahiin hotii ye pyaas nahiin hotii  gori nadiyaa apane men har din mujhako dubaanaa  tum naa sharmaanaa zulfon men apanii kud ko chhupaa lenaa   o o o o o o o o o o 4  naam teraa kisii ko lene nahiin duungaa vo sukh bhii nahiin duungaa  gajaraa tumhaaraa girane nahiin duungaa murajhaane nahiin duungaa  mere alaavaa kisii aurat ko naa paas bulaanaa  tum naa kabhii bhii mother teresa ko chhod ke naam naa lenaa  terii galiyon men koii mard na chhoduungaa aurat bhii naa chhoduungaa  terii hansii ko udane nahiin duungaa mere dil men basaa luungaa   jiivan men priitam tumhen pyaar kii rekhaa paar karane naa duungii  zaakir hussain tabalaa tuu hai kyaa sonaa sonaa teraa chamake ruup salonaa sonaa sonaa cellular phone tum to ho naa

Title: zamiin aasamaan mil jaaen  yaaraanaa yaar kaa naa kabhii
Lyrics: zamiin aasamaan mil jaaen ye to phir bhii mumakin hai magar ek yaar duniyaa men badii mushkil se milataa hai  yaaraanaa yaar kaa naa kabhii chhuutegaa teraa naam le lekar meraa dam tuutegaa yaaraanaa yaar kaa threedots  jahaan gire pasiinaa teraa main to kuun bahaa duungaa tuu hii tuu hai dil men mere chiir ke dil dikhalaa duungaa ki ruuthuun jo tujhase main to kudaa ruuthegaa teraa naam le lekar threedots  ek hain apane sapane saathii tuu jaane main jaanuun apane dil ke nek iraade chehare se pahachaanuun apanaa pyaar mere yaar koii kyaa luutegaa teraa naam le lekar threedots

Title: tujhase badaa na koii  bajarang balii terii jay ho
Lyricist: anand raj anand dev kohli rajesh malik
Lyrics: bolo hanumaan kii jay jay jay bajarang balii kii jay tujhase badaa na koii tuu hai badaa mahaan jay ho jay ho terii jay ho jay ho terii hanumaan raam base hain dil men tere tuu rahataa hai man men mere tuune kar dii kripaa terii shakti milii bajarang balii bajarang balii bajarang balii terii jay ho tujhase badaa na koii threedots  jay hanumaan gyaan gun saagar jay kapiish tihun lok ujaagar raamaduut atulit baladhaamaa anjaniputra pavanasut naamaa tuune vo bal diyaa hai mujhako parabat se takaraa jaauun main jay ho terii jay ho terii bhakti aur shakti se har vipadaa pe chhaa jaauun main log bajaaen teraa dankaa jaise tuune phuunk dii lankaa vaise hii main toduun dushman kii nalii bajarang balii threedots  duniyaa ko dikhalaa duungaa main kitanaa sachchaa bhakt huun teraa paap mitaa duungaa dharatii se he balashaalii pran hai meraa ye sab teraa chamatkaar hai mujhape teraa adhikaar hai jisane bhii dekhaa sabakii aankhen khuliin bajarang balii threedots

Title: siine men dil hai dil men sanam aur sanam men jaan merii
Lyrics: siine men dil hai dil men sanam aur sanam men jaan merii ishq hai dhadakan ishq hai saajan ishq hai pahachaan merii palon kii judaaii ham naa sahenge saath jiyenge saath marenge ik duuje ke binaa ham naa rahenge har ek janm men vaadaa karenge tujh bin kuchh bhii naa chaahuun main siine men dil hai threedots  aankh khule to dekhuun main tujhako band hon aankhen terii chhavi ho har ik rang men chhaayaa ho terii us chhaayaa men merii zindagii ho saath men tuu to ho jaayegii har mushkil aasaan merii jisamen terii khushbuu hogii bas usako phuul kahuungaa jisamen tuu naa shaamil hogaa us jiivan ko bhuul kahuungii tere sur men bas jaaegii tuutegii jab taan merii siine men dil hai threedots

Title: pandit jii ne haath meraa dekhaa thaa nainiitaal men
Lyrics: pandit jii ne haath meraa dekhaa thaa nainiitaal men kahaa thaa mujhase kyaa kahaa shaadii terii hogii athaarah saal men  pandit jii ne haath meraa dekhaa thaa bhopaal men kahaa thaa pyaare kyaa kahaa kabhii naa padanaa shaadii ke janjaal men pandit jii ne haath meraa threedots  athaarah saal aur ek mahiine kii main ho gaii raajaa ghode haathii sang baraatii leke jaldii se aajaa baahon ke haar se bhar de maang pyaar se chain mujhe aaegaa jab main aauungii sasuraal men pandit jii ne haath meraa threedots  shaadii shudaa mardon kii haalat dekhii hai maine raanii maine sunii hai logon se dukhabharii unakii kahaanii jaa piichhaa chhod de shiishaaedil tod de main naa phansane vaalaa huun terii adaaon ke jaal men pandit jii ne haath meraa threedots

Title: mere chehare pe likhaa hai afasaanaa aapakaa  maine bhii kabuul kiyaa hai
Lyrics: mere chehare pe likhaa hai afasaanaa aapakaa sab jaan gae ki main huun diivaanaa aapakaa mere chehare pe likhaa hai threedots  maine bhii kabuul kiyaa hai nazaraanaa aapakaa dilabar ye meraa bhii dil hai diivaanaa aapakaa  mahabuub kasam hai rab kii ikaraar kiyaa na maine sab jaan gae phir kaise ijahaar kiyaa na maine chupake se sanam chorii se mulaaqaat huii hai tumase sab jaan gae phir kaise jo baat huii hai tumase are raaz bataa detaa hai ghabadaanaa aapakaa sab jaan gae hain ki threedots  jab phuul khile baahon men khushbuu to bikharatii jaae har baat chhupaa le koii par pyaar chhupaa na paae jab aag lage is tan men uthataa hai dhuaan saanson se tasviir merii dikhatii hai hamaraah kii do aankhon se bechain mujhe karataa hai tadapaanaa aapakaa dilabar ye meraa bhii dil threedots

Title: tumase hai jitanaa pyaar ye ham  o mitavaa tujhe meraa pyaar pukaare
Lyrics: tumase hai jitanaa pyaar ye ham kah nahiin sakate tumase bichhad ke ham to zindaa rah nahiin sakate o mitavaa tujhe meraa pyaar pukaare aa re aa re aa re tumase hai jitanaa pyaar threedots  o mitavaa tujhe mere giit pukaaren aa re aa re aa re  mere saanson ke aangan men terii hai tasviir sanam main terii taqadiir aur tuu merii hai taqadiir sajan terii khaatir to duniyaa kii rasmon ko ham todenge chaahe chhuute saarii duniyaa tujhako na chhodenge tum mujhako milate ho jaise apanaapan saa lagataa hai tere pyaar kii baahon men mujhako jiivan saa lagataa hai terii aankhon men din meraa zulfon men hai shaan lage jiivan jisako kahate hain vo teraa naam lage o mitavaa tujhe threedots   o mitavaa tujhe threedots

Title: niind aatii nahiin dard jaataa nahiin
Lyrics: niind aatii nahiin dard jaataa nahiin kyaa huaa hai mujhe chain aataa nahiin nazaren miliin ikaraar ho gayaa chorii chorii chhupake pyaar ho gayaa dil men jo thaa diladaar ho gayaa tumako nahiin hai khabar niind aatii nahiin threedots  jaanejaan merii aankhon men koii hasiin saa cheharaa hai jisakii aankhen kaalii hain baalon kaa rang sunaharaa hai kyaa bataauun khvaabon men koii diivaanaa aataa hai bekhudii deke mujhako shaamosahar tadapaataa hai ek pal dil use bhuul paataa nahiin kyaa huaa hai mujhe threedots  gul chaman hai khushbuu hai chhaae rang bahaaron ke har kalii sharamaaii hai dil javaan nazaaron ke dilarubaa in honthon ke saare rang churaane de har tamannaa kahatii hai duuriyon ko mitaane de ab to tere sivaa koii bhaataa nahiin kyaa huaa hai mujhe threedots

Title: mere man kaa mausam badalane lagaa hai
Lyrics: mere man kaa mausam badalane lagaa hai tere naam se dil dhadakane lagaa hai teraa pyaar siine men palane lagaa hai mere man kaa mausam threedots  nazar se nazar ne kahii vo kahaanii jo ham tum kabhii kah naa paae jubaanii ham ek duuje men aise khoe hue hain na jaage hue hain na soe hue hain ye jaaduu na jaane kyaa chalane lagaa hai mere man kaa mausam threedots  jahaan tak nazar jaae bas tuu hii tuu hai tujhe paa ke ab kuchh nahiin aarazuu hai chale hain kadam manzilon se bhii aage kahaan khiinch laae mohabbat ke dhaage ye kis rang men ishq dhalane lagaa hai mere man kaa mausam threedots

Title: bole chhan chhanan na na  merii paayal bole
Singer: alka yagnik sunidhi chauhan annu malik
Lyrics: chhan nan nan na na shokh hasiinaa ye to bataa de terii adaa men jaaduu kyaa hai kyuun balakhaae kyuun laharaae tere badan men kaisaa nashaa hai chhan nan nan na na  bole chhan chhanan na na chhan chhanan merii paayal bole dole san sanan na na san sanan na na puravaa dole chhan nan nan na na threedots  uii ude aanchal huii jaae halachal chalii havaa anganaa kalaaii men kanganaa khanak jaae aur bole khan khan ye bindiyaa damake ye chunar chamake to nas nas men ho jhan jhan kajare men dhul ke baalon men khul ke raaj hain dil ke khole bole chhan chhanan threedots  naii rut aaii kaii rang laaii nikalii nahaa ke main gajaraa sajaa ke main kaanon men pahan ke baalii tan ho gulaabii jaise jaam sharaabii jaise aise lage honthon pe laalii paas jo aae hosh ganvaae sang mere vo hole bole chhan chhanan threedots

Title: tere dil kii patarii pe daudegii mere dil kii rail
Lyrics: tere dil kii patarii pe daudegii mere dil kii rail aashiq injan maashuuq dibbaa daudaa jaae dil kaa mel pyaar kii jhandii hil jaae yaar kaa signal mil jaae injan meraa siitii maare thodaa saa dhadake tere dil kii patarii pe threedots  dil ko roko na dil ko toko na ye ghadii hai mulaakaat kii dil diyaa tujhako chun liyaa tujhako phir sanam der kis baat kii pyaar kii gaddii chalane de is duniyaa ko jalane de har mausam men daudaa jaae ye tuufaanii mel tere dil kii patarii pe daudegii threedots  terii baahon men dil kii raahon men zindagii hai suhaanaa safar tere pyaar kii is khumaarii men na rahii mujhako apanii khabar tuu hii merii manzil hai tuu hii meraa saahil hai chaahat kaa injan hotaa hai kabhii nahiin fel tere dil kii patarii pe daudegii threedots

Title: is duniyaa men premagranth jab likhaa jaaegaa
Lyrics: aa aa ho aa premagranth is duniyaa men premagranth jab likhaa jaaegaa teraa meraa ho teraa meraa ho teraa meraa naam sabase uupar aaegaa is duniyaa men threedots  band kalii se phuul banii main aaj piyaa ne ang lagaayaa gorii ke kore mukhade par prem ne apanaa rang lagaayaa ab main sajanii tuu meraa saajan kahalaaegaa is duniyaa men threedots  ek anokhii anajaanii sii mere man men pyaas jagii hai baahar hai phuulon kaa mausam dil ke andar aag lagii hai apane pyaar kaa saavan ab ye aag bujhaaegaa is duniyaa men threedots  rok sake to rok le duniyaa rukane vaalii baat nahiin hai ye koii tuufaan nahiin hai ye koii barasaat nahiin hai ye hai pyaar kaa jaaduu ye jaaduu chal jaaegaa is duniyaa men threedots

Title: sajanaa o sajanaa  terii baahon men hai jannat merii  jiinaa terii galii men
Lyrics: sajanaa o sajanaa sajanii o sajanii terii baahon men hai jannat merii pyaarii nayanon kii do galiyaan terii jiinaa terii galii men sajanii o sajanii threedots  ye rangiin nazaare hain mastii ke ishaare hain o kahiin duur chalen baahon ke sahaare hain aramaan dil ke mil ke pukaare hain jiinaa terii galii men threedots  hamako kyaa zamaane se isake ruuth jaane se baaz nahiin aaegaa ye diivaaren uthaane se ham to milenge kisii bhii bahaane se jiinaa terii galii men threedots

Title: saagar sang kinaare hain phuulon sang bahaaren hain
Lyrics: saagar sang kinaare hain phuulon sang bahaaren hain aise men tum mere ho aur ham tumhaare hain saagar sang kinaare hain threedots  dil jo hamaaraa thaa kal tak kyuun vo kisii kaa hone lagaa usake tasavvur men din rain jab dil meraa khone lagaa merii kasam hai tumako sanam dil se judaa na karanaa ham tum donon aise rahenge jaise chaand taare hain saagar sang kinaare hain threedots  ham hain tum ho aur ye dekho rang birangii vaadii hai baarish bhii thande mausam men aur bhii aag lagaatii hai dar lagataa hai in baaton se kuchh duurii zaruurii hai tan man jab tak donon milen na pyaar kii pyaas adhuurii hai pyaar kii baazii men rab jaane kyaa jiite kyaa haare hain o jaanam tum mere ho ham tumhaare hain saagar sang kinaare hain threedots

Title: maine jii liyaa mar liyaa prem kar liyaa  jitanaa daranaa thaa dar liyaa
Lyrics: maine jii liyaa mar liyaa prem kar liyaa jitanaa daranaa thaa dar liyaa prem kar liyaa prem kar liyaa threedots  har ek prem kahaanii men is dariyaa ke paanii men duub gae naadaanii men kitane log javaanii men prem kaa hamako sahaaraa nahiin lenaa tay kar liyaa prem kar liyaa threedots  duniyaa vaale kahate hain prem galii jo rahate hain dard hazaaron sahate hain aankh se aansuu bahate hain prem galii men hii rahane ko hamane ghar liyaa prem kar liyaa threedots  hai zaalim sansaar kahaan raste hain diivaar kahaan aae hain majhadhaar kahaan kaate hain talavaar kahaan hamane aaj hathelii pe sar apanaa dhar liyaa prem kar liyaa threedots

Title: dil dil dil na todo gumasum tum rahanaa  ye pyaar bharaa dil tere lie hai
Lyrics: dil dil dil na todo gumasum tum rahanaa chhodo dekho kab se kahate hain sanam ye pyaar bharaa dil tere lie hai dil dil dil naa threedots  dil ko sanbhaalo yuun na uchhaalo pahaluu se jo dil gayaa meraa naam loge ilzaam doge rusavaa karoge piyaa sach hii kahataa hai terii khataa hai tuune churaayaa hai dil jiivan ke safar men har ek dagar men tuu hai merii manzil dil dil dil naa threedots  tuu pyaar kar le ikarar kar le bas aarazuu hai yahii tuu paas aaii dil men samaaii kyon duur phir bhii rahii tuu to hai ladakaa dil meraa dhadakaa har baat tuune kahii main to huun ladakii main kaise kahatii dil kii to dil men rahii dil dil dil naa threedots  ye pal nashiile chhaliyaa rangiile kal honge jaane kahaan mausam kaa raahii degaa gavaahii ham tum mile the yahaan in vaadiyon men kaisii kashish hai kaisii hai jaaduugarii dil chaahataa hai mil ke guzaaren ham tum yahiin zindagii dil dil dil naa threedots  ab ham saath jien mar jaaen pyaar men kisii kii jiit naa to haar hotii hai pyaar men bhare takaraar kii manzil to pyaar hotii hai miyaan andar hotaa hai biivii bhii andar hotii hai

Title: koyaliyaa jab gaatii hai paayaliyaa chhanakaatii hai  nadiyaa ke paanii ne chhuaa
Lyrics: koyaliyaa jab gaatii hai paayaliyaa chhanakaatii hai sard havaa jab aatii hai suii chubhaa ke jaatii hai nadiyaa ke paanii ne chhuaa kaise bataauun kyaa huaa  koyaliyaa jab gaatii threedots  miithaa miithaa dard hai miithii miithii pyaas hai chadhatii javaanii kaa ehasaas hai baahon men samet luun mahakii bahaar ko dil kahe rok luun nadiyaa kii dhaar ko dolo tum balakhaao bin saavan laharaao nadiyaa ke paanii ne threedots  thandii thandii aag hai bhiigaa bhiigaa ang hai dasen tanhaaiyaan koii nahiin sang hai saansen hai dhuaan jalataa hai man meraa rah rah ke ghabaraauun jal men na jal jaauun nadiyaa ke paanii ne threedots

Title: khaamoshii thii mach gayaa shor  aayaa aayaa mere dil kaa chor
Lyrics: khaamoshii thii mach gayaa shor aayaa aayaa mere dil kaa chor vo tum nahiin vo tum nahiin vo to hai koii aur khaamoshii thii mach gayaa threedots  main bhalaa kyaa karuun vo sune na merii daastaan beraham bekhabar hai use kyaa khabar usape to meraa na chale jaaneman koii zor khaamoshii thii mach gayaa threedots  main yahaan to kahaan dhuundhatii hai usii ko nazar chhode naa berukhii meraa jaanejaan meraa dardejigar husn kii ye adaa dekh na dilarubaa na jude dil ke aramaanon se chaahat kii dor khaamoshii thii mach gayaa threedots

Title: ishq naa karanaa kabhii tum ishq naa karanaa
Lyrics: balleshaah kade ishq naa karie ishq de khel niraale ishq le mittii vich milaae taajaan takhtaan vaale  ishq naa karanaa kabhii tum ishq naa karanaa ishq kii baajii koii naa jiitaa sab aashiq gae haar kabhii tum ishq naa threedots  ishq men laakhon dard bichhode ishq ne laakhon ke dil tode sohanii ne bhii jaan ganvaaii sarasii ghar vaapas naa aaii ishq kii baat kare jab koii mat karanaa aitabaar ho ho ishq naa karanaa threedots  do raahen hain par jab aa jaaen aashiq ko kuchh samajh naa aae chhod ke raanjhaa takht hazaaraa naukar banake kare gujaaraa ishq ke diivaanon ne dhokhaa khaayaa har baar ishq naa karanaa threedots

Lyrics: sukh jo afasaane dil ne bune       unako koii dil hii sune       ham haule haule pyaar kii dhundalii fizaaon men aaye       gahare gahare hain kvaab kii niilii ghataaon ke saaye       ham tum donon khoye khoye       sapane dekhen jaage soye       gumasum hairaan  ko ye jo zindagii hai koii daastaan hai       kab hogaa kyaa ye khabar kahaan hai       ye jo zindagii hai koii kaaravaan hai       kahaan jaayegii ye khabar kahaan hai 2  sujaabahatii hain chingaariyaan jaise       sar se paanv tak nas nas men       halkaa halkaa hosh hai lekin       kuchh bhii nahiin ab mere bas men        mere ang ang men bechainii bijalii banake laharaaye       ek miithe miithe dard kaa baadal tan man par chhaaye       saansen ulajhe dhadake ye dil       jaane kaise merii mushkil       hogii aasaan  ko   ye jo zindagii hai koii daastaan hai       kab hogaa kyaa ye khabar kahaan hai       ye jo zindagii hai koii kaaravaan hai       kahaan jaayegii ye khabar kahaan hai 3  sukh are kaash merii in aankhon kii ab roshanii bujh jaaye       main ne dekhaa thaa jo kvaab vo mujhako na kabhii yaad aaye       aise barase gam ke tiishe       tuute dil ke saare shiishe       dil hai viiraan  ko   ye jo zindagii hai koii daastaan hai       kab hogaa kyaa ye khabar kahaan hai       ye jo zindagii hai koii kaaravaan hai       kahaan jaayegii ye khabar kahaan hai 2

Title: aawaaragii barangetamaashaa burii nahiin
Lyrics: aawaaragii barangetamaashaa burii nahiin zauqenazar mile to ye duniyaa burii nahiin  kahate hain terii zulfepariishaan ko zindagii ai dost zindagii kii tamannaa burii nahiin  hai naakudaa kaa merii tabaahii se waastaa main jaanataa huun niiyatedariyaa burii nahiin  is rahazanehayaat zamaane se duur chal mar bhii gaye to chaadaresaharaa burii nahiin

Lyrics: kushiyon kii saugaat hai naarii 2  duniyaa men ham sab kii jananii hai naarii 2  bhuumi pe bhii svarg men bhii anamol daulat hai naarii   anamol daulat hai naarii   he ladakii dekhii bhuukh ud gaii   ladakii dekhii niind ud gaii   ladakii dekhii baat ban gaii hoy   ka ka ka ka ka ka college ke saathii  ka college ke saathii 4  saathii mile pyaarepyaare kisse huye dil ke saare   kaashmir jaisaa gulashan capco king kaa garden   har din hai fashion show    aankhen silicon graphic ladakiiyon se jam hotaa traffic    gaal aise chamaken jaise laser  teraa love letter kahataa hai pager   main pyaar kaa computer aur tuu hai software     sundar ladakii har dam hai inspiration aage badhatii unase younger generation         ka ka ka ka ka ka college ke saathii ka college ke saathii

Title: gair se aankh ladaaii to ladaaii hogii
Lyrics: mere hamasafar bolo sochakar mujhamen tujhako achchhaa kyaa lagaa teraa muskuraanaa teraa sharamaanaa nazaren jhukaanaa mere hamasafar threedots  teraa yaaraanaa baaten banaanaa sapane dikhaanaa  ruup kaa ras yuun hii piite bhar to naa jaaegaa dil kahiin mujhase jab tak phuul khilenge phuulon pe hogii shabanam jab tak aag milan kii ho naa paaegii kam mere hamasafar threedots  terii pyaarii aankhen terii miithii baaten dil kaa to kyaa kahanaa  saare jahaan kii nazaron se chhupakar har ghadii har pal pyaar karenge dhuundh naa sakegii hamako kabhii judaaii sab kuchh maine paayaa jo terii mohabbat paaii mere hamasafar threedots  teraa tadapaanaa teraa bahalaanaa teraa paas aanaa  mere hamasafar threedots

Title: kaun kisake haath aayaa aur khilaunaa ho gayaa
Lyrics: kaun kisake haath aayaa aur khilaunaa ho gayaa chhodiye is baat ko jo bhii thaa honaa ho gayaa  usake kuuche kii zamiin jis roz mainne odh lii aasamaan us roz se meraa bichhaunaa ho gayaa  dekh luun to der tak letii hai chatakhaare nazar jaayaqaa ab usake chehare kaa salonaa ho gayaa  merii qiimat sirf piital ke baraabar thii qatiil chhuu ke paarasbadan ko main to sonaa ho gayaa

Title: terii saanson kaa merii saanson se sangam ho ke rahegaa
Lyrics: terii saanson kaa merii saanson se sangam ho ke rahegaa terii aankhon kaa merii aankhon se sangam ho ke rahegaa aa terii aankhon kaa threedots  jab pyaar kiyaa to pyaar kiyaa har aag se ab ham khelenge kitane bhii bade gam kyon naa hon chhote se dil par jhelenge terii raaton kaa merii raaton se sangam ho ke rahegaa tere khvaabon kaa mere khvaabon se sangam ho ke rahegaa aa terii saanson kaa threedots  mujhamen aag jo lagii hai use aur bhadakaa de o jitanaa dhadak rahaa hai dil use aur dhadakaa de terii baahon kaa merii baahon se sangam ho ke rahegaa terii raahon kaa merii raahon se sangam ho ke rahegaa aa terii saanson kaa threedots  chaahe suuraj uganaa chhod de chaahe nadiyaa bahanaa chhod de chaahe patajhad hanse bahaaron men chaahe kaliyaan khilanaa chhod den tere jiivan kaa mere jiivan se sangam ho ke rahegaa tere har gam kaa mere har gam se sangam ho ke rahegaa aa terii saanson kaa threedots

Title: ladakii badii anjaanii hai
Lyrics: oh oho he eye he he la la la ladakii badii anjaanii hai sapanaa hai sach hai kahaanii hai dekho ye pagalii bilkul naa badalii ye to vahii diivaanii hai  ladakaa badaa anjaanaa hai sapanaa hai sach hai fasaanaa hai aa haa ye pagalaa bilkul naa badalaa ye to vahii diivaanaa hai  paas rah ke bhii thii duurii jaane kaisii thii majabuurii vaqt vo bhii ajiib thaa jab tuu mere kariib thaa kho gaii ye kis jahaan men main yahaan huun dekh to zaraa ladakaa badaa anjaanaa hai threedots  bhiid men bhii thii tanhaaii yaad har pal terii aaii roke koii mujhe zaraa bhar naa aae ye dil meraa bahake bahake mere kadam aise men tuu sambhaal to zaraa ladakii badii anjaanii hai threedots  tum ne naa jaane kyaa sapane dikhaae jaage naa sotaa hai kuchh kuchh hotaa hai

Title: saavan barasataa hai  tujhase mil kar bhii yah dil tarasataa hai
Lyrics: saavan aayaa saavan barasataa hai tujhase milane ko tujhase mil kar bhii yah dil tarasataa hai saavan barasataa hai threedots  thahar thahar jaage man men lahar koii thar thar tan kaanpe aise lahar lahar par bin maanjhii ke naiyaa dole jaise jhuum ke baadal ghire tuut ke barasii ghataa chuum ke bhiigaa badan chhede yah thandii havaa saavan barasataa hai threedots  taras taras gae kitane baras yahaan tab hain ye baadal barase badhatii jaae man kii dhadakan dekh na pyaasii nazar se pyaar kii pyaas badhe jab bhii javaanii men jii chaahe jal jaauun barakhaa ke paanii men saavan barasataa hai threedots

Title: dil meraa luteyaa gayaa
Lyrics: zing lak lak zing ik duunii duunii te do duunii chaar kii gal hoii tuu das mere yaar mainuun ishq daa chadheyaa bukhaar dil meraa luteyaa gayaa luteyaa gayaa luteyaa gayaa ho mere yaar dil meraa luteyaa gayaa  he lad gaii lad gaii aankh ye lad gaii tere ruup kii mastii chadh gaii he tuu chaahe to hosh udaa de suulii pe tuu mujhe chadhaa de kuchh bhii kar le yaar  ke dil meraa luteyaa gayaa threedots  pahalii baar meraa man bhatakaa dekhake tujhako lagaa hai jhatakaa maine sochaa mil gayaa baankaa jud gayaa mere pyaar kaa taankaa dil baithii main haar ai dil meraa luteyaa gayaa threedots  ik duunii duunii te do duunii chaar das phir aage huaa kyaa yaar kii dasiye akkhaan jad ladiyaan pyaar diyaan lagiyaan hathakadiyaan oe tuune kar diyaa mujhe diivaanaa ab tuu mujhase duur na jaanaa chhid gae dil ke taar ke dil meraa luteyaa gayaa threedots  aaag lagii sholaa ik bhadakaa usape tuune paanii chhidakaa tuune kiyaa hai kaisaa jaaduu ho gayaa meraa dil bekaabuu kar le aankhen chaar ke dil meraa luteyaa gayaa threedots

Title: zor dekho shor dekho thodaa kaho thodaa suno
Lyrics: zor zor dekho shor dekho thodaa kaho thodaa suno zor dekho shor dekho thodaa ruko thodaa chalo kisii ne kisii se kahaa machaa hai shahar men ye shor ye hai zor  zindagii khushanumaa vaqt khilataa huaa jo sapanon men thaa vo bhii haasil huaa dil ko baandhe hue pyaar kii dor hai ye kahaanii to hai jab talak zor hai zor dekho shor dekho threedots  jab bhii dar saa lage chaand chhupane lage ho andheraa badaa tum agar ruk gae ye nahiin dekhanaa raat ghanaghor hai yaad rakhanaa zaraa tum men bhii zor hai zor dekho shor dekho threedots

Title: jinako jiine ke dhang aate hain
Lyrics: jinako jiine ke dhang aate hain waade aksar wo bhuul jaate hain  kaate katatii nahiin shabehijraan kaise kaise sitam wo dhaate hain  aashiqon kii ajiib manzil hai dil ko kho kar hii chain paate hain  haath uthaa kar duaaen mat diije dil men laakhon kayaal aate hain  bhiid men rah ke ho gaye gumanaam yuun judaaii se dil lagaate hain

Title: laakhon aashiq mar jaate hain merii ik muskaan men
Singer: udit narayan abhijit alka yagnik jaspindar narula
Lyrics: laakhon aashiq mar jaate hain merii ik muskaan men laakhon aashiq mar jaate hain terii ik muskaan men mere jaisaa koii nahiin hai saare hindustaan men tere jaisaa koii nahiin hai saare hindustaan men oe hoe  khan khan khan khan chuudii khanake chhan chhan chhan chhan paayal baaje ho sar sar sar sar chunarii sarake chham chham chham chham gorii naache o balakhaa ke zaraa thumakaa lagaa dilajaanii ab jalavaa dikhaa aa o ho laakhon aashiq threedots  main huun khushbuu main huun shabanam main huun sholaa main huun bijalii bachake rahanaa mujhase logon aag lagaane main huun nikalii merii bijalii chal bijalii giraa ye jalenge hamen aaegaa mazaa aa o laakhon aashiq threedots

Title: mhaare hivadaa men naache mor tak thaiyaa
Film: hum saath saath hain we stand united
Singer: kavita subramaniam hariharan anuradha paudwal kumar sanu alka yagnik udit narayan
Lyrics: mhaare hivadaa men mhaare hivadaa men naache mor tak thaiyaa thaiyaa bhanvare ne machaayaa shor khilii dil kii kaliyaan badalaa mausam badale nazaare yaa badalaa hai najariyaa mhaare hivadaa men threedots  tuu naii navelii dulhan hai teraa ruup pyaar kaa darpan hai o tere menhadii se tere gajare se mahakaa mahakaa meraa jiivan hai mere savaalon kaa javaab ban ke tuu aaii sajaniyaa o mhaare hivadaa men threedots  aisii bandhii pyaar kii dor huii main baanvariyaa badalaa mausam badale threedots  ye pyaar kaa saavan aayaa hai sang priit kaa mausam laayaa hai o jo dil men chhupaa ke rakhaa thaa vo raaz labon par aayaa hai dil men basaa ke apanaa banaa ke le chalo prem nagariyaa mhaare hivadaa men threedots  chaahe le jaao jis or sang chaluungii saiyaan badalaa mausam badale threedots  ye chaand sitaaron kii baaraat laaii hai ghadii suhaanii kyaa baat hai mere saath hai mere sapanon kii raanii barason sataayaa tuune chain churaayaa main aaj na chhoduun baiyaan haan haan o ho huun huun

Title: dilabar dilabar hosh naa khabar hai
Lyrics: dilabar dilabar haan dilabar dilabar hosh naa khabar hai ye kaisaa asar hai tumase milane ke baad dilabar dard hai chubhan hai kyaa diivaanaapan hai tumase milane ke baad dilabar dilabar dilabar threedots  tuu meraa khvaab hai tuu mere dil kaa karaar dekh le jaaeman dekh le bas ek baar chuum le jism ko hamanashiin paas aa chain kho gayaa hai kuchh to ho gayaa hai tumase milane ke baad dilabar dilabar dilabar threedots  ishq betaab hai husn kii mahakii bahaar duuriyaan kisalie kisalie ab intazaar tuutataa hai badan kyaa huaa kyaa pataa pyaas men dhalii huun raat din jalii huun tumase milane ke baad dilabar dilabar dilabar threedots

Title: saajan saajan terii dulhan tujhako pukaare aajaa
Lyrics: chaandanii raat taaron kii baaraat hai dil kii mahafil sajaane men kyaa der hai kyaa der hai dhadakanen dil kii shahanaaiiyaan ban gaiin ab to saajan ke aane men kyaa der hai kyaa der hai  merii zindagii meraa pyaar yaad aa rahaa hai aane vaalaa hai jo vo yaad aa rahaa hai saajan saajan terii dulhan tujhako pukaare aajaa aakar mere haathon men menhadii tuu hii rachaa jaa aajaa aajaa o merii zindagii meraa threedots  paayal kaajal kangan daaman saare tujhe bulaaen aajaa saajan aajaa tere apane tujhe bulaaen aajaa aajaa saajan aajaa mere mahabuub o mere hamasafar tujhako kyaa pataa hai tujhe kyaa khabar ehasaan tere itane hain mujh par rab pe yakiin hai jitanaa utanaa hai tujh par aajaa aajaa aajaa meraa mahabuub meraa sanam aa rahaa hai ham to mar hii chuke the phir janam aa rahaa hai saajan saajan threedots  chunarii merii rangii huii hai tere rang se saajan aakar rang de meraa ang ang apane rang se saajan aajaa aajaa saajan aajaa tumase vafaaen bahut main karuungii kasam terii ab ye dil kisii ko na duungii aa tujhe bataa duun mere dil men kyaa hai dil lene vaale tujhe jaan apanii duungii aajaa aajaa aajaa dhadakanen badh rahii hain vo kariib aa rahaa hai khushanasiibii banake meraa vo nasiib aa rahaa hai saajan saajan threedots

Title: koii jhanakaar hai nagamaa hai
Lyrics: amit koii jhanakaar hai nagamaa hai sadaa hai kyaa hai2 tuu kiran hai ki kalii hai ki sabaa hai kyaa hai suresh koii jhanakaar hai nagamaa hai sadaa hai kyaa hai tuu kiran hai ki kalii hai ki sabaa hai kyaa hai koii jhanakaar hai nagamaa hai sadaa hai kyaa hai  amit terii aankhon men kaii rang jhalakate dekhe2 suresh terii aankhon men kaii rang jhalakate dekhe2 amit saadagii hai ki jhijhak hai ki hayaa hai kyaa hai koii jhanakaar hai nagamaa hai sadaa hai kyaa hai suresh tuu kiran hai ki kalii hai ki sabaa hai kyaa hai koii jhanakaar hai nagamaa hai sadaa hai kyaa hai  ruuh kii pyaas bujhaa dii hai terii qurbat ne2 amit ruuh kii pyaas bujhaa dii hai terii qurbat ne2 suresh tuu koii jhiil hai jharanaa hai ghataa hai kyaa hai koii jhanakaar hai nagamaa hai sadaa hai kyaa hai amit tuu kiran hai ki kalii hai ki sabaa hai kyaa hai koii jhanakaar hai nagamaa hai sadaa hai kyaa hai  amit naam honthon pe teraa aaye to raahat sii mile2 suresh naam honthon pe teraa aaye to raahat sii mile2 amit tuu tasallii hai dilaasaa hai duaa hai kyaa hai koii jhanakaar hai nagamaa hai sadaa hai kyaa hai suresh tuu kiran hai ki kalii hai ki sabaa hai kyaa hai donon koii jhanakaar hai nagamaa hai sadaa hai kyaa hai

Title: tapakaa re tapakaa ik aur tapakaa
Lyrics: tapakaa re tapakaa ik aur tapakaa do men se ek gayaa ek kaa ye matakaa tiisaraa hai tapakaa dhing dhaatum dhidhing tapakaa re tapakaa threedots  ab teraa number hai dar naa jaanaa marane se pahale tuu mar naa jaanaa honthon pe tere dam teraa atakaa do men se ek gayaa threedots  chaar men se chaar gae phod do ye matakaa chauthaa hai tapakaa phod do ye matakaa tapakaa re tapakaa threedots  chaaron ne apane yaaron ko maaraa yaaron ne milakar chaaron ko maaraa baakii rahaa naa koii bhii khatakaa chaar men se chaar gae threedots

Title: o priyaa priyaa kyon bhulaa diyaa
Lyrics: purushh o priyaa priyaa kyuun bhulaa diyaa bevafaa yaa beraham kyaa kahuun tujhe sanam tuune dil todaa hai bhuul kyaa huii ye bataa jaa o priyaa priyaa threedots  strii o piiyaa piiyaa main terii piiyaa aansuon ko pii gaii jaane kaise jii gaii kyaa hai merii majabuurii kaise main bataauun huaa kyaa  purushh o priyaa priyaathreedots  tuu bevafaa hai jo main jaan jaataa  tujh se kabhii bhii dil na lagaataa	2 strii mujh pe yakiin kar yuun na ilzaam de de koii sazaa magar bevafaa na naam de purushh merii dilarubaa tuune ki jafaa par tujhe bhuulegii na merii vafaa strii o piiyaa piiyaathreedots  purushh jii chaahataa hai ki kudako jalaa duun maut ko apane dil se lagaa luun strii aake zaraa dekh le dil meraa chiir ke rang milenge tujhe terii tasviir ke purushh mere saathiyaa teraa ho bhalaa ye hii mere tuute hue dil kii sazaa strii o piiyaa piiyaathreedots

Title: cholii ke piichhe vaalii maadhurii hai kyaa bol re saale
Lyrics: cholii ke piichhe vaalii maadhurii hai kyaa bol re saale o saale bol re saale o saale kaalii kaalii aankhon vaalii kaajol hai kyaa o saale bol re saale o saale  shilpaa shettii ke jaisaa figure hai kyaa agar tuu naa bolaa ye bhed naa kholaa kahaan usako dhuundhenge kuchh to bataa cholii ke piichhe vaalii threedots  jhilamil madhur chaandanii jaisii shriidevii hai kyaa chhuii muii makkhan jaisii vo ladakii juuhii hai kyaa maniishaa koiiraalaa jaisii sharmiilii hai kyaa natakhat shokh karismaa jaisii rangiilii hai kyaa sonaalii bendre madhu miinaaxii jayaa pradaa mandaakinii he he dil ko jo dhadakaatii hai tabbuu hai kyaa tujhako jo tadapaatii hai khushbuu hai kyaa agar tuu naa bolaa threedots  aishvaryaa ke jaisii hiire kaa tukadaa hai kyaa bholii bhaalii sushmitaa saa vo mukhadaa hai kyaa rambhaa saa madahosh gulaabii vo cheharaa hai kyaa tvinkal khannaa jaisii usakii chanchal adaa hai kyaa puujaa disko shaanti tiinaa nagmaa bhaagyashrii he he madamast honthon vaalii raviinaa hai kyaa pal men paagal jo kar de ramaiyaa hai kyaa agar tuu naa bolaa threedots

Title: chupake chupake sakhiyon se vo baaten karanaa bhuul gaii
Lyrics: chupake chupake sakhiyon se vo baaten karanaa bhuul gaii mujhako dekhaa panaghat pe to paanii bharanaa bhuul gaii chupake chupake sakhiyon se threedots  pahale shaayad usako mere chehare kaa andaaz naa thaa mujhase aankhen takaraaiin to khud pe maranaa bhuul gaii chupake chupake sakhiyon se threedots  sach puuchho to merii vajah se usako aisaa rog lagaa kaajal mehandii kangan bindiyaa se sanvaranaa bhuul gaii chupake chupake sakhiyon se threedots  kyaa jaane kab usase milane aa jaauun is khvaahish men chhat par baithii rahatii hai vo chhat se utaranaa bhuul gaii chupake chupake sakhiyon se threedots

Title: aatii kyaa khandaalaa
Lyrics: ai kyaa bolatii tuu ai kyaa main boluun sun  sunaa  aatii kyaa khandaalaa kyaa karuun aake main khandaalaa ghuumenge phirenge naachenge gaayenge  aish karenge aur kyaa ai kyaa bolatii tuu   threedots  barasaat kaa siizan hai khandaalaa jaake kyaa karanaa  barasaat ke siizan men hii to mazaa hai merii mainaa bhiiguungii main sadrii khaansii ho jaayegii mujhako chaddar leke jaayenge paagal samajhii kyaa mujhako  kyaa karuun samajh men aaye na kyaa kahuun tujhase men jaanuun na are itanaa tuu kyon soche main aage tuu piichhe  bas ab nikalate aur kyaa ai kyaa bolatii tuu   threedots   lonavalaa men chikkii khaayenge waterfall pe jaayenge khandaalaa ke guard ke uupar fotuu khiinch ke aayenge haan bhii karataa na bhii karataa dil meraa diivaanaa dil bhii saalaa party badale kaisaa hai zamaanaa puuchh le aakhir hai kyaa majaraa are pal men phisalataa hai pal men sambhalataa hai  ai kyaa bolatii tuu   threedots

Title: sapanaa meraa sach ho gayaa  kabhii main kahuun kabhii tum kaho
Lyrics: sapanaa meraa sach ho gayaa kabhii main kahuun kabhii tum kaho ki maine tumhen ye dil de diyaa  kabhii main sunuun kabhii tum suno ki maine tumhen ye dil de diyaa kabhii main kahuun kabhii tum threedots  saath saath ham aas paas yuun baithe rahen ek duusare se yahii kahate rahen paas paas ham saath saath yuun baithe rahen ek duusare se yahii kahate rahen kabhii main kahuun kabhii tum threedots  chalate rahen udate rahen ham bahate rahen ek duusare se yahii kahate rahen kabhii main kahuun kabhii tum threedots  dardedil dardejigar ham sahate rahen ek duusare se yahii kahate rahen kabhii main kahuun kabhii tum threedots

Title: aaj raat aaegaa mazaa diivaane ho jaaenge fidaa
Lyrics: aaj raat aaegaa mazaa diivaane ho jaaenge fidaa jaaduu hai merii adaaon men mastii nigaahon men aa merii baahon men aa aaj raat aaegaa threedots  har dil pe hai chhaayaa rahaa merii aashiqii kaa nashaa main chaahatii kisako yahaan kisii ko nahiin hai pataa aaj raat aaegaa threedots  saansen badii bechain hain labon pe hasiin daastaan tanhaaiiyaan kahane lagiin na duurii rahe daramiyaan aaj raat aaegaa threedots

Title: chalii aa re  chorii se  bach ke duniyaa kii nazaron se
Singer: amitabh bachchan sonu nigam jaspindar narula
Lyrics: chalii aa re chalii aa re chalii aa re chorii se chorii se chorii chorii chorii se aa chorii se chorii se chorii chorii chorii chorii chorii se bole re bole re meraa dil bole bole bole re bach bach bach bach ke duniyaa kii nazaron se are sanam tanhaaii men milo kabhii kabhii he chorii se chorii se threedots  aise vaise kaii savaalon men khoyaa rahuun tere khyaalon men karo zaraa jaldii mulaakaaten tumase karanii hain badii baaten chaandanii sitaaron men ho soii tere mere sivaa ho na koii thandii thandii aag jal rahii ho sard sard havaa chal rahii ho bach bach bach bach ke threedots  milane nahiin degaa ye zamaanaa koii to banaao tum bahaanaa khulii khulii laten bikharaao aur na tum mujhe tadapaao vaqt kabhii kahiin nahiin thahare nikal jaaen mauqe naa sunahare dard judaaii ke bade gahare yahaan vahaan lage kaii pahare bach bach bach bach ke threedots

Title: daulat milii jahaan kii naamonishaan mile
Lyrics: daulat milii jahaan kii naamonishaan mile sab kuchh milaa hamen na magar maharabaan mile  hamako kushii milii bhii to bas aariizii milii lekin jo gam mile wo gamejaawidaan mile  phir kyuun kare talaash koii aur aastaan wo kushanasiib jisako teraa aasataan mile  nazaren talaash karatii rahiin jinako umr bhar darshan ko wo sukuun ke lamhe kahaan mile

Title: is tarah aashiqii kaa asar chhod jaauungaa
Lyrics: is tarah aashiqii kaa asar chhod jaauungaa 3 tere chehare pe apanii nazar chhod jaauungaa 2 is tarah aashiqii kaa threedots  main diivaanaa ban gayaa huun kaisii ye muhabbat hai zindagii se badhakar ab terii zaruurat hai mujhako tuu chaahie teraa pyaar chaahie ek baar nahiin sau baar chaahie har saans main apanii tujhape lutaauungaa dil ke lahuu se terii maang sajaauungaa tere chehare pe apanii threedots  pyaar kyaa hai dard kyaa hai diivaane samajhate hain ishq men jalane kaa matalab aashiq hii samajhate hain main tadapataa huun tujhase kuchh na kahuun bin kahe bhii magar main to rah na sakuun is bekhudii men aakhir kahaan chain paauungaa mar ke bhii main tujhase judaa ho na paauungaa tere chehare pe apanii threedots

Title: hamako tumase pyaar hai jiyaa bekaraar hai
Lyrics: hamako tumase pyaar hai jiyaa bekaraar hai aajaa merii bulabul teraa intazaar hai  tere bin o jaanam niind bhii aatii nahiin chain bhii aataa nahiin jaan bhii jaatii nahiin dil teraa biimaar hai ek sau tiin bukhaar hai aajaa merii lailaa teraa intazaar hai hamako tumase pyaar hai threedots  ladakii hai hasiin tuu dikhane men namakiin tuu tere hansane se lage tabiiyat kii rangiin tuu bangalaa nadii ke paar hai honda bhii taiyaar hai aajaa merii sonii teraa intazaar hai hamako tumase pyaar hai threedots

Title: mujhase qaafir ko tere ishq ne yuun sharamaayaa
Lyrics: mujhase qaafir ko tere ishq ne yuun sharamaayaa dil tujhe dekh ke dhadakaa to kudaa yaad aayaa  chaaraagar aaj sitaaron kii qasam khaa ke bataa kisane insaan ko tabasuum ke liye tarasaayaa  nazr karataa rahaa main phuul se jazbaat use jisane patthar ke khilaunon se mujhe bahalaayaa  usake andar koii fanakaar chhupaa baithaa hai jaanate buujhate jis shaks ne dhokhaa khaayaa

Title: mujhe aapakii yahaan chaahat lekar aaii hai  maine aapase shoharat
Lyrics: mujhe aapakii yahaan chaahat lekar aaii hai sach maanie merii baaton men sachchaaii hai maine aapase shoharat kii manzil paaii hai ab main kahaan jaauungaa jab tak kahaa gaauungaa mujhe aapakii yahaan threedots  churaa le gayaa ye dil to meraa mujhako ye dekhane kaa andaaz aapakaa khvaabon tale kho gayaa huun diivaanaa main ho gayaa huun ab main kahaan threedots  koii saamane nazar ke rahe to jhuum ke gaataa jaa ye dil meraa kahe ye aap maanen na maanen aayaa huun nagmen sunaane ab main kahaan threedots

Title: patnii pati ke lie de de apanii jaan
Film: hum aapke dil mein rehte hain
Lyrics: kaaryeshudaasii karneshumantrii bhojeshumaataa shayaneshurambhaa patnii pati ke lie de de apanii jaan aurat se badhake na koii yahaan sukh men bhii saath de dukh men bhii saath de ye bane sevikaa premikaa patnii pati ke lie threedots  tyaag aur samarpan hai patnii kaa naam ye pati kii sevaa kare subahoshaam vrat rakhe duaa de pujaaran bane sirf prem dhaage se jiivan bandhe mamataa kii chaandanii ye aisii roshanii jo har andheraa mitaa de ye nayaa ruup hai devii kaa patnii pati ke lie threedots  jo nahiin hai patnii to kyaa hai pati isakii mannaton kaa silaa hai pati jo kabhii bhii patnii se dhokhaa kare vo na zindagii men kabhii khush rahe jisane bhii hai kahii ye baat hai sahii samajho ise isako jaano ye to hai sundar mallikaa patnii pati ke lie threedots

Title: kyaa sochataa hai ai dil kyaa savaal karataa hai
Lyrics: kyaa sochataa hai ai dil kyaa savaal karataa hai ye pyaar to sabhii kaa buraa haal karataa hai kyaa sochataa hai ai threedots  jisane pyaar kiyaa dil kaa etabaar kiyaa usane to khud hii apanaa bas jiinaa dushvaar kiyaa pahate to dil lagaa ke phir dard miithaa paa ke kyaa kamaal karataa hai ye pyaar to sabhii kaa threedots  jaataa hai ik nazar men dil kaa sukuun saaraa detaa jo bekaraarii lagataa hai vo hii pyaaraa kyaa ham bataaen kaise mat puuchho kaise kaise kyaa kamaal karataa hai ye pyaar to sabhii kaa threedots

Title: kahaa kare koii churaa liyaa dil ko
Lyrics: kahaa kare koii churaa liyaa dil ko main to kahuun tumane bachaa liyaa dil ko aarazuu hai yahii ke nasiibaa khule aap jaisaa hamen phir mile naa mile kahaa kare koii threedots  ik baat puuchhuun sach sach kahoge aankhen badal ke chal to na doge bas isii kauf se dil hamaaraa jale aap jaisaa hamen threedots  ye jaanodil sab rakh duun lutaa ke ik baar dekho to aajamaa ke zindagii daal dii hamane kadamon tale kahaa kare koii threedots

Title: main koii aisaa giit gaauun  agar tum kaho
Lyrics: main koii aisaa giit gaauun ki aarazuu jagaauun agar tum kaho tumako bulaauun ki palaken bichhaauun kadam tum jahaan jahaan rakho zamiin ko aasamaan banaauun sitaaron se sajaauun agar tum kaho main koii aisaa giit threedots  main titaliyon ke piichhe bhaaguun main juganuon ke piichhe bhaaguun ye rang hai vo roshanii hai tumhaare paas donon laa duun jitanii khushbuen baag men milen main laauun vahaan pe ki tum ho jahaan jahaan pe ek pal bhii thaharo main gulistaan banaauun agar tum kaho main koii aisaa giit threedots  agar tum kaho to main sunaauun tumhen hasiin kahaaniyaan sunogii kyaa merii jabaanii ek parii kii daastaan yaa main karuun tumase bayaan ki raajaa se raanii milii thii kahaan kahaaniyon ke nagar men tumhen le ke jaauun agar tum kaho main koii aisaa giit threedots

Title: haal kisase bayaan karen dil kaa
Lyrics: haal kisase bayaan karen dil kaa mehar meraaj hii nahiin milataa  kohebarfiin pe dhuup kaa aalam aabzuu men kanwal nazzaaraa  lab pe afasuun nazar men afasaane dilarubaa jism soch men duubaa  gaalirii kuubasuuratii ke na giit har sadaf men gauhar nahiin hataa

Title: kuchh naa kaho kuchh bhii naa kaho
Lyrics: kuchh naa kaho kuchh bhi naa kaho kyaa kahanaa hai kya sunanaa hai mujhako pataa hai tumako pataa hai samay kaa ye pal tham saa gayaa hai aur is pal men koi nahiin hai bas ek main huun bas ek tum ho  shaanu kitane gahare halke shaam ke rang hain chhalake parvat se yuun utare baadal jaise aanchal dhalake sulagii sulagii saansen bahakii bahakii dhadakan mahake mahake shaam ke saaye pighale pighale tan man  lataa khoe sab pahachaane khoe saare apane samay kii chhalanii se gir girake khoe saare sapane hamane jab dekhe the sundar komal sapane phuul sitaare parvat baadal sab lagate the apane

Title: paradesiyaa itanaa bataa sajanaa  terii kaun huun main
Lyrics: paradesiyaa itanaa bataa sajanaa kudarat kii chunarii laharaaii puuchh rahii paagal puravaaii ho paradesiyaa paradesiyaa itanaa bataa sajanaa terii kaun huun main  merii rishton men terii saanson kii hain doriyaan merii jaan hai tuu ye jaan le tuu  jo na tujhe dekhuun ye dil na maane milane ke banaae kyaa kyaa bahaane maine to ye sochaa samajhaa hai jaanaan tere lie dil kyuun itanaa diivaanaa mitavaa mitavaa terii priit men jaaduu jaaduu ho jaae meraa man bekaabuu jaaduu jaaduu o mere dholanaa duniyaa se jaa bolanaa terii kaun huun main threedots  tere lie chhodii saarii khudaaii terii ho ke ho gaii main sabase paraaii diivaanii is mauj pe kisakaa hai paharaa milane kii ghadii hai pal bhii hai thaharaa mitavaa aayaa jo mausam sinduurii mehandii rachii huii chaahat puurii o ho jind meriye jind meriye rab se ye maine kahaa merii jaan hai tuu threedots

Title: pyaar pyaar karate karate tum pe marate marate dil de diyaa
Lyrics: pyaar pyaar karate karate tum pe marate marate dil de diyaa haan dil de diyaa uuii baabaa bababaa aaii baabaa  aa banaa ke kvaab tumako dekhatii rahuun chaahaton kii aarazuu men duubatii rahuun chuum le mere labon ko mujhako thaam le dekh jaaneman diivaanaa ho gayaa huun main reshamii in gesuon men kho gayaa huun main aahen bharate bharate tum pe marate marate dil de diyaa haan dil de diyaa yaa yaa maine sab paa liyaa pyaar pyaar karate karate threedots  na koii aramaan hai na koii pyaas hai bas terii tasviir aankhon me samaaii hai maine jo maangii duaa vo paaii hai main terii baahon men aauun ki vahaan jaauun soch men duubaa huun jaanaan main kahaan jaauun yaaraa darate darate tum pe marate marate dil de diyaa haan dil de diyaa pyaar pyaar karate karate threedots

Title: merii duniyaa hai tujhamen kahiin
Singer: sonu nigam kavita subramaniam sonu nigam
Lyrics: merii duniyaa hai tujhamen kahiin tere bin main kyaa kuchh bhii nahiin merii jaan men terii jaan hai o saathii mere merii duniyaa hai threedots  palakon men tere ruup kaa sapanaa sajaa diyaa pahalii nazar men hii tujhe apanaa banaa liyaa hai yahii aarazuu har ghadii baithii raho mere saamane merii duniyaa hai threedots  tere bin main kuchh bhii nahiin aisaa lagaa mere sanam ham jo yahaan mile saharaa men jaise shabanamii chaahat ke gul khile ye zamiin aasamaan kah rahe ham to kabhii na honge judaa merii duniyaa hai threedots merii duniyaa hai tujhamen kahiin tere bin main kyaa kuchh bhii nahiin merii jaan men terii jaan hai o saathii mere merii duniyaa hai threedots  palakon men tere ruup kaa sapanaa sajaa diyaa pahalii nazar men hii tujhe apanaa banaa liyaa hai yahii aarazuu har ghadii baithii raho mere saamane merii duniyaa hai threedots  aankhon ke raaste mere dil men utar gaii saanson men tere jism kii khushbuu bikhar gaii har jagah raat din pyaar se main jaaneman teraa naam luun merii duniyaa hai threedots

Title: dhak dhak dhak dhak dil dhadake  tan jale haan haan man jale
Lyrics: dhak dhak dhak dhak dil dhadake dil dhadake re baabaa dil dhadake tan jale haan haan man jale sholaa bhadake  are sholaa kyaa apun angaaraa hai angaaraa khaalii phuunk men jal jaaegii kyaa chal phuut naram labon se aajaa tere honthon ko chuumuun hosh men naa rahe daaman se tere jhuumuun kuchh ho yahaan sanam aankh merii phadake dhak dhak dhak dhak dil threedots  mand havaa kaa jhonkaa angon men aag lagaae pyaas kii aanch mere badan ko jalaae pyaas bujhaa gale se lagaa pyaasaa dil tadape dhak dhak dhak dhak dil threedots

Title: in the morning by the sea  tuu naa milii dil padhaaii men lagaa nahiin
Lyrics: tuu naa milii dil padhaaii men lagaa nahiin ek bhii din bin tere college gayaa nahiin din hain padhane likhane ke tum aahen bhar rahe  padh lo zaraa likh lo zaraa o mere hero varanaa imtihaan men aa jaaegaa zero  ippii yaa yaa ippii yaa yaa hai gulaabon men cheharaa teraa khvaabon men cheharaa teraa padhataa huun jab main aataa hai nazar kitaabon men cheharaa teraa  naukarii ke binaa milegii chhokarii nahiin naukarii ke bin hii mujhe tuu jo mil gaii

Title: kaliyon sii palaken hain palakon men kaajal hai
Lyrics: kaliyon sii palaken hain palakon men kaajal hai  chaandanii saa cheharaa hai kaise sambhaalen dil  zulfen ghataaon sii gaalon pe kaalaa til  kamasin adaayen hain kaise sambhaalen dil   khilatii javaanii hai rut bhii suhaanii hai  phuulon ke cheharon pe kis kii kahaanii hai  panchhii kii tarah kyuun chaahaten hain chanchal  thandii havaaon men aaj kaisii halachal   honthon pe chhalakii hai ikaraar kii shabanam  tere kayaalon men hai pyaar kii saragam  laharaa rahaa hai yuun kaamanii kaa aanchal  laharaa rahaa jaise nadiyaa kaa nirmal jal

Title: hanii teraa dilavaalaa hai reshamii rumaal vaalaa

Title: donon hii mohabbat ke jazbaat men jalate hain
Lyrics: donon hii mohabbat ke jazbaat men jalate hain vo barf pe chalate hain ham aag pe chalate hain ehasaas kii shikast se kuchh ashq nikalate hain  zindagii hai aur dilenaadaan hai kyaa safar hai aur kyaa saamaan hai mere gamon ko bhii samajh kar dekhie muskuraa denaa bahut aasaan hai ehasaas kii shikast se threedots  ye barf ke tukade hain garmii se pighalate hain ek raat thahar jaaen ham ghar men tere lekin tumhaare ghar daravaazaa hai lekin tumhen khatare kaa andaazaa nahiin hai hamen khatare kaa andaazaa hai lekin hamaare ghar daravaazaa men nahiin hai ek raat thahar jaaen threedots  mere kaam kaa hai na duniyaa ke kaam kaa are dil hii tumhen kudaa ne diyaa das graam kaa ek raat thahar jaaen threedots  chhat par na sulaa denaa ham niind men chalate hain chorii kii mohabbat men aksar yahii hotaa hai aadamii kaa hai aajakal haal ek sahamii sii chaah ho jaise aur log yuun chhup ke pyaar karate hain ki pyaar karanaa gunaah ho jaise chorii kii mohabbat men threedots  yuun to hansate hue ladakon ko bhii gam hotaa hai kachchii umron men magar tajurbaa kam hotaa hai chorii kii mohabbat men threedots  daravaaze se jaate hain khidakii se nikalate hain jis din se huii shaadii ye haal hamaaraa hai haldii se darate hain mehandii se ghabaraate hain ummiidevafaa rakhen kyaa unase bhalaa koii na jikr kiijie merii adaa ke baare men aur sunaa hai vo bhii muhabbat kaa shauq rakhane lage jinhen khabar hii nahiin vafaa ke baare men ummiidevafaa rakhen threedots  kapadon kii tarah naa jo chehare badalate hain donon hii mohabbat ke threedots

Lyrics: ishq chaandii hai ishq sonaa hai sonaa sonaa baabaa sonaa sonaa baabaa sonaa sonaa sonaa hai javaanii to ishq honaa hai  is umr men to aisaa hotaa hai niind udatii hai chain khotaa hai yaad aatii hai jaan jaatii hai premii jagate hain jag sotaa hai kabhii hansanaa hai kabhii ronaa hai sonaa sonaa baabaa threedots  ham diivaanon se log jalate hain aisaa karate hain bhaag chalate hain dil jo kahataa hai ham vo karate hain is zamaane se ham kyaa darate hain ishq jaaduu hai ishq tonaa hai sonaa sonaa baabaa threedots
